<br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑风格：骑楼建筑</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑特色：外型呈弧型，五个开间，采用骑楼形式，外观大方。采用潮汕特色大跨度彩色玻璃。“百载商埠”的见证。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"242\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60292\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625611101830.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/24/123403p1iyg44aixiux4xd.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/24/123403p1iyg44aixiux4xd.jpg\" aid=\"60292\" initialized=\"true\"/> </p><p><br/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#9acd32\"><strong>编号：B06</strong></span></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">地址：同平路27号</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">名称：不详</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">历史功能：不详</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">结构类型：砖混结构</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑层级：3层</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑风格：骑楼建筑</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑特色：建筑外立面为红砖结构，外立面简洁，顶层阳台镂空栏杆，潮汕特色阳台。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"232\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60293\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625611106228.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/24/123406hzmilb4kt5teet4e.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/24/123406hzmilb4kt5teet4e.jpg\" aid=\"60293\"/> </p><p><br/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#9acd32\"><strong>编号：B07</strong></span></span></span><br/>