60295\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625612236588.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/24/123409h1m6uclz0inceg21.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/24/123409h1m6uclz0inceg21.jpg\" aid=\"60295\"/> </p><p><br/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#9acd32\"><strong>编号：B09</strong></span></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">地址：国平路39号</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">名称：飘香小食店</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">历史功能：宗祠建筑、学校建筑（原叫徐厝祠，民国年间是岭东学校分校，解放后到公私合营前是汕头私立觉世小学分校）</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">结构类型：砖木结构</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑层级：1层</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑风格：潮汕风格宗祠建筑</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑特色：该建筑物又粗又大的衍架和石立柱，是老城区建筑物中少有的，也使它屹立至今。火型山墙特点，显著的潮汕宗祠建筑。同时为汕头市老字号。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"257\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60296\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625612810030.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/24/123411q2dm8ns3qz75hqmz.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/24/123411q2dm8ns3qz75hqmz.jpg\" aid=\"60296\" initialized=\"true\"/> </p><p><br/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#9acd32\"><strong>编号：B10</strong></span></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">地址：国平路35号</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">名称：不详</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">历史功能：不详</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">结构类型：砖混结构</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑层级：3层</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑风格：骑楼建筑</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑特色：三开间三层，中段为两个凹进去的阳台，阳台栏杆造型精致，且在上部有拱形造型，并有彩色玻璃。两边各有四个双扇木质百叶长窗，窗框造型富有特色。总体上建筑立面得体大方又十分优雅。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"262\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60297\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625612168254.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/24/123413uzrelzccscwk29ch.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/24/123413uzrelzccscwk29ch.jpg\" aid=\"60297\"/> </p><p><br/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#9acd32\"><strong>编号：B11</strong></span></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">地址：国平路34,36号</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">名称：不详</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">历史功能：商业、住宅</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">结构类型：钢筋混凝土框架</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑层级：4层</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑风格：骑楼建筑</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑特色：后现代简洁立面，3.4层设置极具潮汕特色和的悬挑阳台，阳台采用铁栏杆，后现代风格的碑亭完美的将后现代建筑风格与潮汕传统建筑有机融合。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"259\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60298\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625612130214.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/24/123414bf721znit2091bqt.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/24/123414bf721znit2091bqt.jpg\" aid=\"60298\"/> </p><p><br/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#9acd32\"><strong>编号：B12</strong></span></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">地址：国平路31号</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">名称：丰棉大楼</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">历史功能：商场（原为经营布业的花纱布公司，附设汕头市布业公会，解放后后改为汕头国营纺织品公司，专卖针织品，上世纪六十年代中期称丰棉。）</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">结构类型：钢筋混凝土框架</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑层级：5层</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑风格：骑楼建筑</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑特色：除了1-2层局部改变原貌外，外观基本保留原貌。外观建筑也颇有特色。后现代简洁立面，独具特色的灯具装饰，是的建筑有一定的历史记忆。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"253\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60299\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625612989472.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/24/123415a60ql1x0oa7c1wcz.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/24/123415a60ql1x0oa7c1wcz.jpg\" aid=\"60299\"/> </p><p><br/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#9acd32\"><strong>编号：B13</strong></span></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">地址：升平路60号</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">名称：汕头老电信局</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">历史功能：邮政大楼</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">结构类型：钢筋混凝土框架</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑层级：4层</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑风格：后现代公共建筑</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建筑特色：为汕头市第一面五星红旗升起地方。后现代简洁立面，简洁的立面体现后现代主义建筑风格，3-4层均设置阳台，阳台采用铁栏杆，有新艺术风格的造型。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"267\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60300\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625612722933.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/24/123417zqjzx2ttjlgu9wnu.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/24/123417zqjzx2ttjlgu9wnu.jpg\" aid=\"60300\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"color:#9acd32\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">▏</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">历史沧桑百年，很多建筑物已经人去楼空，历史信息缺失，而这正是作为历史建筑的重要参考依据。关注公众号，未来几天我们还有其他特色老建筑的推介。如果您了解上述历史建筑线索的名称、历史沿革、人物故事，占地或建筑面积等信息，或者有更好的历史建筑推荐，可将你的故事和意见建议寄往汕头市黄山路32号投资大厦4楼汕头市城乡规划局建设工程科，邮政编码：515041，或发送电子邮件至<a href=\"mailto:stghjcxk@126.com\" target=\"_blank\">stghjcxk@126.com</a>。</span></span><br/><span style=\"color:#9acd32\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">▏</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">如果您不了解，请举手之劳转发此文向朋友们征集意见。赠人鲜花，手留余香，汕头的历史建筑保护和利用，将有你的一份贡献。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60285\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625612717339.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/24/122444zbmb1a3k56kdsvoa.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/24/122444zbmb1a3k56kdsvoa.gif\" aid=\"60285\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">汕头橄榄台综合报道 转载请注明出处</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">来源/时事汕头</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">实习小编/博尔</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img id=\"aimg_179685\" aid=\"179685\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151208/1449579005435524.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><br/><p></p>','2015-11-04 16:27:56',0,NULL,1,NULL,2405,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (295,'24位“世界杰出华人” 有一位来自汕头潮阳','201511041629571698.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px;\"></span></ignore_js_op></span></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60630\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625760176301.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/25/192227ecs8szyse6c6sno0.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/25/192227ecs8szyse6c6sno0.gif\" aid=\"60630\" initialized=\"true\"/> </p><p><br/></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">在刚刚荣获第十四届世界杰出华人奖的24位杰出华人中，除了中国“杂交水稻之父”袁隆平、“嫦娥之父”欧阳自远等知名人士，还有一名来自汕头潮阳的企业家——骏荣控股有限公司董事长张植炜。张植炜凭什么获得“世界杰出华人奖”？不服来看↓↓↓</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60632\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625760714973.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/25/192251eahf30awkz80ws5f.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/25/192251eahf30awkz80ws5f.jpg\" aid=\"60632\" initialized=\"true\"/> </p><p><br/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">张植炜，美国林肯大学荣誉管理博士，是潮汕籍香港青年企业家、汕头市港澳政协委员、市海外联谊会荣誉会长、汕头市荣誉市民。汕头骏荣纺织有限公司、骏荣国际学校的创办人。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60633\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625760476318.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/25/192252r94qu9txwz9qoyi9.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/25/192252r94qu9txwz9qoyi9.jpg\" aid=\"60633\" initialized=\"true\"/> </p><p><br/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>八十年代两手空空闯香港</strong></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">世界杰出华人奖由世界投资基金会于2003年创办，旨在表彰全球华人对各地华人社会及国家的贡献和影响。张植炜出生在潮阳区谷饶镇一个普通家庭，1989年，20岁出头的他两手空空闯香港，选择从海鲜水产生意做起，起早贪黑，一年只休息2天，靠吃苦耐劳赚得人生第一桶金。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><br/></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>下定决心干实业</strong></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">钱赚到了，这个时候张植炜想要转型办实业，他选择回到家乡——有着“全国著名内衣名镇”之称的谷饶镇，创办骏荣控股有限公司，从内衣代工起步，开始自己的第二次创业之路。创业初期，他斥巨资在谷饶建起了15栋现代化、花园式的厂房，这个举动在当时被人们认为是“很傻”的，但满怀抱负的张植炜说，他的竞争对手是珠三角，目标是国际市场，因此一定要眼高手快。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60634\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625760497017.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/25/192253tn4jo7yz78h04b8x.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/25/192253tn4jo7yz78h04b8x.jpg\" aid=\"60634\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>年近半百开始三次创业</strong></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">是出于不服输的个性，也是出于对品质严苛的要求，张植炜的工厂历经15年的发展已成为中国设备最完善的内衣厂之一，并与英国玛莎等国际高级内衣品牌建立长期的战略合作伙伴关系。近年来，骏荣纺织加快企业转型升级步伐，成功应对各种挑战，企业订单源源不断。如今即将步入知天命之年的张植炜并没有停下前进的脚步，就在今年9月，他投资5000万元，在谷饶创办起骏荣国际学校，拿出年轻时的满腔热情，开始了人生的第三次创业。他希望以此进一步改善当地办学环境。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60635\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625761685453.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/25/192254nv1omfrvml22mlf5.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/25/192254nv1omfrvml22mlf5.jpg\" aid=\"60635\"/> </p><p><br/></p></ignore_js_op><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60636\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625761112222.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/25/192255b4uxzaettls4zaa6.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/25/192255b4uxzaettls4zaa6.jpg\" aid=\"60636\"/> </p><p><br/></p></ignore_js_op><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60631\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625761546073.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/25/192234nb84y464iwd42zot.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/25/192234nb84y464iwd42zot.gif\" aid=\"60631\"/> </p><p><br/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">来源/汕头电视台《汕头新闻》</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img id=\"aimg_179685\" aid=\"179685\" src=\"http://yao.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p></ignore_js_op><br/><p></p>','2015-11-04 16:29:57',0,NULL,1,NULL,3348,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (296,'【老挝潮商】于无声处起惊雷','201511041632569438.png','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px;\"></span></ignore_js_op></span></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60815\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625910790967.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/102940ajrjosabktj8w7ea.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/102940ajrjosabktj8w7ea.gif\" aid=\"60815\" initialized=\"true\"/> </p><p><br/></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>编者按：</em></strong></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>潮商，一个如向日葵般永远朝有商机的方向而盛开的族群；老挝，一个东南亚乃至世界地区都排名后端极不发达的国家。当这两个看似南辕北辙的名词凑到一起，奇特的化学反应却就此产生，造就了一个意义丰富的新名词——老挝潮商。我们都知道，有海水的地方就有潮汕人，在这个东南亚唯一的内陆国家，潮商将怎样演绎传奇？小编从今天起，以汕头电视台《天下潮商》为蓝本，向您介绍老挝潮商的创业故事，以及他们挥洒在这片土地上的情感。</em></strong></span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61614\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625911100879.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/154339lpbt2otrzz6wvtph.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/154339lpbt2otrzz6wvtph.png\" aid=\"61614\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">这里地势高而险峻，80%的国土都是山地和高原，且只有雨季和旱季两个季节。檀香曾经是这里盛产的昂贵木头，大象是这里的标志，这里就是<span style=\"color:#8b0000\"><strong>老挝</strong></span>——东南亚唯一一个内陆国家。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61615\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625911217955.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/154340i1mppnnpydpmxnpm.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/154340i1mppnnpydpmxnpm.jpg\" aid=\"61615\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">老挝人民民主共和国，也称寮国，东面与越南相邻，西面与泰国连接，南面比邻高棉，北面与中国接壤，国土总面积23万多平方公里，共有600多万人居住在这个国家。老挝崇尚佛教，民风纯朴，素有“<span style=\"color:#a0522d\"><strong>万象之邦</strong></span>”的美称。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61616\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625912329752.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/154340mt0x8c2t7ewu8o2i.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/154340mt0x8c2t7ewu8o2i.png\" aid=\"61616\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">国境内拥有优美的原始自然景观和肥沃的土地，木材、金属、矿产资源非常丰富。但是，这样一个资源等各方面条件都得天独厚，本该繁荣发展的国家却长期处于世界最不发达国家之列，其背后的原因很多，是地理位置、政治环境等各方面因素综合影响的结果。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">即使在<span style=\"color:#a0522d\"><strong>万象</strong></span>，这个老挝最为繁华的城市，我们能看到的也仍旧是建筑低矮，马路窄小破旧，人群热闹喧杂的景象。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60805\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625913391287.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/102917kaiuki3pi1563iai.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/102917kaiuki3pi1563iai.png\" aid=\"60805\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">万象位于湄公河畔，是老挝的首都，也是国家的经济文化中心。湄公河岸边的休闲广场和中国许多城市里的休闲广场一样，一到日落时分就开始逐渐变得热闹起来。在这里的人们散步、跳舞、运动，尽情享受着这难得的悠闲时光。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60806\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625913463151.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/102917yy2iqqphjhaxawhq.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/102917yy2iqqphjhaxawhq.png\" aid=\"60806\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">湄公河从他们身旁向南缓缓流去，在河的对面，能看见一片盎然绿意。这个与老挝一河之隔的国家就是泰国，同样信奉佛教，也是全世界范围内潮汕人第二多的地方。居住在泰国的潮人目前已经有五百多万，但居住在老挝的潮人却只有不到两万。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61617\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625913126689.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/154340swh96qbrmqziqafb.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/154340swh96qbrmqziqafb.jpg\" aid=\"61617\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">如果说，越来越多的潮汕人已经熟悉和亲近被称为暹逻的泰国的话，那么老挝在绝大多数潮汕人眼中，就是一个至今仍蒙着一层窗户纸的国度。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61618\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625913101240.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/154340dlds60g6pdcds1pd.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/154340dlds60g6pdcds1pd.jpg\" aid=\"61618\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">有一句俗语说得好，“<span style=\"color:#4169e1\"><strong>有海水的地方就有潮汕人</strong></span>”。逐海水而居一向是精明的潮汕人热衷的选择，然而老挝却是一个例外。这片地处内陆，交通不便，也不发达的土地，或许会让很多人心生疑问，为何那个生性拼搏、耐劳、勤俭的潮人群体，会选择这里落地生根，而他们创业道路又是如何发展前行的？ </span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61619\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625914685625.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/154341zxszxcr8j8xfj778.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/154341zxszxcr8j8xfj778.jpg\" aid=\"61619\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">目前在老挝的华人当中，潮汕人占了绝大多数，因此，从一些历史的统计数字当中就可以轻易地获知潮汕人在老挝的发展轨迹。根据史书的记载, 华人最晚在明代就有迁居老挝的先例。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">法国殖民当局在1910年向老挝居民发放过居民身份证，当时统计得知当地共有68名华侨。1921年，老挝又在法国的主持下进行过一次人口普查,当时统计得知的华侨人数已上升至6710人。由于在那之后，华人想进入法国控制下的东南亚地区都会受到法国限制,因此直到20世纪30年代，老挝的华侨人数下降至约3000人。到50年代初期,老挝华侨人数再度上升，已有1万多人。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60966\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625914875911.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/124203iz8p8zxciyx51t5c.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/124203iz8p8zxciyx51t5c.jpg\" aid=\"60966\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">而在这一地区的法国殖民统治结束之后，老挝华侨的人数逐年上涨,1958年统计显示为3万多人，到60年代增至5万多人,70年代已有将近10万人,1972年曾达到约12万人。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">老挝也许并不是飘洋过海的潮人先辈最佳的选择，但当他们向西北方向一路迁徙，从泰国、越南等国家千里迢迢来到老挝的时候，这片土地的肥沃和富饶，让那些饱受饥荒折磨的潮人倍感惊喜。因为对当时的潮人而言，潮汕老家人多地少，解决温饱是很难实现的奢望，但在这里却没有太大的问题。这让许多人心甘情愿地留在了老挝。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61620\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625914134689.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/154341v1thrf8fep2jritr.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/154341v1thrf8fep2jritr.jpg\" aid=\"61620\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">这个说着潮汕话的族群就这样迈出了自己在这里繁衍生息的第一步，到上世纪70年代的时候，旅居老挝的潮籍华人华侨人数近十万，达到了一个高峰，其中集中于首都万象的潮人占绝大多数，当时万象的总人口数当中，潮籍华人华侨占了近三分之一</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">这个国度信奉佛教，国民大多知足常乐，过着与世无争的生活，而老挝潮人的特性却是<span style=\"color:#8b0000\"><strong>吃苦耐劳、善于经商、敢于拼搏</strong></span>。这一点在老挝国民当中显得相当特立独行。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60812\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625914106714.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/102918vwxgx0d2c5e0g33v.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/102918vwxgx0d2c5e0g33v.jpg\" aid=\"60812\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">大多数潮人都很快就跻身老挝的富裕阶层，这种现象在首都万象尤其突出，“<span style=\"color:#808000\"><strong>处处潮州话，座座胶己厝</strong></span>”，曾经是这里最生动而贴切的写照。老挝潮人辉煌历史的印迹至今仍存在于这个并不繁华的老挝首都，沿街矗立着一幢幢二三层的小楼，那里面曾经居住着的家庭便有许多都是用潮汕话交流的。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60813\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625914132146.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/102918v8lssq8zrldpqlnz.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/102918v8lssq8zrldpqlnz.png\" aid=\"60813\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">潮商就是这样一个神奇的族群，能够在富裕和充满希望的地方捕获商机，也能够在少人问津的地方，用自己独到的眼光、拼搏精神和勇气创造新的希望。于无声处起惊雷，这是老挝潮商令人惊叹的能力，也是这个族群在任何地方都能风生水起的一大倚靠。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61621\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625915484494.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/154341pv8t4dhmm1q8uazv.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/154341pv8t4dhmm1q8uazv.png\" aid=\"61621\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span> <ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60814\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446625915335346.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/102940xu9be0rmt5gbsnbs.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/102940xu9be0rmt5gbsnbs.gif\" aid=\"60814\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">来源/汕头电视台《天下潮商》</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/关雪&nbsp;&nbsp;博尔</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img id=\"aimg_179685\" aid=\"179685\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151208/1449578977302513.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p></ignore_js_op></span></span>','2015-11-04 16:32:56',0,NULL,1,NULL,2118,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (297,'【老挝潮商】潮州帮：撑起老挝华侨华人的一片天','201511041635208773.png','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60884\" src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201510/26/105553l3yricdzfeyymcmz.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/105553l3yricdzfeyymcmz.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/105553l3yricdzfeyymcmz.gif\" aid=\"60884\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>编者按：</em></strong></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>潮商以团结而闻名，也以博爱而闻名。在远赴老挝创业发展的过程中，不少杰出商人聚集在一起，形成潮州帮，在当地中华理事会当中占据了重要地位。他们拧成一股绳，在商场并肩作战的同时，也发挥能量，为老挝华侨华人撑起了一片天。</em></strong></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61635\" src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155341m040x1u1nebppk0f.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155341m040x1u1nebppk0f.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155341m040x1u1nebppk0f.png\" aid=\"61635\" initialized=\"true\"/><br/><strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\">老籍潮商陈成丰</span></strong>告诉记者，现在的万象市在当时名为永珍市，在这座城市当中，有八成五十年以上的水泥建筑物都是当年潮州人的产业。那个时候，随处可见潮州人的招牌，可以说没有任何一条路会看不到。1972年是老挝相对的黄金时期，当时潮州人起到了巨大的作用。</p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61636\" src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155342ezc2apjxjyl7zda4.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155342ezc2apjxjyl7zda4.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155342ezc2apjxjyl7zda4.png\" aid=\"61636\" initialized=\"true\"/><br/>陈成丰是老挝二代潮人，现如今已有七十多岁，是老挝华人华侨的那段最辉煌历史的见证者之一。陈成丰至今仍然记得，这个国度的商业虽然不发达，但在上世纪七十年代之前的商业领域上，老挝潮人的地位盛极一时，尽管当时的大多数潮人经营的都是小生意，但也有一些企业家经济实力较强，因此已开始涉足<strong><span style=\"color:#808000\">机器修配、木材加工、汽车销售</span></strong>等行业。</p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61637\" src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155342w4ui79bh59dque99.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155342w4ui79bh59dque99.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155342w4ui79bh59dque99.png\" aid=\"61637\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">发展到后来，潮人企业成为除部分政府企业之外的各个行业的领军人物，他们将潮商独特的勇于拼搏，敢于创新的特质发挥得淋漓尽致，在老挝基本找不到竞争对手。<span style=\"color:#008000\"><strong>潮州帮</strong></span>也就是在这个时候应运而生的。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61638\" src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155342nlhhrfwzjey0berm.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155342nlhhrfwzjey0berm.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155342nlhhrfwzjey0berm.jpg\" aid=\"61638\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">陈成丰介绍说，当时的潮州人之所以成立了潮州帮这个帮会，是出于按照在中国国内各地的风俗习惯，给予潮州人一个聚会的地方，方便大家彼此照应。潮州帮成立后，海南人和客家人也分别仿照潮汕人，组织起各自的帮会，总共有了三个帮。由于老挝还没有开发，对一些勤劳，有开拓精神的人来说，是一个扎根发展的好地方，因此来到老挝的人后来也不断上涨。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61639\" src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155343nfmftveeskexx4es.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155343nfmftveeskexx4es.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155343nfmftveeskexx4es.png\" aid=\"61639\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">潮州帮于1937年牵头成立了<span style=\"color:#0000ff\"><strong>老挝万象中华理事会</strong></span>，这三个帮会正是理事会的基础。其如今已发展为万象主要华人组织之一，而且一直由潮籍华人担任理事长这一理事会最有号召力的职位。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60871\" src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201510/26/105529mdzdeudjfj9q9z47.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/105529mdzdeudjfj9q9z47.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/105529mdzdeudjfj9q9z47.jpg\" aid=\"60871\"/><br/>陈成丰告诉记者，即便在中华理事会内部，也是用潮汕话进行交流的，这是潮人形成的一种无形的力量。但与此同时，我们也很照顾其他的华人，不会拒绝或歧视他们。有的人虽然不会说潮州话，但只要进入中华理事会，潮州人同样会对他们加以照顾。<strong><span style=\"color:#808000\">不欺负他人，接受和帮助他人，这是潮州人一贯的传统美德。</span></strong></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61640\" src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155343k4x11mffmlm7mtoz.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155343k4x11mffmlm7mtoz.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155343k4x11mffmlm7mtoz.png\" aid=\"61640\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">尽管老挝潮人或是为了温饱，或是为了躲避战乱，或是为了其他原因而背井离乡，但仍旧对中华传统文化一脉相承，心系故国家乡。因此，在老挝潮人先后成立了潮州帮和老挝万象中华理事会之后，老挝的华文教育也于1937年开始着手准备。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61641\" src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155343f2421jo355ljtmvl.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155343f2421jo355ljtmvl.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155343f2421jo355ljtmvl.jpg\" aid=\"61641\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">陈成丰告诉记者，来到这里的潮人起初是因为对下一代的教育寄予厚望而开设私塾，请来老师为华人华侨的后代授课。后来参加的人数越来越多，其中还包括了从中国国内其他城市迁居老挝的华侨子弟，组织成立一所学校的决定就此产生。于1937年正式成立的<span style=\"color:#a0522d\"><strong>寮都公学</strong></span>，也正是以中华理事会的名义组织成立的第一所学校。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61642\" src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155343wbong3belz0bgmnp.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155343wbong3belz0bgmnp.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155343wbong3belz0bgmnp.jpg\" aid=\"61642\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">老挝潮人对办华文教育一事都非常积极，有钱出钱，有力出力，谁也不愿被落在后头。他们都懂得华文教育对远在异国他乡的潮人的意义所在。因此只要有愿意就读的学生，哪怕付不起学费，公学也同样接收。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61643\" src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155344bc2u6uex2e8db0rd.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155344bc2u6uex2e8db0rd.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155344bc2u6uex2e8db0rd.png\" aid=\"61643\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">陈成丰告诉记者，虽然是潮州人出钱开办学校，但即便不是潮州人的子弟，比如客家人、海南人甚至是当地的老挝人，只要有意愿上学，他们都会用同样的态度来对待和接收，尽力想办法为他们解决问题。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61644\" src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155344tjs69ves6yjsnene.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155344tjs69ves6yjsnene.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155344tjs69ves6yjsnene.png\" aid=\"61644\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#008000\">在寮都公学最辉煌的发展阶段，全校师生共有5000多名，校友更是遍布天下，</span></strong>老挝当地也有不少孩子也选择就读寮都公学，寮都公学也为促成华人融入当地社会提供了巨大的推动力。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61645\" src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155344iwndzswax11p9y8x.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155344iwndzswax11p9y8x.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155344iwndzswax11p9y8x.png\" aid=\"61645\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">陈成丰告诉记者，虽然老挝政府也拥有档次很高的学校，但他们还是尽可能地想让自己的孩子在寮都公学上学。理事会对于所有人都来者不拒，经济上的困难也会尽力帮忙解决，这一切都源于潮州人的美德。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61646\" src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155344x8g2z4u4k8ragr28.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155344x8g2z4u4k8ragr28.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155344x8g2z4u4k8ragr28.png\" aid=\"61646\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">陈成丰对公学的学生有很大的期望，希望在五年十年以后，这些老挝当地人会有一部分成为政府机构的公务员，而这些人作为学校师生的同学、前辈、后辈，在遇到问题的时候，他们能够帮助出手我解决一部分。因为公学对他们而言可谓百利而无一损，做好事无伤害。</span></span><br/><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">许多上了年纪的老挝潮籍华人对家里的生意，仍然是自己亲力亲为地加以打理，他们在经历了人生当中的大起大落之后，遇事都显得更加的从容，对待生活保持着积极乐观的态度，先辈艰苦奋斗的优良作风也始终秉承。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61647\" src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155345c4wdl5uql4bd6z69.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155345c4wdl5uql4bd6z69.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155345c4wdl5uql4bd6z69.png\" aid=\"61647\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">陈成丰谈起老挝潮商，显得很是自豪。这些在老挝创业成功的潮州人，尤其是70岁以上的人，每一个都亲力亲为，愿意为事业终生奋斗，至死方休。他们或者帮忙扫地，或者帮忙洗东西，即使家中的助手有十几名，仍然自己洗自己的袜子。这些小事在无形中形成一种传统美德。孩子看着家中长辈如此行为，自己也不好意思不效仿，这样等到上年纪之后，习惯也已经形成了。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61648\" src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155345zbb0bwwx1p0lpshh.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155345zbb0bwwx1p0lpshh.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155345zbb0bwwx1p0lpshh.jpg\" aid=\"61648\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">老挝潮商在七十年代初的黄金期，为自己，为潮商，也为老挝做出了巨大贡献，而他们最大的贡献并不在事业的成功，而在于为潮籍华人华侨，为所有在老挝奋斗的华人华侨所撑起的一片天。潮州帮也好，中华理事会也罢，最终其实不过是一句话——<strong><span style=\"color:#556b2f\"><em>天下华人是一家</em></span></strong>。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61649\" src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155345ejcew4j9z1x4kxxe.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155345ejcew4j9z1x4kxxe.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/155345ejcew4j9z1x4kxxe.jpg\" aid=\"61649\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span> <ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60883\" src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201510/26/105553i1716zt11nnr86zy.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/105553i1716zt11nnr86zy.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/105553i1716zt11nnr86zy.gif\" aid=\"60883\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">来源/汕头电视台《天下潮商》</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/关雪&nbsp;&nbsp;博尔</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img id=\"aimg_179685\" aid=\"179685\" src=\"http://yao.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p></ignore_js_op><br/><p><br/></p>','2015-11-04 16:35:20',0,NULL,1,NULL,2212,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (298,'【老挝潮商】老挝解放的危机和机遇','201511041637016444.png','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60944\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626163112097.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112951uijjw3hx3i9fhaxa.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112951uijjw3hx3i9fhaxa.gif\" aid=\"60944\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong><em>编者按：</em></strong></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong><em>老挝的解放，对老挝人民来说是一大喜事，但对于当时在老挝发展的潮商来说，却无异于一场危机。这场危机充满了危险，却同时也充满了机遇。一部分潮商用自己非凡的毅力坚守了下来，渡过了最艰难的时期，终于收获了新的果实和希望。</em></strong></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61683\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626164778014.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/161218d4hna84nh4xax44d.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/161218d4hna84nh4xax44d.png\" aid=\"61683\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">老挝自第二次世界大战以来，就始终蒙受着国际区域政治斗争的影响，缓慢的社会经济发展速度，低下的当地居民消费能力，这样的背景让得旅居老挝的老一辈潮人在事业上很难实现大的飞跃。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#808000\"><strong>1975年，老挝的君主制废除，老挝人民共和国成立，全国得以解放。</strong></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61682\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626164309054.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/161218xe24et6s1verrde7.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/161218xe24et6s1verrde7.png\" aid=\"61682\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">解放前夕，出于对新政府上台后会实施反华政策的担忧，许多当时已经家境富有的潮籍华人华侨都选择了迁居美国、法国和其他国家，仍然留在老挝的只有一小部分。这一次的迁徙之后，只剩下不到原来一成的老挝潮人，这种情况持续到80年代末，剩下的也只有1000多户、5000人左右。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60929\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626164466464.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112927baspm7ornl9ys979.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112927baspm7ornl9ys979.jpg\" aid=\"60929\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">对于留下来的潮人来说，这段社会变迁期实在令人刻骨铭心，他们做足准备要迎接那充满未知的新生活的挑战，但内心却难免忐忑不安。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">著名的</span><strong><span style=\"color:#a0522d\">老挝侨领林振潮</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">如今已年过八旬，他当时由于经济原因无法离开老挝，成了留下来的少数人之一。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61684\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626181117984.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/161218i4o6jmbwa6rtz2rq.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/161218i4o6jmbwa6rtz2rq.png\" aid=\"61684\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">解放前他涉足不少生意，包括代理三菱汽车，出售二手的ISUZU（五十铃）货车，建油站和卖汽车零件，他的父亲还有一个锯木厂。因为他用分期付款的方式经营汽车生意，当时债务人都离开了，他的欠账难以收回，变得血本无归。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60932\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626182442366.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112928zsvyvkdsy44qz8r7.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112928zsvyvkdsy44qz8r7.png\" aid=\"60932\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#556b2f\">老挝万象中华理事会历任理事长当中，有他的外公和父亲，而他本人在上世纪70年代进入理事会之后，也曾在理事长一职连续工作了五任之久。</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">老挝政权于1975年改换，在那之前，离开老挝的念头也曾在他的心头闪现，但他出于孝义，最终选择留下来。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60933\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626182340381.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112928yjkyi4xlljscblce.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112928yjkyi4xlljscblce.jpg\" aid=\"60933\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">他告诉记者，他的老父亲在老挝解放时已经70多岁了，当时他的兄弟都离开了，大哥已经不在人世，因此长子的责任和义务应该由他承担，赡养老父亲是必须做的事情，无论前往哪里都不能丢下自己的父亲。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">不过，老挝的新政府并没有将林振潮的家产全部没收，最终将</span><strong><span style=\"color:#556b2f\">一家锯木工厂</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">和</span><strong><span style=\"color:#556b2f\">一家汽车修理厂</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">留给了他，一家人的生活来源不至于被彻底断绝，这是很值得庆幸的事情。如今时间已过去三十多年，儿孙绕膝的林振潮在闲暇时会热心潮社事业，在他的脸上，除了岁月留下的痕迹，曾经的辉煌和磨难都已经很难再看到了。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61685\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626183339606.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/161218hwm1la12z16hz6lx.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/161218hwm1la12z16hz6lx.png\" aid=\"61685\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">陈复潮与林振潮情形一样，同样是当年没有离开老挝的潮汕之一。他之所以选择留下来，是因为他当时已经倾注无数心血，在万象拥有了一家当时老挝最大的</span><strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\">私营印刷厂</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61680\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626184742986.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/161214pxxixl600xovvqxi.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/161214pxxixl600xovvqxi.png\" aid=\"61680\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">陈复潮告诉记者，开印刷厂的起因，是由于在妻子的哥哥店里打工时发现，一些印刷品业务收到之后，需要先去泰国曼谷印刷，印完之后再运回老挝才能交货。他当时到市面上调查了一下印务公司的总数，并观察了一下印刷情况。当时陈富潮发现，他们使用的字粒老旧，印刷效果差，没有中文印刷，但仍然能维持经营，因此他决定自己创业，参与印刷行业，同时增设中文印务。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60937\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626185928109.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112929xpk5bgeozapgoack.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112929xpk5bgeozapgoack.png\" aid=\"60937\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">刚起步的时候他只有一台机器，印刷工作都由他亲力亲为；经过一定发展后，他已拥有六台机器，雇佣十几个工人生产，很快从小作坊经营成老挝当时最大的私营印刷厂，联合国援助老挝的印刷工程和大量华人印务都被他的印刷厂长期承接。1974年，陈复潮亲眼看见身边的很多朋友开始携家带口离开老挝，于是自己也开始犹豫。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60938\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626187404756.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112930ssf5sceameb26by8.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112930ssf5sceameb26by8.png\" aid=\"60938\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">他当时的心情非常矛盾，虽然并没有参加什么政治活动，心绪相对平静，但毕竟很多人的离开都是亲眼所见的事实。不过他由于有不动产作为后盾，所以并没有产生太大的担忧情绪。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">在一番反复的思想斗争之后，他最终选择是坚守。出乎意料的是，他的留守并非给他带来灾难，反而是新的机遇。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60940\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626188128251.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112930sct1j3663aanb966.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112930sct1j3663aanb966.jpg\" aid=\"60940\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">陈复潮回忆起当时的经历，记忆犹新。老挝解放后最初的一段时间里，由于其他私人印务的公司都已离开，他们成了独家生意的原因，生意比之前更加红火，一旦有政府工厂完不成的印刷任务，他们的印刷厂就成了唯一的选择。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60939\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626188867951.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112930j0ztpla67a0se36p.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112930j0ztpla67a0se36p.jpg\" aid=\"60939\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">但在那之后的几年间，由于地方经济缺乏动力，因此陈复潮工厂的生意虽然红火，但工厂的利润不升反降。到上世纪80年代，妻子向陈复潮提出举家移居泰国，投靠在泰国定居的亲戚的建议，但陈复潮早已经习惯了老挝的生活环境，寄人篱下也非他所愿，于是没有同意妻子的建议，而是坚持用自己的努力养家糊口。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60941\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626189118251.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112930c2pd152h11vgt5dp.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112930c2pd152h11vgt5dp.png\" aid=\"60941\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">陈复潮回忆说，他当时告诉妻子，他们夫妻二人加上六个孩子，总共八个人去泰国，又没有生活来源。尽管妻子的哥哥有些积蓄，但只怕不会愿意长期帮助他们。那时他们在老挝仍有印刷的业务，有工作就能生活，机器尚在运转就有生计，不愁温饱。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#008000\">只要事业尚在，就要坚守不懈，这般锲而不舍，百折不挠的精神，并非陈富潮所独有，而是老挝潮商共有的品质。</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">前路漫漫，任谁也不知道自己一生当中会遇到多少险阻，陈富潮这样的人之所以能够在大风大浪中始终不倒，或许只是因为他比别人多了那一点坚持。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61681\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626190149664.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/161217b26ri8lj2zro4uj5.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/161217b26ri8lj2zro4uj5.png\" aid=\"61681\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60943\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626190111280.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112951lt9upy9rur8uyqg8.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/112951lt9upy9rur8uyqg8.gif\" aid=\"60943\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">来源/汕头电视台《天下潮商》</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/关雪&nbsp;&nbsp;博尔</span></span></span></p><p><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></p><p><img id=\"aimg_179685\" aid=\"179685\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151208/1449578923324803.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2015-11-04 16:37:01',0,NULL,1,NULL,2109,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (299,'【老挝潮商】张忠麒：事业的第三个春季','201511041638526984.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61091\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626282177893.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/153153umnxx210rjkhrwsp.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/153153umnxx210rjkhrwsp.gif\" aid=\"61091\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>编者按：<br/> 老挝解放时的商业危机终究是暂时的，老挝新政府同样明白改革开放的重要性，也带给了那些在七十年代不得已逃出老挝，前往他国谋求发展的潮商新的希望。他们曾经在老挝洒下过奋斗的汗水，那里成为了他们充满归属感的第二故乡。在新政府新政策的鼓励之下，张忠麒等潮商重返老挝，在这里书写出新的创业篇章。</em></strong></span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61080\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626282199151.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/153049asspsyvikmqskpvv.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/153049asspsyvikmqskpvv.jpg\" aid=\"61080\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">老挝在1986年实施了“<span style=\"color:#556b2f\"><strong>新经济机制</strong></span>”，走对外开放路线，对外资和外国援助的引进十分积极。逐步改善的政治局面让一部分逃离老挝的潮商为求发展选择了重返老挝，<strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\">张忠麒</span></strong>就是其中之一。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61079\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626283957887.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/153049zhmj1tdd55jd1t1m.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/153049zhmj1tdd55jd1t1m.png\" aid=\"61079\"/><br/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">张忠麒刚到老挝创业时只有20多岁，到上世纪60年代，已有六七家锯木工厂归在他名下，而由于张忠麒拥有较强的经济实力和良好的信誉，因此当时老挝锯木行业公会的带头人经过推举后也由他担任。但是，老挝政权在1975年的变更让他无奈地选择了逃亡澳洲。</span></p></ignore_js_op><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61081\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626283655460.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/153050tw538d8jskj23jkd.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/153050tw538d8jskj23jkd.jpg\" aid=\"61081\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#a0522d\">老籍潮商张忠麒</span></strong>告诉记者，他在老挝十多年的努力工作，所挣得的丰厚积蓄，短短数小时内蒸发殆尽。在他事业的巅峰时期，拥有六七家工厂，一百多辆车，无数财产，上百万段木料，却在一夕之间尽数被没收了。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61912\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626283138794.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/094746f8kdc7dcc7cdn8j3.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/094746f8kdc7dcc7cdn8j3.jpg\" aid=\"61912\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">张忠麒富有经商头脑，自然不甘就此沉寂，逃亡到澳洲之后，他只稍作休整就决心卷土重来，并且在澳洲的创业也很快成功，而他收获的新财富来自于建筑行业。或许真的是命中注定，因缘巧合之下，他在澳洲选择的建筑业为他奠定了重返老挝的基础。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61913\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626283172643.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/094746lff1mpp6679zz1h9.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/094746lff1mpp6679zz1h9.jpg\" aid=\"61913\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">张忠麒回忆到，当时的老挝国家主席受澳洲政府邀请，前往澳洲访问，主席参观了一些居民区，而后询问起唐人街和华人市场的开发建设者。当时旁人将张忠麒的名字告诉了老挝主席，他后来也因此找到了张忠麒，让张忠麒返回老挝进行投资。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61914\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626284136643.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/094747yelzrospmlzxjjgr.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/094747yelzrospmlzxjjgr.jpg\" aid=\"61914\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">张忠麒就通过这样的机会重返老挝，他人生中的第三次创业由此开始。1992年的张忠麒已经63岁，却仍然有如年轻人般的拼劲，毅然集资500万美元，与人合作创立了<strong><span style=\"color:#008000\">永珍商业银行</span></strong>，当时老挝最大的酒店也是他随后投资兴建的。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61915\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626284135050.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/094747leo1euokli642dsz.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/094747leo1euokli642dsz.jpg\" aid=\"61915\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">张忠麒告诉记者，2008年的时候，没有人帮忙处理银行的工作，而那时他也已经将近80岁，于是决定退休。旁人都知道他对银行业没有任何从业经验，但后来的业绩却超过其他老牌的银行，经营得风生水起。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61916\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626284868467.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/094747eqoz4bqqposorspm.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/094747eqoz4bqqposorspm.jpg\" aid=\"61916\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">大部分潮商在老挝经营的是<strong><span style=\"color:#a0522d\">商业、企业和服务业</span></strong>,从业范围将木材、土特产、建材、金银及其制品、服装、汽车配件、日用百货、印刷厂、餐饮、汽车和机电修理、加油站等等全部囊括在内。老挝潮商与东南亚其他国家的潮商相比，经营规模大、资本雄厚的比例不大,但老挝的进出口和国内市场却受到了他们的巨大影响。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61911\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626284443571.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/094746x2cuysdeugsg2hyd.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/094746x2cuysdeugsg2hyd.jpg\" aid=\"61911\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">有一座非常壮观的建筑物建成于1969年，是<strong><span style=\"color:#808000\">为庆祝老挝独立所建造的纪念碑</span></strong>，如今矗立于老挝万象市中心。老挝于1975年解放时，万象市群众组织游行队伍庆祝胜利的时候，队伍就从这里经过，为此，<strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\">凯旋门</span></strong>成为这座纪念碑的别称，而现在，外国游客的必游地点之一就是这里。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61089\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626284262493.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/153053ztbbkkvfbetc1fvb.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/153053ztbbkkvfbetc1fvb.jpg\" aid=\"61089\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">潮人先辈旅居老挝，在这片土地上历经挫折，仍然咬牙坚持，攻克难关，终于盼来了一个和谐稳定的社会，如今当政者已经凯旋，潮商中的后来者面前又慢慢敞开了一扇新的希望之门，<strong><span style=\"color:#006400\">或许不远的将来，就会有新的成功人士涌现，也会出现更多的老挝潮商。 </span></strong></span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61078\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626284516381.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/153049ael8uhee3mhnfn3d.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/153049ael8uhee3mhnfn3d.jpg\" aid=\"61078\"/></p></ignore_js_op><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61090\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626284108706.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/153153fukz9wkby8hywcyw.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/153153fukz9wkby8hywcyw.gif\" aid=\"61090\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片<br/> 来源/汕头电视台《天下潮商》<br/> 橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/关雪&nbsp;&nbsp;博尔</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img id=\"aimg_179685\" aid=\"179685\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151208/1449578908741437.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p></ignore_js_op><br/><p></p>','2015-11-04 16:38:52',0,NULL,1,NULL,2128,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (300,'【老挝潮商】姚滨——机会永远靠自己争取','201511041640559341.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61141\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626381632653.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/160217epm95ae5nz5bb45f.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/160217epm95ae5nz5bb45f.gif\" aid=\"61141\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">编者按：</span></span></em></strong><br/><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">坚持是一种难得的品质，但放弃也有自己的妙处；危机将大多数人置于危险的绝地，但也总有那么几个可以从中找到良机。对于姚滨而言，泰国的放弃和老挝的坚持，金融危机中得到的机遇，或许不能否认运气的存在，但他的成功，绝无侥幸。</span></span></em></strong><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61124\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626381888003.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/160158p2rlula7rlkgau6k.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/160158p2rlula7rlkgau6k.jpg\" aid=\"61124\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">有一块黑色大理石卧碑，一直安静地伫立在老挝首都万象的广场中央，上面用老中英三种文字镌刻着一句碑文：“<span style=\"color:#006400\"><strong>中国政府和人民赠送给老挝政府和人民的礼物</strong></span>”。 中国政府在二十世纪六十年代末捐资1000万人民币，帮助老挝政府将凯旋门和广场重新修缮了一番。如今这里已成为开放式公园，也是中老两国友谊的一大见证。</span></span> <br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61708\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626381139328.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162340t96j1kg2wdqigdh6.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162340t96j1kg2wdqigdh6.png\" aid=\"61708\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">在东南亚的每一个有潮人居住的国家，一定不会缺少<strong><span style=\"color:#4169e1\">伯公庙</span></strong>，老挝自然也不会例外。在湄公河畔就存在着这样一座伯公庙，本地人将其称作<strong><span style=\"color:#00bfff\">本头公庙</span></strong>。逢年过节，老挝潮人集中祭祀的地方就是这座伯公庙。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61125\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626381997304.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/160159cccwxpof5fv6ztki.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/160159cccwxpof5fv6ztki.jpg\" aid=\"61125\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">就在距离伯公庙不远，河岸的另一端，一片建筑群沿河畔拔地而起，正是由<strong><span style=\"color:#a0522d\">老挝吉达蓬集团</span></strong>投资建设的一座酒店和几十间别墅建筑。吉达蓬集团这个企业是一个叫姚滨的潮籍华人所创立，在老挝当地赫赫有名。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61709\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626382911413.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162340dke0hnoffz6gseye.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162340dke0hnoffz6gseye.png\" aid=\"61709\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\">姚滨</span></strong>祖籍潮阳棉城，上世纪八十年代末于华南理工大学本科毕业，之后毅然离开家乡怀揣着创业梦想来到东南亚，在这里寻求发展机会。 </span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61128\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626382255608.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/160159kcr9a4cazalzz94z.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/160159kcr9a4cazalzz94z.jpg\" aid=\"61128\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">吉达蓬集团公司董事长、老挝中国商会名誉会长姚滨告诉记者，在当时中国，正是出国热的时期，他的同学有的去了澳洲，有的去了美国，于是他也赶上了这阵出国热潮，希望能通过出国寻找机会。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61710\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626383108861.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162341nsam5mow95uxnnis.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162341nsam5mow95uxnnis.png\" aid=\"61710\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">东南亚地区中，潮人最为熟悉的国家毫无疑问是泰国，这里有很多华侨在此安居乐业，姚滨初出茅庐，到泰国寻找机会是他最开始的选择，但那里的竞争</span>太过激烈，让他望而却步。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61711\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626396126272.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162341zhhjgpe3j3dq9ejp.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162341zhhjgpe3j3dq9ejp.png\" aid=\"61711\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">姚滨觉得在泰国不好做生意，于是另择出路，选择了老挝。刚到老挝，他没有像别人一样先去拜神，而是选择逛市场。他当时很快注意到看到市场里的日用品普遍价格昂贵，比如一辆脚踏车200美金、1平方米瓷砖13.8美金等等，几乎是天价级别。他询问了商家入口的渠道，等到问清楚之后，他已敏锐地捕捉到商机，并立即下定了决心。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61131\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626396992743.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/160200lyo19yijjowjjow7.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/160200lyo19yijjowjjow7.png\" aid=\"61131\"/><br/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">经过一番的深思熟虑，姚滨回到中国，不久就在广州购进了一批货物，将其通过正当手续顺利地运送到老挝出口，挣得第一桶金。</span></p></ignore_js_op><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61132\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626396273165.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/160200v6tdaq6ddqwk1ddd.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/160200v6tdaq6ddqwk1ddd.jpg\" aid=\"61132\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">姚滨告诉记者，他第一次运进来的货物是一个货柜，很快取得成功。来到老挝不到一周的时间，他进口的货物就宣布售罄。价格是成本的两倍，净收入有一倍之多。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61712\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626396134577.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162341u0j60t0l5sv1kzv9.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162341u0j60t0l5sv1kzv9.png\" aid=\"61712\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">20多岁的姚滨从第一次的成功试水当中首尝创业的甜头，于是他的冲劲被充分激发，开始想方设法去对这个国家和市场进行更深入的了解。他发现老挝以农业为经济的主体，工业基础十分薄弱，是全球范围内最不发达的国家之一，再加上本身地处内陆，需要从邻国转运各种物资，市场物价非常高。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61713\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626396129680.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162342c0ce7mzaum155ma7.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162342c0ce7mzaum155ma7.png\" aid=\"61713\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">老挝同时还是一个与上世纪七十年代以前的中国极其相似的，封闭的国家，很少与外面打交道。他到达老挝的的时候，老挝正好刚实施开放政策，本地也有很多财富雄厚的老挝人。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61714\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626396164811.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162342sagg601dajj33q60.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162342sagg601dajj33q60.png\" aid=\"61714\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">在越战时期，很多美军驻扎在这里，他们在这里肆意消费，战争时期的军人大多有及时享乐主义精神，一有收入就尽情花费，因此将大量财富留存在老挝民间。国家开放之后，人们开始想要建房、享受，购买大量商品。姚滨正是从人们的消费需求当中寻得了商机。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">姚滨也正是从那时候开始，从中国往老挝运送自行车、空调、灯饰等产品，后来拓展到建筑材料贸易领域，生意越做越大。1997年席卷东南亚各国的亚洲金融风暴，让许多企业遭受的打击非常严重，但姚滨却幸运地逃过了那次危机。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61136\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626396588158.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/160201j4tgekzs584gsvp5.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/160201j4tgekzs584gsvp5.jpg\" aid=\"61136\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">姚滨告诉记者，老挝货币在金融危机爆发期间贬值了1000%，许多公司因此倒闭，房产和土地的价格都一落千丈。他的运气不错，由于从事国际贸易，收支使用的都是美金，所以手头只有美金，没有老币和泰铢。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61715\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626397402175.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162342mmexu0ujiuuzrbbe.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162342mmexu0ujiuuzrbbe.png\" aid=\"61715\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">危机的到来往往伴随着机遇，富有商业头脑的姚滨也正是在此时，发现了千载难得的投资机会。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61716\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626397747031.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162342nppa577l6zz65pja.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162342nppa577l6zz65pja.png\" aid=\"61716\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">企业向银行的贷款无法偿还，企业拥有的房产和土地因此被银行作为抵押，进行拍卖，姚滨便将这些价格便宜的土地和房产大量购入。五年之后，这些土地和房产的价格涨了至少四五倍，甚至有的涨幅达到五六十倍之多。他抓住了这个机会，金融危机成为别人的噩梦，却成为他的大好良机。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61717\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626397749613.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162343pm1zct1nsik810qc.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162343pm1zct1nsik810qc.png\" aid=\"61717\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">姚滨的成功路上，似乎从来不缺乏机会，占尽天时地利人和的他，运气也似乎不能不让人艳羡。但是上天是公平的，运气好的背后，是他一路的大胆闯荡，勇敢取舍和独到的商业眼光。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61707\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626397848070.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162340t3308m00fbnzqnv8.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/162340t3308m00fbnzqnv8.png\" aid=\"61707\"/></p></ignore_js_op><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61140\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626397725429.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/160217pzt3aiutcui3maeh.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/160217pzt3aiutcui3maeh.gif\" aid=\"61140\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">来源/汕头电视台《天下潮商》</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/关雪&nbsp;&nbsp;博尔</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img id=\"aimg_179685\" aid=\"179685\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151208/1449578891226347.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p></ignore_js_op><p></p>','2015-11-04 16:40:55',0,NULL,1,NULL,2309,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (301,'【老挝潮商】吉达蓬集团：兄弟齐心其利断金','201511041642254351.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61213\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626492796130.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/164541zcccyjjfyzkoytfc.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/164541zcccyjjfyzkoytfc.gif\" aid=\"61213\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><br/><p></p><p><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>编者按：</em></strong></span></span></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>现如今捕获万千少男少女心的电视剧当中，十部有九部都涉及豪门恩怨，兄弟相争，但现实生活当中，却并非所有的富人阶层的兄弟，都不能够和睦相处，共同经营事业。姚滨和姚勇这一对手足兄弟，正是携手共创事业新高峰的典型代表。</em></strong></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61195\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626492669703.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/164527petsf0dttexndqsz.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/164527petsf0dttexndqsz.jpg\" aid=\"61195\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">老挝的<span style=\"color:#a0522d\"><strong>吉达蓬集团</strong></span><span style=\"color:#000000\">在董事长姚滨的打理下快打开了局面，不断地拓展新业务，但姚滨在企业的迅速扩张和膨胀当中，却开始产生力不从心的感觉。于是他希望说服自己在国内经商的胞兄姚勇前来老挝，助自己一臂之力。</span></span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61986\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626492393869.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100246a43w3qamx0yw1114.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100246a43w3qamx0yw1114.jpg\" aid=\"61986\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op><br/><p></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#a0522d\">吉达蓬集团公司副董事长、时任老挝中国商会副会长的姚勇</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">告诉记者，他第一次来老挝是在</span><span style=\"color:black\">2002</span><span style=\"color:#000000\">年，而他弟弟姚滨已经先一步来到了这里。姚滨让叫他到老挝进行一次考察，寻找适合投资的商机。在中国国内，姚勇经营的是</span><span style=\"color:black\">IT</span><span style=\"color:#000000\">行业，属于科技产业的一种，但来到老挝之后发现这里缺乏科技产业，甚至连工厂都很稀少，只有一些手工作坊，与国内相比反差巨大。</span></span></span></p><p><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61987\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626492998638.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100246e99w6600ix9wnk99.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100246e99w6600ix9wnk99.jpg\" aid=\"61987\"/></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">在中国内地的生意，姚勇一直经营得不错，让他将辛辛苦苦打拼出来的事业就此放弃，实在不是一件容易的事情，姚勇在2007年做出正式转战老挝商界的决定之前，也着实经历了一段时间的思想斗争和酝酿，而最终促使他做出选择的，是他与姚滨深厚的兄弟情谊和对未来发展的憧憬。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61198\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626492649822.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/164527h53n6733i6ug62n3.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/164527h53n6733i6ug62n3.jpg\" aid=\"61198\"/></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">姚勇告诉记者，他来到这里之后，首先做的事情就是了解这里的市场。他在和弟弟的交流中察觉到，虽然老挝不发达，但另一方面却也因此拥有更多的机会，所以把中国国内的业务都慢慢地处理完毕，同时把人才、资金都逐渐转移到了老挝。</span></span></span></p><p><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61985\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626493134685.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100246nh2llz3s96346hpq.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100246nh2llz3s96346hpq.png\" aid=\"61985\"/></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\">红酸枝木</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">的重要产地之一正是老挝，因此，一直以来，木材加工也是老挝的传统产业。在中国国内，姚勇经常能感受到现在有不少人近乎痴迷地热爱原木家具，因此，他也就以此作为转战老挝之后的突破口。</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61200\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626493109860.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/164528i7vpgg4f874tpzbv.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/164528i7vpgg4f874tpzbv.jpg\" aid=\"61200\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><br/><p></p><p><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">姚勇来到老挝之后，看到很多用粗糙的制作工艺生产商品的工厂，甚至有一些工厂在连接木料时使用铁钉，将原本上好的木料都破坏了。</span></span></span></p><p><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61988\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626493131776.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100247izfsk4sy8dzsr2da.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100247izfsk4sy8dzsr2da.jpg\" aid=\"61988\"/></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">中华民族一直崇尚木，中国人的生活中从古至今不可或缺的材料之一就是木材，中国人对木不仅只有使用和喜爱，还在木制品中添加了深厚的文化内涵，对木材的打磨加工雕刻等传统工艺要求都很高。</span></span></span></p><p><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61989\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626493845015.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100247auekup7fquqrj7bs.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100247auekup7fquqrj7bs.jpg\" aid=\"61989\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">姚勇认为，自己完全可以向老挝引进中国国内那种对木料制作的传统工艺到，同时充分体现这种工艺蕴含的文化底蕴。这既是一个给自己带来艺术享受的过程，又是能将老挝的劳动者培养成技术工人、技师、艺术师的渠道。因此他开始以此为理念，开办加工红木的工厂。</span></span></span></p><p><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61990\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626493121982.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100247tdpmlrkwk9mdzlzy.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100247tdpmlrkwk9mdzlzy.jpg\" aid=\"61990\"/></p><p></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#a0522d\"><strong>红木成材要经过几百年的生长，属于不可再生资源，</strong></span><span style=\"color:#000000\">所以姚勇十分用心地对待木材加工的工作，每一块木材都力求以精细的作品作为最终面貌展现在世人面前。</span></span></span></p><p><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61991\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626493140115.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100247p7u4v96v61126au6.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100247p7u4v96v61126au6.jpg\" aid=\"61991\"/></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">姚勇坚守的原则中，第一个就是一定要把出自中国人之手的东西做好，不能弄虚作假。本着这样的原则，他的作品没有用过一块假木头。第二个是坚持榫卯结构，不用铁钉。他们现如今已积累了一些原木，有手艺的师傅们能够得到一个更好的舞台，于此同时，他也在这个过程中得到了一种满足感和成功的喜悦。</span></span></span></p><p><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61992\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626493656449.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100247go929785nlojnj6h.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100247go929785nlojnj6h.jpg\" aid=\"61992\"/></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">所谓“</span><strong><span style=\"color:#006400\">兄弟同心，其利断金</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">”，姚勇成功地让自己的红木加工厂成为老挝最大最好的木业工厂，但同时也不忘给予弟弟姚滨的事业大力支持。姚滨近几年来对中工国际等中国大型国企积极引入，让它们到老挝进行投资，与自己所创的吉达蓬集团实现深层次的合作。哥哥姚勇便为他承担了项目管理事务，保证了各项工作的顺利推进。</span></span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61993\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626493102919.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100247r82b228322bc1283.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100247r82b228322bc1283.jpg\" aid=\"61993\"/></p></ignore_js_op><p></p><p><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">姚勇告诉记者，很多项目在他们的努力下已经做成，并且全部取得了巨大的成功。这其中包括建设琅勃拉邦的机场，采购老挝国内支线飞机，以及为老挝发射“老挝一号”卫星的准备，这一系列的操作他们都非常顺利地进行着。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61210\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626494134616.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/164530kcudd4duyf093mjj.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/164530kcudd4duyf093mjj.jpg\" aid=\"61210\"/></p><br/><p></p><p><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">姚勇认为，他们在这里创业的目的，就是要做好该做的事情，与人为善，自己捕获商机的同时，也要把更多的商机带给老挝的人民和中国的企业。老挝的政府部门和相关领导可以在这个过程中对他们慢慢地进行了解，最终认可潮汕人华人在这里所做的事情和贡献。</span></span></span></p><p><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61994\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626494109511.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100247liu08bujk8ugdeck.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100247liu08bujk8ugdeck.png\" aid=\"61994\"/></p><p></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">他们是这样想的，于是也就这样做了。逐渐发展扩大的姚家兄弟事业所创造的社会价值，他们对老挝社会的积极回馈，随着时间推移而开始得到老挝政府的认可，</span><strong><span style=\"color:#808000\">兄弟俩终于携手，踏上了另一个新的高度。</span></strong></span></span></p><p><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61984\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626494722503.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100246p8ptblt3btr0t1z3.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100246p8ptblt3btr0t1z3.jpg\" aid=\"61984\" initialized=\"true\"/> </p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61212\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626495849834.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/164541os4zq7i438i0qeqv.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/164541os4zq7i438i0qeqv.gif\" aid=\"61212\"/><br/></p><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">来源/汕头电视台《天下潮商》</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/关雪&nbsp;&nbsp;博尔</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img id=\"aimg_179685\" aid=\"179685\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151208/1449578877453899.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p></ignore_js_op><p></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2015-11-04 16:42:25',0,NULL,1,NULL,2296,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (302,'【老挝潮商】风生水起 后浪推前浪','201511041644096372.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61285\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626591112670.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/171309od8w0bee09deoodj.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/171309od8w0bee09deoodj.gif\" aid=\"61285\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>编者按：</em></strong></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>潮商为什么会得到国内外人们公认的好评和敬佩？这绝不是因为他们会挣钱这么简单。他们的拼劲是一面，他们对当地社会的感恩与回馈也是一面。这些优良品质一代代地传承，便造就了一批又一批的潮商，创造了一个又一个的奇迹。</em></strong></span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62017\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626591700772.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101310fb122jn2wj126kb1.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101310fb122jn2wj126kb1.jpg\" aid=\"62017\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">正是姚勇和姚滨兄弟俩的责任心，让他们事事有担当，件件力求完美，同时也让他们获得了老挝的政界中很高的信任度。老挝于11月举行的<strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\">第九届亚欧首脑会议</span></strong>上，老挝政府就将一道“难题”抛给了他们俩。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61262\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626591351268.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/171256ecy7666yu0lmy88v.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/171256ecy7666yu0lmy88v.jpg\" aid=\"61262\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">姚勇告诉记者，老挝的总理对他们尤其重视，他们兄弟俩还曾经专门被总理叫去。见面之后，总理肯定了他们为中老两国所做的贡献，而后告诉了他们老挝政府其时正经历的，包括接待出问题，房间不足等困难，希望他们能为政府分忧。他们兄弟俩当即表态，答应总理的请求，并表示一定尽力而为。姚勇和姚滨都有一个的态度，他们认为自己已经得到了老挝人民和老挝政府非常周到的照顾，在这样的前提下，承担这些责任于他们而言义不容辞，他们应当以此回报老挝人民。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61263\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626592623487.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/171256ibcfi88y4cvfq2y4.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/171256ibcfi88y4cvfq2y4.png\" aid=\"61263\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">国家出席亚欧首脑会议的政要有近50个，用于接待外宾的老挝首都万象的酒店能力非常有限，无力应对。为此，吉达蓬集团将50栋别墅的建设工程任务接了下来。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">当时，姚勇进行的第一个步骤就是确定了前来老挝的首脑共来自48个国家，要为每一位首脑提供一套入住的别墅，外加会所和配套设施，总共有50栋别墅的建设任务。他们选择了中国中工国际为合作对象，老挝政府则将靠近湄公河河边的这块土地划定为建筑区域，那里也是首都万象最好的土地。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62018\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626592961114.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101310kr2hxotmx2fhs2zd.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101310kr2hxotmx2fhs2zd.jpg\" aid=\"62018\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">吉达蓬集团与中工国际的合作绝不仅于此，他们还共同收购了<strong><span style=\"color:#a0522d\">东昌酒店</span></strong>，这座老挝最高楼层的建筑物，并且为了让这所五星级酒店发挥会议接待的作用，而对它进行了升级改造。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62019\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626592763771.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101310k5kyxwkm5xxpxfft.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101310k5kyxwkm5xxpxfft.jpg\" aid=\"62019\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">不过，对于一个众多国家的部长，随员和相关人士都会出席的会议来说，不可能只需要一个五星级酒店。因此，在次年二月份，老挝政府决定再划出一片土地，沿着湄公河畔的50栋别墅，再兴建一座亚欧峰会大酒店。这个任务，姚勇姚滨兄弟俩自然责无旁贷。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62020\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626592444561.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101310y1toazrrrotza110.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101310y1toazrrrotza110.jpg\" aid=\"62020\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">姚勇对当时突然接到任务的时候所感觉到的压力，依旧记忆犹新。既要做土地的平整，又要找资金。3亿人民币左右的资金是他们的初步估算，而这个预算还很可能被超过。另外由于2月份才提出的酒店建造方案，启用日期为11月6日，等于完工时间必须在9月底，工期太短，挑战性很大。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62021\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626592107755.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101311uqxw3jx3r3nqk3ez.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101311uqxw3jx3r3nqk3ez.jpg\" aid=\"62021\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">吉达蓬集团在进行细致论证之后，决定通过中国工商银行进行融资，并让中国云南建工集团有限公司对项目进行承包施工，迅速投入高效率的建设当中。酒店的一期工程已按时完成，并交付使用。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">姚勇告诉记者，他们当时很多人是抱着怀疑的态度看待这个工程的，对其能够完成持悲观看法。他们正是凭着一种一定要为我们中国人、我们华人、我们潮汕人争口气的信念坚持到了最后。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62022\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626592122515.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101311eg2dduauplj4lpfu.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101311eg2dduauplj4lpfu.jpg\" aid=\"62022\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">对外开放对于老挝来说可谓是天时，至于地利自然是丰富的物产资源，融入当地生活的外来者与当地人和谐相处，则是人和。天时地利人和兼备，是姚勇姚滨兄弟俩的事业能够蓬勃发展也就不足为奇了。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">姚勇觉得，在老挝，中国的文化、工艺、理念等很多东西都可以找到适合它扎根生长的沃土。在中国，姚勇的很多亲戚朋友都对他远赴老挝的行为不能理解。姚勇告诉他们，老挝等同于一张白纸，在那里不会有负担，可以写所有自己想写的，画所有自己想画的。你有机会在这里实现自己的理念和理想。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62023\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626592815753.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101311atih96sh6qvwyy3e.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101311atih96sh6qvwyy3e.jpg\" aid=\"62023\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">潮汕人不惜漂洋过海去追逐自己的梦想，足迹踏遍世界各地，在不同的地方扎根发芽。他们用积极的态度融入当地社会，缔造了一个个商业传奇。一批批年轻人也在前辈们的影响下，出门闯荡捕捉商机，去实现自己的创业梦想。<strong><span style=\"color:#a0522d\">揭阳惠来人胡学章</span></strong>在七月份来到老挝，之后与几个朋友合租了一个店铺，住在了那里。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62024\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626593791225.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101311twjkizqti29jqs3q.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101311twjkizqti29jqs3q.jpg\" aid=\"62024\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">胡学章告诉记者，他原本并非为了创业，而是来这里旅游的，感受到当地人的和善，也发现社会秩序没有想象中的那样混乱。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61274\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626593134435.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/171258rk0qqlbqxb8kcpub.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/171258rk0qqlbqxb8kcpub.png\" aid=\"61274\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">胡学章原来在深圳经营的是电子产品，生意规模较小，收入也不高，所以动了出国寻找良机的念头。如今他正计划着将老挝的水产品收购，而后进口到中国销售。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">胡学章认为，做水产生意可大可小，风险很大，有可能一夜暴富，也有可能很快破产，而他们要做的生意是收购水产品。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62025\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626593156248.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101311ng2jy388dhdd6qc7.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101311ng2jy388dhdd6qc7.jpg\" aid=\"62025\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">胡学章舍弃家乡舒适的生活。来到老挝谋求发展，除了现实生活的艰苦之外，其他一切都还是未知数。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61277\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626593504203.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/171259iidjm8z94rpp4mnn.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/171259iidjm8z94rpp4mnn.png\" aid=\"61277\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">来到这里对胡学章而言，真的是一件很辛苦的事情，不过胡学章坚信，不论身处哪个地方，只要你吃得了苦，决定做一件事情，并且有耐心、有毅力去坚持，那么就可以大胆地尝试一下，任何事情都不可能一蹴而就。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62026\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626593103874.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101311kk0qma1e05kd7679.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101311kk0qma1e05kd7679.jpg\" aid=\"62026\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">老挝对于大多数人来说时至今日仍然是一个陌生的国度，仍落后于其他大多数国家，但老一辈潮商也正是在这片神秘的土地上，书写出曾经的“<strong><span style=\"color:#006400\">处处潮州话，座座胶己厝</span></strong>”的辉煌。<strong><span style=\"color:#808000\">如今新一代潮商已风生水起，在他们的努力下，一定会不断创造出新的事业、新的业绩、新的辉煌。</span></strong></span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62016\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626594107136.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101310xye4e9w99k86ka9l.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/101310xye4e9w99k86ka9l.jpg\" aid=\"62016\"/> </p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61284\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626594222000.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/171309rrdz1tw0twsmrfrv.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/171309rrdz1tw0twsmrfrv.gif\" aid=\"61284\"/><br/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">来源/汕头电视台《天下潮商》</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/关雪&nbsp;&nbsp;博尔&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img id=\"aimg_179685\" aid=\"179685\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151208/1449578866120265.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p></ignore_js_op><br/><p></p>','2015-11-04 16:44:09',0,NULL,1,NULL,2377,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (303,'过趣味！潮汕阿伯的“农具总动员”','201511041647109236.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61907\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626701118595.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/094120p3arfa5et2ei5z9a.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/094120p3arfa5et2ei5z9a.gif\" aid=\"61907\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>潮汕老物件很多，特别是耕作用的农具，凝聚了农人的精巧心思。在潮汕，有位阿伯，闲散在家，玩心大起，组织了一场农具总动员，其间巧思，令人爱不释手。</em></strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61944\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626701115540.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095744xq2ddqda4c2q8dp4.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095744xq2ddqda4c2q8dp4.jpg\" aid=\"61944\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">文章开始之前，先给大家看一件物件，都来猜猜，这是什么，做什么功用的呢？</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"187\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61945\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626702167307.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095744mxqyntkteuh04qkn.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095744mxqyntkteuh04qkn.jpg\" aid=\"61945\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color:#008080\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">猜不到吧？</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">其实，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">上面这</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">东西</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">，叫做旋桶（也作潠桶）。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">潮汕话里的“旋桶”，“旋”字不念“凯旋”的旋（五声阳平），而是第六声，音同潮汕话里形容小孩便溺的“旋”字。这是因为潮汕话是保留最多古汉语字词的地方方言，“旋”字有喷射之意，早在两千多年前的《左传》里面就出现了：“夷射姑旋焉。”夷射姑是一个小国的大夫，这句话是他随地小便之意。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">那么，旋桶有什么用呢？看下面这图就一清二楚了。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61949\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626702541770.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095745q4vmy3xmg83oi444.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095745q4vmy3xmg83oi444.jpg\" aid=\"61949\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#008080\">没错，旋桶，就是浇菜用的农具。</span>它根据共通器原理，通过适度倾斜桶身来让水从管子里喷射出来，浇到菜上。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61946\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626702121573.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095744fvdevjxellorzzbn.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095744fvdevjxellorzzbn.jpg\" aid=\"61946\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">千百年来，旋桶都是杉木做的。现在再用杉木来做，费工费钱，所以都用塑料或金属了。<span style=\"color:#008080\">但是，偏偏还有人，现在还在坚持用木料手工打造农具，而且，做的还是没有实用性，只有观赏性的缩微作品。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#008080\">他，就是潮汕民间手工艺术家，陈作泉。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61947\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626702553302.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095745g2rtzl1nnta7agtd.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095745g2rtzl1nnta7agtd.jpg\" aid=\"61947\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建阳，是澄海苏南地区一个远近闻名的文化乡。醉心于缩微农具制作的陈作泉，便和老伴在本村世泽巷老厝居住。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61968\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626702223421.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100003vpdmrijkrirarkkv.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/100003vpdmrijkrirarkkv.jpg\" aid=\"61968\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">现在的潮汕农村，像世泽巷这么干净、雅洁的老巷，真的不多了。这里随便一户人家走进去，都是花香鸟语，能在这样的老巷老宅里安度晚年，想想也是醉了。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#008080\">就在这里，已过古稀之年的陈作泉老伯，硬是靠双手复制了一个农耕社会。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61948\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626703617161.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095745zbgcq7kgqlwhlhqn.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095745zbgcq7kgqlwhlhqn.jpg\" aid=\"61948\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">△部分作品图</span></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000\"><strong>年轻乐落，年老乐活 </strong></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">陈伯年轻时务农，为生计，跟农具结下不解之缘。潮汕农村大多数的老农民，一辈子面朝黄土背朝天，对农具的感情其实是很微妙很复杂的，用又爱又恨来形容，恐怕还难以尽道其详。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61950\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626703495209.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095746r0032i2mmfnfrn1y.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095746r0032i2mmfnfrn1y.jpg\" aid=\"61950\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61951\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626703865541.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095746fm29thbq0it8t98b.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095746fm29thbq0it8t98b.jpg\" aid=\"61951\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">还在种田之时，陈伯就喜欢木工活。他没正式拜过师，这一身手艺，都是“偷”来的。不管走到哪里，一看到有人做木工，他就会痴痴站在一旁偷师学艺。一般木工师傅都不太介意有人看，但你不能问，一问就会被呵斥甚至驱赶。<span style=\"color:#008080\">因为“目识”好，陈伯就这样学来了过硬的木工本领，家里的眠床、沙发、椅、柜等，全都是他自己打造的</span>。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">洗脚上田之后，陈伯曾在本村菜市场工作过，参与市场管理。<span style=\"color:#008080\">退休之后，也是这两年，他才萌发出做缩微农具的念头，并以此为乐，一发不可收拾地做起来。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61952\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626703400711.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095746se1t7xfxzx0hj0rk.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095746se1t7xfxzx0hj0rk.jpg\" aid=\"61952\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61953\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626703725601.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095746r2pcxozliz60p3o0.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095746r2pcxozliz60p3o0.jpg\" aid=\"61953\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">△每个成功的阿伯，背后总有个默默支持的阿姆</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><br/></span></span></p><p><strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">人</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">比不了，欢喜就好</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></span></span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">“人比不了，欢喜就好。”这是陈伯常说的话。子女成家立业，晚年生活无忧，总得干点什么，才能让人生充实、欢喜。<span style=\"color:#008080\">对于陈伯来说，做缩微农具，用精雕细琢还原精耕细作，既是重拾年轻时的爱好，也是让青春重返的最佳选择。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"482\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61943\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626705424637.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095743iy4t0f6hs5rarh0y.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095743iy4t0f6hs5rarh0y.gif\" aid=\"61943\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">△石磨，陈作泉作品，把米、麦、豆等粮食加工成粉、浆的一种人力机械</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">陈伯对饮食要求不高，经常因为做这些手工而耽误吃饭时间，被老伴一催再催，唠叨不停，他都一笑对之，不告一段落不吃饭。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#008080\">包括老伴在内的家人，开始也不理解，甚至责怪他，后来也都被他的执着所感化。</span>特别是看到他的作品那么精致那么人见人爱，也就引以为荣，转而默默支持起他来。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61954\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626705329537.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095747amkfwwnnd28zmm2f.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095747amkfwwnnd28zmm2f.jpg\" aid=\"61954\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">有人晒钱，有人晒命，陈伯只晒快乐。他常热心向孙儿辈讲解各种农具的用法，虽然他们不一定懂，他依然乐在其中。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"></span></span></p><p><strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><br/></span></span></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">只</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">做藏品，不当商品</span></span></span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">因为所有的创造都只是图个乐，陈伯说他没有系统规划，也不画图纸，年轻时使用过的农具，谁先跳进他的回忆里，他就把谁创造出来。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">随着作品渐多，名头渐开，也有人打这些作品的主意。但陈伯还是那句话，“欢喜就好”，心血结晶他不卖。<span style=\"color:#008080\">有时碰到真心喜欢的小孩，他却会慷慨地送他一件。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61955\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626705346664.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095747zpp1w1m1x41wpz2d.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095747zpp1w1m1x41wpz2d.jpg\" aid=\"61955\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">这小女孩全神贯注地看着陈老伯雕琢作品，最后，老伯送了她一件作品。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#008080\">虽然只是做着玩，但陈伯把每一件缩微农具都当成真的来做，仿佛完成之后它们就可以在农活中派上用场一样。</span>下面这部水车，就是陈伯的得意之作。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"581\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61942\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626706514574.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095742t4fbabdjua1agyji.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095742t4fbabdjua1agyji.gif\" aid=\"61942\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">△水车，陈作泉作品，龙骨水车，传统灌溉农具，可把水往高处引。这是流行于广东的手摇水车，可单人操作。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61956\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626706651501.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095747j0cmvkf04fcv9fop.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095747j0cmvkf04fcv9fop.jpg\" aid=\"61956\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">△涂砻（音笼），碾谷用。由上下两个圆墩构成，下墩有砻脚和砻轴，用于固定位置和限制上墩；上墩有砻耳和砻槽，用于连接砻臂和添加稻谷。砻墩外围用竹篾编织，中间用粘土填满打实，填时两墩间留有一些浅沟并铺设一些木砻齿。当砻臂推动砻墩转动碾压时，砻齿会使稻谷脱壳，变成糙米和粗糠，然后经浅沟流出。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61957\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626706284009.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095747ni6dzkqzi2m6kd7u.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095747ni6dzkqzi2m6kd7u.jpg\" aid=\"61957\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">△风柜，通过手摇鼓风，分离稻谷中的糠等杂物。这个风柜也是陈伯最有成就感的作品。因为构造复杂，陈伯追求纯手工制作，不用胶水，所以耗时特别长。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61958\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626706111882.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095748i4xueurxxuppuxqp.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095748i4xueurxxuppuxqp.jpg\" aid=\"61958\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61959\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626706104162.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095748njurfr8ruh7r2haz.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095748njurfr8ruh7r2haz.jpg\" aid=\"61959\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">△舂碓（潮音对），可将稻谷、玉米、豆类等原粮加工成米粒或米粉，潮汕人做粿最离不开它（上图为陈伯作品，下图为舂碓示意雕塑）。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"> </span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">陈伯也编了不少缩微竹制品。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61960\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626707823284.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095748c5a36gfddmz6mnvs.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095748c5a36gfddmz6mnvs.jpg\" aid=\"61960\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">△鸭笼</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61961\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626707942998.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095749jq1ublquqdgdrg6i.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095749jq1ublquqdgdrg6i.jpg\" aid=\"61961\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61962\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626707954617.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095749bltlp55ne081d51k.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095749bltlp55ne081d51k.jpg\" aid=\"61962\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61963\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626707544179.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095749i8878g5s8ij88s3j.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095749i8878g5s8ij88s3j.jpg\" aid=\"61963\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61964\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626707587469.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095749iyxwgqzabn9aauml.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095749iyxwgqzabn9aauml.jpg\" aid=\"61964\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">△以上为各种各样的木桶。左下为传说中的饭桶，装干饭用；右下分别为大脚桶、细脚桶、腰桶等。大脚桶洗衣服用，细脚桶洗女人衣物用，腰桶专为老妇人设计，高腰，她们使用时不用大幅度弯腰。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61965\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626707138743.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095750j7ijtj04ziint7it.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095750j7ijtj04ziint7it.jpg\" aid=\"61965\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">△这些是</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">掏粪、装粪用的“粗gong2”和“粗桶”（潮汕话将粪便讳称为“粗”）</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><br/></span></span></p><p><strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">玩</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">物长志，老有所依</span></span></span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">陈伯的作品还有很多，令人叹为观止。篇幅所限，只能选择性地跟大家分享。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">现在流行一个网络热词，叫“城会玩”（你们城里人真会玩）。如果较个真，不知哪个城里人，在陈作泉面前敢说他会玩。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">专家说，中国已提前进入“超级老龄化社会”，比例逐年升高的老年人，特别是空巢老人的精神生活，成了一个绕不开的社会问题。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">麻将、拜佛、广场舞等等，这些都不失为老年人充实生活的选项，但陈作泉展示了另一种可能：玩物长志。创作的过程，身体得到锻炼，精神得到快乐；而创作的硕果，又愉悦了周围的人——还有比这更好的安度晚年的方式吗？</span></span><span style=\"color:#008080\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">人的成就感，在名利之外，真的还有很多实现的途径。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">惭愧，我们只能以这样的方式，向这位民间艺术家致敬。</span></span></p><p><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61966\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626708911585.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095750gspsg11x6gugppag.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/095750gspsg11x6gugppag.jpg\" aid=\"61966\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61908\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626708797809.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/094120oaw1qnw2m2ixw0zn.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/094120oaw1qnw2m2ixw0zn.gif\" aid=\"61908\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">汕头橄榄台综合报道 转载请注明出处</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">来源/微信公众号：潮汕物食</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">实习小编/博尔</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img id=\"aimg_179685\" aid=\"179685\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151208/1449578852908271.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2015-11-04 16:47:10',0,NULL,1,NULL,2906,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (304,'一个潮汕姿娘对手绘艺术的坚持之路','201511041648592591.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px;\"></span></ignore_js_op></span></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62090\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626877644013.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103749r3r33yjyj5796q79.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103749r3r33yjyj5796q79.gif\" aid=\"62090\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">热爱手绘的人，会把它当做一种生活态度；欣赏手绘的人，会从中发现不一样的生活情趣。手绘，小小一张图画里，住着大大的世界。</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62071\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626877142004.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103737d9iko0mius1iue0s.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103737d9iko0mius1iue0s.jpg\" aid=\"62071\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#008080\"><strong>她，叫黄锦清，一个土生土长的80后潮汕姿娘。</strong></span></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">从小喜爱绘画，在父母的帮助下，开始了最初的手绘创作。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">由于对美术的热爱，高中报读了美术院校，经过多年的学术熏陶，让她更加笃定了自己对于绘画的由衷热爱。毕业后从事设计工作，并在不久步入婚姻殿堂，现在是两个孩子的母亲。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62072\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626883882151.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103737udv47gumvvj64yqj.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103737udv47gumvvj64yqj.jpg\" aid=\"62072\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> <ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62083\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626883212749.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103740ufka0xypcq00xf9k.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103740ufka0xypcq00xf9k.jpg\" aid=\"62083\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">在潮汕有这样一个传统习俗，大部分潮汕姿娘一般结婚之后都以家庭为重，放弃工作，在家里相夫教子。因此，潮汕姿娘向来就以贤妻良母而著称。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">然而，在她眼里却不仅仅是这样。<strong><span style=\"color:#008080\">她不仅把家庭料理得很好，而且每天仍然坚持手绘。而且无论多忙，她总能挤出时间来手绘。</span></strong></span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62076\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626884377905.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103738mu9yry4yy0f9ptuy.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103738mu9yry4yy0f9ptuy.jpg\" aid=\"62076\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#008080\"><strong>她坚持每天一张手绘作品赠送自己。</strong></span></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">她说，“她只是想简简单单的画画。画画就像是她的一位熟络多年的旧友，每天只要跟这位旧友说说话，谈谈心，她就会感觉到很快乐。”</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62077\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626884225658.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103738q199vr5iit5199as.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103738q199vr5iit5199as.jpg\" aid=\"62077\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span> <ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62075\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626884235211.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103738yzhq0a0k0skfxxnq.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103738yzhq0a0k0skfxxnq.jpg\" aid=\"62075\"/> </p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62074\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626885137047.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103737wfooo46ymx5x8xs4.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103737wfooo46ymx5x8xs4.jpg\" aid=\"62074\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"/><br/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#008080\">在绘画的世界里，她总是可以如此快乐。或者，这就是一种骨子里的爱吧，无欲无求，只是一种陪伴。</span></strong>在如今纷扰嘈杂的世界里，能够如此静下心来一直坚持做自己喜爱做的事情，没有任何利欲追求，确实是少之又少。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62079\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626885497361.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103739oes9fvvn993rcks5.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103739oes9fvvn993rcks5.jpg\" aid=\"62079\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> <ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62070\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626885131178.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103736rmulbz8ubtgmsbwb.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103736rmulbz8ubtgmsbwb.jpg\" aid=\"62070\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#008080\">在她的画里，你可以找到一种对于线条与色彩最纯粹的追求。</span></strong></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">当然，她不仅追求线条和色彩自身的表现力，而且追求画面的平面感、装饰性和寓意性。她以浓厚的、稠密的颜料浆，以婉转柔绵却别具一格的笔触，沿着画笔脉络，通过线条的张力，将前景和背景统一在同一个视觉区域里，形成一种独特的个人风格。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62078\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626888129654.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103739j45jjjjzidpvgz53.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103739j45jjjjzidpvgz53.jpg\" aid=\"62078\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#008080\"><strong>在她的画里，你总是可以感受到快乐。</strong></span></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">对于生活，她总是比别人多几分在乎与关心。有时候总是让你有这么一种感觉，看她的画就如同在为自己疗伤。那些悲伤的情绪总是可以那么容易地就被画里那些孩子的笑容拉扯揉拧，之后渐渐被放逐到另一个二次元时空里，瞬间遗忘。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">好像，她画里有一种叫做忘记悲伤的魔力。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62085\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626888123931.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103741xmb2wpbp32621m1s.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103741xmb2wpbp32621m1s.jpg\" aid=\"62085\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#008080\"><strong>看着她的画，你可以感受到一种随意、自由抒发内心感情的风格。</strong></span></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">她总是喜欢观察生活那些细小的事物，来诠释她内心里温情美好的小世界。那些孩子的童真童趣，孩童眼中对于这个世界单纯美好的理解，那些生活细节与自然万物，总是能够轻而易举的在她画里游走。一条弯曲的长线，一条断续的短线，二者交互糅合，以抽象的表现手段，呈现出炫目奇幻的童趣世界。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62087\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626888649865.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103741lvwbwvffcxhxcia7.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103741lvwbwvffcxhxcia7.jpg\" aid=\"62087\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span> <ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62080\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626888227724.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103739wtlk8sw8l3p69xp7.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103739wtlk8sw8l3p69xp7.jpg\" aid=\"62080\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#008080\"><strong>有时候我们只顾仰头凝视雄伟壮丽的建筑，却忘记了身边细小可爱的生活细节和自然事物。或许慢下脚步来，就在我们身边，也能发现生命里的小幸福呢?</strong></span></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62092\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626888995755.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/104045bvahvvaij6661vhb.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/104045bvahvvaij6661vhb.jpg\" aid=\"62092\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span> <ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62091\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626888876815.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103749pr6l7r69vzpzxu79.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/103749pr6l7r69vzpzxu79.gif\" aid=\"62091\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汕头橄榄台综合报道 转载请注明出处</span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">来源/微信公众号：清心艺术</span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">文/林泽芝<br/></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">图/黄锦清</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">实习小编/博尔</span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img id=\"aimg_179685\" aid=\"179685\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151208/1449578843699438.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p></ignore_js_op><br/><p></p>','2015-11-04 16:48:59',0,NULL,1,NULL,2904,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (305,'永新记忆：两百多年的水仙古庙 九月初三的水仙爷','201511041650141359.png','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61763\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626980917609.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/164051txkkjkkdndknkjh9.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/164051txkkjkkdndknkjh9.gif\" aid=\"61763\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>编者按：</em></strong></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>拜祭神灵，其实是一种对自然的敬畏，一种精神的寄托，一种对美好生活的祝福和向往，也是古代先民借以娱乐的盛会。而在潮汕人坚守传统</em></strong><strong><em>的</em></strong><strong><em>字典里，就有写满神灵的一页。</em></strong></span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"500\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61759\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626981132925.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/164050mawg7wk2v0j6hmh0.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/164050mawg7wk2v0j6hmh0.jpg\" aid=\"61759\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">潮汕人一向来以对神明的敬畏和对大自然的崇拜著称。神明在潮汕，有一个高大上的称呼：“老爷”。<strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\">九月初三，是澄海区莲上镇永新居委的“水仙爷生”，让我们也去凑一下热闹。</span></strong></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">九月初三那一天，整个永新居委正处在热闹的氛围中，特地搭起来的戏台唱着才子佳人的剧目，还有木偶剧的表演等活动。看到我们前来采访，当地人把我们带到了水仙古庙。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"500\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61757\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626981971829.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/164049iozmy3uz3hsyhrup.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/164049iozmy3uz3hsyhrup.jpg\" aid=\"61757\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">水仙庙里的水仙爷是什么出处呢？<strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\">据老一辈人介绍说，水仙爷的起源是水涝神。</span></strong>当初水涝神来到这里，先是搭了个草棚，乡里人就来拜水仙爷，拜了水仙爷之后，乡里人感觉自己的确变得很幸运。因此，诚心一拜的乡民就逐渐增多。乾隆31年，全乡决定集资建设水仙宫，这座水仙宫的名字就叫做水仙古庙。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">潮汕人靠海，和福建、台湾等地一样，讨掠为生的海边人大多拜妈祖娘娘，所以，妈祖生在潮汕地区是最常见的“老爷生”，<strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\">但在永新，水仙爷才是他们这里最权威的水域之神。</span></strong>一般来说，水神泛指大禹，水仙爷宫也大多供奉大禹，永新水仙爷的“水涝神”指的是什么神灵呢？</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"500\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61755\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626981129396.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/164048j9ut7m8ecf28m8eo.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/164048j9ut7m8ecf28m8eo.jpg\" aid=\"61755\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">听说，这得回溯到200多年前的历史了，那时候这里还是一片海，而水仙宫就在海边，那时“挨缉”的人就在这附近干活。但是干活的时候渔夫总是不小心捞到水仙爷，重复了好几次，“挨缉”的人就说如果水仙爷真能显圣，就让他捕捞满满的一笼鱼。结果真的如此，“挨缉”的人就把这尊水仙爷带回去，并决定水仙爷的绳子在哪里断开，就把水仙爷安置在哪里。就这样，水仙爷最终在这里安置下来了。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"500\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61754\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626982703827.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/164047a8xtenx3n0fkfzne.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/164047a8xtenx3n0fkfzne.jpg\" aid=\"61754\"/> </p><p><br/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000\"><strong>永新人说，他们的水仙爷，其实也不光是水涝神，也是大禹，还是“水父水母”神，他们选择九月初三这个日子纪念，就是一个与众不同的时间。</strong></span></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">那为什么永新人的水仙爷会有这么多身份呢？原来，潮汕地区传统拜祭“水父水母”就是在九月初三， 所以他们就用水父水母的纪念日祭拜水仙爷 。另一个是民国时期，国民政府下令禁止祭祀这个“无稽的神”，所以乡民就不敢直接说是拜水涝神，而是用了大禹的名字——大禹治水有功，把水神称作大禹也不失尊敬。最后一层原因，是潮汕的水神有很多种，水父水母、水涝神都有，所以最后永新人的水仙爷就集中了这三者。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"500\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61760\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626982126694.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/164050wooe7kc8h8zyh9ke.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/164050wooe7kc8h8zyh9ke.jpg\" aid=\"61760\"/> </p><p><br/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">在永新，关于九月初三“老爷生”还有一说，说是农历九月初三有天文大潮，是潮汕沿海江河潮水涨得最高的日子，也是水父水母的的神诞日，所以就成了永新“老爷生”的日子。<strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\">200多年来，永新人用自己的方式，虔诚地表达对神明的敬畏，不管是什么神，自老辈人传下来的规矩和仪式全部都得传承，即使是在物质不富裕是的年代里，永新人还会继续保持自己的那份虔诚。</span></strong></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">“水仙古庙”这四个字的牌匾颇有古意，悬挂于此经历了风雨摇曳的年代，遭受过不少磨难，永新人没有忘记祖辈留下的信仰，一直尽他们的力量保护着这座古庙。虽然民国时期禁拜无名神和解放后破四旧的历史原因，水仙古庙有一段时间被默默掩盖着。但改革开放后，恢复原来传统文化的乡民不遗余力地恢复了古庙的往日神采，水仙古庙仍旧安存在永新乡民的心里。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"500\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61761\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626982130334.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/164050jf6xmpvovccnozj7.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/164050jf6xmpvovccnozj7.jpg\" aid=\"61761\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">在水仙古庙，还有几块留下来的原石碑，上面有乾隆年间的碑文，当地人为其加朱色，可以很清晰地看到当时捐资建设水仙古庙的善男信女的名字。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"500\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61756\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626982675340.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/164048h6bbupsbyse5p6kx.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/164048h6bbupsbyse5p6kx.jpg\" aid=\"61756\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">在水仙古庙里面，供奉的也不止一尊神，当然，中间的是水仙爷，旁边还有护法、圣人爷；水仙爷的左边是两尊女神，分别是圣夫人和太圣夫人，还有保护孩子的花公、花嫲；水仙爷的下方还有五谷神，保护大家五谷丰登。这和潮汕地区诸多庙宇诸神共奉的做法是相似的。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\">永新水仙爷生，有几个很重要的议程：刣鹅、拜神、做桌、看戏和猜谜语。</span></strong>永新至今还沿用过去南宋时期传下来的灯谜仪轨。<strong><em>在没有现代娱乐方式的过去，我们完全可以想象得到那是多么热闹的场面，而这也代表着这里的人们对美好生活的憧憬和向往。</em></strong></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(244, 164, 96);\">讲述昔日的故事，更多潮文化节目，请关注汕头电视台《民生档案》相关报道</span> </span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_61764\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446626983434965.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/164052c7r9ri956utsiqp9.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/27/164052c7r9ri956utsiqp9.gif\" aid=\"61764\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">来源/汕头电视台《民生档案》 李君 义成</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">实习小编/博尔 </span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img id=\"aimg_179685\" aid=\"179685\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151208/1449578824136729.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p></ignore_js_op><br/><p></p>','2015-11-04 16:50:14',0,NULL,1,NULL,3172,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (306,'汕头合唱团 合唱出了友谊之花','201511041651439199.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62113\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627060523696.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105640ylcdlpphcgwdwjkd.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105640ylcdlpphcgwdwjkd.gif\" aid=\"62113\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>编者按：</em></strong></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>歌曲之妙，在于它是一种传承人类情感的艺术。一个声符，一丝情动，这一曲，关乎人与人、人与家之间情感的永恒谱写。</em></strong></span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62111\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627060287452.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105639t6aci6tuj6z1cetc.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105639t6aci6tuj6z1cetc.jpg\" aid=\"62111\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">今年是中、新两国建交25周年,也是新加坡建国50周年。<strong><span style=\"color:#ff8c00\">国庆期间，汕头市合唱团应新加坡音乐家协会、雅歌爱乐协会的邀请，赴新、马进行为期6天的文化交流演出。</span></strong>此次演出不仅提升了我市合唱艺术的表演水平，还让友谊之花越开越灿烂。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62108\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627060642636.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105638vclo8ccpepefjpcm.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105638vclo8ccpepefjpcm.jpg\" aid=\"62108\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">10月2日晚，汕头市合唱团一行80人与新加坡最有代表性的合唱团体“雅歌合唱团”,在维多利亚音乐厅联合举行庆祝音乐会。<strong><span style=\"color:#ff8c00\">市合唱团分别演唱了《茉莉花》、《蓝色多瑙河》等7首混声合唱歌曲，以及《芦花》等5首独唱、男声合唱、男声四重唱、女声三重唱中外歌曲。</span></strong>合唱团成员饱满的演唱，宽广的音域，均衡的声部，细腻的音色深深感染打动了所有观众，展示出团员们训练有素的功力，赢得观众们的满堂喝彩。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62109\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627060702450.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105638rdwvljggh9djjgbz.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105638rdwvljggh9djjgbz.jpg\" aid=\"62109\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">汕头市合唱团自2009年成立以来，曾屡获国内多项合唱大赛大奖。在本次展演中，合唱团挑选了一首高难度的歌曲《春天的芭蕾》，经过精心改编和排练后，以三重唱的形式作为送给新加坡友人的一份特别的贺礼。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62110\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627060417322.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105638i7yy0ieneee0qqxe.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105638i7yy0ieneee0qqxe.jpg\" aid=\"62110\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">这首歌原本是独唱的，最多也仅仅是两个声部的改编先例，所以这一次分成三个声部进行演唱，在音准、强弱、歌唱者配合度等方面的处理中，也是挺考验三位演唱者的功夫。因为三个人配合得当，对歌曲精确的把握，在歌曲和声部分的处理和音高达到一般人难以企及的高度，所以他们的这次演出在新加坡引起了轰动。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#ff8c00\">新加坡维多利亚音乐厅已有110年历史，良好的演唱环境使合唱团的歌艺得到充分展示，这也是合唱队多年来一次十分难得的经历。</span></strong>经此演出，许多团员非常感慨，都觉得自己能在这样一个艺术殿堂里献出自己的声音是人生最美妙的一个体验，不仅如此，与汕头合唱团进行交流的新加坡合唱团的水平也是非常之高，双方的互动，有了很多可以互相增进的东西，也是对自己的一个促进、进步。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"500\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62106\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627060222388.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105637m9w48awchiv88jkl.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105637m9w48awchiv88jkl.jpg\" aid=\"62106\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"500\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62104\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627060684979.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105635xzj60uk59uj96evu.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105635xzj60uk59uj96evu.jpg\" aid=\"62104\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#ff8c00\">10月4日晚，合唱团应邀赴马来西亚演出，与新山、天后宫等八大社区的合唱团体联合为纪念抗战胜利70周年同台演唱。</span></strong>在演唱中，场面热闹非凡，台上台下300多人放歌《黄河大合唱》，大合唱中年龄最大的有85岁老人。新山华人在马来西亚已历经数十代，他们至今仍源源不断传承中华传统文化和潮汕文化，其爱国、爱乡的情怀令团员们为之敬佩和感动。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"500\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62105\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627060742040.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105636or5rcwn4iyiy1116.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105636or5rcwn4iyiy1116.jpg\" aid=\"62105\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">汕头市合唱团指挥方萍就被他们这种传承中华文化的精神所感动，本来合唱团到马来西亚演出是为了展现传统文化艺术，殊不知在马来西亚的侨民世世代代坚守着中华文化，着实令人感动。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"500\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62107\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627061167737.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105638b6op3mjnpjppknkb.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105638b6op3mjnpjppknkb.jpg\" aid=\"62107\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>在采访中我们了解到，市合唱团自2009年建团以来，已经从70多人发展到140多人，他们都是来自各行各业的业余音乐爱好者，每周都坚持两场次的排练。近年来，演唱团不仅屡获佳绩，还先后千万台湾、泰国进行文艺交流，成为我市一道对外文化艺术交流的桥梁。</em></strong></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(244, 164, 96);\">讲述昔日的故事，更多潮文化节目，请关注汕头电视台《民生档案》相关报道 </span></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_62114\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627061631018.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105640t3g5uckfdr0ee5ef.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/28/105640t3g5uckfdr0ee5ef.gif\" aid=\"62114\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">来源/汕头电视台《民生档案》 欣莉 奕斯</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">实习小编/博尔 </span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img id=\"aimg_179685\" aid=\"179685\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151208/1449578814120897.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><br/><p><br/></p>','2015-11-04 16:51:43',0,NULL,1,NULL,2680,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (307,'猪脚烹制哪家强？百年风味出隆江','201511041652494169.png','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span></ignore_js_op></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60845\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627135277468.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103806q55m468c95mmc44r.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103806q55m468c95mmc44r.gif\" aid=\"60845\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>编者按：</em></strong></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>嚼一口香喷白饭，就一块隆江猪脚，对于追求饱腹的人来说，平常而美味的一餐就这样囫囵解决了。而对于负有盛名的隆江猪脚来说，制作过程可是大有讲究的。</em></strong></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"500\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60841\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627135828189.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103802gns5a5lfm22qygyq.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103802gns5a5lfm22qygyq.jpg\" aid=\"60841\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000\"><strong>揭阳市惠来县隆江镇有一种十分出名的特色食品——隆江猪脚。当地人以特别的方式处理和烹制猪脚，让这种本来普通的食材声名远扬。</strong></span></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">据当地人介绍，隆江人烹制猪脚至少已有上百年的历史。旧时的隆江镇有一个集市，来自附近乡村的众多小商贩在此谋生。生意人、挑夫、干杂活的人辛苦忙碌。为了支撑一整天的劳累，他们早上就会买一大碗白饭，配上香味浓郁的猪脚，淋上几勺卤汤，以此作为早餐。后来，这种习惯渐渐演变成隆江的一种商业文化。而这一习惯流传至今，仍有人坚持。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"500\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60842\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627135268346.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103803y2mnvex4tmqrx3qt.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103803y2mnvex4tmqrx3qt.jpg\" aid=\"60842\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">在物质贫乏的时代，吃猪脚饭并不像现在这样平常，一只猪脚能提供给多人佐餐，因此很多人也希望挑选最为美味和口感最好的猪脚入饭，隆江做猪脚的师傅也就根据不同特点将猪脚分段出售。<strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\">据了解，这种传统制法是将每一只精选的猪脚切成四块，第一段称为“头圈”，第二段称为“回轮”，第三段称“四点”，第四段称“蹄尾”。</span></strong>其中，“头圈”相对比较肥腻；“回轮”筋骨比较多，“四点”是骨头多，而且外面有猪皮，不会太肥腻；“蹄尾”的筋比较多。<strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\">这四段猪脚，最受欢迎的是“四点”和“蹄尾”。</span></strong></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"500\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60836\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627136119223.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103800zljj35jj9fx3xp3z.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103800zljj35jj9fx3xp3z.jpg\" aid=\"60836\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">今年60岁的唐瑶增在隆江镇一条繁华街道上开店卖猪脚饭，他们家从祖上开始经营猪脚饭。他传承了父辈的手艺，经他烹制的猪脚经常供不应求。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"500\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60838\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627136103861.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103801pa4kkbgww01apkzw.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103801pa4kkbgww01apkzw.jpg\" aid=\"60838\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">唐瑶增说，<strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\">猪脚的烹制，首先是去毛。</span></strong>猪脚用火烧一下，烧过的猪脚皮煮起来会更容易松软、入味，会使口感变得不一般。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"500\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60843\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627137198548.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103803lbfv8abkbkyyh8ai.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103803lbfv8abkbkyyh8ai.jpg\" aid=\"60843\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">除去猪毛的同时，与明火的接触也让猪脚的外部皮肉在入锅之前先经受了一次烤制，较好地锁住肉汁。洗净去完毛的猪脚就可以入锅烹制了。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">唐瑶增介绍，一般煮猪脚刚开始要用大火，煮开了之后再调中火。用中火熬煮一个多钟头就要将猪脚翻个，再煮上一个钟头就完成了。<strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\">在熬煮的过程中，特别需要注意的就是要多用筷子搅动，使得这一锅猪脚汤呈粘稠状，像熬糖浆一样，才会使猪脚有胶质感，口感更佳。</span></strong></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"500\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60839\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627137252854.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103801a51lfl7bpydzs88c.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103801a51lfl7bpydzs88c.jpg\" aid=\"60839\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">猪脚含丰富的胶原蛋白，古人认为猪脚具有和气血、润肌肤的美容功效。隆江猪脚皮滑而且具有光泽，骨肉松散，品尝时口感滑嫩胶黏，让人回味无穷。<strong><span style=\"color:#8b0000\">而让隆江猪脚展现独特口味的还是靠那锅不停熬煮的卤汤。</span></strong></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">隆江猪脚在烹制过程中采用中药材，将香叶、桂皮、陈皮、八角等原材料装在小布袋里，放入装有清水的砂锅中，熬制成卤汤。烹制的过程中讲究火候的控制，使得隆江猪脚肥而不腻，非常有特色。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"500\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60837\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627137799444.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103800xlwazm22xc7ctmuz.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103800xlwazm22xc7ctmuz.jpg\" aid=\"60837\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000\"><strong>据当地人说，不同的商贩的卤汤也略有不同，世代相传的卤汤成了制作隆江猪脚的“秘笈”，甚至还有家庭因此而闹起了矛盾。</strong></span></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">据说，有一家猪脚店的商号叫做“牡丹”，家中有兄弟好几个，是饮食世家。后来，兄弟要分家的时候，家中其它财产分配得十分清楚，唯独为了争砂锅而引起了争论。旧时隆江猪脚是用砂锅烹制，其中的卤水是日日翻滚，以此卤制猪脚。所以，这个宝贵的砂锅让几个兄弟很为难，最后还是由兄弟们的舅舅主持分配。可见，这个砂锅对于这家店来说就是“镇店之宝”。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"500\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60840\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627138510873.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103802qx3in0n4oosvfo0j.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103802qx3in0n4oosvfo0j.jpg\" aid=\"60840\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>潮汕人素有精耕细作的传统，在烹制食材上也多有展现。如今，经烹调技师多年的不断研制传承，隆江猪脚已经走出了隆江，也走出了潮汕，这一美味食品不再是当年只求温饱的早餐，而是成为弘扬潮汕美食文化的一块招牌。</em></strong></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(244, 164, 96);\">讲述昔日的故事，更多潮文化节目，请关注汕头电视台《民生档案》相关报道 </span></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_60846\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151104/1446627138101202.gif\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103806nu2223j2zi2alriv.gif\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201510/26/103806nu2223j2zi2alriv.gif\" aid=\"60846\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">来源/汕头电视台《民生档案》业军 义成</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">实习小编/博尔 </span></span><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img id=\"aimg_179685\" aid=\"179685\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151208/1449578800933875.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p></ignore_js_op><br/><p></p>','2015-11-04 16:52:49',0,NULL,1,NULL,4997,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (308,'【柬埔寨潮商】这里有一个“小潮州”','201511051658344343.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><img src=\"/uploads/20151105/1446710014124873.png\" title=\"1446710014124873.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></p><p><strong><em><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">编者按：</span></em></strong></p><p><strong><em><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">柬埔寨对于许多潮汕人而言，就像一首走调的歌，陌生又熟悉。迷人神秘的古文化，东南亚特有的风土人情，让许多人慕名前往。当明朝那个著名的海盗林道乾踏上这片土地，潮人落地生根的超强能力再次得到印证，尽管他最后留在了泰国，随他而来的手下却成了潮人在柬埔寨的最早移民，数百年下来，一个“小潮州”在柬埔寨崛起。</span></em></strong></p><p><video class=\"edui-upload-video  vjs-default-skin    video-js\" controls=\"\" preload=\"auto\" width=\"420\" height=\"280\" src=\"/uploads/20151105/1446710822758865.mp4\" data-setup=\"{}\"><source src=\"/uploads/20151105/1446710822758865.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/></video></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(195, 214, 155);\">神秘国度：柬埔寨</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">每天，吴哥的太阳最先照亮巴肯山，来自世界各国的游客陆续登上这里，沐浴着神圣绮丽的吴哥之光，大家尽情地领略着这片古老大地的悠然神韵。孩子们在河里戏耍,妇女们在河边洗着衣服。遭受了无数磨难的柬埔寨到处都呈现出一片安定祥和的气氛。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><img src=\"/uploads/20151105/1446713072250918.jpg\" title=\"1446713072250918.jpg\" alt=\"暴风截图2015115633675062.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">柬埔寨位于</span><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/88420.htm\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">中南半岛</span></a><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">南部。东部和东南部同</span><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/4205.htm\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">越南</span></a><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">接壤，北部与</span><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/7471.htm\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">老挝</span></a><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">交界，西部和西北部与</span><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/7026.htm\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">泰国</span></a><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">毗邻，西南濒临</span><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/561915.htm\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">暹罗湾</span></a><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">。9至14世纪吴哥王朝为鼎盛时期，国力强盛、文化发达，创造了举世闻名的吴哥文明。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1863年起，柬埔寨先后被法国和日本占领，1953年11月9日独立。20世纪70年代开始，柬埔寨经历了长期的战乱。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20151105/1446713437663980.jpg\" title=\"1446713437663980.jpg\" alt=\"暴风截图2015115633582578.jpg\"/><br/>1993年恢复了君主立宪制。此后，随着柬埔寨国家权力机构相继成立和民族和解的实现，柬埔寨进入和平与发展的新时期。</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><img src=\"/uploads/20151105/1446713447764115.jpg\" title=\"1446713447764115.jpg\" alt=\"暴风截图2015115633661609.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">柬埔寨因为神秘的吴哥文化而闻名于世。吴哥古迹位于暹粒市北6公里处，分布在45平方公里的莽莽丛林中。吴哥是高棉人的精神中心和宗教中心。<br/><img src=\"/uploads/20151105/1446713678119761.jpg\" title=\"1446713678119761.jpg\" alt=\"暴风截图2015115633704031.jpg\"/><br/>吴哥王朝曾统治着中南半岛南端及越南和孟加拉湾之间的大片土地，其势力范围远远超出了今天柬埔寨的领土。历代国王在此大兴土木，留下了古今奇迹吴哥城、吴哥窟和女王宫等印度教与佛教建筑风格的寺塔。<br/><img src=\"/uploads/20151105/1446713695744148.jpg\" title=\"1446713695744148.jpg\" alt=\"暴风截图2015115633721046.jpg\"/><br/>直到公元1431年泰族军队攻占并洗劫了吴哥，从此这座闻名于世的城市遭到废弃。19世纪60年代，法国科学家亨利•莫阿寻访吴哥。在这里，他做了大量详细的调查记录，并公布于世，吴哥文化受到世界的关注。近年来，在世界古迹基金会的资助下，吴哥的恢复工作有所进展。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(195, 214, 155);\">潮人与柬埔寨的化学效应</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">“小时候乡愁是一枚小小的邮票，我在这头，母亲在那头，长大后，乡愁是一张窄窄的船票，我在这头，新娘在那头......”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">在距离吴哥窟240多公里的金边端华学校，孩子们大声地朗诵着余光中的《乡愁》，开始了一天的学习生活。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><img src=\"/uploads/20151105/1446713719840754.jpg\" title=\"1446713719840754.jpg\" alt=\"暴风截图2015115633787156.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">对于这群风华正茂的少年人来说，乡愁更多的是一种意境，他们可能并不知道，对于那些跋山涉水，从遥远的中国来到柬埔寨的祖辈来说，乡愁是一种真真切切的感受，它不仅让人望眼欲穿，也让人在几经劫难之后，还能奋斗不息，拼搏不止。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><img src=\"/uploads/20151105/1446713740397828.jpg\" title=\"1446713740397828.jpg\" alt=\"暴风截图2015115633811640.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">柬埔寨古称扶南、真腊或吴哥，土地肥沃，物产丰饶。元朝时期，一个名叫周达观的温州人曾经在这里居住过一年，并写下了8500字的《真腊风土记》。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">书中记载：“<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(149, 55, 52);\"><strong>国中不著衣裳，且米粮易求，妇女易得，居室易办，器用易足，买卖易为，往往逃逸于彼。</strong></span>”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><img src=\"/uploads/20151105/1446713773297564.jpg\" title=\"1446713773297564.jpg\" alt=\"暴风截图2015115633876500.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">如此一个适合居住的地方，当然不会少了潮人的足迹，见于记载的最早到达柬埔寨的有名有姓的潮人是林道乾。<br/></span></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/20151105/1446713799323039.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1446713799323039.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/20151105/1446713799663033.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1446713799663033.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\"><br/>林道乾是澄海人，曾为潮州小吏，后来聚众走私，成为武装商旅集团的领袖人物，在明嘉靖、万历年间，他纵横海上30余年，足迹遍及台湾、安南、吕宋、暹罗、柬埔寨等地。尽管林道乾后来定居泰国，但当时跟随他到柬埔寨的潮人，却成了潮人在柬埔寨的最早移民。据记载，到1946年，柬埔寨的潮人有20万，而到了上世纪五六十年代，这里的潮人已有30多万。</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><img src=\"/uploads/20151105/1446713814420592.jpg\" title=\"1446713814420592.jpg\" alt=\"暴风截图2015115633958125.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">潮人经商务农，有“舍华人无生意”的评价。虽然人数不多，但这个独特的族群在柬埔寨当时的经济社会上已备受瞩目。1956年，首都金边有工商行号约3000家，其中属于潮人的商号就占了三分之一。时任柬埔寨潮州会馆秘书长的李捷贵说，在金边一出门就讲潮州话，就听潮州曲，家家户户都在放潮曲，所以才叫“小潮州”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><img src=\"/uploads/20151105/1446713829118268.jpg\" title=\"1446713829118268.jpg\" alt=\"暴风截图2015115634008375.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">64岁的黄平是柬埔寨首位女记者，她现在仍就职于柬埔寨《华商日报》，热心的大姐带我们来到一条叫“大街”的地方。在上个世纪中期，大街是金边最繁荣的中心区，也是潮人集聚的地方，在这里，至今仍然留存着大姐难以抹去的童年记忆。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><img src=\"/uploads/20151105/1446713845131341.jpg\" title=\"1446713845131341.jpg\" alt=\"暴风截图2015115634037531.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">黄平出生在乡下，母亲每隔一段时间就会带她到金边玩一次。每次来到，她总是很惊奇。一条街上居然会有那么多人买东西，几乎都是唐人。在幼时的记忆中，这条街非常繁荣，来往之人也非常有素质，整洁卫生。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><img src=\"/uploads/20151105/1446713857107166.jpg\" title=\"1446713857107166.jpg\" alt=\"暴风截图2015115633836984.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">潮人所到之处，凭着族群的坚毅性格和开放心态，都能随时融入他乡之境。在柬埔寨，“小潮州”隐藏的是潮人在他方也能站足一片土地的非凡能力，把他乡变成故乡，潮汕人时时记住的是潮汕人的文化身份。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(250, 192, 143);\">讲述昔日的故事，更多潮文化节目，请关注汕头电视台《民生档案》相关报道&nbsp;</span></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/20151105/1446710027912316.png\" title=\"1446710027912316.png\" alt=\"图片2.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 7px;margin-bottom: 7px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">来源/汕头电视台《天下潮商》</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">实习小编/博尔</span></p><p><img id=\"aimg_179685\" aid=\"179685\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151208/1449578786421840.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p>','2015-11-05 16:58:34',0,NULL,1,NULL,3464,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (310,'【柬埔寨潮商】在战火纷飞的岁月中书写传奇','201511091007406349.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px;\"></span></ignore_js_op></span></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66457\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034755597065.png\" initialized=\"true\" aid=\"66457\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/094326ubijp2jk26kkt6ts.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/094326ubijp2jk26kkt6ts.png\"/><br/><strong><em>编者按：</em></strong></p><strong><em> 欣赏文中这句话——只有历经劫难的人，才知道国家和平和发展来得如此的不易。而对于生活在这片土地上的潮人来说，那曾经的劫难更是令人刻骨铭心。<br/> 在动乱的日子里，柬埔寨潮商们并没有全部选择转身离开，留下来的人们，以天生的坚韧演绎了一段段“火中取栗”的传奇。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66459\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034755140356.jpg\" initialized=\"true\" aid=\"66459\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/094433nuuubul4v1g761vi.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/094433nuuubul4v1g761vi.jpg\"/></p></ignore_js_op></em></strong>当年的柬埔寨，有“小潮州”之称的金边市的一条大街上聚集生活着众多的潮人潮商，这条大街，也是当时金边最繁华的区域之一。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66460\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034755281858.jpg\" initialized=\"true\" aid=\"66460\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/094632xhe123t8tbcf0fqs.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/094632xhe123t8tbcf0fqs.jpg\"/> </p><p><br/></p></ignore_js_op><strong><span style=\"background-color: yellowgreen;\">柬埔寨的潮商们</span></strong><br/> 这个时期，潮商已经是柬埔寨众多行业的翘楚。83岁的许书利勋爵是第二代潮人，上个世纪五十年代，只有二十多岁的许书利在柬埔寨建筑业已经是知名人物。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66461\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034756453253.jpg\" aid=\"66461\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/094725eun6nn7nnyh6uh2z.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/094725eun6nn7nnyh6uh2z.jpg\"/></p></ignore_js_op>在此后十多年时间里，年轻的许书利承建了柬埔寨的大学、国家运动场、金宝殿宾馆以及水利、公路等基础设施，直至今天，其中的一些建筑物在柬埔寨依然很有名气。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66462\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034756624262.jpg\" aid=\"66462\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/094811ma7pazpm1rrrb1x3.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/094811ma7pazpm1rrrb1x3.jpg\"/></p></ignore_js_op>在上个世纪六十年代，比许书利小八岁的杨国璋同样是金边卓有成就的人物。当时，这个年仅21岁的小伙子一接管家族的酒业生意，就以独特的方式将企业推向无人可及的高度。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66485\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034756557734.jpg\" aid=\"66485\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095105u4i334lh1moliqv4.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095105u4i334lh1moliqv4.jpg\"/></p></ignore_js_op>原来，他做广告的宣传手法独具一格。据杨国璋介绍，那时候他所用的广告手法在柬埔寨算是首创，因为当时的人们还不太懂得广告是怎么一回事，而自己看过不少这方面的书，深谙广告对于产品宣传作用之大。正因为掌握了广告这把利剑，杨国璋在那时的柬埔寨酒业里可以说是最大的一家。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66463\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034756578648.jpg\" aid=\"66463\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/094859f0p0qzpzcaxtrwqa.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/094859f0p0qzpzcaxtrwqa.jpg\"/></p></ignore_js_op>1972年，风华正茂的杨国璋被全柬华人公推为金边中华医院的董事长，这是一家汇集全柬华人力量创办的福利医院，也代表全柬华人社会公益的最高领导机构。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66486\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034756967913.jpg\" aid=\"66486\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095116ssumsf0s4ybp4gbj.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095116ssumsf0s4ybp4gbj.jpg\"/></p></ignore_js_op>除了全柬最大的酒业，杨国璋还经营进出口贸易、戏院等，甚至，他自己还有一架当时全国最好的客机D47，还租给柬航，而正是这架客机，在最关键的时刻，救了杨国璋和许书利两个家庭。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66487\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034757199796.jpg\" aid=\"66487\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095150sd9dts72gigqfkkk.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095150sd9dts72gigqfkkk.jpg\"/> </p><p><br/></p></ignore_js_op><strong><span style=\"background-color: yellowgreen;\">当年的动乱 是否给潮商带来致命打击？</span></strong><br/> 这是一个晴朗的日子，蓝天、白云和金碧辉煌的柬埔寨皇宫构成了一幅极富东南亚风情的唯美图案，站在皇宫广场远眺，上湄公河、洞里萨河、下湄公河与巴萨河在此交汇，奔流而去。<br/><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66488\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034757229660.jpg\" aid=\"66488\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095306u90d0zg1veuyd1p0.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095306u90d0zg1veuyd1p0.jpg\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">每年雨季末期，湄公河和洞里萨湖的水位下退，柬埔寨人就迎来最重要的节日------“送水节”，他们以热烈多彩的活动，祈求灾难病魔随湄公河水一起流走。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66490\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034757501191.jpg\" aid=\"66490\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095420gig4efry4mzewrmv.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095420gig4efry4mzewrmv.jpg\"/></p></ignore_js_op><strong><span style=\"color:darkred\">人们在为自己祈福的同时，也不会忘记为自己的国家祈福，因为，只有历经劫难的人，才知道国家和平和发展来得如此的不易。而对于生活在这片土地上的潮人来说，那曾经的劫难更是令人刻骨铭心。</span></strong><br/> 从20世纪70年代开始，柬埔寨经历了长期的战乱。</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66491\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034757414008.jpg\" aid=\"66491\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095639ghh54eq9wfdrqocs.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095639ghh54eq9wfdrqocs.jpg\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1970年到1975年，朗诺将军成立的民族主义政府执政，华文学校被禁，华文报纸被迫关闭，中文成了受孤立和敌视的语言。1975年，波尔布特执政，直到1979年1月退出金边，在其执政的三年零八个月中，柬埔寨人民经历了一场惨绝人寰的空前劫难，而华人社会更是首当其冲。当时，柬埔寨全国170多万人，包括20多万华人，死于饥饿、疾病、酷刑与屠杀。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66492\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034757381218.jpg\" aid=\"66492\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095702eus19nphu62hsc9s.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095702eus19nphu62hsc9s.jpg\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66493\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034757668283.jpg\" initialized=\"true\" aid=\"66493\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095703rltlt88l1tj8ytz5.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095703rltlt88l1tj8ytz5.jpg\"/></p></ignore_js_op>战乱初始，一些信息灵通的潮商得以逃离，从而最大限度地避开了这场灾难。在波尔布特进入金边前夕，许书利与杨国璋就前后一天分别乘坐杨国璋租借给柬航的飞机离开了柬埔寨，前往泰国逃难。说起当时出逃金边的情形，杨国璋至今心有余悸。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66494\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034758853363.jpg\" aid=\"66494\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095756koqa5airwkfiotqi.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095756koqa5airwkfiotqi.jpg\"/></p></ignore_js_op>杨国璋回忆，当时飞机四个引擎坏掉一个、关掉一个，只剩下两个了，原则上只能坐60人。但柬航居然在这辆飞机上载满127人，由于飞机只剩两个引擎，起飞困难，但是迫于形势，最终只能硬着头皮起飞，当时飞机上的杨国璋在搭乘的过程中一直坐立不安。<br/><strong><em>战乱给柬埔寨的经济带来了毁灭性的打击，而首当其冲的潮人经济也被彻底摧毁。</em></strong><br/> 可是，不管时局如何，却总有一些人，他们不甘放弃，即使面对战火纷飞，也依然无畏无惧，勇敢向前。潮商们，还在续写他们的传奇。<br/><br/><strong><span style=\"background-color: yellowgreen;\">传奇 从动乱开始</span></strong><br/>1979年1月，波尔布特退出金边，原来被挟持、迁徙到山区的人们纷纷踏上重回家园的漫漫道路，其中，就有那些家破人亡的潮人家庭，只不过，回到城市，已回不了原来的家，也没有了一切。于是，这群生性坚韧的潮人，有人决定留在当地，从头开始；而动乱中，也有不少潮人选择永远离开柬埔寨。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66501\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034758125915.jpg\" initialized=\"true\" aid=\"66501\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095928duumrz9ujuj8llu9.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/095928duumrz9ujuj8llu9.jpg\"/></p></ignore_js_op>在高楼大厦稀少的金边市，高高矗立的加华大厦显得如此与众不同，这栋金边最高的大厦，它的主人是今年64岁的柬埔寨潮商方侨生。在动乱时期，方侨生的家庭包括他表兄在内总共18人，由于饥饿和病痛，死剩下9人。而方侨生坚强地存活下来，出逃到泰国，并于1980年辗转去了加拿大。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66502\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034758816011.jpg\" aid=\"66502\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/100011bc6fuqiqw0ycmtln.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/100011bc6fuqiqw0ycmtln.jpg\"/></p></ignore_js_op>当时，方侨生才32岁，但他的传奇故事却从这里正式拉开序幕。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66506\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034758112678.jpg\" aid=\"66506\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/100051ujq62rr9jc3qgg9k.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/100051ujq62rr9jc3qgg9k.jpg\"/></p></ignore_js_op>从打金起步的方侨生很快在加拿大华人圈中建立了良好的信用。随着金铺生意逐渐壮大，他又开办了东方金行及东方财务公司。上个世纪90年代，柬埔寨百废待兴，这个时候，方侨生的叔父，也是当时柬埔寨政府顾问方炳祯力邀方侨生回来柬埔寨投资。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66512\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034758128264.jpg\" aid=\"66512\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/100141teoljve28vvsz58s.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/100141teoljve28vvsz58s.jpg\"/></p></ignore_js_op>在亲戚的支持下，方侨生集资35万美金，创办了柬埔寨黄金与信托有限公司。很快，这家公司发展为银行，命名加华。然而，创业道路并非都是坦途，1997年柬埔寨国内又发生动乱，很多人逃走，许多行业停摆，大批银行关门，金融业危机四伏。加华银行却顶住压力，在战争第二天开门营业。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66513\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034758330699.jpg\" aid=\"66513\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/100217nvav3ilvse6ujqin.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/100217nvav3ilvse6ujqin.jpg\"/></p></ignore_js_op>当时的方侨生认为，顶着风头也要开门，这是银行的责任所在，一旦银行关门，许多人就无处取钱，特别是工厂，如果发不出工资，工人就会砸抢工厂，对于工厂损失很是严重。正是这样的决心，使得加华银行的信用建立得非常快，许多华侨很是相信加华银行。也正因如此，在银行最困难的时候，加拿大的华侨成了加华银行最坚强的后盾。许多华侨了解战时的银行会有许多人兑钱，银行容易被掏空，资金可能会运转不周，所以都约定好不去取钱，甚至还把钱拿进加华银行储存投资。 <br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66514\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034759115165.jpg\" aid=\"66514\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/100317snnj29fiozsznntn.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/100317snnj29fiozsznntn.jpg\"/></p></ignore_js_op>由于当时的混乱是两大政治派系之间出现的一场小规模的武装冲突，两天时间，事态平息，危机过去，但很多商业却迟迟未能恢复，就是这段时间加华银行凭借他们在危机中表现出来的义气建立了良好的信用，后来银行的业务因此不断攀升。现在，加华银行已拥有24家分行，存贷款量占柬埔寨全国银行业务量的30%以上，成为柬埔寨最大的商业银行。而在发展银行业之外，方侨生还投资建立了工业园区，经营购物中心、房地产开发、酒店、民俗村文化村旅游项目等产业，成功实现了国际化的多元发展。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66515\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034759236889.jpg\" aid=\"66515\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/100317xr11eruj5g5gremg.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/100317xr11eruj5g5gremg.jpg\"/></p></ignore_js_op>从难民到柬埔寨最大商业银行的总裁，方侨生以他的坚韧、敏锐、果敢以及良好的信用赢来了无限的商机，神奇地实现了人生的飞跃，也成为柬埔寨潮商发展史上的一个传奇。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66458\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151109/1447034759264645.png\" aid=\"66458\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/094326zslzdxwnkxdds2ml.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/09/094326zslzdxwnkxdds2ml.png\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">汕头橄榄台综合报道 转载请标注下方图片<br/> 来源/汕头电视台《天下潮商》<br/> 实习小编/博尔</span></span></span></span><br/><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><ignore_js_op><p><img id=\"aimg_179685\" aid=\"179685\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151208/1449578635118617.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><br/><p></p>','2015-11-09 10:07:40',0,NULL,1,NULL,2945,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (311,'【柬埔寨潮商】在劫灰中浴火重生','201511101021328343.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><ignore_js_op></ignore_js_op></span></span></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66917\" src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201511/10/095432h118kzicrg668g88.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/095432h118kzicrg668g88.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/095432h118kzicrg668g88.png\" aid=\"66917\" initialized=\"true\"/></p><strong><em>编者按：<br/> 人的命运总是与国家的命运联系在一起，尽管那只是侨居国。当战火停息，生活重新回到平稳的轨道上，曾经的苦难与坎坷让潮商们迸发出更大的力量，他们浴火重生，把事业之树深深扎进这片土地，花果繁茂，摇曳生姿。</em></strong><br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66919\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151110/1447122060310732.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/100820fjfp8zbu88fy8ngh.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/100820fjfp8zbu88fy8ngh.jpg\" aid=\"66919\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op>驱车经过柬埔寨的各大公路，经常会碰到一座座“贝雷”钢桥，在柬埔寨，这样的钢桥就有一百座，全长近万米，它一举改变了战后柬埔寨因路桥损毁导致车辆无法通行的局面。而它的投资者就是今年68岁的柬埔寨潮商刘明勤。当三年多的红色高棉统治期结束之后，刘明勤没有远走他乡，而是选择在柬埔寨创业。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66920\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151110/1447122060112700.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/100820n0zqqogddoiosqrn.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/100820n0zqqogddoiosqrn.jpg\" aid=\"66920\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op>战乱之后的柬埔寨有着很多机会 ，虽然很多东西都要从头做起，还是有很多人在这里面都赚到钱。1996年，刘明勤创办了柬埔寨国际投资开发集团有限公司，他的事业也开始进入一个快速发展的辉煌时期。他经营很多生意，包括船务、冷冻厂、木材等，足迹远及泰国印度。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66921\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151110/1447122060778746.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/100859zq3guujd0qdddjqz.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/100859zq3guujd0qdddjqz.jpg\" aid=\"66921\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op>敏锐的眼光让刘明勤时刻都能抓住市场商机，很快，这个祖籍汕头潮阳的第三代柬埔寨潮人开创的事业填补了柬埔寨多个行业的空白。他开展的活动集装箱业务填补了中国货物抵柬的空白；他的木业公司曾经是柬埔寨最大木业公司之一；他的食盐厂几乎垄断了柬埔寨食盐市场；与此同时，刘明勤还投资水电站、工业区、房地产以及正在悄然兴起的矿产资源和农林业项目。<br/><br/><br/><strong><span style=\"background-color: yellowgreen;\">不仅是商人 更是回馈社会的积极分子</span></strong><br/> 三十年，刘明勤的企业王国就这样一步步地垒了起来，采访中，爽朗的刘明勤并没有过多地言及其中曲折艰辛，而是跟我们谈起了他对慈善事业的理念。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66933\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151110/1447122061166231.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/101024ijowwd4fdxczw6x6.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/101024ijowwd4fdxczw6x6.jpg\" aid=\"66933\"/></p></ignore_js_op>刘明勤说，商人所赚的钱是从群众中来，所以商人也要回报给群众。因为跟社会很多方面接触比较多，心态也会豁达不少，会把身外之物看得更淡一些。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66935\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151110/1447122061318650.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/101126ikkdwp8i8ikuvspn.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/101126ikkdwp8i8ikuvspn.jpg\" aid=\"66935\"/></p></ignore_js_op>近年来，刘明勤多次捐资，用于建学校、医院、修公路、建桥等公益事业。在柬埔寨的华人圈里，他是华人奋发图强的创业典范，更是柬埔寨华人的光荣。这份光荣来自于2006年柬埔寨王国参议员选举。当年4月，刘明勤获选柬埔寨王国第二届参议员，从而开创了华人在柬埔寨参政的历史。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66934\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151110/1447122061627833.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/101024hp2b5prpp1mmcrp6.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/101024hp2b5prpp1mmcrp6.jpg\" aid=\"66934\"/></p></ignore_js_op>在历经劫难之后，柬埔寨潮人筚路蓝缕，重新创业，很快在柬埔寨商界开辟了一片新天地，在柬埔寨经济领域中成为一方群雄。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66936\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151110/1447122061296445.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/101201s939ozg9zml5lmeg.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/101201s939ozg9zml5lmeg.jpg\" aid=\"66936\"/></p></ignore_js_op><br/><strong><span style=\"background-color: yellowgreen;\">回首往事 血泪终成一感慨</span></strong><br/> 当留守在柬埔寨的潮商致力垒建自己企业王国的时候，在1975年远走法国、香港的许书利和杨国璋也分别于1991年和2000年回到柬埔寨，当年意气风发的两个壮年男人如今已是沧桑老人，然而，这片熟悉的土地，再次激发他们重操旧业的热情，凭着潮人那特有的坚韧、敏锐的基因，在短短几年间，再次抢占了行业的高地。现在，当这两位古稀老人回首往事，总免不了一番感慨唏嘘。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66945\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151110/1447122062815839.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/101416peujj20uffm2mf2k.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/101416peujj20uffm2mf2k.jpg\" aid=\"66945\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op>杨国璋说，历尽沧桑，觉得自己必须自信。很多事情都是在困难中崛起的，并不是偶然的事情，正所谓是一分耕耘一分收获。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66937\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151110/1447122062137310.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/101241hoccgtpoo033b1vc.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/101241hoccgtpoo033b1vc.jpg\" aid=\"66937\" initialized=\"true\"/></p></ignore_js_op>早上六点多，金边，这座有着一百多万人口的城市已经完全苏醒。在这座曾经被称为“小潮州”的城市里，当我们去探寻柬埔寨潮商奋斗足迹的时候，才发现，正是那段苦难、曲折和坎坷，磨砺出柬埔寨潮商这个群体不同一般的坚韧。他们的不屈意志以及浴火重生后的骄人成就足以让人敬仰。<br/><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66941\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151110/1447122062132378.jpg\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/101315q1wrun3zerr1exi9.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/101315q1wrun3zerr1exi9.jpg\" aid=\"66941\"/></p></ignore_js_op><ignore_js_op><p><img width=\"600\" class=\"zoom\" id=\"aimg_66918\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20151110/1447122062684420.png\" inpost=\"1\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/095432pihqa08cfhd1mvzl.png\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201511/10/095432pihqa08cfhd1mvzl.png\" aid=\"66918\"/></p></ignore_js_op><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">汕头橄榄台综合报道 转载请标注下方图片<br/> 来源/汕头电视台《天下潮商》<br/> 实习小编/博尔</span></span><br/><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><ignore_js_op><p><img id=\"aimg_179685\" aid=\"179685\" src=\"http://yao.cutv.com/data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" zoomfile=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" file=\"data/attachment/forum/201512/08/191246nyran8rxyq0iaynv.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></p></ignore_js_op></span></span><br/><p></p>','2015-11-10 10:21:33',0,NULL,1,NULL,2634,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (312,'【柬埔寨潮商】在异乡的土地上，端起一杯工夫茶','201512181114463266.png','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><img src=\"/uploads/20151218/1450408470109128.png\" title=\"1450408470109128.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">编者按：</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在异乡的土地上，端起一杯工夫茶，静看日出日落，目光深邃——这或许是外出潮商的经典姿势。他们血液中澎湃的潮音，驱动着双脚，让他们异域中栉风沐雨，砥砺前行。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=82094&size=300x300&key=77b651bdcd4ff272&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_82094\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">当早上六点多的朝阳撒满街道，金边最大的综合市场——新市，已经是一片热闹景象。这座建于1937年的法式建筑，在经过了七十多年的风霜之后，依然风姿犹存，市场里既卖肉菜、也卖服装和手工艺品，这里，也是做小生意的柬埔寨潮人集中的地方。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">靠近路边的这家小食摊档，人来人往，生意相当不错，正在忙碌的大姐用潮汕话告诉我们，她卖的是地道的潮汕小吃，在这里已经经营了三十年了。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=82096&size=300x300&key=ca15967e2fe16470&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_82096\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=82095&size=300x300&key=ecf52622516e2c4a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_82095\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(154, 205, 50);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(154, 205, 50);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">勇气＋创新＋刻苦＋耐劳＝潮商</strong></span></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">距离新市不远的西哈努克大道，有一个叫幸运超级市场的商场很受金边人青睐，他们喜欢幸运超级市场的原因，不仅是这里琳琅满目的各式商品，还在于这个建于1993年的商场是<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">柬埔寨首家超市</strong>。幸运市场集团有限公司的老板是一个叫王汉明的潮商，他是柬埔寨的第二代潮人。1993年，超级市场在柬埔寨还是一种全新的东西，当时王汉明在新加坡看到了日常用品食品的前景，决意投资建超市。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=82097&size=300x300&key=b5876cec17325c30&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_82097\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">创业不仅需要勇气，更需要吃苦的精神。从1993年到1998年五年时间，王汉明每天都是16个钟头的工作时长，因为超市刚开始的时候，从买货、清洁工作、摆货、卖货等等各方面都是自己亲手干的。没想到，柬埔寨人很快就接受并喜欢上这种购物方式，王汉明的超市火了起来。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">创新和勇气让王汉明尝到了甜头，1996年，他又开创了柬埔寨第一家西式快餐店。随后，他的投资又涉及服装、咖啡店、面包店等多个商业领域。2008年，国际金融危机大暴发，王汉明不退反进，又加大投资的步伐。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=82103&size=300x300&key=c96542b9ef59b313&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_82103\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">王汉明说，之所以敢于逆流而上，是因为当时柬埔寨还没进入世界经济的轨道，所以金融危机对柬埔寨的影响很小，加之他自己对国内形势信心十足，所以毅然加大投资。后来的事实也证明王汉明的做法是对的，他的生意非但没有受到经济危机的影响，反而扩大。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">勇气，创新，刻苦，耐劳，这些典型的潮商特色在王汉明身上展现无遗，也正是这样的秉性，让王汉明的幸运市场集团在柬埔寨王国超级市场、服装销售和快餐领域中一直保持领先优势。</strong></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">现在，王汉明三个女儿都在家族企业任职，她们的出色表现让他感到自豪，而让他更为满意的是她们身上保留的潮汕文化传统。现在王汉明的家庭全部成员都用潮州话，虽然他的每个孩子都到美国接受教育，都在美国住了十年时间，但他们的潮州话依然流利。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=82098&size=300x300&key=5ff9e562841822ca&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_82098\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">事实上，由于柬埔寨的潮人家庭对子女教育的重视，这里的新一代潮人已展露出出色的才能，而同时，他们身上保持着的潮人特性和文化传统又是如此的鲜明，对于已是三代甚至四代的柬埔寨潮人来说，这一点是多么难能可贵。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">王汉明说，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮人家庭子女在柬埔寨这个国家这个社会生长，但他们父母的心还是老想着咱们是从中国来的，所以就保留了中国的传统。</strong></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(154, 205, 50);\">潮商后代的崛起</strong></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在棉美新进出口贸易有限公司办公室里，柬埔寨潮州会馆会长杨启秋和他的大儿子杨宗德融洽地交谈着。在红色高棉的时候，杨宗德一家破碎凋零，妹妹弟弟还有祖父、外公、舅舅，共一百多人几乎全部死光，只剩下三几人。等到解放的时候，从1979到1982年，杨宗德一家开始卖粿条，父亲卖粿条，杨宗德就读书。困难时期一家人相依为命的日子，让这对父子之间有着更多的默契。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">从卖粿条、卖布、卖牛奶到经营进出口，杨家的生意越做越大，1999年，杨宗德开始接手父亲的棉美新公司，此时，他还不到35岁，但却已开始展现出他的能力。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=82099&size=300x300&key=cf6855aaeed72500&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_82099\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">杨宗德说，老公司如何发展，他有自己的新思路。改变公司的经营模式，从原来只做农业设备进出口发展到跨行做酒业、风油精等行业。一个社会的市场相当复杂，如果不多种经营的话， 难以有大的发展。在公司的慢慢改进中，2006年，公司还把盈利投入到柬泰边境兴建工业区。2006年，杨宗德投入巨资，在柬埔寨柬越边境购买数百公顷土地，兴建了柬埔寨第一座国际贸易及产业投资发展特别保税区，吸引世界各国企业前来投资。现在，冠霖国际集团的投资已涉及房地产、酒店、旅游、农业开发、农产品加工、印刷、电力和供水等行业，成为柬埔寨名列前茅的现代化、国际化的新型产业经营体系。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=82102&size=300x300&key=d2e51874b779d728&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_82102\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在金边市钻石岛，一场豪华的庆祝宴会徐徐拉开帷幕，承办宴会酒席的是一个名叫陈金生的柬埔寨二代潮商。在柬埔寨华人圈中，承办酒席还沿袭着潮汕地区的老叫法，叫“做桌”。在金边，今年四十多岁的陈金生在“做桌”方面已享有盛誉。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=82100&size=300x300&key=1c14ff9e05686b4c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_82100\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在接手事业短短十多年的时间，陈金生就成为了目前金边数一数二的承办酒席好手。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">时任柬埔寨潮州会馆副会长的林光辉对陈金生颇为赏识。他说，潮汕一句老话，叫“洗碗钱银难赚”，但年纪轻轻的陈金生就是不怕苦，在父亲反对的情况下，硬是接手父亲的事业。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">陈金生说，当时老人就跟他说做别的生意，不要做这个行业，这个行业太累了。但陈金生夫妻俩商量了以后，觉得基础已经有了，他们只不过是接手老人的生意，成功不成功就靠他们自己来努力了。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=82101&size=300x300&key=2f6d90556eb30e68&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_82101\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=82103&size=300x300&key=c96542b9ef59b313&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_82103\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在金边，酒席承办是一个竞争激烈的行业。立足这个行业，除了要耐劳之外，还必须具备管理筹划的能力以及广泛的人脉。从1997年接手时候只能承办五十桌酒席，到现在承办三百桌酒席，年轻的陈金生经历无数的困难，终于打响了自己的品牌，成为这个行业最年轻的佼佼者。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮语，做桌，以及澎湃在血液中的潮音，文化，传统，让他们在商界的洪流中不忘本源并最终屹立潮头。</span></span></em></strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20151218/1450408480970022.png\" title=\"1450408480970022.png\" alt=\"图片2.png\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台综合报道 转载请标注下方二维码图片</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">来源/汕头电视台《天下潮商》</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">实习小编/博尔</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2015-12-18 11:14:46',0,NULL,1,NULL,2682,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (313,'【柬埔寨潮商】精神家园已经构建，潮商故事还在延续','201512211042149395.png','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><img src=\"/uploads/20151221/1450665721656578.png\" title=\"1450665721656578.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">编者按：</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">当时代的旧色掉落，新贵辈出。过去的辉煌未必过去，新的潮商正在不断崛起。在潮人聚集的地方，精神家园始终在默默构建着，潮商故事也一直在延续。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=82321&size=300x300&key=ea442c4b9601f390&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_82321\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">新潮商的新创业故事还在不断发生</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">每天，新唐人黄绍贵都有接不完的电话，从家乡普宁来到柬埔寨十二年时间，他已是三个孩子的父亲，与人合作在金边经营一所医院、一家潮州菜酒楼，同时，他还拥有自己的货运公司。作为一个从中国来到柬埔寨闯荡的新潮商，他的创业之路其实更加艰辛。与老一辈潮商不一样的是，2000年，黄绍贵来柬埔寨的原因是国内激烈的就业环境，当时他刚从一家医学中专毕业，他觉得自己的文凭在国内难以有所上佳的发展，就想到外面闯荡，凭着自己的吃苦精神想要闯出一番名堂出来。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=82325&size=300x300&key=f551e43d4d0296bc&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_82325\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">刚开始到金边的时候，黄绍贵是一所中资医院的内科医生，做了八年后，他开始与朋友合作投资经营医院。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">黄绍贵性格踏实又好结交朋友，他在家乡普宁的一些同学和朋友随后都跟着他来到柬埔寨，随着资金和人脉的积累，他很快又和朋友合作开起了货运公司和酒楼。从难以找到出路的中专毕业生到在异国成就一番事业， 33岁的黄绍贵创业脉络看上去如此清晰和简单，其背后其实有着说不尽的苦处。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=82326&size=300x300&key=713ff92fc7ebf772&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_82326\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">黄绍贵感慨道，背后说不尽的苦头只能默默咽下，因为创业都是要慢慢成就的。无论如何，他始终秉持一颗责任心去做。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在柬埔寨 潮商拥有自己的精神家园</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">一踏入这座位于金边大街的协天大帝庙，闻到那熟悉的香火味道，家的味道又扑面而来，事实上，这也是柬埔寨几十万潮人共同的家，因为柬埔寨潮州会馆就设在这里。然而，在上个世纪七八十年代那段动荡不安的岁月里，柬埔寨潮人在失去他们辛苦积攒的产业的同时，连同他们共同的精神家园也失去了。那段时间，中文被禁止使用，中文教育受到扼制，华族语言被严禁交谈，甚至，潮州会馆也被夷为平地。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=82316&size=300x300&key=8695fb678e0f3121&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_82316\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">到了1990年，柬埔寨政府实行民族和睦、对外开放的政策。那些一直为传承潮汕文化根脉费尽脑筋四处奔忙的老一辈潮人找到了生性仗义、为人豪爽的杨启秋。面对重托，正值事业高峰的杨启秋作出了合乎他性情的选择。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=82320&size=300x300&key=373e9c861bf30a6f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_82320\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">先重建协天大帝庙、成立潮州会馆了、重建端华学校，杨启秋倾尽其力，一步步地垒砌了柬埔寨潮人的精神家园。他被推选为潮州会馆第一任会长更是实至名归。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=82322&size=300x300&key=3fcce462481caa2c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_82322\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">杨启秋总是喜欢将柬埔寨新一代潮人称为“子孙”，透过这个称呼，能触摸到这个68岁的老潮商那份慈爱和责任。事实上，倾注了杨启秋多少心血的端华学校也被他看成自己的孩子，让他感到欣慰的是，端华学校目前的学生人数已达11000多名，成为东南亚地区首屈一指的华文学校。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=82323&size=300x300&key=f0d1821cfa37e403&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_82323\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">二十年文化断流，仍然阻不断潮汕文化根脉的传承，现在，在柬埔寨，还是能听到正宗的潮州话、经典的潮乐，听到令人动容的中文诗歌朗诵，甚至，在他们的车里，还能听到《我的祖国》《西游记》主题歌等传统的中国歌曲。而无论是潮乐、诗歌还是那老掉牙的歌曲，这些声音总是能直达你的心灵，因为，你知道，这里面有一种特别的感情，这样的感情在几经劫难之后仍然历久弥新。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=82324&size=300x300&key=7820f578baff7d90&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_82324\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">小时候乡愁是一枚小小的邮票，我在这头，母亲在那头，长大后，乡愁是一张窄窄的船票，我在这着头，新娘在那头......</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20151221/1450665730491939.png\" title=\"1450665730491939.png\" alt=\"图片2.png\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台综合报道 转载请标注下方二维码图片</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">来源/汕头电视台《天下潮商》</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">实习小编/博尔</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></span><br/></p>','2015-12-21 10:42:14',0,NULL,1,NULL,2547,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (314,'【印尼潮商】用脚印垒砌成功的塔尖','201601191603119245.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><img src=\"/uploads/20160119/1453190564810073.png\" title=\"1453190564810073.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">编者按：<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>一艘红头船驶离港口，一段奋斗的故事就开篇了。那艘红头船上承载的梦想之重，也是潮人们在这片土地上肩负的挫折之苦。往日的辛酸泪，如今早已播种出一棵棵参天大树。荆棘之路上，潮人以别样的姿态闯荡出一片天空，放飞了昔日船上那纯真的梦想。</span></em></strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61028&size=300x300&key=25a9c1d647dde3bd&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61028\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">广袤的海洋、迷人的沙滩、悠远的文化、淳朴的土著，那晶莹透绿的碧水、那蓝天白云的对照、那冉冉升起的朝阳、那层峦叠翠的原始森林、那远离繁华的部落族群，还有那海平面上拔地而起的千百个大小岛屿-----这里就是位于东南亚，有着“千岛之国”美誉的印度尼西亚。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(46, 139, 87); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这里有丰富的自然资源和物产，当年下南洋的那一拨拨潮人祖先，有相当一部分就留在了这块富饶的土地，开始了他们新的人生旅程。&nbsp;</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(154, 205, 50);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮人在印尼 数量多建设也多</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61029&size=300x300&key=233ba9addf4407bb&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61029\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">雅加达是印尼的首都，也是东南亚第一大城市，中国驻印尼的大使馆就位于市中心，时任大使馆总领事钟瑞明是一名汕头人，在印尼工作已经有14个年头，对印尼的潮商可谓相当熟悉。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">据他介绍，印尼两亿多的人口数量中，华人有两千多万，大概占十分之一，而华人群体中的潮汕族群大概有一百多万人。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61030&size=300x300&key=edea33fbd6a2fba5&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61030\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">钟瑞明在这边工作的十几年里，特别关注潮汕人，也去过一些潮汕人比较集中的城市，都留下了深刻印象。他说，印尼潮汕人跟其他在印尼的客家人、闽南人一样，为印尼这个国家的经济建设和社会发展都做出了重要贡献，同时为促进中印双边往来也做了很大的努力。他们在这里的职业主要是从商。在商业领域，很多人是白手起家，有的是从国内移民过来，有的是出生在这边，经过这么多年的发展，他们在各个行业都取得令人瞩目的成绩。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮汕人在这里涉猎多方面的行业，包括房地产业、酒店业、木材业、加工业，航空业、电视行业等等。甚至是近几年在印尼发展迅猛的矿业，也有不少潮汕人投资。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(154, 205, 50);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮商在南洋 创业艰辛见品质</strong></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮商是中国传统三大商帮之一，渊源可追溯至明代。</span></strong>与晋商、徽商相比，潮商历久不衰、在世界范围内影响深远，而南洋正是潮商在海外发展的出发点和落脚点。下南洋闯世界成为当年潮人先辈的风潮，红头船也成为承载发财梦想的潮人创业标志。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在异国他乡谋生，几乎一无所有的潮人先辈们，唯一依靠的就是祖祖辈辈传下来的勤劳、刻苦、拼搏的精神，以及血液里面流淌着的与生俱来的商业智慧和灵感。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61031&size=300x300&key=cf9dda109d3876d9&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61031\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">当先辈们漂洋过海来到印尼的时候，他们就发现，这里是一块充满诱惑和财富的土地。但是，当满地的黄金和诱人的蛋糕摆在面前的时候，一切都还得靠自己去努力争取。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">今年88岁高龄的杨金锋老人是早一辈印尼潮商的杰出代表，六岁的时候跟着父亲来到印尼。</span></strong>最初来到这里奋斗所受的苦，杨金锋老人至今记忆犹新，当年奋斗的血和泪历历在目。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61032&size=300x300&key=6716ea9fea09a0e1&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61032\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">杨金锋回忆道，当时跟随父母来到加里曼丹岛，因为穷，生活很艰苦，刚刚小学毕业就要帮助家庭。当时刚好遇上日本侵略者的侵略战争，从此以后的3年8个月里，他们在日本人的铁蹄下生活如蝼蚁，杨金锋甚至还差一点就丢掉了性命。战争的阴云散去后，十来岁的杨金锋为了贴补家庭，到处打工，十分刻苦、拼搏。因而家里的境况渐渐转好，还开了一个小药铺，也就是这时开始，杨金锋就跟弟弟在家里的铺子帮忙。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">当年一碗粥和乌橄榄蘸酱油的日子，杨金锋现在想起来，艰苦的滋味犹在心头。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61033&size=300x300&key=d6f3b7871c766892&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61033\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">苦难的生活并没有磨灭心中的信念，也没能将坚毅、勇敢的潮汕人击垮，小小生意能发家，是靠他们一步一个脚印、一点一滴积累，后来杨金锋和他的弟弟杨金智接过父亲的生意，也开始了他们自己的创业之路。兄弟两人选择了父亲之前的老本行，兄弟二人继承了潮汕人一贯的精明，开始了他们在制药领域的探索。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">从小作坊到代人加工，再到自创品牌，直到现在垄断了整个印尼的国产膏药业，属于这两个潮汕兄弟的药业王国就这样一步步地缔造起来。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61034&size=300x300&key=a4aef641550126ba&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61034\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而回想创业之艰辛，兄弟倆感概良多。当初四十多岁来到雅加达这个大城市，每天工作到深夜，早上还要四五点就出门，经过二三十年的奋斗，才有了今天这样的光景。杨金锋的弟弟杨金智当初没有想到今天的自己能够这么成功，刚开始创业的失败让他们兄弟俩初尝这个行业的艰苦。后来他们发现，当时的印尼只有三个膏药厂，生产的基本都是创可贴，都没有他们这种膏药，也因此他们抓住商机，做起了独门生意，由一种膏药衍生发展出各种各样的膏药，一年接着一年，生意获得了长足发展。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">和杨金锋、杨金智两兄弟一样，现年80岁的潮商蔡为兴也是历尽劫难而后生。</span></strong>他出生在家乡揭阳，父亲早早过世，留下孤儿寡母，母子倆无所依靠，于是便选择下南洋谋生。虽然当时蔡为兴年纪小，但那时出海的情景，一辈子也忘不了。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61036&size=300x300&key=3af7539b29d18f01&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61036\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">据蔡为兴说，当时家里穷得叮当响，一个子儿也掏不出。正月十五的时候，是母舅背他到汕头搭船，是姑母出资让他搭船。因为钱不多，在船上没有床铺位可以睡觉，所以一路颠簸，很是辛苦。等到了新加坡，还被赶到一个小岛，因为当地人说他们有晦气，不能影响别人，为此又受苦了八天。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61035&size=300x300&key=1252c87c48cfee1a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61035\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">和所有早期登上印尼的潮人一样，蔡为兴母子用潮人特有的隐忍、坚韧承载了所有的痛苦，开始了他们的谋生之路。没有知识、没有技术、没有资金、没有土地，从登岛的那一天起，他们就注定了只能是生活在这片陌生土地上最底层的人，如何才能摆脱命运，出人头地呢？潮人天生不服输的秉性时时刻刻刺激着蔡为兴跳跃的脉搏，挑动他不屈的斗志和商业的神经。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">终于有一天，他决定自己单干，出来做生意，从挑担卖东西这样的小生意做起，他把握住了改变命运的机会。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">从1953年2月26日开始，蔡为兴肩担着东西在街头售卖，一直到1960年10月16日才到市镇租了一间铺租60元的小铺子，以此为资本发展起来。当时蔡为兴的想法就是要刻苦，挖空心思寻求上进的办法。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61037&size=300x300&key=81583c8e6b72ff04&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61037\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">正是蔡为兴这种潮人式的精打细算、勤俭持家、艰苦创业，使得他在传统商品的销售领域慢慢做大，从卖菜到批发再到开小食品厂，后来竟然坐上了廖内省富豪圈的头把交椅。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">如今，他的儿子们继承了父亲的衣钵，精细经营，其红茶销售占据了印尼的半壁江山，而黑啤代理更是垄断了整个印尼市场。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61038&size=300x300&key=e498f8ba259d2301&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61038\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">蔡为兴儿子的蔡裕盛感慨，父亲之所以能够成功，是因为他做人处事中一直秉持好信用的品质，所以大家相信他，生意自然就能够成功。另一点，是他从年轻到老一路的刻苦和坚持，造就了如今。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61039&size=300x300&key=57c9dac9a4b7bf0a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61039\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">老一辈潮人的海外创业之路漫漫，但是他们上下求索而坚持不懈的精神支撑着他们走到了今天。一路摸爬滚打，昔日的遍体凌伤，是今日他们成功的一枚又一枚特殊勋章。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">我们在感慨他们的成功之路时，也更感慨于潮人，特别是潮商，不仅有敏锐抓住商机的嗅觉，更有逆流而上、从无到有的本事。潮商现今布天下，并不是偶然，一次次的成功背后，是潮汕人特有的族群性格造就的。身为潮汕人，我们该自豪！</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160119/1453190581459192.png\" title=\"1453190581459192.png\" alt=\"图片2.png\"/><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>来源/汕头电视台《天下潮商》<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/博尔 关雪</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></span><br/></p>','2016-01-19 16:03:11',0,NULL,1,NULL,2319,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (315,'【印尼潮商】潮人经商的一本“正经”','201601201704448616.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><img src=\"/uploads/20160120/1453280670134147.png\" title=\"1453280670134147.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">编者按：</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">红头船书写了不少大实业家的成功故事，但在生意场上的大风大浪下，并非人人都能惊天骇地地闯出一番大家业的，一辈子都在经营着小本生意、随大潮起伏的也大有人在。可是，即使是这些看似平凡的小生意人，他们也一直在秉承着那本积满潮汕人经商准则的“经”。所以即使他们没有庞大的商业王国，也不妨碍他们是“成功的潮商”这一名号。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61104&size=300x300&key=168043d79920a994&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61104\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">并不是每个做小生意的人都能像杨家两兄弟和蔡为兴家族一样，白手起家而最终成为行业老大，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">但是“小小生意能发家”的祖训，成为每一个经商的潮汕人心中始终坚持的信念，这份信念，犹如永不熄灭的导航灯，指引着他们世代坚持、坚守商道，在商海中起起伏伏、打打拼拼，任潮起潮落而矢志不移前赴后继。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(154, 205, 50);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">干面店生意虽小 食品质量却获大众首肯</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61105&size=300x300&key=bd5c89b77b1648ac&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61105\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">坤甸市，位于印尼加里曼丹岛，是西加里曼丹省首府，这是一个华人聚居的城市，华人人口占了全市总人口的三分之一，这也是潮汕人在印尼最主要的一个集聚地。在这里，大街小巷随处可见做各种生意的潮汕人，人们互相用潮汕话打招呼，相互交流，以至于我们刚踏上这个岛屿，油然而生一种家的感觉，一切都是那么的亲切。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">“乌记”干面是城区最出名的地方小吃，他的创始人叫吴合利，是汕头人，他把家乡干面干粿的做法带到了这里，做出了名气，虽是小本经营，但由于追求质量为上，生意蒸蒸日上，每天来吃粿条吃干面的人络绎不绝。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61106&size=300x300&key=100376c65077e0bb&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61106\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">据西加坤甸日报副社长陈得时介绍，“乌记”干面店是坤甸的面店中最出名的一家，在市区内已经有三间店面了，其他人也开面店，但是都没有这个潮汕人厉害。因为创始人吴合利的土名叫做乌记，所以就把店名家叫做“乌记”。虽然现在店铺是由孙子在负责，但是老人家身体还很健康，一个星期会有一两天仍坚持到店里打面。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(154, 205, 50);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">店里的一幅条文 三代人的经商原则</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">印尼是群岛国家，廖内本身也是一组小群岛，这里海岸线曲折，港湾众多，海产品丰富，当年南渡的有些潮汕人就选择留在这个小岛，做起海产品生意。62岁的朱妹妹老家澄海樟林。她从出生就开始在廖内生活，而当年她的爷爷和父亲却是坐着红头船从樟林古港一路漂泊，来到这里扎根。现在他们家的海产店，在当地颇有盛誉。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这家店凝聚了朱家三代人的心血，在店里采访时，墙上的一副效朱公致富营业良规的条文引起了我们的注意。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61108&size=300x300&key=525d15bea14f771e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61108\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">朱妹妹介绍道，这是从她父亲朱天盛一辈传到现在，已经有接近60年的时间了。</span></strong>她15岁开始跟随父亲做生意直到现在，一直在秉承着这一幅条文的警示，一直以它为脊梁走过一段又一段的人生路途，它在不断告诫着她们一家人，做生意要效朱公致富营业的良规、要讲信用的道理。父亲也一直在教导她，做人要走正道，忠直老实终归是好的。做生意尤其要正直，不要耍心机，生意才会永久。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">朱妹妹和她的弟弟跟着父亲做生意知道现在自己的拼搏，也已经有45年了，心血全部投注在这家店里，从刚开始的小店做到现在的大招牌。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61107&size=300x300&key=f37adebe1eda95ff&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61107\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61109&size=300x300&key=bba374298b2ad173&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61109\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">“生意要勤奋，懒惰则百事废；用度要节俭，奢侈则用途竭；接纳要温和，暴躁则交易少；买卖要随时，拖延则机宜失；议价要订明，含糊则争执多”</span></strong>——这就是朱公致富营业良规，没有优美华丽的文字，写的全是经营的规范、致富的秘诀。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61110&size=300x300&key=c9e35e31b9a9caef&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61110\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">勤而俭，精而细，信而义，商业的诀窍！潮人的品性！在这副家传的营业良规中得到了质朴、深刻的诠释，这一切，仅在一个小本经营的潮汕人家族生意传承中就表现得淋漓尽致。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160120/1453280678404326.png\" title=\"1453280678404326.png\" alt=\"图片2.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">来源/汕头电视台《天下潮商》</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/博尔 关雪</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br/></p>','2016-01-20 17:04:44',0,NULL,1,NULL,2660,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (316,'【印尼潮商】狭路相逢勇者胜','201601211037313827.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><img src=\"/uploads/20160121/1453343835140361.png\" title=\"1453343835140361.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">编者按：</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">筚路蓝缕是一个很容易就打出来的词语，而真正要在异乡商潮中杀出一条血路，非有过人的能耐不可。潮商，一个从大海边走出来的族群，天生具有面对惊风骇浪时的淡定和冷静。勇敢，坚忍，对于一纵即逝的商机有着超乎想象的捕捉能力，引领着印尼潮商一步一步走向成功。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61173&size=300x300&key=241f30a5b2f75cc6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61173\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在印尼首都雅加达闹市区的一条内街，安静矗立着一栋四层楼的黄色小楼，在周围水泥森林般的众多摩天大厦的掩盖下，丝毫不引人注目。如果不仔细了解，只怕很难想象得到，这样一栋并无没有醒目招牌的小楼，竟会是印尼潮州乡亲公会所在地。都说商场就是没有硝烟的战场，但到了这里，那些商业上的竞争对手不复存在，彼此相处也可放下警惕，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这里是属于潮商这个大家庭聚会喝茶，用家乡话叙旧谈天的地方，连这里的空气闻起来都让人觉得快乐和轻松，充满暖意。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61174&size=300x300&key=c0398bc072d7e94f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61174\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61175&size=300x300&key=7c04af9fce52fefc&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61175\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">印尼潮商连女士对这种形式非常喜欢。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">她告诉记者，这样的形式是潮州乡亲公会的独创，他们采取的是创办人一人轮流主持一周，会员可以在潮汕会享受免费的午餐，用餐之后有的唱歌，有的下棋，以各种方式消遣，享受礼拜天的休息时光。</span></strong>据介绍，潮州会还设立了合唱团。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61176&size=300x300&key=0b50c13c6a771c29&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61176\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">印尼作为一个群岛国家，聚集潮商之地不仅有苏门答腊、加里曼丹等几个大岛和主要城市，还包括了其它所有藏着商机的宝地。现如今共有18个潮州乡亲公会位于印尼境内，而不同的地方公会之间，也会不时举办各类联谊活动。这些远离家乡奋斗拼搏的潮人通过这种形式，牵住彼此的心，串联起家乡情怀，让潮人的精神和文化借此得到传承与延续。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这遍布印尼各地的18个潮州乡亲公会，是印尼潮人与潮商的代表，而曾国奎这位印尼潮州乡亲公会理事会会长，正是公认的印尼潮商的精神领袖和杰出代表。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61177&size=300x300&key=685ea5a86a95b983&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61177\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61178&size=300x300&key=b32c62590c29d456&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61178\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这些都是曾国奎的地产公司开发建设的，曾国奎是印尼有名的地产大亨，在雅加达，他的地产囊括了很多黄金旺地，公司开发建设了很多高端的写字楼、购物商场、渡假中心。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">曾国奎有一段传奇般的成长历程，他投资多回无一败绩，每次都能让他大获成功。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61179&size=300x300&key=17ecaa1da9d6d712&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61179\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">对于这样令人羡慕的投资经历，曾国奎却从来不觉得这些收获是自己的运气。</span></strong>他对自己包括潮州人的评价，首先一个是很有胆量。据曾国奎先生自己透露，他于1980年成为石油工业的承建商，当时的总包商是洋人，接受了来自政府的整个工程，而他们就把工程分摊给如曾国奎这样的小承包商。他必须每日用英文与人对话，如果连开口说洋文的胆量都没有，这桩生意就只有泡汤一途了。其次，曾国奎同样看不懂洋文文字，在查阅合同的时候，唯一能够校对的只有款项数目，但他仍然胆大地签了下来。虽然签过后才明白后果严重，第一个工程也由于许多细节的不甚明了，而导致无法取得好成绩，但正是这种牛仔不识虎的胆量，让曾国奎拿下了这个项目，赚到了这一桶金。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61180&size=300x300&key=2a614f4ee306c72f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61180\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">当然，光凭胆量不可能让曾国奎做到出手万无一失，未尝败绩，他的独具慧眼，率先捕获商机，出手果决，再加上做决定时超乎常人的勇气，这些都是让曾国奎脱颖而出，大获全胜不可或缺的难得品质。</span></strong>与曾国奎一样，巨港市的印尼潮商蔡明盛也有着过人的胆识。蔡明盛是苏门答腊岛东南部富甲一方的潮商，在当地以橡胶业闻名遐迩。他从年轻的时候开始外出闯荡，一生经历过的商战无数，每次都是果断出手，决定了就绝不迟疑，而这也正是蔡明盛能够成功的一大原因。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61181&size=300x300&key=b6909d6a80c10453&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61181\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">蔡明盛告诉记者，他的投资会随时机的变化而转变。</span></strong>刚开始时，他从印尼粮食供不应求这一点看到了商机，于是奔赴新加坡寻找做生意的方法。由于没有本钱，蔡明盛果断选择将多数利润让于他人，自己只赚取少数利润，通过这样的方法与人合作，进口粮食，赚到了属于他的第一桶金。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">之后，他以此作为手中的资本，频频向印尼本土的优势资源出手，也多次取得了成功，产业越做越大。现在，蔡明盛拥有规模在印尼名列前茅的橡胶园、棕榈园、轮胎厂等产业，他的身经百战，让人们充分了解潮商的勇敢与智慧。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61182&size=300x300&key=b3822a9ee3794715&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61182\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">蔡明盛随后向记者介绍了他橡胶事业起步的过程。当时他在生意上一帆风顺，信用很好。</span></strong>因此，银行将有一间因旧主无力偿还债务而抵押的橡胶厂交由蔡明盛接管。蔡明盛向银行事先申明，他对橡胶没有经验，但还是同意接手了。刚开始的时候，他自己没有信心，旁人也不看好连橡胶为何物都不懂的潮州人却来参与橡胶生意。可是，别人的不信任反而激发了蔡明盛的斗志，他决心无论付出多大的努力，也要打破潮州人对橡胶业几乎零参与的现状。在蔡明盛的努力下，原本基本全部被福建等地的人所包揽的橡胶业被他闯出了一条血路，到最后他连别人的橡胶也大力进货，再销往美国。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61183&size=300x300&key=aac0e3cea0109ef1&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61183\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">初生牛犊不怕虎，千难万险不回头。前者成为曾国奎在人生起步阶段交出了第一份漂亮的成绩单，后者则让蔡明盛登上橡胶大王的宝座。在困难面前，他们永不退缩；在机会面前，他们毫不犹疑。他们，是从潮汕大地走出去的名扬天下的潮商。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160121/1453343845319123.png\" title=\"1453343845319123.png\" alt=\"图片2.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">来源/汕头电视台《天下潮商》</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/关雪&nbsp;&nbsp;博尔</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br/></p>','2016-01-21 10:37:31',0,NULL,1,NULL,2249,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (319,'遇见汕头 35个美丽瞬间','201602171617338118.jpg','<p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011712421625.png\" title=\"1460011712421625.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal;text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">汕头在你记忆里是什么模样</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal;text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">潮汕美食还是百载商埠</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal;text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">是家 还是从未踏足的故乡</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal;text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">遇见了那么多广州大街小巷</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal;text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">我 终于回家了</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102930&size=300x300&key=d8d139a558862638&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102930\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;max-width: 400px\"/><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal;text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;color:#ff0000;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 24px\">中山公园</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal;text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 24px\">小时候常常玩耍的地方</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal;text-align: center