ght: 24px\">这些美美的照片，来自杨伊园（Mango）之手，她还想说：</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 24px\">在广州做一个公众号专门拍广州的大街小巷 他们总说家乡呢</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 24px\">所以这次回家花了两天时间拍摄和整理 又拿出了这几年的存货</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 24px\">只想展现一个跟你们<span style=\"color:#ff0000;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">印象里不一样的汕头</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 24px\">在广州你们总问我</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 24px\">回汕头是不是还住围屋 汕头是不是像广州的老城区一样</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 24px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">其实汕头是多面的 &nbsp;它古老又年轻 它很好地融合了两个矛盾体</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;color:#0000ff;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 24px\">它有历史的沉淀也有光怪陆离的发展</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;color:#0000ff;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 24px\">汕头对我来说 是家乡 是从小长大的地方</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;color:#0000ff;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 24px\">有它独特的味道 不愿有人误会它</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;color:#0000ff;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 24px\">也愿你们可以从我的镜头 重新回忆或者认识它</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 24px\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011721111486.png\" title=\"1460011721111486.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></span></span></p><p style=\";padding: 0;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;text-indent: 0;white-space: normal\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;转载请标明出处及下方图片</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">感谢 Mango 投稿</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">橄榄小编/洪锐</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103036&size=300x300&key=63f91f1ed99f7ef6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103036\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;max-width: 400px\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-02-17 15:39:29',0,NULL,1,NULL,2394,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (320,'【岭东年俗录】以前，潮汕过年是从年廿四开始的','201602171706569670.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011736106658.png\" title=\"1460011736106658.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">编者按：</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">小时候感觉过年的时间很长，从筅囤开始，大人小孩一起忙碌，然后一起迎接新春的到来。当熬制甜馃的炊烟升起，一年中最欢乐的时刻随之启动。那时候的年节，无论贫穷与富有，无论健康与疾病，都无法遮掩人心的欢乐。年味，是年纪越长越难忘的过往。从今天起，本版将不定期转载民俗研究者岭东怒马的年俗美文，一起重温记忆中那渐行渐远又历久弥新的过年的味道。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=98550&size=300x300&key=ca0be22ef95a27d9&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_98550\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">——你觉得年味不够，那是因为少了仪式。</strong></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">城市越来越大，高楼越来越多，物资越来越丰富，娱乐越来越花样。但是，年却过得越来越寡淡。这几年，你有没有觉得春节越来越冷清，越来越没有味道，你有没有起过远行寻找原始年味，有没有在酒酣耳热之后，怀念一下以前充满人情味、粿菜香的忙碌的过大年？</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=98581&size=300x300&key=f5bb6713f7a66d2c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_98581\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">是的，曾经的我们，有着热闹的过大年，有着年味十足的团圆节。但是是什么让这一切全成为了回忆，年的味道是怎样突然间消失在我们的生活当中？先让我们慢慢来回想一下从前吧——从前慢，慢到过个年，不是直接从除夕开始的，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">以前我们过年是从——</span></strong></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">年廿四 老爷上天开始的。</strong></span></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">腊月二十四，每一个潮汕孩子，都会脱口而出“老爷上天”。这是一个从小被奶奶妈妈们念到耳熟能详的暗号，这个暗号如同“芝麻开门”，一旦家里人念起，就意味着年的脚步越来越近，一个充满美味、玩乐、温情的过年大节，开心到仿佛明天醒来就已经来到。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=98551&size=300x300&key=e6361c37e510263a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_98551\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这一天也是过年前最后一个重要的民俗祭祀的日子。从中国民间信仰的系统来说，这一天是祭拜灶神的日子。《淮南子 万毕术》记此日，“<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">具酒果饴糖，置刍豆于灶前，以秣神马</span></strong>”。中原江南一带，此日专为祭灶，送灶神，但是实际上一般的潮人家庭，都会认为，年二四这个日子，是举头三尺的所有神明们，上天庭述职的日子，不唯灶神。因此岭东各地县志所记风俗，是“<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">凡神庙及人家各备仪供养，并印幡幢、舆马、仪从于楮上，焚而送之</span></strong>”。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">流传至今在潮汕仍然保存有的祭品之中，必有“胶罗糍”，纸马纸鹤</span></strong>。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=98488&size=300x300&key=a86fb46bb5dc96ff&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_98488\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">胶罗糍又叫“落汤钱”，是一种重要的民俗祭品，应当是从古俗中的饴糖演化而来。虽然南方也有“糖葱”“豆仁糖”等麦芽糖类的小吃，但是作为以稻米为主要作物及主食的潮汕，很自然会用更为容易得到的糯米来制作改良各种年节祭品。而其之所以会形成这么样一个松软的形状，我相信民俗祭祀的想象以及群众尤其是主妇们主人翁般高涨的创造力一定是决定性的。当她们想象这种带着米香适口柔韧粘牙的甜食，在寒冷的冬天，热腾腾地进了老爷们的圣公嘴，如果花生芝麻的干脆香口还不够分量的话，那粘牙的糯米团子，一定让老爷们再懒得开口说我们太多的不是。而这一切想象，都会在等一会祭拜结束之后，旁边流满口水的孩儿们身上得到完美的印证。而事实上，当胶罗糍还未曾放到红盘子中上供之前，早就被等不及的小孩子们偷偷塞进嘴里，那刚蒸熟的糯米香，黏黏的咬劲加上花生芝麻说不出的脆香，是每一个长大的孩子都无法忘怀的童年美味之一。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=98489&size=300x300&key=c183fd7f786dbafe&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_98489\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=98497&size=300x300&key=6152fdf8f094111d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_98497\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮汕主妇们的贤惠，让胶罗糍比起北方元宵、驴打滚之类的小吃制作更容易，一般的做法，是将糯米舂成粉，加水成糊状，入锅蒸熟，然后拿出来在粿钵中，用棍子不断搅拌，最后再揪出捏成扁扁的铜钱状，放在炒香捶碎的白糖粉、芝麻粉和花生粉中一裹，一个白生生散发着热气，松软甜香的人间美味，就出现了。而当祭拜完毕，在冬天气温下，也可以保存到第二天，稍微入锅再蒸一下，撒上花生芝麻碎，一道美味小吃又依然满血复活。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=98491&size=300x300&key=74374df1bda521b7&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_98491\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">除了让老爷不舍得开口的美食，潮汕先民们还很贴心地备好了草料，水，准备了老爷们的坐骑，因此也催生了这个节日特有的“纸马”，纸马是一种纸镪，印在县志上说的“楮纸”上，也就是钱纸，与元宝、锞丝等冥币一样，是贴心的潮汕人们为上天面圣的神明们准备的坐骑，神仙本来腾云驾雾，一直以来我总是搞不懂为啥还得搞个代步的神兽。直到看到县志的记述，看到纸马上的内容，终于明白，原来神仙与人一样，锦衣不能夜行，飞行技能虽然有，但是排场也是要讲究的。因此男神骑骏马，女神跨仙鹤，一路幡幢飘摇，前呼后拥，老爷们心情愉快，情商才会大好，讲起下界的事情，才会满足我等小民们的良好祝愿。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=98582&size=300x300&key=933ffeafcec2e80e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_98582\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">“老爷上天”这个祭祀节日，是以家庭为单位的祭祀日，中国农耕社会其实是将“灶神”作为人间每个家庭的神格化，而潮汕更是将之直呼为“司命公”，以司性命，这正是“民以食为天”的潜意识表现。而以闽粤为代表的善祀鬼神的民众，笃信鬼神的实质，其实是想将一种秩序借助神力，上升到一种宿命的高度，而保证一个社会在规则之中运行的目的。所以我们现在看到的，众神不外人间，拜神正是省己，神的需要就是人的需要，神的情感就是凡人的性情。年节岁时，便是借助各种仪式，借感恩纳福之际，揖别过去，寄望未来，不管生活如何，日子终将一直要过下去。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=98583&size=300x300&key=4d3a2d7db989917f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_98583\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">是的，老爷上天之后，爸爸妈妈便要用榕枝竹叶芒草，打扫屋宇，潮汕人以前每年一定要进行的“筅囤”。一家人老老少少，高高低低，擦窗洗地，重重的年味，就在热热闹闹，在灶里一阵接一阵的粿香中飘荡开来。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">年，开始了。</strong></span></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011746359401.png\" title=\"1460011746359401.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>文/岭东怒马&nbsp;&nbsp;图/岭东怒马&nbsp;&nbsp;安静<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>橄榄小编/立庵<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=98471&size=300x300&key=7ad1ab7d70c37065&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_98471\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-02-17 17:06:56',0,NULL,1,NULL,2255,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (321,'【岭东年俗录】筅尘与刮鼎 ','201602171707554348.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011760618194.png\" title=\"1460011760618194.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">筅尘，潮语读为“采囤”，这是两个很奇怪的字，就连很多本地人看到，也不知道如何读代表什么意思，这就涉及到了方言学中提到的“文白异读”的问题。潮汕话有很多字是有多种读法的，在口语中有很多词语，甚至无法写出来，平时大家都以为是“无字”，觉得是土话没有文字。其实真相就是文白异读，也即一个字有文字上一个读音，口语上一个读音。例如这个“尘”字，文读读尘，白读就要读囤，本字其实是一个字，本义就是烟尘、灰尘。这是潮汕话所以比较难学的其中一个原因。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=99293&size=300x300&key=6f1e4f0207d07724&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_99293\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">至于“筅”，涉及到一个社会变迁，生活用具的变化过程，筅这种用具和称呼慢慢就被遗忘了。在我们的回忆里，筅是以前用灶台做饭，刷洗生铁大锅的那个竹刷子。但是实际上，在泉州一带，竹子做的扫把还是叫做“筅仔”。前段时间看电视剧，说到戚继光在福建御倭的时候，发明了一种专门用来对付锋利日本刀的武器，叫做“狼筅”，形状就是前端一根带有很多小枝丫的大竹篙。大家都知道，潮汕民系的主要群体，就是由福建泉漳一带移民而来，所以我们也可以由此推断，筅，就是当时很日常的竹扫把。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=99294&size=300x300&key=d91a10f56b7ef1a9&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_99294\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">刚才为了印证这个问题，我用微信让泉州朋友语音了一下“筅尘”，发现除了音调稍有变化，这个词的读音和潮语基本还是一样的。可见虽然岁月流逝，泉潮也远隔千里，中间经过时代变迁，但是我们语言中依然保留着当年日常的用语，这正是我们现在探究民俗背后的意义所在。因为当我们发现，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在习以为常的一个普通习俗后面，其实蕴藏着那么多的历史信息碎片，而通过这个入口，我们仿佛能够一下子穿越，真实地与古人面对面</span></strong>，这是多么让人不可思议，我仿佛已经发现，从此妈妈不用再担心我们看狗血的网剧了。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=99371&size=300x300&key=cb309fe09a469f4a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_99371\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;color:#808080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">竹叶榕枝，潮汕民俗中常见</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">搞清楚读音，我们再来看看，其实筅尘之俗，由来已久。宋朝的《梦粱录》明确记录：“十二月尽，不论大小家，俱洒扫门闾去尘秽、净庭户，以祈新岁之安。”黎明即起，洒扫庭除，本就是朱子治家格言中每日内容。更不要说临近新年，把家里大扫除一遍自然也是应有之义。但是年末的筅尘，必然的要多了一层去秽祈福的这么个意思。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=99372&size=300x300&key=a611b7e37bc8732f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_99372\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=99374&size=300x300&key=37029231710c96b4&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_99374\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family: Tahoma; font-size: small; line-height: 19.5px;\">竹叶榕枝，潮汕民俗中常见</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">因此上当竹筅上除了扫把以外，还要绑上竹叶，榕树叶，芒草，还要洒上红花仙草水就不让人奇怪了。这些典型的潮人民间代表驱邪去秽保平安的标志物，无一例外在各种民俗活动中出现，虽然很少作为主角，但是不可或缺，是当仁不让的黄金配角。潮汕一直以来，是个典型的宗族农耕社会，所以很多习俗带有农耕时代生活的影子。典型的潮汕乡村，在村寨环境上，一直是讲究“前榕后竹”，因为潮语中，竹谐音“德”，而榕在上古音中是读“松”，潮语继承了这古化石般的读法，在口语中读为成功的“成”。前成后德，与祠堂里的“光前裕后”匾额一样，成为宗族社会中奉为圭臬的价值标准，也是每个宗族所孜孜以求的道义与荣光。于是榕树与竹子成为既普遍又神奇的绿色植物，这种神性当然要在一年一度的屋宅清除邪秽上大派用场。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=99377&size=300x300&key=1451b68dbce3b384&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_99377\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">以前年廿四筅尘的时候，还必须要有一个仪式。因为在农村，老式的灶台是烧柴火的，平日用的也是生铁锅，铁锅用了一段时间之后，锅底就会积一层厚厚的黑灰，久了会影响传热。年廿四这天，既要拜司命公，便首先要将灶台收拾干净，那么作为中心的这个大锅，就更要拿出去清洁了。潮语称铁锅为“鼎”，这又是一个古汉语，我们经常读到力能扛鼎称颂勇士，潮汕孩子听到都笑了，在潮汕，鼎专门指的就是炒菜的锅，这又是中古食具在潮方言中的一个遗存。所以这个仪式便叫做“刮鼎”。小时候放假我住在外婆家，勤劳的邻里主妇们几乎是天天有人刮鼎的，而时间就在清晨，经常我放假的一天就是在村里屋外的刮鼎声中自然醒的，当我们赖床一段起来洗漱之后，一碗热腾腾的白糜和鸡蛋就已经在等着我们了。</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=99647&size=300x300&key=0b918992dd08fced&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_99647\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">农村的刮鼎，是把大锅拿到屋外，然后倒盖过来，用铁锄头一下下清除黑灰，这种声音难免尖利难听，但是这一日却成了以前腊月廿四一道特有的风景，刮鼎之声此起彼伏，身边小童的笑声，主妇们的笑叱声，来回邻里的问候声，此时回想，真是声声入心，只是随着煤气与电力的普及，这个带有明显乡愁镜头感的场面，只能等待有心人用电影来再现了。</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=99649&size=300x300&key=f1f0ced06825205a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_99649\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p>传统上潮汕民居多是高大的三合院式平房，如下山虎、四点金之类的，多有一个天井，比较传统的室内还是大木结构，因为崇尚木石雕刻，即便普通人家也多少在柱脚檐下做一些装饰，所以一年到头屋角檐下，难免有一些平时难以打扫的蛛网灰尘，卫生死角。腊月年底，正好利用这个机会全家动员，从卫生角度也好，是心理暗示也罢，不料却成了长大后孩子们心中一道难以忘怀的仪式。一家大小一起动手过新年的感觉，虽然累一点，但是其乐融融，前几年我在峡山上班，每当年廿四走过各村，看见已经放假在家的半大孩子们，在家里主妇的带领下，站在条凳上筅尘，擦洗的场景，总是情不自禁的会心潮澎湃，眼角湿润——为什么我的眼角常有皱纹，那是因为这片土地太多感动啊。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011767427391.png\" title=\"1460011767427391.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: small; line-height: 19.5px;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: small; line-height: 19.5px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: small; line-height: 19.5px;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: small; line-height: 19.5px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: small; line-height: 19.5px;\">文图/岭东怒马</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: small; line-height: 19.5px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: small; line-height: 19.5px;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=99571&size=300x300&key=1f199d9055d08412&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_99571\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-02-17 17:07:55',0,NULL,1,NULL,2207,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (322,'【岭东年俗录】同桌的粿','201602171708412905.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011779618710.png\" title=\"1460011779618710.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101016&size=300x300&key=89b14a9f3078a325&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101016\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">一说起岭东潮人的过年，离不开的一定是各种各样的“粿”。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=100635&size=300x300&key=c02a90eb0d34067a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_100635\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这个“粿”字，林伦伦先生在他的大作《潮汕方言词考释》中曾经批评过，说是一个无中生有的生造的方言字。他根据古籍文献考证，本字应该是代表着饼食点心的“馃”。然而每一个在岭东生活长大的潮汕人，却都更会觉得，恰恰是这个米字旁的“粿”字，才是理所当然的真实表达。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=100632&size=300x300&key=fb5d87c4a424d8c9&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_100632\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=100633&size=300x300&key=b3a6ffca65f29c8b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_100633\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这是因为，几乎所有的粿，都是用米做的。在盛产稻谷的潮汕，不但主食是稻米，就连极其重要的供品，也是把稻米变着花样换着马甲，制成了花样繁多的粿品，这简直就是一个天上人间，唯米为大的族群。所以，身为潮人的林伦伦先生最后也忍不住说，其实写成“粿”也无可厚非。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=100639&size=300x300&key=3c0fd30caa1f8431&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_100639\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">上古文献记载的馃，是中原一带以面为主要作物的人们的日常食品。饼食，作为曾经人们最主要的食物，也自然地成为初民们祭拜神明的供品，随着祭祀的仪式化，供品越来越高级和丰富，但是来自初民时代最基础日常的馃品，因其在日常的触手可及，一直保留在民间祭拜的祭品当中。而这种祭品，随着移民们向南方前进的步伐，随着生活地域的变迁，原材料逐步地由麦子转变成稻谷，供桌祭礼上的供品，米粉类制物也就渐渐代替了面饼类制物。“馃”向“粿”的转变，其实正真实地反映了这一段移民史。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=100640&size=300x300&key=e4e217c4d869a277&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_100640\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">每一个潮汕人，都知道“时年八节”，一直以来，潮汕人都过着一种遵循传统二十四节气日历的生活，这是一种与自然天人合一式的农耕社会生活方式与习惯。二十四节气是根据太阳与自然界农作物微妙变换，糅合了古代阴阳学说而成的一种东方哲学。即便到了现代社会，在重要的季节变换节点上，潮汕人依然都要过节，而“粿”往往就是作为时节祭神和祭拜祖宗的必备祭品。虽然在祭品中的地位不像土豪版的猪叠羊，也不像高配置的猪、鸡、鱼“三牲”，但是作为标配的供品，大小节日，家祭族祭，却断断不能少了。这当然是先民们最最朴素的祭祀仪典的遗存，这个道理，后来贵族们将之如实地写入了《礼记》：“夫礼之初，始诸饮食”。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=100634&size=300x300&key=b748858773900c69&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_100634\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">岭东最主要的作物是水稻，因为气候暖湿，冬无严寒，一年可以种两造，这使得太平年代里潮汕平原是驰名的鱼米之乡。战争年代潮汕更是各路兵马所主要争夺的粮仓。稻米之基本和重要，让农耕时代的潮汕人，衍生出了很多与之相关的祭祀仪式，这些仪式在长年累月中融入到了先民们的生活当中，就形成了一种习俗。随着农耕时代的后撤，仪式被淡忘了，但是这种对稻米近乎痴迷的喜爱和依赖，融入了生活当中，做粿拜神与自用，正是这种历史的映射和遗存。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=100655&size=300x300&key=bd1790766938c459&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_100655\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=100657&size=300x300&key=4895e10fca9bd335&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_100657\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">每个重要的时节，潮汕人都会做粿。而且结合了中国传统阴阳学、中医学的原理，甚至通过合理的想象，用潮人特有的脍不厌精的精致主义精神，讲究“时节做时粿”，不同的季节不同的祭拜对象，不同的祭拜事项，要制作不同的粿。在这一点上，汕头本土的潮菜研究专家张新民先生在他的美食专著上有很精彩的著述，推荐大家阅读他的《潮菜天下》。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=100628&size=300x300&key=9b02c4cde00880c2&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_100628\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=100627&size=300x300&key=953e052fcc7cb708&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_100627\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">传统的做粿过程繁复，工艺细致，充分展示了潮汕人精致文化的本色，是否能够做一个雅粿，可是旧时家族考验主妇们能力的一个重要环节。从舂糈开始，到辑粿，到炒馅料，到包粿、印粿、炊粿，都有一系列的窍门和经验值，一个举重若轻的潮汕媳妇，能够独立承担一个家族过年期间所需要的各类粿品，不但美味可口，而且颜值满分，这其中对家庭的投入付出与热爱，正是潮汕女子中国好媳妇的贤惠担当。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=100630&size=300x300&key=24b294e45b6ce48b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_100630\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">祭祀，用最简单粗暴的方式把它解构，就是仪式和祭品。通过进献给神的祭品，用一种仪式来做为人神之间的约定，小民们最初善祷善祝的目的当然是祈福消灾，好好生活。然而神毕竟是人创造出来的一种超3D虚拟的非生物，所以祭品除了在仪式上作为进献，仪式结束之后，依照“为天地惜物业”的做法，自然是要人们把它消化。也就是说献神的祭品，天生的就带着让人神共享的属性。很自然的，这种作为祭品的食物，祭礼过后，先民们就将它们当做神明赐福过的吉祥物，要平均分给宗族或者信众以承荫纳福，这就是所谓的“分胙”。做为潮汕最基本的祭品“粿”而言，更是当仁不让地承担了这种吉祥物的角色。所以从某种角度上来说，粿就是一种纽带，通过进食这种带有吉祥意义的食物，我们与神仙面对面同桌而坐，一起享用的，除了美味的粿之外，也一同获得了吉祥、平安和幸福。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=100629&size=300x300&key=564b53b0c75e2a0a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_100629\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">今天已经是腊月二十七，虽然城里市场上因为居民们需求大，已经有专门的粿店制作售卖过年的粿品，但是在各村各里，还是有很多自己动手做粿的家庭。我小的时候住在揭阳榕城，这是个千年古邑，人称“浮水莲花”。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=100670&size=300x300&key=b889a81ad55d1d40&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_100670\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=100668&size=300x300&key=dcb03f3beb8f07b6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_100668\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">今天已经是腊月二十七，虽然城里市场上因为居民们需求大，已经有专门的粿店制作售卖过年的粿品，但是在各村各里，还是有很多自己动手做粿的家庭。我小的时候住在揭阳榕城，这是个千年古邑，人称浮水莲花。自从宋绍兴年间把县城建在这里之后，历经明清的繁华发展，传统气息已贯穿居民的血脉，昨天下午我寻找各家做粿的图片，“今晚回家做粿”的回复让人血脉贲张。到晚上十点一看，韭菜粿、红桃粿、芋粿纷纷飞上朋友圈，冬夜萧冷，但是如此场面让人心潮澎湃，仿佛回到三十年前。揭阳姿娘擅长做粿，在老一代的潮汕九县之中早就有口皆碑，如今社会高速发展，女子也要上班成为社会人，已不如从前那样有工夫和精力专注于家务与烹调，但是儿时的耳濡目染，言传身教，早就练就一身好功夫，“做粿”这个充满回忆的入口，使她们在忙碌的晚上，卸下盔甲，洗手做羹汤，进入暖暖的家族回忆，这不正是过年的真义吗？</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011787109851.png\" title=\"1460011787109851.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/岭东怒马 &nbsp;图/岭东怒马 &nbsp;黄冠荏</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=100612&size=300x300&key=4c41881ae55e933a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_100612\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></span><br/></p>','2016-02-17 17:08:41',0,NULL,1,NULL,2364,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (323,'【岭东年俗录】围炉过年','201602171709153490.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011799495295.png\" title=\"1460011799495295.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101071&size=300x300&key=ae5f1e90e4eac3a2&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101071\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">今天是除夕，这个日子，潮人一般会说“廿九夜”，围炉。围炉是一个很有意思的字眼。潮学研究专家黄挺先生早年在《潮汕文化源流》一书中提到，围炉是潮汕过年夜的中心活动，包括吃团年饭、发压岁钱、守岁诸环节。这些活动和我们大中国大部分地区的习俗大同小异，但是独独把“围炉”作为指代，其中一定有一些比较特别的原因。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101065&size=300x300&key=b603261dd1deb14d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101065\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">记忆中的廿九夜，家家户户都要吃团年饭，一般团年饭都是家庭聚餐，小时候奶奶家人比较多，这个时候大家围桌吃饭的时候，中间一定要摆上一个“暖炉”，那是像老北京吃涮羊肉那样的大铜炉，中间是一个烟道，里头烧炭，一家人将祭拜祖先的鹅肉，菜肴，加上年夜采办的食材，围坐一起边温热边吃，这样温馨的场景，一直以来，我们都觉得就是“围炉”的来历。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101066&size=300x300&key=327f3f3f01eed73e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101066\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">但是黄挺先生翻出了顺治版的《潮州府志》，一般方志对岁时习俗的记录都是惜墨如金，一字两字的，一般没有代表性的连话都不废一句。但是这版府志里面记录了这样一句话：“除夕，祀先，易桃符。设火井于厅，相围以食，谓之‘围炉’”。黄先生写到，这实在是很能够引起人们的兴趣的。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101067&size=300x300&key=66baadce20a30da3&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101067\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">我们再看七十多年后雍正朝编修的《揭阳县志》，修志者对岁时的记录，“除夕设火井于厅事，席地团坐以饭，谓之围炉”。两相映照之下，我们应该明白，原来围炉最初的意思，是围着火炉吃饭。设火井于厅，然后围之以食，借以守岁。这其中表达了好几层意思。第一是用火，第二是吃饱，第三是家族抱团，第四是已经上升为超能力的先人们的保佑。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101068&size=300x300&key=a9ef331685031b67&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101068\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">“年”、“夕”作为凶兽的故事，我们已经耳熟能详，先民们用这样一种传说，向后代们描述了初民时代生活环境的凶险，以及抱团取暖的生存策略。火作为一种象征，在民俗中除了代表温暖光明，还代表一种力量，这种力量能够让人类获得能量，驱除外邪。虽然由于生活环境的改善，村寨城市的形成，各种工具的进步，已经不像初民们那样幕天席地，朝不保夕，但是火做为一种带有神性的神秘工具，就算在现代社会的今天，不论是北方的“社火”，还是南方的新年游神中，仍然是一种神圣符号的存在，过几天我们在潮汕乡村将普遍见到“跳火”的活动就是一例。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101069&size=300x300&key=7d5261b43877b5d6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101069\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">顺治到雍正年间所记录的这一习俗，在现在西南少数民族村子中依然存在。设立一个火井，相当于现在云南少数民族地区的火塘灶，例如十几年前我去过云南，丽江的纳西族，泸沽湖旁的摩梭族，他们生活的中心就是祖母房中心的火塘，不管是日常的吃饭喝茶还是年节的祭礼聚会等家庭活动，都在此举行。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101073&size=300x300&key=f15211e56a45a93e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101073\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而师法唐宋的日本茶道，茶寮在冬天，都要有一个开炉仪式，专门要在茶室中间设立火塘，以为煮水事茶。潮汕人的厅，是祖先神龛所在，也是平时主人会客议事的地点，在大厅设火井，全家相围而食，这种很仪式化的设计，紧接在祭神祀先仪式之后，带有一种深刻的暗示。在除夕这样一个团圆的重要日子，人们当然可以想象，借助于火的神性，现实中的子孙与天界上已逝先人们一起分享祭品，一起守岁，既是感恩纳福，又有慎终追远，怀念往昔的意味，在熊熊火光中，家族中人获得力量和信心，携手度过这个传说中有年兽攻击的长夜，一起守护人间家族的平安。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101070&size=300x300&key=e04e65991504e68a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101070\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101072&size=300x300&key=9276cc35d7867a03&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101072\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">黄挺先生怀疑这个围炉的习俗是本地原住民少数民族习俗的遗存。但是实际上，作为中原的汉族，一直是保留着这种除夕夜用火围炉的习惯的。著名的东京梦华录记载宋朝时的杭州：“士庶之家，围炉团坐，达旦不寐，谓之守岁。”只不过宋代并没有说吃团年饭。明清以来，全国各地除夕通行吃团年饭，却又很少见到围炉的做法，我们可以看到相近的习俗，只有“焚松盘”，但那是类似于户外燃烧篝火的仪式。所以方志的编修者们，才将这种独特的过年守岁方式特意记上一笔。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101074&size=300x300&key=8e2d78f18b47f239&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101074\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">至于后来为什么这个点火井的习俗没有流传下来，而缩小成为以吃为主的暖炉，这其中的变迁，实在也还是没有办法弄清楚。岭东虽然很少有像上个月底那种低至零度的超级大寒潮，但是过去传统民居多是半封闭式的小院，冬夜天井风大，一家人若要围坐大厅守岁，如果能生个火炉，当然是极好的。前些年初冬的时候旅行徽州府，冬夜吃完饭之后围着炭炉火盆与老乡闲扯，一边煨着番薯，一边喝着米酒，那场景，如果重现在除夕夜，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">一边焙着芋头，将鼠曲粿放在炉边煨软，一边温着春菜煲，啃着卤鹅翅，再找来一片瓦片，让血蚶在火盆上面慢慢开嘴，再烤上两张南澳头水紫菜，斟上两杯小酒，在蚶壳钱卜卜声中，和家里老人唠唠嗑，与远方回家的兄弟吹吹牛，间或拍拍顽劣小儿的屁股，那真真是极好的。人生那么漫长，生活如此多变，如果没有家人这毫无保留的爱与信任，又将何以消此永夜？</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011808373515.png\" title=\"1460011808373515.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文图/岭东怒马</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101062&size=300x300&key=d75eba22f0b23af0&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101062\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></span><br/></p>','2016-02-17 17:09:15',0,NULL,1,NULL,2158,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (324,'【岭东年俗录】英歌拜年','201602171711319268.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011820380142.png\" title=\"1460011820380142.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">我的朋友安静，生活在普宁塗沟乡，这是著名的英歌舞之乡。塗沟雅称泥沟，现在有壮青少三支英歌队，每年正月廿一泥沟村游神的时候，这三支英歌队轮番上阵，全乡沸腾，可谓万人空巷，依稀能够重现古诗中春社夕阳箫鼓不须归的场面。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101171&size=300x300&key=64c87d1cb471689b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101171\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">安静是个摄影高手，他拍摄的普宁民俗民居，场面隽永，经常能够在有限画面里带给人无限的乡愁，那种乡村人文的美感，在他的镜头下，似乎永远带着魔力。尤其对生于斯长于斯的泥沟乡，安静多角度全方位充满感情的记录，更是常常让人激赏。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101166&size=300x300&key=1098013f63cdcd53&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101166\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在好几年前，安静就告诉我泥沟乡大年初一一种精彩的民俗，英歌拜年。泥沟乡是一个民居成片，祠堂众多的超级大村，大年初一一早，矫健的英歌队仿佛从远古穿越而来，带头大哥们敲响英歌槌，发一身喊，飞一般地穿过寨门，旌旗招展，衣襟猎猎，画着脸谱的汉子们排着队列，充满阳刚劲力的踢腿、挥臂、击槌，浩浩荡荡向着村寨中的人家，开始了一年之中的第一场英歌舞。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101167&size=300x300&key=0fa2d10365129d40&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101167\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">正月初一的拜年，是英歌队一年之中最早的活动，据说也是由古传至今没有改变的正月活动。在这一天，参加表演的英歌队员一大早就起床去到集合地点进行化妆，随后天蒙蒙亮大队伍就出发了，开始在乡中各处巡游及受邀表演。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101172&size=300x300&key=4285b37734d430f2&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101172\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这是一个充满仪式感的拜年，广泛流行于普宁一带有英歌队伍的村子里。而初一拜年这个习俗，则是我大中国大江南北同胞们过年的规定动作。让我们还是先回到老县志中去看看古代人们如何过初一的。雍正版《揭阳县志》记：“元旦祀先，馔用斋。祀毕家众以次庆，二之日，祭用荤，族里咸相过，崇饮为欢。”这段文字如此熟悉，完全可以照抄用来记述今天的情形，<span style=\"color:#a0522d;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">两百多年过去，岭东潮人依然原封不动地保留着古人的生活方式，这是一个古风激荡的区域。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101170&size=300x300&key=4f39d1e57d96c7db&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101170\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">除夕与元旦（古人将大年初一称为元旦，立春才叫春节），均为家祭重要节点，因为追养继孝，目的无非是报本追源，潮汕族群以宗族结构为基本单位的强大生命力，正在于不断地在日常生活中重复地强调这点。<span style=\"color:#a0522d;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">初一用素食进行祭拜和吃食，应该是佛教世俗化以后的一种习俗。</span>从仪式上讲，将对先祖的祭礼与礼佛的仪式看齐，提高了虔诚与恭敬度。从生活实际角度出发，从祭品用斋荤的时间间隔，我们也可以从中看到聪明而会过日子的潮汕人，生活是有多么会安排——除夕才享用了一年之中最为丰富的年夜饭，那么初一上午，转吃清淡的素菜，荤素搭配，既避免了浪费，又保证了身体和口味的舒适。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101159&size=300x300&key=b0ac82944ac08a21&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101159\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101158&size=300x300&key=03e9973a5cb51f63&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101158\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101156&size=300x300&key=9a97542e103b77cd&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101156\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101155&size=300x300&key=fcdbc5dabcee77cd&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101155\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">不过不要以为准备斋菜是一件简单的事情，其实初一用来人神共享的斋菜，也是以前我们小孩子嘴馋不已的美食。一般来讲，除夕夜吃完年饭，家里主妇便会准备明天的斋菜，主要是一些油炸的干货。食材有芋头做的，有番薯做的，有萝卜丝的，有的则是用花生米、芋头与番薯合起来做的。做斋菜的料都应该在下午时就准备完毕，让其晾干。炸斋菜时，等炉火生好的时候，放上一口铁锅，注上大量花生油。等油沸时，用这些料子拌以粉浆往锅里一放，它就在油锅里吱吱地冒气泡。熟时，黄澄澄、香喷喷地格外诱人。<span style=\"color:#a0522d;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">有些地方也会在除夕夜里做胶罗糍，初一早上，还会将腐竹、紫菜、豆干在油锅里过油，这顿人神共享的素菜早餐，吃的是另有一番滋味，每年都是在爆竹声中醒来的小孩儿们不可错过的美味。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101154&size=300x300&key=6adf135df92f87c0&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101154\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101157&size=300x300&key=c6c61c58b19e5b3b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101157\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101152&size=300x300&key=b5602a7bab40ecb4&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101152\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101153&size=300x300&key=58ba383c4dff9bd8&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101153\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#a0522d;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">拜完祖先，循例当然是拜年，这是人类社会的必备社交活动，拜年，又称为“拜正”</span>。初一一早，人们起床穿好新衣后，第一件事是自家对拜，往往是后辈先向长辈请安拜年，然后长辈给小孩们压岁钱称“压腰钱”。早饭后，就各自向自己的亲朋好友拜年。因此有句俗谚说:“有心拜年初一二”。 这个时候，城中村里也开始热闹，随着社交圈子的扩大，从亲戚到朋友，以致商业的发展，各种各样的活动也就随着人流的流动而渐次开展。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101169&size=300x300&key=e8aaad0ead20facc&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101169\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">回过头来我们再看看泥沟村里的英歌拜年。英歌这种形式，是搬演水浒好汉大名府故事的一种广场舞蹈。队伍由十二人以上不等，据说最多是一百零八个人以应水浒故事。每位队员须按照水浒角色勾画脸谱，穿扮戏装。<span style=\"color:#a0522d;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">它的起源现在仍然没有明确的定论，但是从其主要在正月游神时节敷演，及其必须勾画脸谱等元素，基本上认为与“傩”有千丝万缕的联系。傩是上古时期一种驱邪的秘术，后来演变为一种具象征意义的仪式。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">泥沟年初一英歌拜年的完整过程，是从除夕之夜的祭神仪式开始算起的。除夕夜，英歌队的领队就要组织队员，素装起舞，前往当地神庙拜地头老爷。 初一早上天未亮时候，英歌队要集中化妆，之后便扛起大旗，击起锣鼓，舞起槌花，游行乡中各处。遇门前挂有鞭炮或提前邀请的人家，大旗点拜，“军师吴用”的“三角旗”挥舞首先穿入，“时迁”紧随，“李逵”、“关胜”等鱼贯跃入，众舞者均需往其内各房中穿行吆喝，然后选择厝座较为宽敞的阳埕或长巷、天井等进行“穿巷”、“打圈”等队列表演，同时领队还送上贺帖——拜年。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101168&size=300x300&key=17887539485063f3&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101168\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这个过程，不禁让我想起宋代《东京梦华录》的一段记载“至除日，禁中呈大傩仪。诸班直戴假面，绣书色衣，执金枪龙旗。教坊使装将军。装门神。装判官。又装锺馗、小妹、土地、灶神之类，共千余人，自禁中驱祟出南薰门外转龙弯，谓之「埋祟」而罢。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这显然就是把宋代的“大傩仪”搬演至泥沟村的节奏，傩所代表的驱邪净土，迎新纳福的象征意义，无疑也是普罗大众所寄望的新年愿景。在环境恶劣的初民时代，人们只能把美好希望寄托在想象中神奇的巫术上，而流传至后世，更多地是利用这种仪式，从心理暗示上增强了社区宗族民众们的信心和凝聚力。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101174&size=300x300&key=c55eadd32289c9d5&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101174\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">至于在驱邪的原始意义之上，更敷演出欢乐喜庆热闹的过节气氛，便使英歌这种形式成为热闹喜庆广受欢迎的过年形式了。既有驱邪纳福的神秘象征意义，又有活跃气氛、敦睦乡谊的现实意义，在几百年的民间流播中，英歌拜年，就和揭阳的青狮拜年，饶平的布马舞拜年一样，成为了岭东潮汕一带最具年味和地方色彩的大年初一景象。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101173&size=300x300&key=6aaf6453abea785c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101173\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#a0522d;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">好了，今天是大年初一，岭东怒马也在这向您拜年了。</strong></span>祝我的朋友们家庭和睦，身体健康，生活幸福。潮人新年见面第一句话，往往是：新正如意，橄榄粒来试。这也是我为什么要在正月在橄榄台持续发这个年俗录的一个原因——<span style=\"color:#a0522d;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">大家一起试橄榄，得吉祥</strong></span>。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011829125377.png\" title=\"1460011829125377.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: small; line-height: 19.5px;\">/岭东怒马&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: small; font-family: Tahoma; line-height: 1.5;\">图/岭东怒马、安静</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵、梅尼</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101162&size=300x300&key=670e1ac0de03ee36&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101162\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-02-17 17:11:31',0,NULL,1,NULL,2253,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (325,'【岭东年俗录】玄武山拜佛祖','201602171712087775.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011840111047.png\" title=\"1460011840111047.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101761&size=300x300&key=f593c1c8a74a34c0&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101761\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">当我打开电脑写这篇文章的时候，正是汕尾市陆丰县碣石镇玄武山的元山寺最为狂热的时候，每年到了年初四零点的时候，都有人数惊人的善男信女从南方涌来，争插头柱香。而这些人，绝大多数都是潮汕人，一度网传，玄武山已经被潮汕人占领，根据我三十几年的生活体验，这种描述绝对是毫不夸张的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101742&size=300x300&key=d205d755b12924c6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101742\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">民间一直流传一句俗语，“玄武山佛祖，显潮州”，或者说“玄武山佛祖，显外山”。这是潮汕人对玄武山趋之若骛的根本所在。说白了，是说玄武山这里的神明，是最灵的，而且还特别指出，在以前潮州府地域的人前来许愿最为灵验。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101745&size=300x300&key=e332ff6e0933c56f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101745\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这当然不是孤例，中国很多地方都有这样的传说，潮汕本土像潮南胪岗的“妈祖”，也是盛传“显外山”，从人类学角度分析，这显然是为了扩大本地神的信仰圈和信众群，而外地信众不可能时时跋涉祖庙，因此所祈求之事也不能事事俱细，灵验的概率自然大大增强。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101746&size=300x300&key=b147f1567f4b9782&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101746\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">玄武山地处偏远，所在碣石镇是一个偏远的海边小镇，但是历史还颇为悠久，是明洪武年间所建的全国三十六卫之一，曾领辖惠州府一带五个千户所，明清是世袭军户制，所辖军户来自全国各地，碣石卫所因其海防地理位置险要，一直以来重兵把守，在多次战乱中是来回争夺的要塞，它的安全与否，是岭东与东江一带平原安全与否的重要保证。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101747&size=300x300&key=a07f1a04e7c8ea2b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101747\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">做为以军户制为主体的一个军队编制，怎样让漂泊异乡的军人们能够安心地以他乡为故乡，建立信仰是一个十分有效的手段。所以从建卫开始，碣石卫的长官就有意识把“玄天上帝”塑造成为本地的信仰中心，经过历代的不断扩修，尤其是在清代禁海回迁之后，更加进入了它的繁荣昌盛的时期，估计“玄武山显潮州”的说法，就是在那个时候开始流传的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101743&size=300x300&key=899fb8d45175462b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101743\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">玄天上帝，就是北帝、真武大帝。这是一个代表北方星辰的神，北方属水，所以又是主管水的神仙，因此在广东陶瓷之都佛山有它一个最大的神庙。屈大均《广东新语》载:&quot;吾粤多真武宫，以南海佛山之祠为大，称日祖庙。其像披发不冠，服帝服而建玄旗，一金剑竖前，一龟一蛇，盘结左右”。佛山自古以来称国中四大名镇，社区发达，人口众多，最怕火患，北帝管水，因此北帝庙越建越大。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101752&size=300x300&key=3983c8d037635a58&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101752\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">北帝信仰是被古代统治者所批准的官方信仰，而且在宋明两代都得到了最高统治者皇帝的亲自推广，尤其在明朝，因为明成祖朱棣从燕王起事而夺帝位，所以找到了代表北方的真武大帝做为他“承天授命”的依据，在全国范围推广真武大帝，有明一朝，北帝信仰经过官方加持，深入到了人民生活的各个方面，至今在潮汕各地乡村都可以看到不少的“玄天上帝”庙，有些因为避讳，跟碣石这里的一样改称“元天上帝”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101754&size=300x300&key=eb53551037cb0856&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101754\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101758&size=300x300&key=37bbd75f37773d78&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101758\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">玄武帝祖庙其实是在武当山，这是一个道教的重要神仙，但是当碣石卫的主事者，为了照顾其母供佛的需求，而将之以佛寺的形制进行建设之后，玄武山就一直以这种奇特的面貌存在了。至于为什么又叫做“佛祖”的问题，那就要提到潮人信仰的心态问题了。岭东潮汕人秉承先祖闽人多神信鬼的传统，自来对各方神明是大度包容，兼容并蓄，所以在信仰方面是相当博爱的。《中国国家地理》有一期报道，我一直认为最能概括潮人民间信仰的特点和心态，“信仰的义子”——潮人对民间信仰，最看重的并非来源族群宗教，而是它够不够“显”，够不够灵验，退一万步说，只要它有“神力”，我们不妨就把它一起摆上神台，多烧一点香总是不会错的。这种实用主义心态，加上佛教在中国世俗化推进的速度和惊人影响力，将道教“武当飞来”的真神，称为佛祖，并且同殿主位而祀，在潮汕思维里是理所应当的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101745&size=300x300&key=e332ff6e0933c56f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101745\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101762&size=300x300&key=fa2b5b680f176b6e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101762\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101755&size=300x300&key=fae011ccce3866b2&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101755\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">然后为什么一定要赶年初四零点这头柱香，聪明的你一定会猜到，对了，因为从年廿四百神上天以后，年初四众神要从天庭回位，这个“老爷”开工的第一柱香，是多么的可口愉悦，神同此心啊。但是其实以前潮汕人去拜玄武大帝，真正的目的还不在于此。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101750&size=300x300&key=6be380aeb6161a0a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101750\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101753&size=300x300&key=9a42dfc3eaa395a1&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101753\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">玄武山佛祖的灵验，并不简单停留在口头上，每一个去玄武山的信众，都带有一张“红帖”，里面写着家里人的生辰八字，到玄武山奉上祭品之后，便要在神前摇签筒。玄武大帝的神性就附着在这小小的竹签之上。这也催生了玄武山庙外一排的解签的行当。每一个签都会对应着一页诗，里面从家族运势到婚姻到事业，包罗万象，是你未来一年的人生指南，因为全用七绝形式表示，而且全部用戏文里头的典故，所以也叫“签诗”。玄武山庙里出版一本灵签详解，那是每年我们都会去庙里买来的，当签生们把摇到的竹签诗卦号用毛笔写在红纸上，由进香的人毕恭毕敬带回老家的时候，这种仪式感，比起神的承诺，更要让人感动。何况玄武山的签诗真的是导人以善，常常叫人远小人亲君子，要小孩子少近水火，时不时地还关心本地小神的生计，要求信众时不时拜奉，这种友善周到的大神，叫潮汕人如何不爱它呢。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101756&size=300x300&key=14a5b3d9285d1118&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101756\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101757&size=300x300&key=7fc2096a45458bb4&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101757\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101751&size=300x300&key=5e6b810456657499&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101751\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101748&size=300x300&key=14e217467465813a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101748\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011853100229.png\" title=\"1460011853100229.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">图文</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: small; line-height: 19.5px;\">/岭东怒马</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: small; font-family: Tahoma; line-height: 1.5;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵、梅尼</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=101739&size=300x300&key=b4d30b5c07b484d5&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_101739\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-02-17 17:12:08',0,NULL,1,NULL,2391,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (326,'【岭东年俗录】 乡里闹热 ','201602171712502577.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012027461085.png\" title=\"1460012027461085.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">仔细观察中国人的过年习俗，是一个很有意思的时间表，从年廿四到初四是属于家庭的，所以安排这段时间众神上天，自己也得以专心处理家族祖先各种祭祀祈福事项。而到了初四，“老爷落天”，就意味着更为广泛的社区的公共事物的职责和任务来了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102287&size=300x300&key=5f18c29f4755c640&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102287\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">所以在潮汕，年廿四到初四这段时间，是没有人拜神的，主要的重心放在了家族家庭这里。村镇社区的神庙，不免有点门前冷落。讲究点的大庙，好像揭阳城隍庙，这段时间就会在大门贴上封条，说明“上天觐见”，贴心地告诉大家大神不在家，有事初四后再来。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102288&size=300x300&key=71539ead2df96182&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102288\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">但是这是爆发之前的平静，在年初四一番接驾忙活之后，岭东乡村马上就要开启另一个模式，在此后长达两个月的时间里，乡村城镇宛如按动骨牌，一个人神共乐，争奇斗艳，全民出动的民间狂欢节，在这片古老的土地上将华丽丽地次第展开。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102269&size=300x300&key=e3200289a477c2a6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102269\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这就是口耳相传的“乡里闹热”。“闹热”本义就是热闹，潮语中经常有倒装用法，例如“拖鞋”称“鞋拖”，“台风”称“风台”之类。“闹热”已经成为一种专用名词用来特指乡村里这个特定的日子，在这个日子里，潮人要游神、拜神，要请戏，要组织各种仪仗队伍，包括标旗、大锣鼓、潮乐队、英歌队各种游乐节目纷纷粉墨登场，《揭阳县志》说，五日以后乡人傩，谓之禳灾。天启间，士民赛扮故事，备极华丽，以迎关帝、城隍，遍历街巷，以后每岁皆然。乾隆版府志更直接记道“九邑皆事迎神赛神”，当时潮州府下辖岭东九县，游神赛会遍地开花，不但乡里，府城县城一概“闹热”无极限。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102270&size=300x300&key=37658896402fe9cc&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102270\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102271&size=300x300&key=39bb419ea5bc9eaa&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102271\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102272&size=300x300&key=69cfb12ead96faf3&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102272\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102273&size=300x300&key=304dbd00a8508a7f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102273\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102274&size=300x300&key=b75df5648d225237&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102274\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102275&size=300x300&key=3bd46aef563abf5c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102275\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102276&size=300x300&key=3e73ff210f0bb87a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102276\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">正月里的“乡里闹热”，游神是重头戏。潮人管游神叫“营老爷”，“营”字又是一个古化石般的语言，只有在上古典籍里，而且还是专门记载祭祀的志书里，才会用到它的本义，“祠之兆域”。《诗经》说苍蝇来回飞是“营营青蝇”，潮人口语里现在还有“营来营去”这句话，形容没事拿着东西走来走去。这个字考证起来有非常仪式化的内涵，但是在潮汕乡村就直指“游神”，游神需要按照固定的路线，要围绕乡村城镇的边界、农田溪流游行，这一种仪式，是典型的巡土安境，净土驱邪的上古祭“社”的遗存。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102277&size=300x300&key=6d19a58501bba5b2&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102277\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102278&size=300x300&key=047e114615a1bd07&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102278\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">“社”就是土地之神，春社本来就是宋明时期普遍存在的乡村以祈谷祈福为名，村民们结社分胙以纳福的一个日子。这个日子除了祭祀求福的仪式化意义之外，更因为它的聚餐饮宴，团圆社交功能，而渐渐成为一个民间欢乐的节日。在民国以后，北方的春社渐渐式微，但是南方的赣闽潮一带，则依然保留了这种形式，而且根据每一个村子自己的具体情况，灵活地确定了自己村子春社的日子。在潮汕地区，相邻的村子有一起过春社的，更多的是错开的，这种错开有些是有意识的，更好的发挥了联谊的社交功能。因为从本意来讲，祭祀土神，然后分食拜祭的祭品，这是一种“纳福”的象征，邀请外村的亲朋好友一起来获得神明的降福，无疑是一种善意的举动，而错开春社的日子，又增加了一次到别村做客宴饮的机会，感情就在这热热闹闹的你请过来，我请过去的节日里愈发深厚了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102279&size=300x300&key=d0877845b6e6edc0&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102279\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这就是岭东潮人的“食闹热”。我们知道的，潮汕是鱼米之乡，和平年代在饮食方面又是出名的食不厌精，所以在“乡里闹热”这一天，每家每户都拿出最好的特产，广邀亲朋，尤其欢迎远方来客，甚至生疏不拘，我多年来在各村社日游荡记录，经常被好客的乡民拉进家里共进家宴，推杯换盏之后，时常有种穿越宋明的错觉，不知今夕何夕。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012036140253.png\" title=\"1460012036140253.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道 &nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">图文/岭东怒马</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102266&size=300x300&key=c711c4a75ba33b7b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102266\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-02-17 17:12:50',0,NULL,1,NULL,2368,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (327,'【岭东年俗录】七样羹','201602171714299289.png','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012054238353.png\" title=\"1460012054238353.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">今天是正月初七，从昨天开始，市场上蔬菜的价格上涨到了顶峰，某些叶菜的价格已经比猪肉还要贵。这个原因一个是因为上月底潮汕遭遇百年不遇的大寒潮，菜地蔬菜受冻减产，春节期间菜价普遍都上涨。还有另外一个原因，是岭东习俗，正月初七家家户户都要吃“七样羹”，即要做一种由七种蔬菜杂在一起的蔬菜杂烩。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102422&size=300x300&key=f1fb1b816f359920&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102422\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">从现有的文献来看，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这是南朝宗懔《荆楚岁时记》记载的荆楚地带的习俗。</span></strong>因为正月七日，在古代是一个节日，这个节日很有意思，居然是人类的生日。三国的董勋列举了初一到初七是各种生物的生日，与西方上帝创世纪惊人的相似，然而董先生的记载并没有什么依据，可能也是从《东方朔占书》这些阴阳家处抄来的，占卜书上说，七日为人日，八日为谷日，这天晴和阴。可以判断未来一年对应的运气怎样。反正到了<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">清嘉庆二十一年刻本《华阳县志》就这样记载：“七日，古为人日。彩胜、菜羹之俗，今不复闻，惟相传是日晴主人民安。”</span></strong>可见清朝年间，很少有人搞七种羹了。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102423&size=300x300&key=5e6052df40787b81&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102423\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">华阳在四川，编志者没有见过，却不代表失传了。岭东就恰恰保存了这个七样羹的年俗。这里的“羹”只是菜的意思，并没有我们现在词义里勾芡带有点汤水的做法。而且岭东也并不只是潮汕人吃，梅州的客家人也在人日吃，他们与榕江流域一带，直接就叫做“七样菜”。这种习俗的起源及其意义现在还未有确定的考证，人日为什么一定要吃菜，这还是一个谜。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102424&size=300x300&key=c51faef270b3f194&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102424\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在岭东能将这个古老的年俗保留下来的一个原因，一个当然是这里的气候因素，冬无严寒，尚有新鲜应节蔬菜可以出产，代表了这里的宜居程度。另外一个则是和人们新年喜欢好口彩的喜庆心理有关，像“七样羹，七样羹，大人吃了变后生，奴仔食了变红芽”，“芹菜”寓勤劳，“蒜”寓有钱劝等等，这种吉祥寓意和生活必须环节一结合，非常贴近岭东潮人的心理习惯，就像净土宗教人念佛号，各种神庙多神信仰一样，只要吃吃有寓意的蔬菜，来年相应美好的愿望就一一能够实现，这种实用主义消费观，一直是潮人姑妄听之，姑妄从之的很多习俗来源之一。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102425&size=300x300&key=345af9f0ec4ee50c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102425\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">为什么七日才是人日而不是其他，这个涉及到“七”这个数字在中国神秘的重要地位。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">大部分学者现在认为，七是中国古人一个代表生存生殖的数字，而之所以选择它，和月亮盈缺的七天周期密切相关，中国历法是根据月亮运行的太阴历，而从这里推演出的二十四节气，全部都是以七为基数。</span></strong>中国人依赖农耕为生存之本，所有生存的基本，要依赖于“七”这个基数，所以从某种意义上可以说，正是七天这个周期，才有人类生存的基本空间和支持，所以在先秦阴阳学家们看来，“七”这个数字是人之本。于是才有后来班固在《汉书•律历志•上》的说法：“七者，天地四时，人之始也。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102426&size=300x300&key=dbadba8018698830&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102426\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012064478943.png\" title=\"1460012064478943.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">图文/岭东怒马</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102419&size=300x300&key=5feef0c07af6893e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102419\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></span><br/></p>','2016-02-17 17:14:29',0,NULL,1,NULL,2286,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (328,'【岭东年俗录】特殊潮汕民俗 月浦出丁头','201602171715134447.png','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012080115665.png\" title=\"1460012080115665.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102606&size=300x300&key=dcae058ff9a81b71&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102606\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">正月初八，汕头市月浦村一定是地球上最早醒来的村庄之一。凌晨四点，这个古村里，头戴礼帽身穿老式长袍的年青人，在家人簇拥下，唰唰唰地走过街巷，前往灯火通明的太保爷宫前。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102607&size=300x300&key=0ff82c949292917d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102607\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这一天是村里一些家庭一生中意义非凡的大日子，因为村里习俗相传，每一家有男丁年满24岁，就必须在这一天遍请宾客，同时在村里国王庙前集中进行献祭，祭品必须有全猪和全羊，称为“出丁头”。为了这一天的仪式，每个有“丁头”的家庭，都会遍请亲朋好友助阵，从初七开始，一直到初八卯时，热热闹闹举办一场民俗盛宴。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102608&size=300x300&key=c17ff4d4ff885d03&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102608\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这一传统习俗，以前是代表着农耕时代对男丁、壮劳力的重视，体现一种宗族传承。而发展到现在，则更加重了“成人礼”的意义，增加了家族之间互相支持团结，敦睦情谊的因素，同时也成了月浦村闻名遐迩的一张民俗名片。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102605&size=300x300&key=c20a96877d9e9914&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102605\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">月浦这个年俗，是离汕头市区最近的一个颇具特色的节日，固定在每年初八举行。月浦村的历史远长于汕头，现在是汕头市腹地的一个村子，地处潮安县与汕头市交界之处，东临梅溪河，在水路运输时代，扼守潮汕门户。月浦佘氏是鳄浦都一带的强宗大族，一村而有二十座佘氏公祠，仅此已足见其家族之宏盛，加上处水陆要塞，故昔有“上至府城，下至海坪，七都无敌”之说。古代家族强盛，首重男丁，所以月浦村出丁头的习俗本身就有检阅族中子弟兵后备力量的含义在内。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102614&size=300x300&key=209bdb69b2d85122&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102614\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">出丁，是中国传统宗族社会的一项大事，不孝有三，无后为大，因为在以前他代表了宗族实力，代表着宗族未来强盛的基础，是传宗接代的大事。所以中国农耕时代男丁出生之后，必须入祠拜谒祖先，大宴亲朋，以示庆贺。潮汕一般来讲都是在元宵前后举办，由前一年生了男丁的家庭举办，称为“食丁桌”。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102602&size=300x300&key=bdf4d1c43e81ad12&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102602\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">但是月浦佘氏家族的“出丁头”仪式显然有更深一层意义。虽然不清楚24岁这个年龄是出于何种传统确定下来的，但是一个这个年纪的男子已经完全具备成为一个家庭主力的资格与实力，佘氏家族举办这个仪式，除了一般意义上的庆贺与感恩之外，我想肯定还希望得到神的赐福，赐予家中未来支柱实力与幸运；同时让宗族里的年轻一代们第一次成为主角站到祭礼中心，既召集家族中的亲朋与社交圈好友，宣告“社会人”的角色正式启动，同时也开始参与宗族大事，从此成为充实宗族实力的一个基石。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102609&size=300x300&key=22cfcffd099d4fc1&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102609\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">所以月浦村这个习俗值得注意的是这个献祭的仪式。这并非简单的家祭或者族祭，报告祖先的一家一族之事，这已经是在向神界，对外界进行的一个宣誓，是全族、全社区的一个重大公共事件了，因此必须使用全猪全羊进行献祭。这就是古代祭祀的“少牢之礼”。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102612&size=300x300&key=93a931e0e807435d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102612\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102603&size=300x300&key=4f00e66656af57f4&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102603\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">祭礼在中国古代是非常重要的事情，春秋之时，甚至说“国之大事，在祀与戎”，因为祭礼是用来确定秩序的，而且通过神权来确定，在古代中国对民众来说，是比国家法令还要有约束力的约定。用来祭祀的牺牲也是有讲究的，天子祭祀是猪牛羊称“太牢”，次一等级的祭祀者则用猪羊，所谓“诸侯社稷皆少牢”。自明嘉靖朝允许民间修建以前代表诸侯士大夫才允许的宗祠以后，少牢就是民间祭典中最隆重最高等级的祭献了。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102613&size=300x300&key=bf9e53a019b011f6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102613\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102615&size=300x300&key=2aa8686e261e10f5&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102615\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">月浦出丁头仪式的最后，是为23岁的准丁头们举行“受丁头”仪式，从这一天开始，“准丁头”的家里就要专门饲养用来明年献祭的猪或托人来养，这又是一种严格遵循周礼的行为，因为古代“始养之畜”是要经过特别饲养——就是所谓的“牢”——变成“将用之牲”的。这种十分繁复和讲究，并且无法速成的仪式，本质目的只有一个，就是证明仪式本身的极端重要性，说明仪式背后所代表事情的重大程度，同时通过这种种繁复的要求训练求祭者们的能力——这种心情和做法，我们今天当然感同身受，孩子就是一个家庭的未来和希望，虽然我们今天已经远离宗族时代，仪式或者已经简化甚至淡忘，但是仪式心里头那个愿望和祈求神秘力量帮助的遐想，每年高考每个家长不就似曾相识么？</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102616&size=300x300&key=d29182153c71d945&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102616\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">月浦出丁头祭典最后的高潮，是在凌晨吉时到了之后，把被神明们加持过的，带有福祉的祭品从祭礼现场撤离的时候。不知道是什么开始流传说，谁最先到家得到的福气越大越足，因此我们会在天刚亮的时候突然看见水泄不通的庙前广场，突然让出一条道来，各家邀来助阵的亲戚好友此时各发一声喊，抬起几百斤重的大猪，背着全羊，争先恐后地跑出祭祀广场。这是人们又把这个祭典称为“跑大猪”的一个原因。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102617&size=300x300&key=f26837429368c130&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102617\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102618&size=300x300&key=76c2ad77dd0ff24c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102618\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">但是这种说法显然是有悖宗族合祭的本义的，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">祭祀纳福是要分享，而并非争夺，虽然几百年来丛林生存法则的存在，残酷地说明了争夺是一个事实。但是就好像做为主持这场祭典的村里老人组，不断通过喇叭告诉大家不需争先恐后一样，作为中国传统文化来说，神权只是对秩序的一个封印，不管如何神秘，最核心的诉求，都是要保持日常生活的道德秩序。礼失求诸野，这些已经遗失在野的礼俗，其实只是为了提醒我们，克己复礼，尊重规则，才是人类最终的幸福所在。</span></strong></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012089144113.png\" title=\"1460012089144113.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/岭东怒马 图/岭东怒马 肖徽兢</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=102579&size=300x300&key=d28fc052f44d7808&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_102579\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-02-17 17:15:13',0,NULL,1,NULL,2331,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (329,'【岭东年俗录】初十 营灯与烧龙','201602171715467156.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012103113999.png\" title=\"1460012103113999.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮谚说，“正月灯，二月戏”，传统的岭东区域，正月“营灯”是遍布城乡的一个重要场景。“营灯”与元宵灯节既有关联又不是全部，说有关系，是上元灯节是全国性的节俗，在正月十五张灯是自汉唐以来的传统。但是岭东地区的“营灯”习俗，却又明显与游神有关。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103601&size=300x300&key=ba435b453c1fcba4&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103601\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">前几天我们说过，潮人管游神叫“营老爷”。“营”是带有礼仪古义的古语，之所以要确定是这个本字，是因为潮汕人同时有“营灯”之俗。“迎”“攍”这些普通话同音字，在营灯这里都完全不适应，只有这个祭祀专用的本义，带着“绕境”“畛域”这种象征着神明巡视其统治区域的“营”，才极其准确形象地描绘了这种场景。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103605&size=300x300&key=9da36108638eab96&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103605\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮语如同文言，用精炼的一个字表达了非常丰富的场面。所以“营灯”，就是在夜里提着灯笼，抬着神明，继续沿着白天营老爷走过的路线，穿街过巷，沿着乡村、社区的边缘绕境巡游。这是乡村社会的大事，事关祈福禳灾，基本上是全员要参与，而在夜色与灯笼的氛围下，往往晚上的“营灯”，比起白天带着热闹游乐队伍的“营老爷”，又另外呈现了一种不同的景象。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103619&size=300x300&key=47d7535d6f7aafec&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103619\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">营灯是要全村人紧紧簇拥着前进的，有些村子还要边走边喊，一条长长的灯龙，一句句嘹亮的口号，在社区此起彼伏的爆竹中，呈现出浓厚的生命力。因为夜的神秘未知，如同外界生活的多变与考验，只有通过家族与社区的抱团和温暖，以及代表坚强内心力量的“神”，才能与之抗衡。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103614&size=300x300&key=3da8b3b36c7f481a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103614\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在这种仪式风俗里面，“灯”是一个重要的元素。灯有很丰富的含义，岭东潮客区域都一样，把“灯”视为“丁”。岭东的灯笼是竹子编的圆柱型灯笼，灯笼外蒙油纸，要写上姓氏郡望，有很明显的宗族寓意。男丁是古代家庭和宗族兴盛的基石，之所以会形成这种普遍的营灯习俗，这是重要的一方面，尤其在宗族和乡村方面，当夜晚看到村路上络绎不绝，连续不断地游灯场面，自然会欣慰于本村本族的兴盛。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103607&size=300x300&key=5e9cdbe46e73d505&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103607\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">第二个含义是关于“火”的作用，相信原始的绕境是直接用火的，因为火一直是光明战胜黑暗，神圣驱逐外邪的神性力量，这也是为什么白天巡游一次之后，夜晚还要有一次神明出游的原因。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103608&size=300x300&key=c548f82d08b7eba5&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103608\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">直接用火来绕境净土驱邪，在岭东也有一些村子到现在依然保留这种习俗，好像正月初六揭阳阳美村，村民手举火把巡游；黄冈河流域的饶平龙眼城，练江区域的沙陇兴陇乡，也在他们闹热的社日晚上有点火巡游的习俗。更多的村子选择直接烧火堆，并且用全村大小跳火驱邪的方式来表达对火的崇敬与信赖。而更高级的玩法，则是象丰顺埔寨和今天晚上在揭阳的乔林一样，烧火龙。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103613&size=300x300&key=abaa06bda8dc2a61&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103613\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">乔林乡是一个始创于宋朝的古村落，由林氏先祖宦游落籍创建，位于榕江北河边上，与揭阳县城中心毗邻。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">乔林过去称古乔，地饶物阜，殷实富足，到明清时代已经发展成为望族聚居地，并且人丁兴旺，甚至已经进入到县城落籍分枝。潮汕历史上两状元之一的清武状元林德镛，就曾附籍于古乔林氏在县城榕城西门的宗族之处，所以其高中之后，位于乔林的林氏祖祠便高挂状元之匾，以示荣耀。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103616&size=300x300&key=40d031c345ac4af8&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103616\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103617&size=300x300&key=b7c84a39b511f19d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103617\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">乔林既以官宦之家落籍，又财丁两旺，成为一个超级大村，那么在长期的家族发展中，如何保持一个稳固的社会秩序，是古代宗族社会致力解决的大问题。利用礼仪作为凝聚的核心是肯定的，那么作为重要节日的仪式，就会起到事半功倍的作用。这个是烧火龙在乔林乡盛行并且保存到今天的一个内在驱动。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103618&size=300x300&key=2f4fa29f5164290a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103618\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">因为烧龙是一个非常复杂的表演。虽然过年在大中国的很多地方，舞龙舞狮子助兴，是很普遍的传统节目。但是舞龙是一个集体项目，在武术基础上更需要团队组织，因此必须是人口较多的大村或者城镇，而且还需要有强力的组织作为支撑才能玩得起来。烧龙则更厉害，所谓烧龙是指在龙的身上绑上烟花，舞动游走的时候点火燃放，既需要强大的经济实力，又需要有靠谱的安全保障，才能让这种看上去无比绚烂和辉煌的火树银花场面年年重现。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103609&size=300x300&key=dad7c2d7aea93c84&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103609\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103615&size=300x300&key=46380e8051e28c3c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103615\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103610&size=300x300&key=2234f02165b21047&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103610\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">所以首先在仪式含义上，烧龙与营灯是一样的，都是跟随着神明出游的队伍，而龙作为高配的吉祥物则使仪式档次规格更高。当巡境结束之后，插上烟花的的龙进入指定地点，先向乔林乡的主神双忠圣王叩首示意，然后由推选出来的村民进行点火，在烧龙埕上绕地上围成一圈的点燃的烟花绕圈奔跑，这是类似另外一种“送香船”驱邪的仪式。乔林执行烧龙任务的是村里的壮汉，这些汉子们必须头戴竹笠，脱光上衣，只穿短裤，竹笠上放一张神符，生僮打扮，这些流程与做法都是象征着净土驱邪，是为了让“烧龙”有信仰意义上的存在基础。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103612&size=300x300&key=3f800a7bb4d3f94e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103612\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在这个基础上，乔林乡秩序管理者们便根据人神共乐的游神精神——这是让烧龙活动不成为人们精神负担的做法——逐渐丰富完善烧龙活动游乐元素，所以今天我们看到乔林烧龙，不但要烧四条龙，而且还有两只凤，还有鲤鱼，这样难度系数少了，参与的人多了，场面更热闹了，时间也更长了，围观的远近村民就更多了，除了敬神辟邪的心理需要之外，又满足了乡里人的自豪感，增强了乡里人协同合作的感情和经验，也让乔林烧龙成为远近闻名，兹兹在念的话题，乔林乡强乡大族的印象从此深入人心。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103611&size=300x300&key=e61f87d763362905&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103611\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103620&size=300x300&key=47d572e41a75d7eb&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103620\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103621&size=300x300&key=dc2f79b7483fa9e6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103621\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012113356389.png\" title=\"1460012113356389.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/图&nbsp;&nbsp;岭东怒马</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103598&size=300x300&key=adc51fa26343ac6b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103598\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-02-17 17:15:46',0,NULL,1,NULL,2224,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (330,'【岭东民俗录】正月十一 行头桥','201602190910393441.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012125140352.png\" title=\"1460012125140352.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103929&size=300x300&key=7c7ef39bfebf6c51&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103929\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">今天是正月十一，今暝在榕城古城是万人空巷的“行头桥”日子，榕城人手拿榕枝竹叶，沿着古城中心小巷绕走，城内各街巷早已挂满标旗，装灯挂彩，尤其是西马路尾石狮桥一带，更成为人潮的中心，榕城人纷纷以走过石狮桥，亲手摸摸桥头的石狮，为新年吉祥祈福为乐，现场人山人海，欢声笑语一片，业已成为近年来太平盛世图景中的一幅元宵民俗佳景。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103931&size=300x300&key=56e7162b9c692212&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103931\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103930&size=300x300&key=60dfc8b81b3ca59b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103930\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">榕城是古揭阳县县城，这是一个有近千年历史的古城。自南宋绍兴十年把邑治定在这里之后，历经各朝代发展，建成了一个人称“浮水莲花”水系纵横的岭东水乡。榕城内水网交错，池塘遍布，榕江南北两河围绕古城，连通南北河的是称为“三滘”的水系，古榕城三滘六桥，四通八达，以前围绕城墙还有护城河，古时在内河可摇橹行船来往，风光旖旎，不下现今驰名的江南水乡。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103941&size=300x300&key=3ac24322af9f19e4&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103941\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103940&size=300x300&key=3b5fcebe11a17b13&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103940\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">有溪就便有桥，因此上榕城桥也特别多。仅明代崇祯年间就已经有石桥24座，更有无数木板小桥。这其中石狮桥是相当特殊的一座桥。石狮桥地处北滘，本名叫北滘桥，为挡直路之煞，在桥头立有一头石狮，久而久之大家就称之为石狮桥，石狮桥其实特别的短，非常不起眼，但是因为它地处南北滘河的中段，是榕城地理位置的中心，这也是行彩桥大家为什么必走这条小桥的原因。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103934&size=300x300&key=b3dc5464d724f746&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103934\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">“行彩桥”这种形式，其实并非是揭阳的创造，它的历史也不是特别长久。雍正版《揭阳县志》岁时篇记上元：“妇女儿童度桥投块谓之度厄，或采青拾瓶嘴以归，取义宜男”，顺治版《潮州府志》记上元“妇女度桥投块，谓之度厄”。这种行桥过运，以求平安的习俗，现在虽不多见，但是在明清两代，却是北平帝京元宵时候最流行的事情！</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103936&size=300x300&key=e84330ed132b2544&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103936\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">明代沈榜《宛署杂记》说：“正月十六夜，妇女群游，祈免灾咎，暗中举手摸城门钉，一摸中者，以为吉兆。”正月十六日都会「过桥走百病，灯光徹夜。元宵灯市，高楼珠翠，毂击肩摩。」明刘侗、于奕正《帝京景物略·春场》:&quot;八日至十八日……妇女着白绫衫，队而宵行，谓无腰腿诸疾，曰走桥。&quot;</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103933&size=300x300&key=1f4388e9b09cfaea&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103933\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这就是明中叶开始在京城风靡一时的元宵“走百病”习俗，明朝极重视元宵节，国家层面规定放假长达“十夜灯”，以京城为代表的大城市彻夜玩乐，民间一片狂欢气氛，妇女也在此时解除平时的束缚，走出家门，“妇女相率宵行，以消疾病，曰走百病，又曰走桥”。男男女女在一片欢乐气氛中看灯看景看人，成就了多少才子佳人的故事，也把整个元宵的狂欢节属性推向了高潮。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103935&size=300x300&key=e599d459bc68dc29&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103935\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">上行下效，做为流行中心的京城走百病和走桥的习俗至此开始向全国传播，流风所至，江南水乡首当其冲，于今尤留下嫁娶走三桥的习俗。在明代中叶得到大发展的潮州府当然也会受到波及，更何况明代嘉靖万历年间潮州科举盛极一时，嘉靖甲辰、崇祯戊辰年科举，揭阳均有四人同榜登科，风头一时无两，民间盛传“御街呾白话”，这么多京官，对此京城流行年俗在本地之推广亦在情理之中。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103932&size=300x300&key=54ca13b5beaf5239&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103932\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在走桥习俗当中，我们也注意到“摸门钉”的细节，明代刘侗《帝京景物略》记走百病的时候，妇女们“至城各門，手暗触钉，谓男子祥，曰摸钉儿。”清代《北京岁华记》亦说，“妇女俱出门走桥，不过桥者云不得长寿；手携钱贿门军，摸门鏁，云即生男”。这应当就是今天榕城行石狮桥时摸石狮的源头了，带着求子祈嗣的愿望，我们一再分析，是宗族时代的头等大事，所以这是一个全社会公认的正当理由。而当行桥习俗流传到潮汕，没有门钉可以摸的时候，静静坐在那里已经等待了多年的“石狮爷”，自然义不容辞地顶起了班。所以“摸狮耳，生阿弟”这种朗朗上口的顺口溜，就此流传到了今天。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103938&size=300x300&key=fbefab6e54519058&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103938\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这真是一个神奇的时光入口，今天的榕枝竹叶依然青翠，今暝的笑语响彻千年。那羞涩思春的大姑娘们会挤在人群中悄悄说：“行桥中，嫁雅翁”么？那高大的小帅哥们挤到石狮肚前，手上牵着的可是去年桥上遇到的要娶的雅嬷？来吧，朋友们，正月十一的今暝，让我们在石狮桥穿越明清！</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012133114731.png\" title=\"1460012133114731.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/岭东怒马&nbsp;&nbsp;图/黄薇</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103924&size=300x300&key=45ccec22513c5c3d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103924\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-02-19 09:10:39',0,NULL,1,NULL,2210,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (331,'【岭东民俗录】人神共乐','201602221011117904.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012144463538.png\" title=\"1460012144463538.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104618&size=300x300&key=ed54a8a9077d1d9d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104618\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">岭东正月过年时候的年味，集中体现在每个村子的“营大老爷”活动中。我们说过，“乡里闹热”是每个乡村过年期间的大日子，这个日子是由唐宋“春社”活动发展而来的，当然这其中经过明朝初年“里社”制度兴废变革，产生了一些变化。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104624&size=300x300&key=a248bb1709198bf1&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104624\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">岭东潮人族群乡村社会在明朝时期逐渐形成了现在所看到的基层组织，以宗族与神庙为基本架构搭建的组织体系，在这个体系之上发展的乡规民约以及道德规范，是独立于国家管理单位之外的颇为牢固的结构，乡村宗族社会根据它自由的惯性，配合国家单位进行运作，这种结构跨越了战乱和改朝换代，是中国封建社会长期存在并发展的主要原因。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104620&size=300x300&key=0aa587ae2d03d8b9&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104620\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">闹热的主题是“营大老爷”，土神的祭祀而称作“营大老爷”，是因为祭祀过程，必有巡土安境的仪式。照潮汕人通常的说法，营老爷分文营和武营两种。文营的做法，是在祭祀仪式过后，将老爷请上神轿，由选定的丁壮抬着，仪仗鼓乐前导，后面跟着游乐队伍，巡遍社区的每一条巷子，再绕社区的边界游行一圈， 回到神厂。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104622&size=300x300&key=9bd672f25bda79a8&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104622\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104623&size=300x300&key=dfcc6ea03b799b55&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104623\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">武营的做法，将神像捆紧在神轿上，做好疾跑的准备，营神到了特定地点，丁壮们抬起神像，发力奔跑。这些地点，有些是在小巷，有些是在宗祠阔埕，有些是在村外的田洋。尤其是在进入各个祠堂接受祭拜，还有巡游完毕“老爷”回庙的时候，更是群情汹涌，潮汕人把这种做法叫做“走老爷”——潮州话的“走”，是跑的意思，这又是一个文言古语。不管是文营还是武营，其原始意义，都在净土驱邪。不过，这一宗教仪式对于每个社区，实际上又有着整顿社区秩序、强化社区治理的功能。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104619&size=300x300&key=b3c030e1b873222f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104619\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">村庙主神出游，从仪式是模仿封建时代帝王或高级官员出巡的样子，讲仪式、讲排场、讲热闹，规模较大的游神巡境不仅要有足够的财力支持，而且还要有足够的人力与组织能力才能将游神活动搞好。整个游神巡境活动基本就是一次社区居民大动员，村民们不仅要出钱，而且还要出力，因为游神巡境需要众多的志愿人员才可能将之完成。通常一个游神队伍组成部分主要有：鸣锣开道队、标旗队、童男童女队、娱乐队、锣鼓队、潮乐队、神轿队、耆老队等组成，另外还有指挥、放炮、安保（维持秩序，负责防止火灾与打架斗殴）等人员，其中以娱乐队最为庞大，由鼓乐、歌舞、舞狮、舞龙、英歌等分队组成。这些队伍中，大部分都由本村居民充任，义务制，没有任何报酬。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104625&size=300x300&key=dcd43f8d5cb69a91&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104625\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104627&size=300x300&key=5d72b7f7f0e5470c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104627\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104628&size=300x300&key=3d00d293a6c5a1d4&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104628\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这是“乡里闹热”之所以长盛不衰，让人乐此不疲的群众基础，如果没有神像与神轿的话，这完全就是一次娱乐大游行。营大老爷通常娱乐队伍的人数基本上是总数的一半，活动在要求达到神圣性的同时，也要求达到娱乐性，这就是所谓的“人神共乐”——而我们分析过，“神”其实就是人的内心。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104629&size=300x300&key=3d8eda4f7c1a0267&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104629\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮汕民间表演艺术种类和团体非常多，这些大都数是因营老爷的需要而组织起来的。村庙游神巡境组织者或花钱雇请，或自己组织，在一次营老爷中必须有多支民间潮乐队、曲艺队、各种舞蹈队。而在岭东乡村，为了增强本村的凝聚力，扩大影响力，以及出于锻炼体魄的尚武精神，出于面子和底子的双重考虑，尤其是人口较多的大村，这部分的内容大多自己组织演出，时长日久有些也成为了村子的名片，例如英歌、各种动物舞蹈队等等，同时也成为一种职业，以供其他没有队伍的村子聘请助兴。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104631&size=300x300&key=9fcada42e528ba2b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104631\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">因此，在“营大老爷”活动中，可以说集中了民众所有的技艺和活力，也托付了全部的记忆和理想。举办“游神赛会”，包涵了建筑、工艺、美术、厨艺、游艺、戏剧、杂技、音乐、舞蹈、傩艺、特技，包括装饰、绘画、剪纸、面塑、表演等各个流派，涉及布置、组织、统筹、协调、联络等社交技能，而且必须体现公平、公正、公开的原则。钱财必须“取之于民，用之于民”，一定做到“收支上墙”。每年换届的“理事会”，是群众绝对信赖的组织。老百姓从“游神赛会”的组织工作中可以发现人材，举贤任能。各个家族要在“游神赛会”中争取荣誉，以提高自己家族在社区的威望和地位。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 19.2px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104621&size=300x300&key=25d632ce258b7806&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104621\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104630&size=300x300&key=714acbc09c3fe9b2&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104630\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这就是中国传统乡村“游神赛会”在岭东的样子。在现在“游神赛会”朝着展示民间习俗、民间艺术、民族文化的方向发展。如何融入现代社会，这方面，同在东亚文化圈的日本与马来西亚，已经有了非常好的样本，日本的“妈祖祭”“关帝祭”等等，在传统保持与继承，在神秘的扩张与克制等等方面，都做到了相当好的平衡。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104632&size=300x300&key=c651c4f8552e27a5&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104632\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而大马的柔佛新山，这个华人移民社会，把正月二十日的游神，办成了一个世界闻名的狂欢节日，并且延续几天，同样是我们现在需要借鉴和学习的先行者。在现代秩序与年味之间，在未来一定有一个更好的平衡和呈现，而岭东一隅，完全有这样的基础和能力。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104626&size=300x300&key=dcbeaca55deecf06&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104626\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">今天的随笔引用了隗芾教授的观点和文字，隗芾教授以北人而致力研究科普潮汕民俗多年，实不简单。不意于大年初五仙逝，谨以此文向其致敬。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012168890155.png\" title=\"1460012168890155.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/图&nbsp;&nbsp;岭东怒马</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104617&size=300x300&key=0895b0b767978165&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104617\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-02-22 10:11:11',0,NULL,1,NULL,2259,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (332,'【岭东年俗录】庶民的历史','201602221011597626.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012183429457.png\" title=\"1460012183429457.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">最近几年影像来源渠道多了许多，而社会也有了足够的宽容度，所以在网络上我们也看到了很多以前看不到的民间习俗，这些习俗因为涉及“怪力乱神”，即便在古代社会，国家层面上也一直不予鼓励，甚至是禁止，但是在民间一直有顽强的生命力，存在是否合理，我们暂且不予深入讨论，但是从人类学角度去剖析这样的民俗，当然有助于揭示真相，同时人类学一直指出，信仰是社会的再现和集体表征，民俗作为一种长期存在的仪式，它的背后也隐藏着渐不为人知的历史真相。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104764&size=300x300&key=7f7ad82f89c78657&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104764\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104765&size=300x300&key=d11d18c14b7fc4cc&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104765\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这些习俗集中在过年期间举行，典型地区是粤西雷州半岛一带的“年例”，福建兴化平原上的莆田，以及台湾一带以福建移民为主的地区，通过被称为“乩童”的自称能与神明沟通的“灵媒”而来展示一些人类所难以做到及忍受的节目，例如穿金针，打刺球，上刀梯，滚钉床等，从图片及视频看到，这些节目为了宣示神力，同时还有血能辟邪的说法，往往表演的乩童自残身体，搞得头破血流，颇有些血腥狰狞，现场有几分恐怖，而所谓的神迹，则是往往节日过后，乩童们就若无其事，这就是所谓“神上身”。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104766&size=300x300&key=c72fdfe222dcdf7b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104766\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">实际上，这是古代巫术在民间盛行历史的遗存。很巧合的是，上述几个地方都是闽文化圈影响很大的区域，古代人说八闽，是信巫淫祀，当然讲的就是这些地方盛行巫术。那么做为深受闽文化影响的岭东，尤其是潮人有很多族群有着莆田中转迁移而来的历史，民间当然不可避免会受到这种巫术盛行情况的影响。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104767&size=300x300&key=6b38ee15fa226228&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104767\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这种影响首先遗存在口语上。我们将这种法术称为“老爷上身”，而做这种职业的人叫“同乩”，其实就是童乩的潮语白读。 还有一个经常使用的俗语“三牲敢食，钉球敢搬”，形容胸有成竹，既然敢拿人家好处，就有能耐把“搬”钉球这样普通人不能做的事办好。“搬”潮语读【波鞍6】，就是甩动的意思。而所谓的“钉球”便是订满尖利铁钉的大木球，这就是莆田习俗中打刺球流传到岭东的样子。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104768&size=300x300&key=1ba185db1996c291&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104768\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104769&size=300x300&key=d63a2e64504e8146&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104769\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">光绪版《海阳县志》曾经记述岭东此种风俗说：“其祠庙庵观，无一乡一都不有。每有所事，辄求珓祈签，以卜休咎。有曰降乩者，自称为人禳灾，咒水出符……至登刀梯、卧钉床、走火路等事，多属不经，为可粲耳。”显示在过去岭东潮人区域，有与上述地区一样的盛行巫术的一段历史，只不过因为岭东人文相对昌盛，受儒家正统学说影响，官吏与乡绅阶层均秉承“子不语怪力乱神”，对此种有破坏社会秩序风险的事情持反对批判态度。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104770&size=300x300&key=65e76042caa9462d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104770\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">但是我们翻阅文献，就会发现，其实搬钉球，坐刀轿，爬刀梯，这种种奇闻怪事，其实也不是无水之源，种种迹象，都指向了中国道教的一个支派——闾山派。闾山派是以符箓法术为主的一个道教支派，它曾经广泛流传于赣闽浙粤，虽然在官方的道教体系中不属主流，但是在道教世俗化的背景下，它却因为与民间生活联系最紧密，而成为对民间影响最大的一个道教支派。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104771&size=300x300&key=b4c1de6e51a107ee&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104771\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">闾山派原本是江南巫系中的闽越巫法，结合了福建民间女神陈靖姑信仰之后，产生的一个在民间影响很大的巫术体系，尤其在福建闽西一带影响颇大。后来因为宋明禁巫，闾山法转而接近道教，吸收了道教中灵宝派与茅山派的符咒科仪，渐渐固定下来成为道教的一支。因为他们这一派所作的科仪符箓，与老百姓生活息息相关，所以一直以来顽固在民间生存，只不过因为它涉及巫术的怪力乱神，所以经常以神秘习俗的面孔出现，例如在岭东潮人乡村，现在依然流行入宅要举行“净油火”辟邪，这种种科仪便是由闾山派的“红头师公”来主持的。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104772&size=300x300&key=69c117151fc760f1&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104772\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">通过研究闾山派的来源以及科仪，我们就能够相对清晰地分析这种看似荒诞不经却顽固生存在民间的习俗。而通过研究闾山派，我甚至发现，它与岭东的人文存在着千丝万缕的联系，这方面到现在其实还很少有学者研究涉及到。例如为什么在潮普惠这种民性相对彪悍，我们普遍认为社会风俗比较男性化的地方区域，却流行女神崇拜，很多地方乡村的主神都是“阿妈”，这显然与闾山派的女巫崇拜有关，闾山派又称“夫人教”“三奶派”，崇拜临水三夫人。还有感天大帝许真君，为何在普宁一带乡村突兀地成为主神的问题也便迎刃而解，因为闾山法祖，正是东晋道士许逊。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在神秘难解的背后，它是一个历史变迁的载体，我们可以通过它还原一部正史中看不到的中国民间历史，这个世界不但是铭记丹青的英雄史，同时也应该是像你我一样平凡的庶民的历史。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104763&size=300x300&key=cdfff84b24072834&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104763\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">现在依然有举行出乩民俗的有揭阳渔湖的庵前村，而上刀梯、坐刀轿的有过几天的浔洄村，峡山的上东浦，惠来靖海，普宁一带的乡村等等。今天正月十三，轮到庵前闹热了，让我们一起去回溯庶民的历史吧。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012192483074.png\" title=\"1460012192483074.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/岭东怒马&nbsp;&nbsp;图/岭东怒马&nbsp;&nbsp;安静</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104760&size=300x300&key=8b377dbf6f420c1e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104760\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></span><br/></p>','2016-02-22 10:11:59',0,NULL,1,NULL,2185,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (333,'【岭东民俗录】老爷保呵大营灯','201602221012364699.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012205604854.png\" title=\"1460012205604854.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104905&size=300x300&key=d49c9f343e5c407d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104905\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">来岭东过元宵，没有看过这段时间乡村的营灯，就等于白来了。城里例行公事的花灯，各种现代化灯光装饰的大型灯屏，只是闪烁着工业化千篇一律的霓虹，虚假而毫无生气。所以我们要走出去，走向原乡，走向村庄，那里保存着几百年来的生命力，用一盏盏宣示生命的手工灯笼，用温暖灯火下映红的张张笑脸，告诉你人文的魅力；用热热闹闹的上灯，走老爷，跳火堆，营灯，给你一个充满张力并且热血沸腾的元宵。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104906&size=300x300&key=8a168f8d07d8cae7&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104906\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">一般营灯的程序，是每家每户提着灯笼到社区主神庙或者游神的神厂神像前，祭拜之后把庙里的火请到自家的灯笼，点着带回自己家里。这个过程也有叫做上灯的。有些地方是新婚或者刚生男丁的族人，要把灯笼挂在庙里或者宗祠里。有些村子在老爷回宫的那一天黄昏时分，村里人集中提着灯笼过来请灯，这些灯笼仿佛用人工延续了白天的光芒，带着村民们新一年的祝愿，用温暖的桔红灯光，点燃了村里的每条小巷。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104917&size=300x300&key=ee9ad39b79d0c945&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104917\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">从正月初七开始，澄海隆都各个乡村，就开始营灯了。从褔洋到鹊巷，从前沟到后沟，沿着韩江南北溪次第展开，一直到十四十五达到顶峰。后埔乡则是全乡人点着灯笼跟随老爷夜巡，在安路边点燃稻草，熊熊烈火中映照着代表着人丁的营灯队伍，充满了满满的温情。而后沟乡背靠韩江，营灯过程要走上江堤，早春的寒风唤醒了寂寞的夜，乡人沙沙的脚步声延续了百年。那一年我跟着营灯的队伍走了两个小时，当老爷回到大宫的时候，我一回头，突然就又看见了现在也还很年轻的潮学学者陈景熙博士，当年还不是博士的陈博士已经是多次与我在澄海各村营老爷现场不期而遇，如今他在厦门高校任教，已很少能在灯火阑珊处抬头见到他憨厚的笑脸了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104907&size=300x300&key=61407d526a0ed8f6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104907\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104916&size=300x300&key=39da92124a4d2170&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104916\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">最壮观的是在大长陇。大长陇位于广东省普宁市东部军埠镇，有记录的人口约7万余，是全国人口第一村，全村皆一姓陈。大长陇灯笼除了姓氏郡望之外，写得最多的是“千子万孙”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104909&size=300x300&key=30935ab7ded8cc6c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104909\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">正月十四十五这两天晚上，在东门埕神厂前请灯的长龙漫山遍野地蜂拥而来，在黄昏的蓝色天幕下显得极度壮观，让人叹为观止，彼时彼景，真的会怀疑是不是天上真的有决定一切的神，否则如果不是这“千子万孙”的祈求得到神明首肯，又如何能够有现在这般人丁兴盛的大乡旺族？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104910&size=300x300&key=bebf839cf4da772b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104910\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104911&size=300x300&key=ef5880a229e4c71c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104911\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">大长陇十四十五暝的营灯他们称之为“呵灯”，原因是当晚请灯结束之后，村里老爷要集中巡境，村民们在整晚的营灯营老爷过程中，要边游边高声吼叫“老爷保呵”，在寨子里每个宗祠前面的阔埕，要点长串的鞭炮，在炮声中老爷轿要发力奔跑，要在宗祠面前把老爷轿用力上下摇动，这是一个热血沸腾的过程，人和神的关系在这场类似玩耍的过程中得到了更好的亲近，而之中又总是有些什么特别的东西让人感到心潮澎湃。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104912&size=300x300&key=9ad5af686cd80a97&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104912\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104913&size=300x300&key=3fdd55871fd1064a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104913\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">一百六十多年前，大长陇村陈娘康与北山村许阿梅互相呼应，发动了一次席卷潮普惠的农民起义，义兵围攻潮普惠三县县城，震撼潮州府。清政府调动潮惠两府兵力全力打击，两年之后义军失败，陈娘康阵亡。清军围剿大长陇，村民散寨而逃，全村被夷为平地，这个时候是咸丰六年。如果你知道这段历史，你就会明白这个现在允称全国人口最多的村庄，是有着怎样坚强和蓬勃的生命力，在一片废墟之上发展到现在绵延不断的灯龙，你就会明白他们自发排着队拿着灯笼，用“老爷保呵”这种充满爆发力的吼叫里面蕴含着的不屈和坚韧，这是一个永远挺着脊梁，不会低头的族群。这是一个百折不挠，生生不息的群体，这就是最典型的岭东潮人代表。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104914&size=300x300&key=eabbf5abe250c669&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104914\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104915&size=300x300&key=5a50b4e08dde642e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104915\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">今天十四，岭东各个村子营灯已经进入如痴如狂的地步，从南至北，由东到西。不论是在豪放粗犷的南下地区，还是朴质平实的饶客山区，就连一贯被人认为斯文克制的原府城地区，与潮州市区一路之隔的枫溪，这一夜也是彻夜狂欢，营灯上灯，打秋千，围着大榕树走老爷，欢吼声通宵达旦。而沿着韩江、榕江腹地展开生活的村子，则一支支随村里主神巡营村境的灯队，或静静怀思，或群情激昂，或锣鼓声声，或鞭炮不绝，火光四射，人流涌动，融入于斯，吾土吾乡的原乡情怀必然挥之不去，这是民俗绵延千年不绝的原因，也是族群认知高于血缘的中国情怀。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104918&size=300x300&key=f91b78c5f14c4a81&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104918\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104908&size=300x300&key=da5306a1e8f60f0f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104908\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012213480837.png\" title=\"1460012213480837.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道 &nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/岭东怒马 &nbsp;图/岭东怒马 &nbsp;安静</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=104919&size=300x300&key=9e5cf41ebc28a745&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_104919\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br/></p>','2016-02-22 10:12:36',0,NULL,1,NULL,2370,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (334,'【岭东民俗录】 蹈火而来','201602231027238864.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012226986804.png\" title=\"1460012226986804.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=105494&size=300x300&key=89f981160bef18a9&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_105494\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">今天正月十五，元宵佳节，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">作为时年八节中最为欢乐的节日，元宵是中国人最放松、最热闹、最具吉祥意味的一天</span></strong>，自从唐睿宗先天二年开始由皇室掀起观灯的节目以来，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">千百年来，各大城市火树银花，市民们纷纷走出家门，观灯戏耍，宴乐达旦</strong>，正所谓金吾不禁，玉漏相催，东风频放花千树，一派普天同庆，其乐融融的场面，潜意识里也是表达了人类辛苦开发管理这个星球，并在和平盛世里对成果的享受。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=105510&size=300x300&key=ab74b553551cce33&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_105510\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">燃灯来源于佛教</strong>，北宋高承《事物纪原》考证，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汉明帝时开始有正月十五燃灯的习俗</span></strong>，那时候皇帝刚刚派人去天竺取经，带回两位高僧，并且修建了白马寺。而徐坚《初学记》则推测，这与汉武帝祀太一烧火祭天的仪式有关系。并且举出了周礼祭天的记载“乃燎于上帝，告以天命”。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=105487&size=300x300&key=6318419851923eb7&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_105487\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">不管是哪一种来源，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">用火来获得光明，得到温暖，是人类共同的祖先记忆</strong>，而同时，人类还觉得火可以驱除污邪，洁净周围，尤其对超出人类认识能力的一些能量，人类总是臆想用火可以进去消灭和对付<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">，因此不论是在国家层面，还是民间范围，在重要的节日里，都有烧火仪式这一环节</strong>，周礼记载那时候，公务员队伍还有一个专门负责这个环节的岗位，叫司“烜”氏，要求他“凡邦之大事，共坟烛、庭燎”。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=105492&size=300x300&key=e07aa43713178b5e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_105492\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">做为岭东潮人社区，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">元宵夜一直存在两种不同的方式</span>，或者我们可以这样说，那是一个硬币的两面，一面是象《荔枝记》那样的，陈三五娘才子佳人，府城花前灯下的盛世文雅的元宵。而另外一面， 则是广袤乡村下，原始张狂，让人热血沸腾，充满尚武精神的用“火”来构造的狂放元宵。</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=105489&size=300x300&key=e3dd47a43781bcb7&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_105489\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在榕江练江上游一带的乡村，元宵前后流行跳火的习俗，村人称为“跳火煲”。</span></strong>是在村间游神经过的安路，更多地是选择村中的空阔地带，一般在宗祠的大埕，或者庙前的空地，用稻草堆起，候营老爷队伍巡游经过，则组织点火，营老爷队伍则发一声喊，众壮丁抬起神轿，快速冲刺跳跃而过，场面非常刺激，让人热血澎湃，而有些村子神轿众多，有些村子跳几次都不过瘾，村民围观喊叫，神轿往复来回，火光熊熊，群情汹涌，这是岭东一处极度有观赏及参与价值的过年习俗。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=105495&size=300x300&key=6325d2ea3e0c2fb9&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_105495\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=105496&size=300x300&key=d511f4fb651a9b7c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_105496\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">至于在民间烧火何时演变成为一种仪式，现在尚未考定。</span></strong>不过留存到今天的，以莆仙一带的跳火，摆棕桥为源头的闽人正月跳火习俗，应该是岭东潮人跳火的源头。莆田一带在除夕夜要在家门口烧火堆，一家大小要跳过去辞旧迎新。而到了泉州府一带，则称为“跳火群”，从形式上看和岭东已经相当接近。都是夜里巡游的营老爷队伍最后一个环节，也是最为高潮的环节，很多地方在抬着老爷跳过火堆之后，全村人不分老小，也纷纷一展身手，跨火而过，这时候的跳火堆，又变成了一个欢乐的娱乐节目，欢声笑语充满乡村。至于烧剩下的稻草，也有村人争相捡拾回家的，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这又成了一个纳福的象征</strong>，初春的元宵夜，便从人神在公共区域交流而延续到每家每户中去，圆满完成了新年的纳福和祝愿。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=105497&size=300x300&key=f126f11443e05e10&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_105497\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这几年我辗转于各个乡村记录，每次得到有跳火堆的信息，总有抑制不住的冲动，因为我第一次在曲溪横山，看到漆黑夜幕下我们的乡人仿佛从洪荒黑暗之处蹈火而来，熊熊火光映照坚毅脸庞，那种对弱小心灵的冲击永世难忘。而在普宁典詹、玉窖，潮南兴陇，揭阳锡场，在巨大火堆旁情不自禁随着乡人狂声呼吼的畅快，放下所有心魔负担跃火而过的狂放，完全可以成为今天城市人解压的最佳选择。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=105507&size=300x300&key=3e27f80dc58391cb&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_105507\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=105508&size=300x300&key=468b936589793b70&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_105508\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这或许是一个你毕生难忘的童年记忆，又或许是从你未知道的全新世界——但是它已经在城市平静的暗夜那端热闹了几百年。不是说年味越来越淡吗，不是说过节乏善可陈吗？<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">请跟我来，去过一个肾上腺素勃发的正月十五，春天，它来了。</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=105511&size=300x300&key=e66dedde1da16e8e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_105511\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=105512&size=300x300&key=f61fde0d0dd3849c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_105512\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012235101563.png\" title=\"1460012235101563.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道 &nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/岭东怒马 &nbsp;图/岭东怒马 &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵 沐木</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=105514&size=300x300&key=841d353e7d00c2df&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_105514\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br/></span></p>','2016-02-23 10:27:23',0,NULL,1,NULL,2329,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (335,'【岭东民俗录】正月初九 拜天公','201602231054596748.png','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012249135498.png\" title=\"1460012249135498.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103326&size=300x300&key=ed4a90f6a69db4a7&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103326\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">正月初九，天公生，岭东民间相信这一天是“天”的生日。对天神的崇拜是一种原始崇拜，远古人类对于无法抗拒的自然力，产生敬畏心理，所以举凡天地日月星辰，都要拜祭。那么随着社会的发展，自然的威慑力随着就减弱了，由于求同心理，代表着对自然力的原始崇拜就渐渐被改造，人们创造出相对应的偶像和故事来代表，这称之为神的“人格化”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103327&size=300x300&key=b6eec863a0b0151f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103327\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">对“天”的崇拜在民间也是这么样一个演化过程，但是“天”的地位太高，所以在国家层面和民间层面是有不同的。古时历代帝皇都要祭天，这个天，是没有人格化的，称“昊天上帝”。后来道教从南北朝时梁陶弘景的《真灵位业图》开始产生玉皇，到了艺术家宋徽宗先生的时代，可能因为喜欢这个逼格很高的名字，宋徽宗直接就把他当做天帝的人格化偶像，自己也搞了个像在皇宫里祭拜。之后的皇帝大多不是很喜欢宋徽宗这个创意，所以也没有在国家层面继承下去。但是这个“玉皇大帝”与天帝结合的做法从此流传民间。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103330&size=300x300&key=f7f61ab2b1541c93&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103330\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">作为中国本土宗教的道教从善如流，从那时起便不断在自己系统内修改玉皇大帝的位置，再加上后来《西游记》等民间小说的推波助澜，这个修为虽然不是最高，但是权力地位最大的“玉皇逆袭记”从此成功统治民间信仰系统，成为中国大部分人民心目中的天帝。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">明代王逵《蠡海集》“神明降诞，以义起者也。玉帝生于正月初九日者，阳数始于一，而极于九，原始要终也”</em></strong>，解释了正月初九为什么是天帝的诞辰，和“人日”一样，都始于中国文化对神秘数字的解读。一最初而九最大，这不正是天上人间最高统治者最好的八字么？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103334&size=300x300&key=5b24fe6e3313a3cd&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103334\" width=\"206\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">不过在潮汕，天帝是没有偶像的，这个和国家层面保持了高度一致，可能潮汕人并不是很认同这个传说。唯一人格化的元素，就是称之为“天公”。作为祭拜的对象，在寺庙大门前，一般置一个座，称“天恩公”，或者与土地合称“天地父母”，在家里则置“天宫炉”，挂在天井与大厅之间的门梁上。每月初一十五，以及年末谢神都要祭拜，正月初九天公生也是祭拜节日，但是规模不大，只是各家各户进行例行的拜祭而已。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103329&size=300x300&key=1f178ec070eed1fa&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103329\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">天公位高权重，但是人间思维，九五之尊当然不管凡人蚁民小事，所以拜神的时候，敬而远之，潮汕拜神实用主义出发，祈求名利者，天公未必有空去赐福，也造成小民们也不会去在他面前狂热虔诚，许愿下注。总之磕个头烧个香就好，要祈福还是找具体经管的大神，这或许导致了潮汕拜天公习俗渐渐简化的原因吧。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103328&size=300x300&key=4bf57eb3b5f3b841&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103328\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">但是在闽南泉漳，正月初九天公生是一个很重要的节日。漳州天宝玉尊宫每年在初九凌晨集中拜天公，一样是用民间最高等级的少牢之礼，今天凌晨400多头大猪和羊在玉尊宫广场摆成方阵，几千人从子时开始祭典，场面宏大。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103335&size=300x300&key=e1569f63f18af110&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103335\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103337&size=300x300&key=c482bdcd98e34e8b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103337\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">从祭典上来看，因为是祭祀最高神，还用上了磔雄鸡、祭毛血这种更为古老的祭礼。漳州是潮汕民系移民的前站，很多习俗相近相似相应，但是像“天公生”这种似乎应该是最重要神明的仪式，却被简化成例行公事，这其中的变化其实也是研究漳潮民间社会历史的一个入口。前几年我去成田镇的西岐村探访他们出名的英歌队，村民跟我说他们最闹热的时候就是正月初九子时“天公生”，这个与漳州的习俗一模一样，可惜的是到现在为止我还没有机会亲临现场，也就没有办法比较一下两地的一些异同了。至于其他的潮汕乡村，元宵临近，已经全副身心在准备重头戏，“营灯”了。</span></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012257104567.png\" title=\"1460012257104567.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道 &nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/图 &nbsp;岭东怒马</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></p><p><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=103331&size=300x300&key=64094cd07f1e5d0f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_103331\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-02-23 10:55:00',0,NULL,1,NULL,2305,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (336,'【岭东年俗录】趭香船与忌平安','201602290842118349.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012270784039.png\" title=\"1460012270784039.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">虽然十五已过，但是这两天晚上很多村子依然继续举行营灯大闹热，朋友圈一片红火，舞龙跳火，营灯走安，岭东乡村大地上依然一片欢腾，可能因为元宵节还需要祭拜祖先，所以有很多的村子把一年一度的乡里大闹热放在了十六，尤其是一些人口比较多的超级大村，所以每年正月十六，我都纠结要前往哪个地区，实在是诱惑太多，选择太多，每一个都让人目不暇接。&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=106636&size=300x300&key=7ce9d3fbd116eb07&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_106636\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这其中有很多村子都会举行一个甚为神秘特殊的仪式，“趭香船”。“趭”潮语读【而夭7】就是赶的意思，“香”字白读为【何洋切】，音如“乡”。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: medium; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.5;\">香船是一只用竹子编成的鱼，因为为了要装乡人放置的香烛和大金锆丝等冥纸，所以中部肚子的位置会做得特别的大，和潮人在海边见到的“乖鱼”一样，乖鱼就是河豚，所以又叫“趭乖”。各种地方鱼的形状会有差别，潮南一带海边鱼头会做得很凶猛，像张着大牙的鳄鱼，所以他们那边又叫做“妖船”。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=106637&size=300x300&key=2221b73836bc384d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_106637\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">香船一般随营老爷的队伍巡村，走过街巷的时候，各家各户先会用纸钱和香支在家人身上拂拭，象征把邪气和厄运扫掉，然后放到香船的鱼肚子里。营遍全村后，把香船与老爷神像放在村里的活动中心，很多村子会举行一个仪式，象征把秽气驱除。像潮南兴陇村，会有一个带着斗笠的老汉，手持铁剑，一剑刺进妖鱼的嘴里，然后围观村人齐声呼喊，一队人马簇拥着把香船赶出村去。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=106638&size=300x300&key=c39794ee65650e38&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_106638\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">揭阳霖磐桂东村则把趭香船这个环节塑造成为夜晚游神的高潮。在十六夜里吃完饭后，村中主神庙前燃起一个巨大的火堆，掷珓选定一位“老爷”出来驱邪，赶着香船绕着火堆奔跑，左三圈右三圈，现场烈火熊熊，锣鼓阵阵，村人吼声震天。桂东这只香船非常巨大，看起来像一条粉色的巨型鲤鱼，要几个人抬着才能跑动。桂东是揭阳城郊一个大村落，十六那晚场面非常壮观，围观人群里外三层，仪式之前庙外竖一面大鼓，一个大汉有节奏的敲击，有如两军交战，让人热血沸腾。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=106639&size=300x300&key=b42327d0868a0b41&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_106639\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">从趭香船整个的形式与意义来看，这就是古老的“送瘟神”仪式。因为医疗条件不完备，以及对瘟疫爆发的恐怖心理，是人类尤其农村极度担忧的心头大患，送瘟神仪式过去在中国大部分地区都普遍存在。毛泽东解放后还曾赋诗“借问瘟君欲何往，纸船明烛照天烧”，显示对这种民俗仍然记忆犹新。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=106640&size=300x300&key=bc295dcd3c036fec&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_106640\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">对瘟神的崇拜历代官方均视为“淫祀”，大概是因为它渲染恐怖，易于被人利用影响社会秩序。福建一带对瘟神崇拜一度非常盛行，福州人拜五帝，“王爷”就是瘟神的人格化，拜瘟神最后要送“王爷船”，《闽杂记》载“扎竹为船，糊以五色绫纸。。。至海边焚化”。泉州、厦门一带的瘟船还是木制的，乾隆《泉州府志》载：“以纸为大舟，送五方瘟神，凡百物皆备，阵鼓仪仗百戏，送水次焚之。近竟有以木舟具真器，用以漂于海。”送王船后来越搞越大型，厦泉一带用木船装载各种生活用具，竟然漂过海峡来到台湾，1901年台湾苗栗县就发现了泉州漂过来的王船，那时全台轰动，以为神明显灵，前来参拜者络绎不绝，甚至建庙供奉，因此台湾一岛供奉“王爷”的神庙多不胜数，堪称岛内第一。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=106641&size=300x300&key=f614667d11b1aff6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_106641\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">岭东潮地什么时候把船改成鱼尚不得而知，但是这个仪式的指向是很明确的。有记载以前趭香船的时候，村民还要沿途向其扔掷石块，这个环节其实是更为古老的石神崇拜的遗留，投石除了显示对瘟神的打击之外，更因为石头是远古人类的圣物，人们认为可以靠之祈吉驱邪，是有神性的武器。这在我们前面说过的行桥度厄形式中也有出现，现在岭东曲溪行跃龙桥妇女过桥仍然会扔石块到水中。但是这种明显带有危险性的仪式很容易误伤趭香船的队伍，我一直以为早已经过改良，没想到写这文章的时候，安静传来一个视频，潮阳古埕居然到现在还依然有投块，实在不得不惊叹民俗惊人的顽强复制能力。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=106642&size=300x300&key=8cdebee04e75e2fe&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_106642\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">趭香船最大的目的是送走晦气，所以一般在仪式做完之后，是要送出村寨进行处理的。处理的形式一种是顺水飘走，一种是取火燃化，这就是所谓的“祓禊”——或濯于水滨(薛君《韩诗章句》)，或秉火求福(杜笃《祓禊赋》)。因为是送邪除灾，所以送香船出寨之后队伍一般默不作声，民间相传不能说话不能回头，其他人最好也不要撞见，因为要把邪气瘟神赶走，所以香船出了村寨之后，就要关闭寨门，这便产生了另外一种神秘的习俗“忌安”，也有称为“忌平安”的。这些做法在年复一年与不可预见的顺与不顺的新一年年景相结合，使得有些村子更发展为到“忌安”这一天停止所有社交活动，闭门谢客，甚至不允许外村人进村，因为涉及到村寨的运气大事，所以愈发神秘，即便是到了现代社会，也仍然有宁可信其有的村落保持这一神秘的古俗。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=106737&size=300x300&key=bdf9bae9ea2ab147&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_106737\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=106738&size=300x300&key=0683b772ae65b1b7&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_106738\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">当然对比闽地的民间信仰情况，潮汕地区明显的摒弃了很多神秘因素，这体现了岭东民性灵活多变的一面，对于影响生活和秩序的一面，会自觉不自觉的进行了改造，这就是所谓的迷而不信吧。桂东村趭香船那一夜，我跟随着队伍跑到村外的农田，在田埂上看耆老们在灯火下掷筊许久，最后终于把香船在指定稻田里焚化，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">黑暗之中，一股火焰冲天而起，看着象征灾祸不吉的香船，在火中化为灰烬，那一刻心里头真是有一些轻松和庆幸的，这或许和史前人类是感同身受的吧。</span></strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#8b0000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=106643&size=300x300&key=bfead02de111b883&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_106643\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></strong></span></span><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012277699954.png\" title=\"1460012277699954.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/ 图&nbsp;&nbsp;岭东怒马&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=106647&size=300x300&key=2ff4d4315ef61272&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_106647\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-02-29 08:42:11',0,NULL,1,NULL,2185,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (337,'【 岭东民俗录】正月二十 畲族祖图','201602290843094856.jpg','<p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012294463710.png\" title=\"1460012294463710.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107094&size=300x300&key=9b9e1382ef686ec8&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107094\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">正月二十，是所谓的“天穿”节，这是客家人过的节日，与女娲补天穿的上古传说有关。而这一天也是石古坪畲族村民们的“圣”日，他们有“正月二十作田工，不够补天穿”的俗语，因为这一天是他们祭拜远祖以及接待客人的重要节日，这明显受到了客家和潮人的影响。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107100&size=300x300&key=e223f15f2f6be735&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107100\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">石古坪位于潮州凤凰镇山区之中，地处凤凰第三高峰大质山山腰。凤凰山是中国畲族的祖山，据说畲族就发源于此，这也是岭东地区唯一的少数民族，主要分布于凤凰及邻近的饶北山区。从现在的情况来看，岭东凤凰山区域的畲族已经和汉族没有什么两样，因为本身并没有文字，唯一的口语“畲话”也早已很少使用，近客家区域则主要讲客家话，而近潮汕区域则讲潮汕话，有些两者都讲，与“半山客”毫无分别。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107096&size=300x300&key=0db91b30a982b590&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107096\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">唯一能够让他们特立独行于现在社会的，让人想起他们还是一个不同于汉人的民族的，就是在他们的节日，正月二十这一天的祭祖。石古坪村民要去祖祠缅怀他们的远祖及民族来历，这就是石古坪有些神秘的“看祖图”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107095&size=300x300&key=814c6268be1717cb&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107095\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">畲族始祖盘瓠是一头神犬，畲族把盘瓠传说绘成卷轴式的长图，称为《祖图》，世代相传，每逢祭祖，就悬挂出来，供族人奉祀祭拜。这是一种很原始的图腾崇拜，用图画形式来记载表现祖先来源与功绩，称为画传。画传用最通俗的形象表达，同时通过《高皇歌》等民间歌谣的传唱，最大限度地表现了畲族始祖盘瓠生平事迹的传说，易于为群众所接受，尤其是在文化程度较低的畲族社会中，具有强大的影响力和感染力，对于一直生活在偏僻山区，以“刀耕火种”艰难生活的畲族人来说这是最好的祖先教育。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107102&size=300x300&key=b9f8badf9a3dc6d3&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107102\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">石古坪的祖图上书“祖像流芳图”，这幅十多米长卷精致地描绘了传说中的畲族始祖龙犬从出世、成长、揭榜、立功、开基创业到繁衍子孙的传说故事。每年正月二十“拜祖”时，“祖图”就会拿出来挂在村里祠堂，供全村人瞻仰。石古坪是畲族的发源村，因此这里的祖图有着不一样的象征意义，村人均说现凤凰山区七个畲族村保存的祖图，都是来自石古坪这张祖图。据说原先村里一直保存着两幅古老的“祖图”，一幅已经被北京博物馆收藏。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107104&size=300x300&key=eb40a542cb860c7c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107104\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">凤凰山是全国畲族人认为的的祖山和发源地之一，畲族的独特民族服饰“凤凰装”跟凤凰山也有着千丝万缕的牵连。从文献史料的记载上和专家学者的调研分析中都可以看到，各地的畲族同胞的祖先有很多都是在不同朝代由于战乱、饥荒等原因从广东潮州凤凰山直接或间接迁徙出去的。虽然现在畲族村在岭东一带非常少，人口也不多，但是历史上本地带的畲族，曾经有过一段强盛的历史。尤其是宋元之交，以畲族为骨干形成了抗元的主力畲兵。后来战死现今饶平钱东镇的百丈埔许夫人，就是畲兵领袖，这段历史在民间演化成著名潮剧剧目《辞郎洲》，至今尤在搬演。由于畲兵为岭东抗元主力，宋亡后被元朝压制遣散，本地畲族由此散入山区，向外迁移。畲族擅唱歌谣，潮人口语尤将方言歌谣称为畲歌，本地潮剧中也仍然留存有畲歌唱调，可见畲族一度与汉族在岭东一带有着普遍的交流。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107097&size=300x300&key=b70fda730bcaa535&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107097\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮汕民间俗语称“未有饶平县，先有石古坪”，石古坪村至迟在明成化年间就已经存在。石古坪的“古”字，有可能是“牯”字的雅化。现在是大质山里唯一的一个村子，只有五十几户，依然保存有宗祠和祭祖的是蓝氏族人。每年的正月二十，除了看祖图，已经很少见到他们民族特色的元素存在。但是我们在祖图上可以看到一个“闾山学法”的一个片段，而根据记载，最有畲族民族特色的“招兵节”，也是在红头师公主持下的请神祭祀活动，其种种仪式和过程，与浙闽赣一带的闾山一派如出一辙。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107098&size=300x300&key=e2b8770d4820c64d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107098\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">我们前面也分析过，闾山派是从古老的越闽巫术衍化而来的，所以畲族这个著名的具有民族特色的节日，其实就是闾山法的请神仪式。而从田野调查的资料来看，以前畲族平常生活中的种种重要事件，都要通过师公来举行仪式，而从他们使用法裙，龙角，草席这些典型元素的情况看，这和现在汉族民间神秘的闾山道术做法均为一致。所以究竟是畲族这些古老的原住民巫术影响了后来汉族呢，还是汉族整合了原始巫术反过来改造了原住民呢，这实在也是一个很有趣的课题。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107099&size=300x300&key=193b573b4f7af536&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107099\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">现在的石古坪村出产出名的乌龙茶，村民大部分常年在潮州汕头等地，正月二十这天则纷纷返回村里祭祖，这个习俗对于受到强势汉文化同化的畲族来说，是保证其族群认知的最后一幕，过去因为畲族颇受汉民歧视，对其图腾崇拜也有微词，所以他们拜祖图一事也不愿外人参观，如今随着文化遗产保护的大力开展，已日渐好转。多年前我带着小孩上山观礼，与素不相识的村民小孩玩的不亦乐乎，最后还跑去他开在潮州市里的茶叶店喝茶聊天，石古坪的畲民，早已完全地融入了这个现代社会。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107101&size=300x300&key=60fc306f368e4e2c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107101\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107103&size=300x300&key=2e64a121254a2e8f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107103\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012300818894.png\" title=\"1460012300818894.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道 &nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/ 图 &nbsp;岭东怒马 &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107093&size=300x300&key=93f461a106ecff54&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107093\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-02-29 08:43:09',0,NULL,1,NULL,2273,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (338,'【岭东民俗录】英歌春秋','201602290843592248.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012315878708.png\" title=\"1460012315878708.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107372&size=300x300&key=7ac838d4108529b3&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107372\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">因为安静的缘故，我接触到的普宁英歌比潮阳英歌要多，普宁市在每年的初一初二都会把全市各乡的英歌队组织到市政府前广场集中表演，这种类似斗舞的场面，激发了各乡英歌队的热情，而城里原本来自各乡的移民们也通过这个活动找回了家乡印记，所以每年都是人山人海，舞者激昂，观者激奋，将英歌的阳刚之气发挥得淋漓尽致。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107366&size=300x300&key=1a9eff0826873fe1&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107366\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而到了每个乡村闹热的社日，英歌队自然在本乡的巡游中要粉墨登场，按照传统，这是本村娱神娱人的头等大事，而且本乡本土，是最有感情与熟悉的所在，因此在寻访民俗的过程中，每逢遇到比较有特点的英歌队伍，我总要想方设法打听他们村闹热的日子，然后去探寻那原汁原味的场景。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107374&size=300x300&key=231fa40f666dd333&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107374\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">泥沟村社日就是正月廿一，在这个英歌闻名的大乡，每年这一天壮、青、少三支英歌队总要在村里巡游，并会在村中大广场做一个汇演。泥沟英歌是一种中板英歌，速度适中，很适合表演。像普宁的南山英歌则是快速有力的快板，动作节奏恍如狂风骤雨，摄影的镜头都很难跟得上。而像潮阳的古埕英歌，则是一种缓慢有力的极度仪式化的慢板英歌，这三种英歌各有特色，在传播和普及过程当中，均形成了自己独有的跟随圈。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107379&size=300x300&key=8504fb8ad911a8d6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107379\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">英歌舞是现在岭东潮普惠一带盛行的一种集体舞蹈，舞者手持短棒，出动前需勾画脸谱，以为水浒人物，英歌队有锣鼓跟随，多以玩蛇的“时迁”为前导，以头槌和二槌分为两队，有固定的阵式进退变化，两棒翻转相击，边走边击，人数则从十几人不等甚至可以敷演到传说的108人，以应水浒梁山好汉人数。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107373&size=300x300&key=50818dcfcecd985b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107373\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">从现在英歌的形式上来看，有很明显的戏剧表演，尤其是舞台表演的痕迹。胡朴安民国初年的《中华全国风俗志》“所谓唱莺歌。。。以三十六壮年男子，饰梁山泊英雄，半执两棒，棒长盈尺，半执小鼓，鼓大如碗。举步亦趋亦跳，进退不紊”，是现在见到的最早记录英歌这一风俗的资料，当时称之为“莺歌”。而普宁也传说英歌舞是来源于外江戏的武戏，尤以梁山好汉攻打大名府一节为本。从有舞蛇者时迁这样的角色以及脸谱特色描绘来看，这一说法确实是反映了现在大部分英歌的形式。但是因为外江戏在潮汕本土流行最早在清道光年，盛行时间更要晚到光绪至清末，所以是否之前就没有英歌的形式呢？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107360&size=300x300&key=66c933c7d8128d45&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107360\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">我们如果再向前回溯，康熙年间吴震方《岭南杂记》记载：“潮州灯节，有鱼龙之戏，又每夕各坊市扮唱秧歌……饰狡童为采茶女，每队十二人或八人，挈花篮跌进而歌。”民国萧遥天先生据此认定此“秧歌”即为英歌，并由此认为英歌来源于花鼓戏。但是我们从上面对采茶女抬花篮这一描述可以认为，这个那时候唱采茶歌的队伍，就是现在营老爷队伍中的童女挑花篮，只不过十二月采茶歌是一种带有挑逗性质的艳歌，在发展过程中唱的这部分被舍弃了，而且这种“秧歌”怎么说都更适合女子而并非汉子，所以萧先生这种推断并非事实。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107377&size=300x300&key=a29d01c590d20e96&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107377\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">“秧歌”在地方志中记载并非只有一处，明末清初潮州知府吴颖《潮州风俗考》载：“农者春时数十辈，插秧田中，命一人捶鼓，每鼓一巡，群歌竞作，连日不绝，名曰秧歌。”但是这明显并非英歌。在潮语中“秧”与“英”“鹦”“莺”也并不同音，这种乡土风味浓厚，与陕北秧歌、东北二人转类似的带有戏谑和调笑意味的岭东乡土歌舞，现在已退化成挑花篮队伍，据说在埔田的老岭村，现在还有一支这样的“秧歌”队，前几年在正月十五闹热那天还出来巡游，可惜连续几年都不再出动，今年联系村里书记，据说因为生存艰难，这支可能是岭东最后的“秧歌”队，已面临解散，从此秧歌恐将成为绝唱。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107376&size=300x300&key=de52dfc5a630711d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107376\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">英歌在潮汕口语中，多称为敲【白读为“启鸦切”】英歌、舞【白读为“毛乌切”】英歌，前者指其敲击双槌，后者是描述它的形式。以前有“唱英歌”一词，我认为并不是说英歌会边舞边唱——事实上英歌在舞动过程中只会发出威猛的吼叫——而是在说以前英歌队普遍带有“后棚”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107358&size=300x300&key=9fa32a7edb5927b3&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107358\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107370&size=300x300&key=403277a278f06059&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107370\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">一支完整的英歌队是要有前中后棚的配置的，前棚是我们现在习见的英歌舞者，手持双槌，敲击游动。中棚一般是一些扮演文戏的戏曲人物，后棚则是武术表演。后来中后棚也有统称后棚的。一般在营老爷行进时，到达宽阔大埕或者宗祠前，会进行表演，会唱一些脍炙人口诙谐可乐的潮剧片段，如“桃花过渡”等等，而武术表演则以对打，尤其是“拍布马”最受欢迎，敷演传说中的村民与骑马武将对打的场面。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107355&size=300x300&key=85cd46d850cfc402&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107355\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107356&size=300x300&key=1309f413e09a43c3&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107356\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107357&size=300x300&key=f7f2172b96a7d79d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107357\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这种武术对打很明显与闽南的“宋江阵”相类，从这一点上看，发源于明末郑成功抗清时候的宋江阵，或许对潮汕的英歌有一定的影响。当然借民间信仰组织会社，并练武练兵，乃是以前农民兵变的普遍做法，普宁旱塘成技、北山许阿梅，大长陇陈娘康，都有这样的经历。但是作为前棚的英歌队，除了极个别流派有较重的南拳植入痕迹例如南山英歌，西岐英歌等——但是他们的武术植入均是后来有意加入的——大部分还是以表演为主，这与“宋江阵”还是有相当的不同。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107359&size=300x300&key=f05aca2363cf720e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107359\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">从慢板英歌我们则明显可以看到英歌有来源于“傩”的一面，在潮阳棉城的南桂坊英歌，挥槌驱赶的动作就很仪式化，而且我们从宋朝除夕夜宫里的大傩仪记载中也可以看到与英歌雷同的形式。而在民间，则是“乡人傩”，有“打夜胡”，“迓鼓”的形式，舞迓鼓有男子、妇人、僧道、杂色等装扮，也在宋代流行一时。所有这些，应该都是英歌没有结合水浒戏之前的前身。而我们对比福建民间流传的近巫术的一些仪式，例如皂隶舞，例如泰宁大源有手拿戒尺，已经非常类似英歌的傩舞，都至少可以证明，在久远的过去，都早有让水浒英雄们“上身”的存在。这是岭东民间的一部春秋史记。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107367&size=300x300&key=6cdc9508f7ea07a4&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107367\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012323593580.png\" title=\"1460012323593580.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道 &nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/ 图 &nbsp;岭东怒马 &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107348&size=300x300&key=ee157b0e7f33454e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107348\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-02-29 08:43:59',0,NULL,1,NULL,2336,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (339,'【岭东年俗录】与神一战','201602291502061538.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012335398646.png\" title=\"1460012335398646.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107428&size=300x300&key=d343f238470f9656&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107428\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">盐灶拖神，当地人称“缉老爷”，是澄海盐灶乡上社村正月期间最有特色的民俗，群情汹涌，观者如潮，地方之小，人员之多，动作之猛，风俗之奇，都非常极端地放大了如醉如痴的全民疯狂气氛，堪称潮汕狂欢节。正月二十一的晚上，进行第一轮的拖神，凌晨子时时分，其中两台老爷轿，仍然陷在人潮之中不得出脱，攻守双方激战正酣。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107429&size=300x300&key=d047d80e291f9c3b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107429\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107430&size=300x300&key=6a3d02889e183a0c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107430\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">盐灶乡这个“缉老爷”的特殊习俗，远近皆知。其它地方都是营老爷，唯有盐灶是缉老爷。所谓的“缉”，现在还找不到一个合适的本字，这里姑且当做一个同音字来表示。潮语把折腾一种东西叫做“缉”，例如缉面，缉粿，都是把面粉米粉搅拌成固体形状，然后上下左右揉搓。盐灶游神的时候，就是这样对待神偶的。而且不只是本村人可以上去“缉”，也欢迎外乡人来缉。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107431&size=300x300&key=751a3f3bad6f8c37&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107431\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107432&size=300x300&key=2f7c55596637e981&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107432\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">盐灶是澄海与饶平交界处的海边村庄，旧时以渔盐为业，远离潮州府中心，近代还被基督教会选为入潮第一乡。因为据说盐灶神显外乡，所以离它七八公里路程，位于半岛上的大乡汫州最为热衷。以前每到正月廿二下午，乡里人就成群结队赶到盐灶去看缉老爷，汫州渔民剽悍，有很多壮汉更非常向往亲身上阵，并流传下许多在盐灶缉老爷后回来渔获兴旺的故事。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107433&size=300x300&key=03598e5ada1a0918&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107433\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">缉老爷的村叫上社，是盐灶最大的自然村，常住人口有七八千人，但缉老爷经常有几万人参加，这让盐灶平时用来做公共活动场所的“老爷埕”显得人满为患，一位难求。正式缉老爷是在正月廿二下午，但是正月廿一晚上有一场“洗街路”，是老爷夜里巡游净土驱邪的本意， 但由于太过出名，而且可能也是为明日进行预演，近几年参加围观的人也是越来越多。夜色灯火，气氛迷离，站在老爷轿上护神壮汉赤着上身，肌肉裸现，气势轩昂，有一种古希腊极力彰显的雕塑之美。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107436&size=300x300&key=b8bf4664fcbfc2d5&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107436\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107437&size=300x300&key=c0ccb3e3c4b6f70d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107437\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">廿二下午白天正式的缉老爷，则是远近风传的大事件了，四乡八里的人都向上社的老爷埕集中过来，向神发起挑战。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107444&size=300x300&key=c78644b48a65e0fe&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107444\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">一共有五个老爷轿，按照仪式流程要通过老爷埕三次，村里共分为五甲，以甲为单位先掷珓选择各抬那尊神像。老爷被各个宗族抬上专门做的结实的“武轿”捆紧，一个大汉站在上面，轿子上插满了燃烧正旺的香火。前后几十人穿统一的服装，护卫着轿子。大汉站在轿上神像的后面，手中拿满燃香，左右示威，不断用香飞击逼近的人群。而前来缉老爷的人们毫不示弱，一波波地拥上前去，要把老爷轿拉下来。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107439&size=300x300&key=5e22f2668fe4e61d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107439\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这个时候是整个游神最为高潮的部分，护神者与拖神者各显实力，手推足蹬，不知道的以为是一场几万人的大群殴，整个老爷埕群情激昂，水泄不通，除了里三层是人神在角力之外，站在外面的人就像处在汹涌的海潮之间似的，前后左右只能随波逐流，那种冲击力无法言表。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107440&size=300x300&key=bc9897b8607ab7f6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107440\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">当然这种场面是有控制的。每年负责组织这项活动的是村里威望极高的“老大”们组成的老人组，护神的队伍本身就起着护卫队与纠察队的职责，只要是场面有过火的苗头，就会一队人冲进去把人群隔开，而除了“妈祖”神像是重点要拦下来“缉”之外，其他神像也不是非要拦下不可，这种种的规则都会被大部分人认同与遵循，因此盐灶这场看似不可思议的大游行，就在乱与不乱之间，呈现出独有的魅力，既是释放雄性荷尔蒙的试验田，又是乡村自治显示其控制力和威望的平台。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107441&size=300x300&key=039f7e3156e66272&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107441\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">据说在过去，抬老爷的壮汉全部是“托手尾”，轿子是高高擎起来的，要缉老爷的人不但要靠近，还需要施展各种手段爬到轿子上面去缉。这俨然就是一个武术电影的镜头。以前护轿的人还要赤身涂油，上去的人拉他的手也拉不住。难度之高，也挡不住艺高人胆大的外乡过江龙。而且据说老爷须是特别有神性的“圣物”，所以尤其是当神像在从祠堂里抬出来的时候，总是有高手一纵而过要来揪老爷须，这也让这个缉老爷的习俗从开始到结束，都一直充满刺激和高潮。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107442&size=300x300&key=d92ce2ec3dcb4036&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107442\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">很多人都奇怪为何在盐灶这里有如此奇葩的习俗。有很多人都讲述这样一个故事，说是当地一个贫穷渔民，因无钱承担正月营老爷的费用，走投无路之际，把神庙里的偶像拖下来泄愤，并沉于池塘，当夜出走过番，不料出洋之后竟然发了财，后来回乡之后告知乡人真实情况，并且把老爷像捞出重塑。盐灶因为这样开始了拖老爷的风俗。这个故事据说也被盐灶乡志收录，但是它的来源，却有很多疑问。根据汕头大学学生一份田野报告指出，当地负责抬神多年的一位老汉，其实从没有听说过这个故事，而缉老爷的真实源流，他也说不清楚，只说自古有之。澄海多年从事文物考古和潮文化研究的蔡英豪先生，也称此故事是以前特殊年代收集整理民间文化时工作人员生造的，因为盐灶并非侨乡，向来没有出洋的传统，而且以前出洋，有幸衣锦还乡者，起码也要几十年，等到此人回乡，早已物是人非，不可能有如此大之号召力改变一乡的风俗。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107443&size=300x300&key=4d7fc2cfc955ed1c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107443\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">蔡先生认为这个风俗的起因，是与潮地以前普遍存在营老爷时的“走安”形式演化而来的，走安，要抬神的大汉们扛着老爷轿奔跑，在这过程中可能会一时失手而把神偶摔倒，巧的是那一年的年景收成非常好，因此上乡人以为需要用这样的方式来敬神，所以逐渐形成这一种风俗。黄挺教授描述到这个风俗的时候指出，盐灶乡的神偶是水捞神，即神偶是由他处漂到盐灶乡，被当地村民捞起供奉的。这或可解释绑神、抢神、拖神这种种对神毫不恭敬的游神方式的起因，是因为要向这里的神偶曾经的经历进行怀念和致敬。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107434&size=300x300&key=2746bc2375dfb524&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107434\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">但是近几年我从文献，通过大量的田野调查，并与浙闽一带仍然举行的一些民俗进行互相对照，就发现这种被指为独一无二的游神方式，实际上也并非盐灶这个地方凭空生造出来的。民国翁辉东在《潮州志 风俗志》中记民国潮州之俗，“游行之夜，多行撞尪，或走尪，取麻皮紧缚神座，出全乡丁壮，抬座互撞，每将偶像撞至手脚堕折。”——所谓“尪”，就是闽南语里神像的意思，既读“王”，又读“安”——并特别说“饶属某乡，将神像缚以草绳，向田垄拖之”。从这个记载来看，虽然翁先生并没有提到偏远海边的这个小村的风俗，但是饶属，即与盐灶交界的饶平一带拖神像的习俗他是有风闻的，而且说道“撞尪”，让我们也联想到离府城很近的卧石乡，据记载过去它是有更猛烈地直接撞击所谓的“舂老爷”的风俗的。因此上盐灶的缉老爷，在以前这个区域，不会是孤独突兀的一个存在。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107435&size=300x300&key=d2a136cb5ae14c67&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107435\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">近年以来，我们又发现漳州龙海洪塘村有撞尪，据传是因为该地为郑成功军与清兵鏖战之地，杀戮过多，村人用神像互撞以镇邪。连城一带有在泥泞水田里戏耍神偶的“抬菩萨”。更远的有浙江苍南蒲城“拔五更”，永安大湖的“抢佛”。而从潮州腹地一带的其他村子来看，其实也存在着与盐灶目的相同的以拦住老爷神轿为目的进行祈福的过程。例如榕江流域的长美村，老爷回宫的时候，拦住不让进宫，两班人马互相争夺。枫江流域的北洋村，老爷会被放在阳埕上不停的转圈。韩江边上的独树村，有“格安”，也是不让特定的神像回宫。这些用人阻挡神像的仪式过程，乡人们都有说道，基本上是认为让神像慢一点入宫，与村人在一起多一会，会对这个村来年的运气有利，只不过是他们没有达到盐灶上社这样剑拔弩张，气势恢弘，让雄性荷尔蒙爆发到顶点的这个程度而已。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107438&size=300x300&key=c028848efdbcd23b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107438\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">不管从哪个角度来说，盐灶这一天是凡人自信最为爆棚的一天，当我们在万人的现场里，热血沸腾参与这场人神之战的时候，每个人的心里，都会经历从恐惧到豪迈的过程，这是一个对险恶自然与社会的自我激励和自我加持，这是一个尚武族群培养血性的全民洗礼，是现代社会不可多得的野性复活之旅。</span></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012342861238.png\" title=\"1460012342861238.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/ 图&nbsp;&nbsp;岭东怒马&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107425&size=300x300&key=f85fea6a231dd811&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107425\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-02-29 15:02:06',0,NULL,1,NULL,2325,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (340,'【岭东民俗录】城隍公与青龙爷','201603021558059235.png','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012352918298.png\" title=\"1460012352918298.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">岭东这个名词，在文化的指认上，即为古潮州府地。古潮州府在历史沿革上，历代有称为揭阳县、义安郡、潮阳郡的，都大体指的是这个区域，在上千年的历史演变过程里，虽然辖区有大小不同的变化，但是以“一府三阳”作为经济文化中心辐射整个地区，影响力非常深远，一直到今天，各种民间俗语和习俗，依然留存着痕迹。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108532&size=300x300&key=6eca01b363ca486f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108532\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">作为潮州府最古老的三个县，揭阳、海阳、潮阳这“三阳”（其中海阳县就在府城之中），在经济和文化上，是本地区马首为瞻之所在，而在最为兴盛的明清时代，这三个城市的正月营老爷，盛大壮观，场面恢宏，既录于方志笔记，更是其他都镇所津津乐道，悠然向往的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108533&size=300x300&key=2b723909083a27b6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108533\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这三个地方的主神“大老爷”，却很奇怪的各自不同，潮阳县“双忠圣王”，揭阳县“城隍公”，府城“青龙爷”，既各自代表了本地区民众信仰的不同倾斜，同时又更折射出在地区政治中心，国家权力影响民间信仰的不同轨迹，从流传到今天的民众记忆和认知来看，一种民间信仰无疑是对历史的一种可资传承的文化印记，在民众选择哪一个神成为“最大”的那一个的背后，是一个国家管理机器和民间信念互相磨合的过程。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108531&size=300x300&key=6718a1c72da7f449&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108531\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">除了潮阳双忠庙会在二月举行之外，府城的“青龙庙会”，揭阳的“城隍出巡”，循例都在正月头“卜杯”，选择二十二至二十四中一日作为“正日”巡游。揭阳城隍庙创建于宋，到明代已经发展为一个“神灵显赫”而名闻粤东的大神。清代林大川所著《韩江记》称：“我潮神灵显赫，以揭阳城隍为最。” &nbsp;而明太祖在洪武年间大封天下城隍的做法，更是推波助澜，根据他的管理办法，县城隍是“显佑伯”，官至四品，官阶待遇远远大于人间七品的现职县令。这在怕讼畏官的古代，足以让揭阳城隍庙香火鼎盛。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108519&size=300x300&key=c14e2f4156aa4eba&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108519\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">城隍神做为古代官方正式认可的城市守护神，在岭东各县曾经普遍设庙奉祀，到明代中期由于潮州人口大增，各地开发，开始形成一府九邑的格局，在区域较大而且商贸活跃的棉湖还增设“佐堂”进行管理，在这个“副县级”也建立城隍庙，所以民间流传潮州“九县十城隍”。实际上因为人们认为只要设有城墙，就有城隍神，所以后来很多卫所，像饶平所城，惠来靖海，蓬州所城等驻扎军队的千户所，也建城隍庙以作保护神，因此实际上岭东民间城隍庙远不止十座。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108520&size=300x300&key=6ce7fc9cffc70202&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108520\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108521&size=300x300&key=8a25c07c7de6ccba&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108521\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">揭阳县城隍庙建筑堂皇华丽，一直以来为各县翘楚，而民间也附会流传了该神如何灵验的故事，历代官府则乐于利用其民间威信，有意无意地引导民众，举凡大旱求雨、转运解厄等非人力所能解决问题，以及需要教化民众的，均通过城隍之手宣之以神，因此揭阳“城隍公”之名更加煊赫，成为揭阳城首席“大老爷”，正月出巡鼓乐喧天，万人空巷，为了使这个“伯府大人”多巡游几个地方，呆多一天，还编造出下围村姑娘游神时心仪城隍公，被城隍收为夫人的传说，从此城隍成为揭阳女婿，既神又亲，人神共乐的日子，就其乐融融，于今盛传不衰了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108527&size=300x300&key=8a875d04a31a202f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108527\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮州府城又做为海阳县城，照例也是有城隍神的。而且府城的城隍品级更高，洪武御封正二品“威灵公”，以前府城县城二级城隍也均有庙，但是在潮州府城，城隍的影响力就没有这么大。潮州的“大老爷”叫做“青龙爷”，现在是奉祀王伉，庙在城南的韩江堤旁。而从历史演变看，这个庙其实是拜祭青蛇的蛇王庙。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108529&size=300x300&key=35571f5c0f3ffe45&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108529\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108528&size=300x300&key=d473751f1ee4912f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108528\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这是南方土著古老的蛇崇拜遗留，岭东潮客两个民系，多从闽赣迁来，而福建的蛇崇拜由来已久，是南迁的汉人改造继承的土著的崇拜。根据吴榕青先生的研究，从现有的文献来看，自宋以来青蛇崇拜就做为水神流行在赣、汀、梅、潮一带，并且多次获得宋朝廷的封号，所谓“安济圣王”便是来源于此，人们奉祀其借以保护赣闽粤到岭东一带的水系安全。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108530&size=300x300&key=db719830b28b8bca&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108530\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108526&size=300x300&key=2c5476470804e150&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108526\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而自唐以来名为“恶溪”的韩江水患一直是地处江边的潮州城之心腹大患，所以安济王庙的蛇王做为能够“安澜”的神明，一直是地方所虔信的对象。然而做为精英文化代表的士大夫，尤其是代表着管理阶层的府城官员，则一直要对这种“怪力乱神”进行改造，自宋以来就有沈造与胡颖杀蛇罪僧的事情被记录在国家史书与士人笔记之中。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108568&size=300x300&key=f597507f5956c991&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108568\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">明清以后，这种民间与国家力量之间的较量得到了有效地磨合，因此宋以前对大蛇的这种“凶祀”转化成了“青龙”这种以不伤人为特点的灵物崇拜，同时又适时植入有功德于国民的云南永昌太守王伉做为一个人格化的神，在官方与民间有意识的引导之下，安济圣王、青龙爷、王伉渐趋一体，而这个神则因为能够预测洪水大小，并且能够保护潮州城免遭水患侵袭的重要能力，而逐渐逆袭成为府城的主神。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108560&size=300x300&key=cea16274958a930c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108560\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108563&size=300x300&key=a39e3385fc1fba16&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108563\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">清人林大川在《韩江记》有：“安济王即青龙王，安济其封号也，庙在城南，屹立长堤，冲当洪水，保护全城，我潮福主也” 又在《青龙王寿诞》一篇记：“王极灵爽，郡人称为活佛，每神降见有灵物蜿蜒凭龛次香案间，其色青翠，头有王字，是日青龙来去悠忽，隐见无常，郡人以得见为吉，然不可必也。。。神多降于神坛花瓶，柘石榴枝上，万人瞻仰，郡人一逢神降，奉之益虔。”自咸丰以后，到民国以降，王伉更因为进入了官方认可的“祀典”目录，因此在屡次禁“淫祀”活动中能够独善其身，因此就有了民国沈敏在近八十年前纪录的全城出游，如痴如醉的长达三天的府城青龙庙会，犹然成为今天过番留洋的老华侨，兹兹在念的辉煌场景。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108561&size=300x300&key=8659b03d21e947d5&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108561\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">营老爷本盛行于乡村，因为其朴素的净土安邪的出发点，以及结社纳福的自然需要，在乡村自治的宗族管理结构下，作为精神层面与行政管理构成了稳定社会的两极，因此在岭东得到了发展和发挥。然而在府城与三阳的中心，做为城里这种相对复杂和难以平衡的大社会里，商业利益就成了仪式的核心推动力了，为什么青龙庙会成为蜚声全潮，近百年犹然让人津津乐道的盛事，这其中的原因恐怕就不仅仅是单独一个信仰所能够解释了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108562&size=300x300&key=8bda61927f1299bc&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108562\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012360343996.png\" title=\"1460012360343996.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/ 岭东怒马 &nbsp;图/网络&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108534&size=300x300&key=14776b4858ddb6f8&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108534\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-03-02 15:58:05',0,NULL,1,NULL,2323,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (341,'【岭东民俗录】丁秋故事','201603070924251276.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012372807276.png\" title=\"1460012372807276.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">荡秋千，是频见文献记载的春天的游戏。《荆楚岁时记》记载：“春时悬长绳于高木，士女衣彩服坐于其上而推引之，名曰打秋千。” 据五代王仁裕的《开元天宝遗事》记载：“天宝宫中至寒食节，竞竖秋千，令宫嫔辈笑以为宴乐，帝呼为半仙之戏，都中士民相与仿之。唐宋诗人经常将之与春风佳人等元素结合起来，描摹清明时节旖旎动人的初春野游图景。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=109607&size=300x300&key=05553345f8e6b807&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_109607\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">关于秋千的起源，宋人高承《事物纪原》记：“秋千，山戎之戏，其民爱习轻矫之态，每至寒食为之。自齐桓公北伐山戎，此戏传入中国。”没有简化字之前，“鞦韆”是一个专用词语，即是言秋千揪皮绳而迁移之意。在明代，秋千因为它的轻盈旖旎，已经成为京都到江南普遍的女子喜闻乐见的初春游戏，明代甚至把清明节定为秋千节，与上巳踏青之俗相结合，成为太平盛世里士女嬉游的重要节目。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=109610&size=300x300&key=3b72748617ef0013&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_109610\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">随着中原移民成为岭东主要居民，荡秋千这种嬉游的节目，也渐渐被记录在地方志上。较早的有明万历《普宁县志》：“正月……男子小儿或妇人，竞打秋千，至十五夜止。”从出土的明嘉靖《荔镜记》剧本中也有打秋千的记载，由此可知，至迟在明代潮汕便有荡秋千之俗。此后历代方志都对潮俗荡秋千活动有所记载，清顺治《潮州府志》载：“（上元）儿童以秋千为戏，斗輋歌焉，善者为胜”；雍正《澄海县志》云：“（正月）十一日起，各神廟、街张灯，士女嬉游，放花爆、打秋千，歌唱达旦”；乾隆《揭阳县志》谓：“（上元）乡村架秋千为戏，斗輋歌，善者胜”；光绪《海阳县志》曰：“（上元）秋千之戏，鱼龙曼衍之观无不具”。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=109603&size=300x300&key=051af68e688cb249&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_109603\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">从这些记载中，我们可以发现，至少从明朝开始，流行在中原与江南一带的打秋千之俗，也已经风靡岭东大地，但是岭东民众玩秋千的时间是在上元灯节期间。另外一个是方志记录，岭东玩秋千的群体是“男子小儿或妇人”，而玩秋千的地点则城里也有，乡村也有。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=109602&size=300x300&key=8de05b7ba0847117&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_109602\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">表面上来看，我们可能会很容易得出推论，因为岭东春早，气候较北方和江南为暖，所以将这个春天的活动提前到了正月。但是根据多年来田野调查获得的信息来分析，似乎这不是一个主要因素。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=109604&size=300x300&key=ad042347fd7f7008&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_109604\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">从前面我们讲述的丰富多彩的岭东年俗来看，岭东民间大部分过年期间的活动，都是作为一种有象征意义的仪式来开展的，要么是净土驱邪求平安，要么是感恩纳福得庇佑。而根据我的考察结果来看，岭东正月荡秋千其实是一个与“求嗣得子”相关的仪式，这才是它在上元灯节举行的主要原因。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=109611&size=300x300&key=342f44cda79f7f94&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_109611\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">我们说过，岭东无论潮客，都将“灯”与“丁”等同，所以元宵期间，很多活动都与添丁得子有关系，例如一定要去祠堂上灯，求灯，要在这期间举办“丁桌”，当年得子或者新婚的被称为“丁头”，而岭东潮语口语里，就将秋千称为“丁秋”。澄海东沟村在大年初一开始搭秋千，必须由去年的丁头来搭，秋千棚搭完之后，要由去年最先添丁的“大丁头”开荡，之后村中新婚男子接力荡起，以承接大丁头添丁之福气。揭阳桃山龙畔村，初一搭建秋千的费用是去年添丁家庭负责，搭建之后新婚男子要先上去荡。饶平樟溪龙潭埔，除了由丁头搭秋千之外，丁头们还要在秋千架起来之后上去扔花生，在元宵夜营老爷时候，想求子的村民就会把注生娘娘请到秋千上荡起来，然后大家争着上前去摸摸神明以求沾福。这些都是相当明显的求嗣祈福，希望通过接触而获得已经添丁者的福气和运气，以达到自家得子的期望。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=109609&size=300x300&key=276afc1678da5d89&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_109609\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">昨天正月二十六，是饶北山区的上饶西片石吉路村的闹热日，他们村的中心是一座始建于明朝的土楼“华封楼”，土楼前也搭有一个秋千。大年三十由当年添丁者和新婚男子把楼前池塘的秋千架捞出来，搭建一个八米多高大型的秋千，这一天营山上庙里的“佛祖娘娘”的队伍，来到土楼的时候，一个接一个地上去荡秋千，一直到正月廿八才拆掉。这个秋千每年正月十一只能让妇女上去，而平时还流传“丁秋架顶【so6】一【so6】，有缘男女来相遇”， 除了有求子的寓意之外，又成为一个青年男女相识相爱的平台，因此还被称为“情秋”。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=109606&size=300x300&key=4acf67706e3a954e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_109606\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">从现今存在荡秋千习俗的村子来看，大部分村子是把秋千架搭建在宗祠前的阔埕之上，而这个阔埕，一般也是营老爷时候神明临时停靠接受祭拜的“神厂”所在。村民们在神明和祖宗前面举行荡秋千的活动，以仪式化的形式祈求传宗接代，添丁旺族，而在东沟、桃山这些村子，还特别规定元宵这一天，是只能由女子上去荡秋千，这其中的隐义就更是不言而喻了。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=109612&size=300x300&key=9a769fda2c2d0d2b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_109612\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在澄海的港口村，村里的主神庙定安庙门口，在每年的正月十一到二十，也会搭建一个高达三层楼的秋千架。这个秋千架则有着迥异其他村的神秘色彩。港口村奉祀玄天上帝、关帝、妈祖等主流大神，但是和秋千相关的则是哪吒三太子，他们相传秋千是三太子从南澳赢回来的，并且禁止妇女接触秋千。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=109605&size=300x300&key=6b00e72a6c4621b7&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_109605\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">村里老人组言之凿凿，说凡是女子动了秋千架，则一定会有人出事，到时就必须在三太子神前许愿还神，方能求得平安。或许因为这个缘故，港口村的秋千架造得特别大，一般人要高举双手才能碰到蹬板。港口村在澄海东郊，宋代称辟望港，曾是宋末陆秀夫驻军之地，此种讲究或许与古时候军队的禁忌有关。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=109608&size=300x300&key=ffdec4d1f1bfcc56&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_109608\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">岭东的秋千形式也有多种多样，因为荡秋千可以锻炼人的胆量与力量，所以做为体现尚武精神的乡人而言，夸耀自家的秋千也就成了仪式之外所津津乐道的事情了。港口村人就经常自豪地说，潮州丁秋四脚，东沟丁秋三脚，而本村只用两脚。说的就是它们的秋千架，一边只需要两根大圆木就可以固定。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=109601&size=300x300&key=de6de886e8c4fe27&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_109601\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">上饶西片石吉路的秋千，则是一种升级版的秋千，由两根硕大的柱子作为支架，柱子顶端穿着轴木，轴木中间穿锁着两段等长的摆架，摆架两端则均是可以坐人的架子——这是冀北称之为“木驴”的秋千，形似可以360度旋转的跷跷板——而桃山村和惠来的后山村，则树一种更加复杂化的秋千。这种秋千在支架上再架一个方形大木轮，轮子四角各吊一副小秋千，玩起来如同风车，我们同样可以在远在河北的邯郸地区找到它的原型：过梁悠。这几种复杂而又惊险的秋千，究竟是如何从北方引入到南方，并且被岭东的村人继承并保留到现在，又是另外一个满有意思的话题。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=109600&size=300x300&key=549d5c131fe07480&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_109600\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012381128914.png\" title=\"1460012381128914.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/ 岭东怒马&nbsp;&nbsp;图/岭东怒马 安静</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=109613&size=300x300&key=60b054b4c3e6a7e8&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_109613\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span><br/></p>','2016-03-07 09:24:25',0,NULL,1,NULL,2195,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (342,'看怒马笔下的岭东民俗……','201603070942296398.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012393550290.png\" title=\"1460012393550290.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">《以前，潮汕过年是从年廿四开始的》、《筅尘与刮鼎》、《围炉过年》、《正月十一 行头桥》<span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">、《庶民的历史》、《老爷保呵大营灯》、《趭香船与忌平安》、《正月二十 畲族祖图》……相信很多橄榄用户都看过<span style=\"color:#a0522d;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">《岭东民俗录/年俗录》</span>，作者<span style=\"color:#a0522d;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">岭东怒马</span>的名字也已是耳熟能详，但他</span></span><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;font-family: 宋体;font-size: medium;line-height: 24px\">究竟</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5;font-family: 宋体;font-size: medium\">是何许人也？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108076&size=300x300&key=e28cf3730a9f9d5e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108076\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;max-width: 400px\"/><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/><strong style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;font-family: 宋体;font-size: medium;line-height: 24px\">岭东怒马，青年民俗研究者，资深影友，镜头常年对准民俗与风光。</strong><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108120&size=300x300&key=911fa73b4ea1899e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108120\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;max-width: 400px\"/><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">△岭东怒马接受橄榄台记者采访</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">岭东的民情风俗，是岭东怒马笔下一道道历史情感的风景线，也是一幅幅瑰丽的民俗画卷。文字中、照片中都可以听到声音、看到人物活动，更能感受到人的思想感情，生动再现了岭东百年来的丰富多彩的百姓生活。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;color:#a0522d;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><strong style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">岭东是哪里？</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">北魏郦道元《水经注》载：“岭南背靠五岭而面大海，岭东则为五岭之东，而穷于海，盖以五岭为始，而讫于揭阳也。”从历史记载来看，“岭东”泛指<span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 24px\">历史上古潮州府，范围包括了现今潮汕、兴梅客家、漳州西部，作为文化现象互相融合与影响，是一个整体。</span></span><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108195&size=300x300&key=ba33c8cf1de07ddf&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108195\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;max-width: 400px\"/><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;color:#a0522d;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><strong style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">礼失而求诸野</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">当下，人手一部高清拍照智能手机，互联网时代分享图片的便利和积极性不言而喻，随着“发现身边之美”活动、《今日视线》随手拍平台等分享美图方式的兴起，汕头市民逐渐培养起分享见闻美图的习惯。岭东怒马曾在发文中提到，越来越多的图像信息被传播出来，越来越多的潮汕人正越来越走近乡野，走近传统，这片土地积淀已久的美好，终将被世界欣赏。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 24px\"><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 24px\">因为岭东保留有很多来自古代甚至远古的一些仪礼风俗，<span style=\"color:#a0522d;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">通过学习已经卓有成绩的潮州学专家学者们的研究成果，来对照我们丰富的民俗</span>，可以得到很多趣味，而知道民俗背后的故事，能够让我们更明白地去参与，有意识的去参加，能够更有意义的去传播，作为一个地区文化的继承者与传播者，我们每一个人都自觉不自觉的成为其中的一部分，因为<span style=\"color:#a0522d;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">民俗就是庶民书写的历史</span>。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108193&size=300x300&key=be8a354333f0a2b9&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108193\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;max-width: 400px\"/><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;color:#a0522d;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><strong style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">习以为常的普通习俗之后</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;color:#a0522d;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><strong style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">蕴藏着丰富的历史信息碎片</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">“大地如此丰富，原乡这般饱满，传统多么带劲，仪式就是当今一切非遗的基础。”在岭东怒马看来，我们当下所习以为常的节日与习俗，其实正是<span style=\"color:#a0522d;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">历史场景的入口</span>。如中山大学陈春声教授所说的“走进历史现场”，只要我们吃起七样羹、观看“营老爷”、参加乡里闹热，便可以置身于相同的情感与情景中，时代变迁，不变的是古俗。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108196&size=300x300&key=73744969409f0733&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108196\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;max-width: 400px\"/><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;color:#a0522d;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><strong style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">丰富的民俗信息</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;color:#a0522d;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><strong style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">等待您来了解</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">从年廿四至今，岭东怒马已在汕头橄榄台APP原创发布了超20篇民俗美文。“每天都有不同的故事，每个乡里都有不同的节日”民俗知识涉及学科多、稍欠整理便容易碎化，岭东怒马从十年前便开始着手“田野调查”搜集第一手资料，本次通过橄榄台以栏目的形式呈现出来，给岭东民俗爱好者与市民带来一餐饕餮的文化盛宴。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108194&size=300x300&key=1260f3b53f45c971&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108194\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;max-width: 400px\"/><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">除了发布在汕头橄榄台APP玩食版块外，小编也为您<span style=\"color:#a0522d;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">将《岭东民俗录/年俗录》集中呈现在橄榄台互动版块的“天下潮人”之中</span>，欢迎橄榄用户前往阅读。</span><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108191&size=300x300&key=81eb3cd0aa403aea&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108191\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;max-width: 400px\"/><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=108192&size=300x300&key=da21a956fb5c9d8c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_108192\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;max-width: 400px\"/><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:宋体;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012403100875.png\" title=\"1460012403100875.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:宋体;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">汕头橄榄台原创报道 转载请标明下方橄榄台二维码</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:宋体;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">橄榄小编/梅尼</span><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=107929&size=300x300&key=0da471ec9aa2c5d0&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_107929\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;max-width: 400px\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-03-07 09:42:29',0,NULL,1,NULL,2181,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (343,'【印尼潮商】沧海横流见本色','201603090940348628.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012421133708.png\" title=\"1460012421133708.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">编者按：</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在航海技术尚不十分发达的最初，几乎每次远航都有生命在付出，幸存的人到达目的地时也多是身心疲惫。然而，他们就这样面对陌生的土地陌生的人，一切从零开始，扎根、发展、成功、壮大，靠自己的双手搏出一条康庄大道，成为当地异乡人的杰出榜样。这种永不言败的精神已经深入到每一代潮商的血液里，随着大海的呼吸而澎湃、激荡。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61287&size=300x300&key=1e325b85b9c096f8&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61287\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">上世纪90年代，金融风暴席卷亚洲，东南亚无数商人因此血本无归，印尼潮商也在其中。许多人的财富一夕之间蒸发殆尽，多年的努力在这场金融大灾难中化为飞灰<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">。很多商人经此打击变得心灰意冷，而印尼潮商却没有因此一蹶不振。在债台高筑的逆境中，潮商顽强地生存着，坚持着，努力地积累力量，始终不放弃东山再起的希望。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">印尼潮州乡亲公会董事会主席吴福泰正是经历过这场金融风暴的潮商之一。据他回忆，他开始经商的时候是18岁，最先接触做布的生意。第一桶金顺利得手，此后又代理香烟，刚开始投资仍然获得了成功，但在一次投资烟厂时，他却初次尝到了失败的滋味。1990年开始投资煤炭，后来又开始参与汽车类的投资贸易，生意一直蒸蒸日上。可是在1998年印尼金融风暴中，由于进口时在银行的贷款是美金，最后收到的货款却是印尼盾，损失惨重。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">但吴福泰并没有因此放弃，经过短暂的总结与调整，吴福泰抱着从头开始的信念，再度进军煤炭业，最终成为印尼数一数二的煤炭大王。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61288&size=300x300&key=17ceab8790337ba6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61288\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">吴福泰认为自己的经历可以给年轻人不少启发。</span></strong>首先一点是做生意应该懂得公司的行政管理，他第一次失败正是败在不懂管理上。其次就是要有对风险的充分预设，不光是自身的问题会导致失败，外界影响，尤其是诸如金融风暴这样世界经济的影响，往往会让投资一败涂地，这样的起起落落对于商业投资而言是正常的，一定不能让自己被其轻易击垮。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61289&size=300x300&key=7e034bbf34639bb9&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61289\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61290&size=300x300&key=83d3d3bb517e51ff&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61290\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">印尼巴厘岛每天游客络绎不绝，是闻名世界的旅游度假天堂，很多投资者从中敏锐地察觉到了商机，潮商张天来洞察先机，很早就发现了这个极富潜力的投资项目。金融危机爆发时，酒店业跌入萧条期，不少商人因此撤离旅游业。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">但张天来却逆流而上，利用那些人急于撤资的心理，用极低的价格入手了岛上的一个大型度假村。</span></strong>他独到的商人眼光准确预测到了海岛旅游业的复兴，但就在行业即将复苏的时候，因为接连两次恐怖爆炸而再度跌入深渊的巴厘岛旅游业，却让张天来蒙受了始料未及的巨大损失。&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61291&size=300x300&key=e1f994093f3a51ed&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61291\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">张天来告诉记者，那个时候，度假村内无论是外国游客还是本地游客都寥寥无几，最困难的时候，400多间房间一晚只入住了两间房间，从2005年到2009年，四年时间生意惨淡，连水费都缴付不起，此外还有酒店固定的电费，人工费等等。不论生意好坏，几百个工人的工钱月月照还，从不拖欠。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61292&size=300x300&key=36eabe137356e45b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61292\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">每当张天来谈起那段最艰难的时期，显得颇有感触。</span></strong>那时候巴厘岛旅游业投资风险太大，人人闻之色变，银行也不同意贷款，张天来只能用自己的积蓄倒贴进去经营。亏本数年，即便想转手他人也卖不出去，但张天来坚信困难只是一时的，巴厘一定有旅游业复苏的时候，只要能够支撑到那一刻就是胜利。张天来认为做生意需要的是时间，顺境之时自然一片坦途，而身处逆境，就要想办法坚持下去，过了山重水复，就能收获柳暗花明。谈起现状，张天来很是骄傲：“现在生意真好了，定房子你一定要先定，2012年到年底，我的酒店的房间都给人定完了。”</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61293&size=300x300&key=57ad8e18f2da4973&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61293\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮商正是凭着用于拼搏奋进的精神，和永不服输的倔劲，用外人所想象不到的顽强挺过了一次又一次的挫折与危机，让潮商这个族群在印尼乃至全世界都始终拥有一片属于自己的广阔天地。潮商的精神让他们可以在最艰难的时候不气馁，也可以做到在最得意的时候不忘形。这样的精神，不仅是潮商的精神，也是千千万万潮汕儿女的宝贵品质，是祖祖辈辈留传下来的最大的财富。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012428340037.png\" title=\"1460012428340037.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">来源/汕头电视台《天下潮商》</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/关雪&nbsp;&nbsp;博尔</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61240&size=300x300&key=fc321dfd5ca76152&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61240\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></span><br/></p>','2016-03-09 09:40:34',0,NULL,1,NULL,2159,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (344,'【印尼潮商】守信而立 大爱无疆','201603090941348381.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012441832234.png\" title=\"1460012441832234.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">编者按：</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮商是一个特殊的族群，他们彼此之间没有血脉相连，却情意相通；他们每个人都极富个性，却总能在关键时刻达成共识，彼此默契，团结合作，共同进退。印尼潮商能够在各行各业脱颖而出，离不开潮商的品质与美德。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61358&size=300x300&key=b1d9b5dcf7f0dd23&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61358\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">人无信不立，对于潮商来说，做生意要讲道义，守信用，那些在生意场上尔虞我诈，出尔反尔的人不值得为伍。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">正是潮商这种诚信为本的宝贵品质赢得了生意伙伴的信赖，也让他们在身处低谷之时，能够得到建立在信任基础上的援助，以信义化解危机，为自己东山再起积蓄力量。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮商张天来在打算投资巴厘岛度假村进军旅游业的时候，尚未和度假村正式签订合同，当地的恐怖爆炸事件就给予了旅游业一个重大打击。那种情况下，要反悔完全来得及，但张天来从未想过反悔。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在他看来，信守承诺是最基本的品质，即使只是口头的诺言。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61359&size=300x300&key=6dfbe77f500e90cd&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61359\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(46, 139, 87); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮商王永顺说，潮商向来说一不二，只要说出口了，就一定不会变卦。这是潮商与他人进行生意场上的合作时坚守的底线。</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">恪守信用，这是潮商的美德，是潮商的标签，也是潮商的活品牌。潮商将品牌建设看得和信用一样重要，在他们做生意时始终不忘的，是对企业品牌、产品品牌、人格品牌等多方面品牌文化的积累与沉淀。在精益求精，追求极致的品牌意识的指引下，潮商在印尼的各行各业都将自己的品牌做好做大，赢取了极高的口碑。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61370&size=300x300&key=ac6b35c67c14e901&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61370\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮商黄财利一开始帮厂家卖鞋，而后替厂家加工鞋，积累充足的经验之后，他自己创办了鞋厂，注册品牌商标，经营连锁店，整个发展历程足有二三十年。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">如今，“富嘉丽”的品牌众口称赞，家喻户晓，是在印尼名列前茅的畅销商品。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">黄财利谈起自己的品牌很是自豪。每回“富嘉丽”的新款问世，印尼就会有很多鞋厂仿造该品牌新型的款式，但“富嘉丽”有口碑在前，不需要费财费力多做广告，就足以让它稳居印尼品牌榜首。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61360&size=300x300&key=2dc41ea2a32d9e47&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61360\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61361&size=300x300&key=e28260cb594de062&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61361\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">铁锤商标在印尼服装界中，就是时尚品质的代名词。创始人邹南柄从一开始就确立了相当明确的创业思路，明白必须拥有自创品牌，创业才能成功。他注册商标，努力发展原创品牌，让自己的服装厂、服装店跻身印尼名厂名店之列。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">回想起自己的创业路，邹南柄感慨到，铁锤商标之所以能够有如此辉煌的成就，正是源自于对品牌和质量的坚持。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61363&size=300x300&key=56f2f782904045c9&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61363\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">邹南柄告诉记者，他选择在服装界奋斗源于他对服装的浓厚兴趣。刚开始的时候，邹南柄用几台缝纫机进行尝试，起步很好，于是他马上注册铁锤商标，紧接着向百货公司进发，建立自己铺头的同时，在百货公司也发展了部分销售渠道，生意规模日渐扩大。之后，他又注册其他商标，到现在已有4个商标握在邹南柄的手上。他认为，目前服装业竞争激烈，想要进一步发展，就必须用全新的眼光，积极地向国外看齐，学习国外的流行时尚，永不满足于现状。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61362&size=300x300&key=31befd58b3598730&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61362\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在潮商的生意经里，品牌无疑是在生意上抢占先机，获得成功的法宝，而对于潮商来说，还有一种品牌是属于他们特有的法宝，就是潮菜。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">有一句话总结得很精辟，天下潮人，天下潮商，天下潮菜，精致可口的潮菜一向人见人爱，有潮人走过的地方，就会留下潮菜的踪迹。</span></strong>将远近闻名的潮菜做大做强，从来都是潮商的拿手好戏。在雅加达首都这座千万人口的国际大都市中，每天来自世界各地的客人南来北往，客流量极大。而潮商杨明丽经营的潮州菜馆，就矗立在这个大城市的繁华街区之中。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61364&size=300x300&key=f69ed4d20ba8ec80&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61364\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">杨明丽告诉记者，她的父亲杨楚元在占碑创业，于1969年开始经营这家潮州菜馆。1975年迁到雅加达，一直以潮菜为事业立足的根本，经营地道的潮州菜，功夫茶、潮汕粥以及火锅等。她自幼跟在父亲身边，帮助她的父亲经营菜馆。杨楚元去世之后，菜馆由杨明丽接手，尽她所能将潮汕人做事精致、热情好客的优秀品质淋漓尽致地发挥到潮菜当中，展现在人们的面前。菜馆里每日来往客人络绎不绝，光顾流连菜馆里地道的潮菜和飘香的功夫茶的人当中，有很多都是老顾客，当回头客数十载，仍旧对潮菜百吃不厌。大家都夸奖她有人缘，会做生意。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61365&size=300x300&key=afc6ae276301231c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61365\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61366&size=300x300&key=07e35b304b36911e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61366\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61367&size=300x300&key=27fa1fa03167b2ec&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61367\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61368&size=300x300&key=06be682b4bde3a47&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61368\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">记者随机采访了一些潮州菜馆的客人，其中一位顾客告诉记者，杨明丽很懂生意之道，一直热情真诚地对待朋友，服务非常周全，因此人缘也一直很好。印尼有好几个社团都吸收了杨明丽为其中成员，她非常好客，因此广交良友，朋友们会时不时来菜馆聊天喝茶。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61369&size=300x300&key=535255181b9c751b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61369\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">印尼这个处处胜景的群岛国家，历经数代潮商不懈的拼搏努力，留下了一个个他们亲笔写下的商战传奇。</span></strong>他们在发家致富之后，积极回馈社会，在印尼筑路修桥，捐钱办学，扶危济困。2011年夏天，飓风席卷印尼西爪哇岛，岛上无数灾民流离失所。印尼潮州乡亲公会的潮商们在听到这个消息之后，迅速组织起来，慷慨解囊，帮助灾民重建家园。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61371&size=300x300&key=f0cebd2e85bbfc30&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61371\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">百善孝为先，潮汕儿女最看重的就是孝道，向来有尊老的美德。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">印尼潮州乡亲公会将做善事的重点放在了关爱孤寡老人的相关行动上，</span></strong>大家有钱出钱有地捐地，为孤寡老人们建起了一座乐龄居敬老院，并且将地址选在了风景秀丽的雅加达后花园，更加适宜疗养。这个敬老院交由公会拥有管理，建成至今已有十余年的历史，各地潮商一直争相接力认捐，传递爱心，让不少老年人得以在此处颐养天年，享受舒适快乐的晚年生活。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61372&size=300x300&key=d27e605cd806422f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61372\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">一位现正居住在乐龄居敬老院的老人告诉记者，他自五年前搬入敬老院居住，今年已有78岁。他认为这里空气清新凉爽，环境舒适，工作人员照顾周到，每年除夕都会请他们吃年夜饭，过年还会为他们准备红包，让他们充分享受到家一般的温暖。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">另一位住在这里的老人也对敬老院赞不绝口：“两年多了，环境空气好，吃得也不错，三餐还有水果，还有医生。”</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">印尼潮商纪逢贞说，在印尼的华人中，潮州人在做慈善这件事情上要比其他人更加坚持回报社会，更加团结，做得也更好。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61373&size=300x300&key=8eb7fa1e424c1e55&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61373\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">每一位成功的潮商都有属于自己精彩绝伦却不为人所知的故事，他们各具特色，但也有共通之处，而这种从个性中提炼出来的共性，就是人们所说的潮商精神。</span></strong>它的精髓定义很广，包括了勤劳节俭、团结拼搏、聪明灵活、精明能干、胆识过人、敢为人先、义字当头、信守信用、慈善为怀、大爱无疆等等优秀的潮商品质。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61374&size=300x300&key=aaae027b20405861&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61374\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">印尼地产大亨曾国奎对于潮商集体有自己的认识：“我们是很小的一族群，我们能够生存，就是大家在一起，团结在一起，抱团。”在他看来，潮商之所以有从祖辈世代传承，生存下来并壮大的力量，正是因为他们的团结。他们的父辈、祖辈一穷二白，都是白手起家，靠的就是彼此之间的彼此团结，一方有难八方支援，才能在激烈的商业竞争中创出属于潮商的一席之地来。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61375&size=300x300&key=67367284f488a73e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61375\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">真金不怕火炼，潮商在商海沉浮中无畏无惧，不言放弃，信守承诺的精神，是他们取得成功的关键；而成功后知恩图报，饮水思源，能够用自己的力量奉献爱心，回馈社会，则是潮商英雄本色更全面的体现。潮汕人的脚步踏遍天涯海角，潮汕人的精神也会随之得到继承与传扬，不仅是在潮汕本土，还会随着潮商的步伐，绵延全世界。</em></strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012448825263.png\" title=\"1460012448825263.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">来源/汕头电视台《天下潮商》</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/关雪&nbsp;&nbsp;博尔</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=61326&size=300x300&key=9760b51e7c1216a4&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_61326\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></span><br/></p>','2016-03-09 09:41:34',0,NULL,1,NULL,2164,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (345,'【北京潮商】进京！带上我的兄弟姐妹','201603090942454788.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012465225486.png\" title=\"1460012465225486.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">编者按：</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">作为天下潮商的一部分，北京潮商的奋斗过程同样充满精彩。他们捕获了商机，打响了名头，获得了利益的同时，还为自己，为潮商群体挣得了众口称赞的好口碑。北京潮商用行动为潮商历史添上了一笔浓墨重彩的传奇。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59356&size=300x300&key=ed10150bc7bec8eb&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59356\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">北京是中国的首都，也是全国政治、经济和文化中心，距今已有3000多年的建城历史。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">北京这么多年的沉淀，所谓人才荟萃之地、藏龙卧虎之所，不外如是。</span></strong>它是城市当中拥有全球世界文化遗产最多的一个，也是全球拥有世界500强企业总部第二多的城市。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59368&size=300x300&key=5390d7fd40b24403&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59368\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">虽然潮汕地区与京城相距很远，但早在几百年前，就有相当比例的潮籍人士千里迢迢从潮汕大地来到这里。</span></strong>明朝期间，潮籍人士就有36名在京登进士、点状元和出任六部高官。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">出门在外，由于人生地不熟，他乡游子总希望互相之间有个照应，于是，为联络乡亲，北京在清朝初期便建有潮州会馆，在造福桑梓，沟通商贸，方便学子等方面都作出了很大贡献。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">随着商品贸易的发展，清代商人累积财富，地位也因此得以提升，长途贩运的商贸需要对会馆的发展产生了积极的促进作用，而<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮商作为广东商会的一支重要力量，从清雍正开始，与北京城的商贸往来也逐步频繁起来。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59358&size=300x300&key=2689580d6dac6a8e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59358\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 128, 128); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">天津是红头船商人北上贸易的一个据点，也是北京的“卫城”，因此潮商与天津间的贸易，也可看作是潮商与北京间的贸易。</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59359&size=300x300&key=7e17878ddff9e670&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59359\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">北京潮人商会创会会长张善德告诉记者，据记载，潮商在清代乾隆年间最早与北京有关系。</span></strong>当时在北京的琉璃厂，苏州的潮州商会曾经买了一套房子作为北京潮州会馆新馆，说明苏州的潮州商人正是从那时候开始资助北京的。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59360&size=300x300&key=110bdce9ddcec27e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59360\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">尽管潮人与北京的关系可以追溯到数百年前，但在北京的潮汕人数量一直不多，而且直至改革开放前，潮汕人仍然多分布在国家机关、国营企业、军事部门、科研教育、文化艺术等领域，从商的潮汕人几乎没有。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">北京潮商与地处江南一带的苏州、南京等地的潮商相比较而言，影响显然有限，直到改革开放之后，北京潮商才步入兴盛时代。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59361&size=300x300&key=13c8811f63bb563a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59361\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">当改革开放的春风从东南沿海席卷而来，逐渐吹拂过整个华夏大地的时候，尤其是到了上世纪九十年代之后，首都北京逐渐成为一个充满商机的城市，来自四面八方的潮商们在这座城市，开始了他们创业的征程。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">他们将开拓的汗水撒在这座城市里，将独特的潮商精神留在这里，也同样在这里谱下不朽的篇章。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59362&size=300x300&key=7ecf4d8a5f45d230&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59362\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">北京中关村自改革开放以来，迅速发展，已成为初具国际影响力的科教创新资源密集区、我国最具特色和活力的创新中心和高技术产业发展的引领区。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在上世纪80年代初，第一批从本土来到北京的潮汕人就瞄准并聚集在中关村这一带，与此同时他们也把率先开放的特区精神与市场意识，改革开放之初的懵懂与淘金心理，潮汕本土的电子产品、音像产品，和少得可怜的一点积蓄都一并带到了这片沃土之上。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59363&size=300x300&key=28b51ddd4823a08f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59363\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59364&size=300x300&key=4b2e1f0e2f5303b9&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59364\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">时任北京科宏伟业科技有限公司总经理的余映丰告诉记者，他们最开始都是以电子电容起家的。</span></strong>由潮汕人经营的档口在这里大约有300家，占整个市场的四成左右，光是他在这个市场就同时拥有好几个档口。在这里，随处都能听见潮汕乡音<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">。而潮汕人之所以在这里聚集，除了能把电子元器件产品从本土潮阳等地带来以外，还由于潮汕人闯天下的时候，一直将 “哥哥先出门，发展好了把兄弟姐妹都带出去”的模式延续至今。</span></strong>余映丰自己在来北京之后，就将他的姐姐妹妹，以及堂妹和周围的很多亲戚朋友都一并带了过来。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59366&size=300x300&key=af9429aaab417d30&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59366\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">一家电子城商户告诉记者，他的户口在汕头，但人来到这里已经有十年了。他身旁还跟着一个年轻人，也是从汕头过来的。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">中关村的潮汕人都是从最草根的平民阶层而来，他们赤手空拳，能够凭借的只有自己的勤劳、智慧，却通过努力把根深深地扎在了中关村。如今在中关村，这个北京潮商最为聚集的区域之一，一部分潮商至今仍在追逐着自己商业梦想的道路上奋斗拼博，也有一部分如今已经出类拔萃，成为巨富。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59365&size=300x300&key=3fd54f6c96d053c5&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59365\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59367&size=300x300&key=fc551a2676cce0e3&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59367\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮汕人在历史的长河中一直流动不息，这个从中原移民到潮汕的族群会奔赴任何一处，有商业机会，和良好生存条件的地方，在那里创业求索，获得自身发展的同时，潮商也推动着当地的发展。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012472481525.png\" title=\"1460012472481525.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台综合报道 转载请注明出处</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">来源/汕头电视台 《天下潮商》</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/关雪&nbsp;&nbsp;博尔</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59308&size=300x300&key=e44fc38ba5900b1d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59308\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></span><br/></p>','2016-03-09 09:42:45',0,NULL,1,NULL,2206,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (346,'【北京潮商】张章笋——一个大写的地产界奇迹','201603090943335579.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012486154914.png\" title=\"1460012486154914.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">编者按：</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">有道是三十年河东，三十年河西，在北京的城南，这片原本少人问津的地方，在短短一二十年间就成了北京的黄金宝地。或许很多人并不知道，创造出如此奇迹的并不是北京商人，而是远赴首都拼搏奋斗的潮商。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59445&size=300x300&key=e00721948a9abfa0&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59445\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮商长途跋涉2000多公里，从南方的潮汕来到北京，他们迅速融入当地社会，充分发挥他们的聪明才智，尽情挥洒他们的执着与汗水，在这座伟大的城市当中努力地生存和发展，将属于他们的印迹深深地烙在了这里。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">上个世纪90年代以后，特别是跨入二十一世纪之后，北京城的城市建设被迅速拉开，得益于国际大都市的定位和申奥成功的欢呼声，其建设势如破竹。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">旧城改造也同样展开，速度一日千里，其中的机会被嗅觉敏锐的潮汕商人迅速捕捉，利润最为丰厚的地产行业也因此被他们杀出了一条血路。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59433&size=300x300&key=f385758d48a115ac&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59433\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59434&size=300x300&key=39492722734ad05e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59434\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在北京潮商当中，有一些诸如“旧城改造领军人”、“商业地产改革家”等的新词汇，都与一个名字紧密相连，他就是张章笋，北京国瑞兴业地产有限公司的董事长，时任北京潮人商会会长。</span></strong>张章笋何其有幸，能够让自己的名字与一个时代的新生事物联系在一起，但对于张章笋来说，这种幸运的背后，是他的非凡胆识。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59435&size=300x300&key=a5a56d4ee2fb910c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59435\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">老北京人有一种口口相传的说法：“崇文穷、宣武破，长安街以南无商机”。在老北京人眼中看来，南城的风水不如北城，后者是居住的宝地，而前者则不适合居住。因此，尽管开发南城的倡议一再被政府部门提出，但仍然没有愿意去南城的开发商和北京市民。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">一位老北京市民告诉记者，北面是上风上水，而南面相对较差，从传统的风水来讲，北面风水优于南面，加上南面水质也不是很好，因此北京人都喜欢上北来。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">然而在张章笋眼中，不仅热是商机，冷的更加充满商机。</span></strong>南城表面上一潭死水，有大片需要改造的旧房，但张章笋却从中嗅到了商机。潮商向来勇于开拓、敢于冒险，张章笋也因此毅然率先投身南城开发行伍当中。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59436&size=300x300&key=10fd455113ec8ef1&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59436\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">张章笋告诉记者，他1999年来到北京的时候，北京的房地产市场正处于活跃的增长期，旧城改造、建设新的住宅区都相对较早，他拿下的富贵园项目在二环内，位于广渠门大街，是当时北京旧城改造的试点项目，这个项目共建了4800多套住宅，占地面积230亩，建设规模为630万。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59437&size=300x300&key=9b36b82ddd1eebae&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59437\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">富贵园在2003年以9.70亿元的销售总额一炮打响，跻身北京十大热销楼盘。</span></strong>张章笋过人的胆识和独到的眼光，让他在京城掘到第一桶金，也由此打出了属于国瑞地产自己的品牌。他不仅将充满南方、汕头特点的建筑带给北京城，更是把开拓进取的精神留在了这片土地上，潮商这个群体也因此令北京人刮目相看。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59438&size=300x300&key=3c8d818b3f7e5aeb&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59438\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 128, 128); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">国瑞城是张章笋继富贵园之后，在京城开发的第二个项目，该项目同样处在北京城南。</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">国瑞城占据的位置是崇文商圈的心脏区域，占地面积共有16公顷，对人们在商务、办公、居住、购物、休闲等多个方面的需要都能同时满足，被称为“长安街畔的建筑航母”。 这座“城中城”也是北京二环内最大体量的建筑综合体，成为京城又一个新地标。张章笋所构筑的北京国瑞兴业地产历经十多年的奋斗与拼搏，如今已是一家综合性地产企业，公司规模不断扩大，已经不仅限于北京范围，而是逐渐向河北、沈阳、海南等多地扩张。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59442&size=300x300&key=350e691b92ac0d50&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59442\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59440&size=300x300&key=06b8f43d20b41d45&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59440\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59441&size=300x300&key=89b0acfde603ee6b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59441\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">永清国瑞生态城于2011年8月16日在河北廊坊永清县举行奠基典礼。</span></strong>整个生态城计划开发时间预计在10至15年，总投资200亿元，规划占地37平方公里。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59443&size=300x300&key=1fc4fbf70e90c0fc&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59443\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">张章笋认为，改善城市，营造新的生态环境，创造新的产业园、现代农业，是自己应该进行的一种积极探索，因此，他在城郊建设生态城，希望能够以此将城市城郊的休闲农业、家庭小农场的概念摸索创造出来。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59444&size=300x300&key=e37aa07b21b8a757&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59444\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">从经营酒店，到进军房地产，再到参与一座城的开发建设，张章笋不断创新、颠覆传统商业地产模式，一步步稳健前行，创造地产奇迹。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012493851082.png\" title=\"1460012493851082.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台综合报道 转载请注明出处</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">来源/汕头电视台 《天下潮商》</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/关雪</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59409&size=300x300&key=217c89ec609f0d9c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59409\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br/></p>','2016-03-09 09:43:33',0,NULL,1,NULL,2311,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (347,'【北京潮商】到北京去  成就自己的事业','201603090944101057.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012505135016.png\" title=\"1460012505135016.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">编者按：</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">不是每一次伟大的创业都需要白手起家，但是每一次的成功都离不开机遇和胆识。首都是一个充满机遇的地方，这也使得天子脚下的商战显得扑簌迷离。北京潮商，就是在混战中逐步成熟发展的。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59386&size=300x300&key=b0620b8d2631e8f8&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59386\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">与赤手空拳在北京白手起家的潮商不同，有另一类进京的潮商大军，他们的原始资本积累是在改革开放的前沿广东完成的，而后也没有错过在北京发展的历史机遇，因而在北京进行投资，成就自己的事业。</span></strong>其中，以合生创展的朱孟依、国瑞兴业的张章笋、联美投资的苏壮强、阳柳集团的陈才雄、华旺集团的林辉勇等人是这一类潮商的典型代表。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">时任北京潮人商会秘书长的孙夏安告诉记者，一部分在京的潮汕房地产企业家是在广东迈出第一步，而后在天时地利人和的时机来到北京的，比如陈总，他就是先在广东打下良好的基础，有自己的房地产，接着才来到北京的。现在他在潮阳仍有项目。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59387&size=300x300&key=5117c51c2a9a6fa2&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59387\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">孙夏安口中的陈总，指的就是上世纪80年代在汕头创立阳柳集团的陈才雄。</span></strong>他从经营包装、建筑材料和进出口业务开始，一步步脚踏实地，让多元化经营的格局逐渐形成。1996年，阳柳集团耗资数亿参与汕头的旧城改造，以此正式进军房地产。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">当时正是房地产发展得如火如荼、势头强劲的阶段，陈才雄毅然参与到北京的房地产开发当中。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">阳柳集团董事长、时任北京潮人商会常务副会长陈才雄说，在他看来，潮商有属于自己的阳光大道，所以还是应该走出来，这是潮商的生命源泉，只要有金钱和商机的地方，不论是北京，还是美国，如流水一般的潮商都可以前往。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59388&size=300x300&key=c26942b5e45d2000&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59388\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">陈才雄2005年在北京开发建成了一片花园式的洋房，是他在京投资的第一个项目——北京洋房。</span></strong>北京洋房拥有户户跃层的别致设计上中下三叠空间可以在保持低容积率的前提条件下，让空间层次的形成更为丰富，这里的居所看似别墅，实则并非别墅，京城寸土寸金，花园洋房在这里可谓是一大创举。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59390&size=300x300&key=5c5c8759504177af&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59390\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59391&size=300x300&key=d44f2787bf51eabd&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59391\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">洋房的业主告诉记者，这房子在当时的北京来说是绝无仅有的。</span></strong>它兼备一般小区的亲切感和别墅的气质，小区活动的地方很大，而在这里所感受到的别墅的气质，也要比真正的别墅更胜一筹。这在那时候的北京是绝对独此一家的，因此这位业主认为物有所值，住得越久，越发觉得有趣。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 128, 128); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">北京洋房开盘当天成交总额突破1.5亿，尚未真正竣工就已宣告售馨，如此傲人的成绩，一度在北京地产界传为佳话。</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59392&size=300x300&key=82bc3896834ec307&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59392\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">陈才雄说他刚开始到北京时，就下定决心要做一个品牌。</span></strong>他觉得北京已经被钢筋水泥所包围，所有的生活当中都没有生气。阳台、露台是南方人的特色，而北方由于风沙的缘故，则会选择全部封闭起来。在南方人的理念中，应当像花园洋房一样有天有地，敞开式的空间，如果做开发商却不舍得浪费空间，为了多挣钱把它都封起来，这绝不是他愿意做的事情。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">陈才雄在北京开发房地产一贯的理念，就是要做就做品牌。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">所谓的品牌，指的不仅是阳柳集团，还包括了潮商这一伟大商帮的诚信。</span></strong>陈才雄曾经赠送每一位业主一套功夫茶具，这样做是为了让大家知道，北京洋房是潮商投资建成的。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59393&size=300x300&key=da2066fd04266612&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59393\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在上世纪90年代末，北京定位为国际大都市；2001年，北京申奥成功。这两点让潮商中顶尖级的投资者从中看到了商机，因此被吸引而来。数年的时间里，香港长江实业的李嘉诚、泰国磐谷银行的陈有汉、正大集团的谢炳、南洋商业银行的庄世平和香港健兴利珠宝的许先坚等具有广泛国际影响的潮商纷纷进军北京，他们让北京潮商成为国际性的群体，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这也成为北京潮商群体的发展进入成熟阶段的标志。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59394&size=300x300&key=50fa2b5d4515e278&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59394\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">王府井大街是京城最繁华、最热闹的大街，在这条大街上，有一间占地近4000平米的珠宝饰品专营店，是京城同类专营店中最大的一家，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">有“中国翡翠第一家”之称，名为健兴利珠宝。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59395&size=300x300&key=ade1f7bde5e59e79&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59395\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59396&size=300x300&key=0df797799bf0bf92&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59396\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">著名潮商许先坚于1992年创建健兴利珠宝，第一家店面设于香港，这一中国翡翠珠宝品牌在国际上具有很大影响力，港澳台及东南亚地区中高端翡翠市场六成以上的份额都归它所有。</span></strong>健兴利珠宝在2005年开始将发展的目光从香港转到北京，并进军内地市场。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">时任香港健兴利珠宝有限公司董事的许先辉告诉记者，他们进驻大陆做零售是在七年前，广州是第一站，第二站是北京的旗舰店，发展到现在已经有28家。因为北京作为首都，拥有浓厚的玉文化底蕴，所以他们决定在北京大力投资，光是王府井大街的旗舰店就投入了7、8个亿的资金。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59397&size=300x300&key=9c861572177bfc15&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59397\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">商人逐利，因此不惜远赴他乡开拓事业；但对于潮商来说，还有比钱更加重要的东西，那就是自己的品牌和潮商的名声。君子爱财，取之有道，绝不错过任何一个商机，也绝不为了眼前的蝇头小利而损害消费者的利益，这是北京潮商，也是天下潮商取得成功的一大原因。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012513136109.png\" title=\"1460012513136109.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台综合报道 转载请注明出处</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">来源/汕头电视台 《天下潮商》</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/关雪</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59374&size=300x300&key=70e5a957e8972f91&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59374\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br/></p>','2016-03-09 09:44:10',0,NULL,1,NULL,2169,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (348,'【北京潮商】上善若水  顺势而为','201603090945006041.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012527525848.png\" title=\"1460012527525848.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">编者按：</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮商想要在异地他乡取得成功，想要在北京这个人才济济之地崭露头角，搏一方广阔天地，光靠自己显然很难做到。所谓滴水易干，而大海无涸，融入北京社会，是北京潮商在事业上致胜的一大法宝。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59643&size=300x300&key=49ff47637123a907&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59643\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 128, 128); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">有一句话说得好，叫潮商如流水，广大潮商来自遥远的南方，在北京投资、创业，他们需要迈出的第一步，就是想办法融入这座北方的城市，让这座城市接纳自己，而后方才能在这个市场中开疆拓土。</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">改革开放初期进京创业的第一代潮商当中涌现出许许多多的成功人士，林鑫就是其中一个。</span></strong>身为北京金天坛食品有限责任公司董事长的他，仍旧清楚地记得自己初到北京时感受过的陌生、不安、甚至彷徨。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59644&size=300x300&key=dbf326505858ea5b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59644\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">林鑫说：“我来北京以后也确实不容易，在后面当老板，刚才这个大哥是北京人，跟我十几年，一直都是他挂的法人代表，我在后面经营。”</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59645&size=300x300&key=06d086501614145b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59645\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">由于北京人排外的缘故，除了周日以外，市容（管理）、工商、税务等各个部门轮番上阵，很难有舒服的日子过。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">后来，林鑫意识到自己就必须进入主流社会，否则在北京将更加寸步难行。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">跻身主流社会是林鑫为了融入北京城、谋求事业发展而选择的一种方式。</span></strong>如今，他除了要发展自己的企业，还同时肩负着如北京市东城区政协委员、民建北京市委委员等多项社会职务。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59646&size=300x300&key=98b89c8a223715de&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59646\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">林鑫向记者展示了一张他在2009年参加新中国成立60周年列兵仪式的照片。</span></strong>他认为这张照片很是有趣，当时他就在天安门对面，人民大会堂的看台上。他于十年前就成为政协委员，至今已是第二届了，等换届之后就是第三届。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">他去年还因认真撰写了十几份提案而获得优秀提案奖的殊荣。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59647&size=300x300&key=6e99247da1b12c87&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59647\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">林鑫写的提案当中，有一份是关于将北京前门地区建设为“东城区京味文化产业发展总部基地”的。这份提案在当年荣获东城区政协的优秀提案奖。</span></strong>如今，前门大街已经完成了改造，其中一些部位的改造设计方案正是参考林鑫的提案进行的。从一个北京城里的看客，华丽转身成为城市发展的建设者；一个来自外地的客人在京城成为主任，林鑫融入北京城，并跻身主流社会的梦想顺利完成。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59648&size=300x300&key=13ba5d071d5c1b76&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59648\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59649&size=300x300&key=f0c7569b4e0e6ccb&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59649\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">林鑫告诉记者，经过好几次调研之后他发现，工厂不适合设在崇文区和东城区，因为这两个区是中心城区，但是这里也有属于自己的特色，诸如饮食文化的背景等，都应该得到体现，因此林鑫拟了一个提案，建议在北京前门建成京味文化一条街。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59650&size=300x300&key=5a5520cfb8aeb531&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59650\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">林鑫通过这样的一种融入之后，北京已经被他当成了第二故乡。</span></strong>林鑫认为，想要融入北京，就应当为当地社会尽自己更大的努力，只有把自己的社会责任全力承担起来，才能得到这座城市的认同、接纳。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">林鑫认为，对于全世界的潮州人来说，主题已经不是做生意赚钱，而是如何走进主流社会，后者才是潮州人真正要思考的问题。</span></strong>商会有责任把包括在加拿大、澳大利亚，在全世界各地的优秀潮州青年推进两会，让潮州人能够借此传达出自己的声音来，所以商会必须有一定要融入主流社会的意识。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59651&size=300x300&key=3c0a660325caa91f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59651\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">北京华流文化发展有限公司董事长郑康淳同样是潮商，但他选择了和林鑫不同的融入京城的方式，他的做法是广交朋友。</span></strong>在他的手机通讯录当中，潮汕人只有几十个，但总数却有一千多个朋友的联系方式。郑康淳的广交朋友和广结人脉为他赢得巨大商机，他后来也因此获益，得到了后奥运时代场馆运营机会，进入主流经济集团。郑康淳谈起自己的经历感触颇多。当初他们也遭到过很多白眼，迈过的艰辛坎坷无数，也曾经在很多陌生的地方跟他人进行过交流。思想文化等各方面的碰撞，得到的收益最大，越往外走，思想迸发也会越多，也能提升自己的智慧。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59652&size=300x300&key=aded05a34eeffe42&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59652\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">新时期潮商的其中一个基本特点就是融入主流社会与主流经济，我们可以在每一个成功的潮商身上听到一个类似的故事：他们不断发展自己的事业，同时不断造福当地，尽自己所能回馈当地社会，最终成功融入当地社会，获得大家认可的过程。比如谢炳、朱孟依这两位潮商顶尖人物都是全国政协委员，时任北京潮人商会会长张章笋担任了北京市政协委员、北京工商联执委等等。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59653&size=300x300&key=e572ef7673b9f99c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59653\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮汕人有一句话说得很贴切——“入乡随俗，入湾随湾”。历经多年的风雨飘摇，潮商虽乡音未改，潮风依旧，但他们所拥有的惊人的适应能力和融入能力，以及因此所带来的巨大推动力，让潮商这个群体在事业上取得了巨大成功。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012538903280.png\" title=\"1460012538903280.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台综合报道 转载请注明出处</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">来源/汕头电视台 《天下潮商》</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/关雪</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59574&size=300x300&key=6dc07a79d3b1459e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59574\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span><br/></p>','2016-03-09 09:45:00',0,NULL,1,NULL,2156,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (349,'【北京潮商】潮汕文化“软植入”放大招：美食在北京','201603090945403427.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012549331387.png\" title=\"1460012549331387.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">编者按：</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">民以食为天，悠久的历史文明之中，不论海内海外，古人今人，一个绝对缺少不了的话题就是美食。在北京的潮菜酒楼用餐，如今已经被看做是高大上的代名词之一，潮汕美食文化在北京的推广，自然也离不开许许多多潮商的努力。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59598&size=300x300&key=026f19ac89c8a109&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59598\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮汕美食闻名遐迩，潮商进入北京的同时，也将潮汕的美食文化带到了北京。</span></strong>北京饭店座落在长安街上，自开业至今已有上百年。1949年10月1日晚，一场盛大的宴会在北京饭店举行，周恩来总理亲自审定了所有的菜单，这次宴会后来被公认为“开国第一宴”， 北京饭店也由此奠定了自己在中国餐饮业的地位。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59592&size=300x300&key=bd5b45c4018cbdb0&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59592\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59593&size=300x300&key=c849320d7751fe5f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59593\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59594&size=300x300&key=c0f41bc91c72de6c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59594\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">北京饭店是国家旅游局涉外的指定饭店，它的其中一个重要功能就是展现中国历史悠久、博大精深的饮食文化。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮州菜是广东菜三大菜系之一，潮商黄锡昂于2000年将其带进了北京饭店。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">踏入北京饭店的大门，饭店的前台位于左侧，右侧是安华城的入口，顺楼梯而下就能到达安华城。安华城占地4000多平方米，有北京饭店地下金銮殿之称，整个餐厅都是中式奢华的装修风格，除就餐大厅之外，还有23个各具风格的包间，贵客如云的气势扑面而来。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59591&size=300x300&key=e6a5236269f4b6cd&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59591\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">时任北京市安华食品有限公司总经理助理的黄泽强告诉记者，这种中式的奢华，在下了楼梯进入安华城之后，真的有切身体会。北京是文明古都、古色古香，装修等各方面都有讲究，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">与此同时，一些潮汕的特色也融入其中，当时请了一些有名的木雕师，还有一些地方贴了999金。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59596&size=300x300&key=4bcc7e39ce0b9048&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59596\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">安华城酒楼的董事长黄锡昂有一句座右铭，非常能代表在京潮商的精神：“为首都打造精品，让世界了解潮人”。 潮汕崇尚奢华的黄金装饰文化，鲍鱼、红烧官燕这两样最具代表性的潮菜都被安华城带进了北京，让北京人也得以真正体领略潮汕美食的风采。现如今，已有无数家潮汕酒楼落户北京城，包括周泽荣的潮皇食府、张成雄的好世界海鲜大酒楼、张章笋的一道香酒楼等等，都在北京城声名远扬。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">他们不仅是简单地经营一家酒楼，更重要的是把为京城带来潮汕的饮食文化。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59595&size=300x300&key=8505b3719218fcd1&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59595\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59597&size=300x300&key=d8a3bf317cd1b1ce&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59597\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">北京潮商的群体从配角到主角，从默默无闻到声名显赫，在短短二三十年间逐步扩大。</span></strong>据不完全统计，目前大约有10余万在京潮人，其中绝大多数为商界人士。这些潮商来自四面八方，在拼博创业的发展过程当中，他们都将自己的汗水挥洒在北京这座城市的建设之中，同时也在首都的历史之中镌刻下潮汕的人文精神。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮商精神和潮文化的哺育，六朝古都厚重底蕴的影响渗透，让一大批潮资企业和潮籍企业家迅速崛起，一个秉承着潮商精神和潮文化精华的当代潮商群体在中国首都茁壮成长。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">北京潮人商会于2004年应运而生，从此在首都北京，广大潮籍乡亲拥有了一个共同的家。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59599&size=300x300&key=7f7b73bf1e58152b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59599\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">时任北京潮人商会秘书长的孙夏安告诉记者，到记者采访时，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">他们的商会已历经七年时光，大概有500名商会会员，囊括了房地产、建筑装修、建材、文具玩具、服装百货，酒店餐饮，IT，网络，服务等各行各业的人士。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59600&size=300x300&key=d02b0c953afaef27&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59600\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在京潮商实力的一大见证便是北京潮人商会的成立，新一届商会会长张章笋在宣誓就任时，就以团结、促进、服务、回报的核心理念为基础，为商会的未来发展提出四项新举措，分别是创立“北京潮商财富基金”、建立“潮商产业园”、组织骨干企业参与北京和潮汕两地建设。此外，张章笋还组织会员继续加大投入公益慈善事业。他们不仅尽其所能帮助扶持在京企业继续发展壮大，更是最大限度地彰显潮商品牌与价值，回馈社会、造福大众，勇敢肩负潮商的责任。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 128, 128); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">时任北京潮人商会常务副会长的林辉勇告诉记者，他们成立商会的主要目的是提供服务，成立的财富资金先为企业服务，为我们在京的小企业雪中送炭。</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59601&size=300x300&key=10485e8b43a6fd63&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59601\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">张章笋介绍到，今年主要为防止建筑工地艾滋病蔓延等原因，给红丝带捐赠1000万。在他看来，扶贫济困、助学公益这一方面随着经济发展和生活质量改善，变得越来越窄，人们的生活水平逐年提高，需要扶贫济困的人也越来越少，因此，公益和慈善应该潮更大的社会面，更深的深度去伸展，真正办实事，发挥积极作用。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">时任全国政协港澳台侨委员会副主任委员的张伟超认为，把全国的潮商都联系起来，让大家都像一家人一样相处，彼此保持联系，这样对潮商自身业务的发展很有助益，可以增强实力、提高水平，还能将海内外的各国潮商都联络到一起，让潮商的影响变得非常巨大。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮商在改革开放三十多年间，成就大业的一大重要舞台就是首都北京。</span></strong>这些年，所发生的事，所经历的人，都是北京潮人商会成长与北京潮商发展壮大的见证。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在人民大会堂举行了第三届北京潮人商会年会，潮商这个独特的群体也因此让世人刮目相看。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59602&size=300x300&key=0c48193fd1fb2833&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59602\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">时任全国政协副主席、全国工商联主席的黄孟复告诉记者，面向大海的潮汕风土让潮商拥有大胆创新的精神，艰苦勤劳的作风，以及爱国恋家的品德，为潮商赢得了国人的尊重。如今的中国正处在十二五规划期，经济发展面临新机遇，黄孟复相信，我们广大的民营企业包括潮商在内，都一定能够在我国调整经济结构和转变发展方式当中，发挥越来越重要的作用，诸如潮汕美食等潮汕的文化软实力，也一定能让北京乃至世界各地的人们，都充分领略和惊叹。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012556166403.png\" title=\"1460012556166403.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台综合报道 转载请注明出处</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">来源/汕头电视台 《天下潮商》</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/关雪</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59603&size=300x300&key=a09ee328a15d943d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59603\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></span><br/></p>','2016-03-09 09:45:40',0,NULL,1,NULL,2177,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (350,'【北京潮商】潮商精神在北京：当一个做蛋糕的人','201603090946233382.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012571723364.png\" title=\"1460012571723364.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">编者按：</em></strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">对于潮商来说，按部就班，延续前人做法从来都不是他们的第一选择，不断地开拓创新才是潮商贯彻始终的创业法则。无论是经营模式上的改良，还是产品设计上的创意，都只是潮商改革创新精神的冰山一角。</em></strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59625&size=300x300&key=13921fc31a7dcd48&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59625\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在北京站稳脚跟、发展壮大的有不少实力非凡、势头强劲的京城地产界潮商，其中既有老牌，也有新秀。</span></strong>不论是朱孟依的珠江地产，黄光裕的鹏润地产，还是林辉勇的北京永利多，所有的地产潮商背后都有一段充满了传奇性的精彩故事，潮汕商人的辉煌篇章也正是由他们共同谱写而成的。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">时任中国房地产行业协会会长的聂梅生告诉记者，她曾经参加过在北京举办的潮汕商会成立大会，当时来了很多名人，热闹非凡，带给她很大的震撼，那时候她就意识到，潮商的经济理念在中国可以说独具特色，也已经扎根在京城了。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">好啃的骨头总会被人捷足先登，但善于冒险的潮商丝毫不惧，他们勇于进取，迎难而上，有一种先啃硬骨头的执着。</span></strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59615&size=300x300&key=bfd3582273303b38&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59615\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">北京城作为中国的政治文化中心，在思想意识和体制机制等方面都显得传统和保守。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮汕商人为北京城带来了沿海开放的精神与市场经济的气息，他们用自己的经商头脑为中国的首都注入改革开放的活力。</span></strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59616&size=300x300&key=75f23ff93d77dbaf&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59616\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59617&size=300x300&key=fa0c4ae9adbe0038&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59617\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">1988年，北京市万家利食品有限公司总经理陈俊兴开始进入北京，发展食品贸易，当时行业的销售模式还很落后，正是陈俊兴为进行的大胆创新改变了传统的销售模式。</strong></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">陈俊兴对当时的经历依旧记忆犹新。那时候北京的食品公司，国营单位仍旧占绝大多数，体制也尚未脱离计划经济的桎梏，。这些公司被称为副食品公司，又称糖酒公司。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59618&size=300x300&key=5a64245a35f03a38&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59618\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在那样的背景下，他们成立了传统模式的营销公司，负责为卖场、门店配货，几乎是坐销的性质，但是陈俊兴在售后服务方面下足功夫，进行上门服务，并且通过海报等方式进行形象宣传。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">陈俊兴改变了计划经济时期坐等顾客上门的销售模式，主动出击，通过积极营销、开拓市场，改变了北京食品零售行业暮气沉沉的状态带，也因此脱颖而出。</span></strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59619&size=300x300&key=ee521d873c29d975&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59619\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">最开始进行的是嘉宝、集味村、雅士利等潮汕本土品牌的代理，发展至今，他的公司代理的食品品牌已有一千多个，北京几乎所有的商场超市都被覆盖。</span></span></span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">陈俊兴一直为自己是潮商的一份子深感自豪。他很清楚潮商的思想与文化与北京当地差别很大，但在他看来，北京的潮商如今已经很成功了，未来也一定会不断努力，继续前行的。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">郑康淳同样是一匹黑马，不同的是他所投身的是北京的旅游市场。</span></strong>身为来自潮汕大地的六零后，郑康淳胆识过人、善于创新，能力出众，凭此在残酷的商业竞争中取得胜利，无论是国家奥体中心的运营商，还是代表国家形象的水立方、鸟巢的中间服务商，最终都成为他的囊中之物。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59620&size=300x300&key=dd0154038c41a1f0&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59620\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">郑康淳告诉记者，当时在建设奥运场馆的时候，就考虑到奥运会结束之后的一些运营事项，因此在当时的设计方案中，就有戏水乐园的设计，同时根据奥运场馆在奥运会之后的转型为游客进行配套设施的准备。比如孩子们身上穿的水立方的泳衣，就是他们开发的，此外，他们还完成了餐饮等配套设施设备的建设。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59621&size=300x300&key=10e0ba5a8b5c9b03&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59621\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59622&size=300x300&key=ebda37294ad4cec7&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59622\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">现在，包括颐和园在内的很多景区，对他们打造旅游快餐品牌的概念都已逐渐持接受的态度，因此郑康淳的公司的经营范围已经从旅游服务纪念品延伸到餐饮。</span></span></span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">创意设计是郑康淳的公司当中，公认的最核心部门，他的公司拥有北京最大的创意设计团队，从这里诞生了上千种在市场上销售的奥运场馆纪念品。郑康淳的旅游产品、品牌化运作模式极具创意，对旅游产品缺少个性、同质化严重的现状进行了彻底的颠覆，也在很大程度上让人们对传统旅游纪念品的印象大为改观。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59629&size=300x300&key=75d34b74c6a687de&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59629\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">郑康淳向记者介绍了正在申请、筹备阶段的中国旅游商品研发设计中心。</span></strong>郑康淳以公司为主体，进行这个中心的筹备申请，如今在这个中心里面，已经开发了包括鸟巢、水立方的、中国科技馆的，还有戏水乐园、颐和园等的系列产品。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">他们的产品现在是水立方的主要旅游商品，接下来他们还打算进行更多的项目，包括还要北京著名商标，以及中国驰名商标的申请等。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59623&size=300x300&key=d26ff32aa264aa6f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59623\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">事实证明，品牌化运作旅游产品是郑康淳的一大正确决定，也取得了巨大成功。</span></strong>水立方的门票收入在2010年达到1.1亿元，场馆内旅游纪念品零售额也随之大幅提升，突破7000万元大关，这样的业绩在当时的北京旅游纪念品市场当中，是当之无愧的史上第一。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">郑康淳考虑得更多的不是分一杯羹，怎样在原有的基础上，通过创新来制造一块更大的蛋糕。</span></strong>而他们自己只会分享其中的一块，这样做首先提升了这个行业，为这个行业做出自己的贡献，其次在提升之后进行区分，帮助这个行业身边的同行业，如此一来，郑康淳与同行业的人士都能够和睦相处，合作共赢，而不至于引来他人的仇视。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59624&size=300x300&key=77e0a69f07156649&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59624\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">有这样一句霸气十足的标语一直高悬在郑康淳的公司入口处：行业因我们而改变。</span></strong>在旅游市场分蛋糕从来不是他的选择，当那个做蛋糕的人才是他一直追求的目标，他希望通过自己的努力，能改变整个行业。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012581216449.png\" title=\"1460012581216449.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台综合报道 转载请注明出处</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">来源/汕头电视台 《天下潮商》</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/关雪</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59608&size=300x300&key=660c3427abdc96a7&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59608\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-03-09 09:46:23',0,NULL,1,NULL,2274,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (351,'【广州潮商】日久他乡即故乡','201603090947187436.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012594135279.png\" title=\"1460012594135279.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">编者按：</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">粤地之奇，乃因此处聚粤潮客三种地方文化，内部文化差异大，多种文化色彩绚烂。但是地方语言与地方习俗的差异却没有让潮人停下脚步，潮人在这些地方感受着异乡风味，仍不忘手里抓住潮文化的根，生活于兹，却把这里活出了别样的“潮味”。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59771&size=300x300&key=ca7ef1ff40ecfe64&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59771\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(139, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮汕人所到之处都会留下自己的点点痕迹，远至海外，近在广府，皆有迹可寻。</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">“潮人善经商，尤不可及者，为商业冒险进行之精神，其赢而入，一遇眼光所达之点，辄悉投资于中，万一失败，犹足自立，一旦胜利，倍蓰其赢，而商业上之挥斥益雄。”&nbsp;&nbsp;——《清稗类钞》</em></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">广州，北缘珠三角，濒临南中国海，西江、北江、东江三江在此汇合，隔海与香港、澳门特别行政区相望。它是海上丝绸之路的起点之一，曾经“商贾如云，货物如雨，万足践履，冬无寒土”，而今，它依然是中国最具活力的城市之一。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这里有优越的地理位置，也是商业贸易的天堂。在这座2200年历史的广州城，潮人几时涉足这里，时间已不可考。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59770&size=300x300&key=29678880e46e1fa0&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59770\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(139, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">现如今，在广州白云区钟落潭镇红旗村的大庄，就居住着一批210多年前移民到广州的潮汕人后裔，在这里，街头巷尾，无论耄耋老人还是黄口小儿，都能讲一口潮汕话，因此也被称为“潮汕村”。</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59772&size=300x300&key=ce0ebc8b631a6f6f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59772\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这里多聚集的是谢姓和吴姓的人家，谢姓祖宗来到广州后卖菜种地，而吴姓祖宗则是做竹筐、卖竹筐的，因此两姓人家俱兴俱荣。经历两百多年繁衍，由最初的两人发展成现在近千人的小村庄，像他们这么大规模的潮汕人聚集成村在广州并不多见。按照族谱，村里辈分最大的已经是第6代的“远”字辈，在这一辈人中，年纪最轻的也已经69岁，而村里辈分现在已经排到了“义”字辈。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">尽管在广州已久，不过在潮汕村还是保留着一些潮汕特有的传统习俗。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">比如在这里有男丁出世，就在正月十五上灯，而广州本地人的习俗则是在初二或初四上灯的。在这里的小孩也是从小就是以潮汕话为母语的。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59773&size=300x300&key=5ae57cd7c82ea858&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59773\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这里如同一个缩影，浓缩着广州与潮汕早期渊源和联系。</span></strong>几百年来，许多潮商在广州落地生根，他们努力融入当地文化，遵从当地习俗，但骨子里依然保存着潮汕人独特的内涵，他们以吃苦耐劳、坚忍不拔著称，他们审时度势、灵活变通，诚信为上、以义致利，他们勇于探索、持续创新，他们是喜欢厚结人缘的工作伙伴，他们特有的人文特征形成了强大的社会竞争力。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59774&size=300x300&key=6660370ff259f230&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59774\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">时任中山大学副校长的陈春声评价道，潮汕人有一种商业理性，或者可以说是某种商业的实用主义，所以相对来说，以潮汕人特有的传统或者思维方式，他们比较容易适应不同的环境、不同的文化、不同的制度，也比较善于跟不同的族群、甚至是不同文化背景下的人打交道。</span></strong>潮州商人相对来说自主性会比较强，因为相比于徽州商人和山西商人在整个发家经营过程里面，跟政府，特别是传统时期跟王朝的关系会比较密切，潮州商人更多的是依靠自己的自主发展。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59775&size=300x300&key=8235ba18a0ecd531&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59775\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012602777455.png\" title=\"1460012602777455.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">来源/汕头电视台 《天下潮商》</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/博尔</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59745&size=300x300&key=78987d282b4947cb&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59745\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></span><br/></p>','2016-03-09 09:47:18',0,NULL,1,NULL,2265,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (352,'【广州潮商】另辟蹊径不是问题','201603090948025663.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012615130855.png\" title=\"1460012615130855.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">编者按：</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">世上的路都是人走出来的，但是如果走的人过多了，这条路也就被走烂了。然而总会有那么些眼光独到之人，能够在尘世繁杂中找出一条生僻的路。虽然生僻之路无人垦荒，遍布扎人的荆棘，但是一旦走出来了，便成就了一条康庄大道。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59816&size=300x300&key=30dd7a9f55bc56eb&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59816\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在广州荔湾区，依托西关文化深厚的底藴和积淀，这里有一个全新打造的动感小西关，而中国日化行业领军者立白集团就位于这里，它的当家人正是潮商陈凯旋。</span></strong>在业界，很多人都惊叹陈凯旋敏锐的眼光和灵活的经商头脑，但这位企业领路人给人的第一印象却是温和而低调。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59811&size=300x300&key=df2d81a3eebc0866&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59811\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">陈凯旋说，立白的传统精神其实是潮商的精神，根植于潮汕人的文化——拼搏进取、勤劳节俭、艰苦奋斗、敢为人先、敢于超越、尽忠尽孝、低调谦虚、求真务实、永不言败、永远创业。立白的“五立”文化就是立信、立责、立质、立真、立先。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">因为自己是从潮汕走出来的人，带着潮汕优良的传统。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(244, 164, 96);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">嗅出商机 果断入行</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">1994年，正是改革开放的春风吹遍大地之时，处在改革开放前沿的广州更是充满了商机。</span></strong>这一年，拥有“浪奇”等当时华南市场知名民族日化品牌的广州浪奇，与刚刚落地广州不久的宝洁和黄有限公司合资3000万美元组建了广州浪奇宝洁有限公司。曾做过洗衣粉代理商的陈凯旋敏锐地嗅出，日化，必是一个庞大的市场。当时，陈凯旋可谓一无资金二无货源，别说建工厂、请工人，甚至没有足够的钱去买洗衣粉的生产配方。但对于敢于冒险的潮商来说，该出手时绝不拖泥带水。陈凯旋灵机一动，用了一招前无古人的做法——“OEM贴牌生产”，他找到了一家生产日化产品的工厂为他们加工产品。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">虽然贴牌生产现在是普遍的经营模式，但在当时却是开了全国日化行业的先河。也是在这一年，“借鸡生蛋”的立白洗衣粉终于在广州破壳而出。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59815&size=300x300&key=3269c3b6d01c7b8d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59815\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">当时，外资企业、外资品牌纷纷进入中国，全方位地收购国内品牌，竞争对手的强大压力让立白挣扎于夹缝之中：日化行业领头羊宝洁公司就驻扎在广州，强大的广告宣传优势让他们傲立潮头；本地的浪奇公司则位居全国销量第二。想要在这其中分一杯羹，其竞争之激烈、创业之艰辛可想而知。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">但陈凯旋身上那股坚忍不拔的闯劲，促使他一个一个经销商去“磨”，一家一家的零售场去跑，沉下心跟客户打交道、做朋友，每天工作十五、六个小时是经常的事。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59812&size=300x300&key=287766a053468cf6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59812\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">陈凯旋回忆当时艰辛，仍是滋味余绕：他从1994年来到广州，从7个人租三间办公室的小规模做起，白天当老板，晚上睡地板，艰辛熬过。创业初期，大众不认可品牌，所以他还要上门一个又一个地推销，到处去推广、叫卖。潮汕人有谚，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">“钱银出苦坑”</span></strong>，而陈凯旋的一分一厘的确都是在“苦坑”里捞上来的。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(244, 164, 96);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">创新策略一路走来 从骂声到掌声</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">如果单靠刻苦勤勉，立白也许还无法达到今天的高度，从借鸡生蛋到农村包围城市、专销专营、体育营销等战略性决策，才是立白决胜千里的关键，而这幕后调兵遣将、运筹帷幄的正是陈凯旋。</span></strong>陈凯旋说，当时的农村市场是一个广阔但又让人头疼的大市场，品牌良莠不齐，渠道混乱，很难有一个品牌处于权威的引领地位。为了让新产品进入市场初期的运作能按照立白决策运作，陈凯旋决定在重要的区域设立立白专销商。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">专销商，在今天看起来并无特殊之处，但这在当时又是首创先河，也是一招险棋。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59818&size=300x300&key=fdcafd2592167b4d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59818\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(139, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">所谓专销专营，就是要经销商只能经营立白一个品牌，决定一出，马上招来骂声一片。</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">陈凯旋解释，设专销商，就是双方的互选，公司在这个地方的销售就只交由这一家专销商，反过来，这个专销商也只能售卖单一的公司品牌。而盈利把公司和专销商挂钩起来，双方必须积极相互配合，才能做成功，虽然这种双赢的规则很简单，但是当时却受到很大的阻力。因为很多经销商很难接受这样的条件，以致当时反对声非常激烈，有的经销商甚至当场在会议上拍桌抗议，质疑陈凯旋所提的销售策略。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59817&size=300x300&key=872c53aa31bc0c1b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59817\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">但是，没有经销商也不能坐以待毙！</span></strong>陈凯旋发动亲戚朋友来担任专销商。与一般的经销商不同，立白的这第一批专销商就像一个完全服从命令的士兵一样，专一卖力、上下一心、执行到位，在这样具有杀伤力的营销下，效果立竿见影，立白的产品很快进入流通渠道。榜样在前，经销商们开始认同之前非议极大的专销和款到发货模式。1997年，立白在广东56个县扎根。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">当年底，日化行业三角债危机整体爆发，全国四分之一的日化企业不是被拖死就是被逼死，而立白模式却成为日化行业的新标准。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">陈凯旋说，行业现在已经基本按照这个套路了，因为立白的销售策略很成功，很多经销商也都愿意跟着这样的模式走了。他认为，这个策略不仅救了立白，也救了整个行业的模式，否则如今国内的洗涤用品行业就很有可能被外资品牌垄断，而改革后的现在，本土品牌在国内市场占有半壁江山。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(244, 164, 96);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">不被牵鼻走 另辟蹊径妙夺市场</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">1995年底，洗衣粉原材料价格整体上扬，许多企业都做出涨价的举措， 1997年，洗涤用品市场又陷入了降价风潮。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">不过两年，急剧的一升一降让许多跟风的日化企业吃不消，而当时的陈凯旋却审时度势，走了另外一条绝然不同的路子。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59819&size=300x300&key=d11bb3c60b383b97&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59819\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">当时，原材料提价了，各家产品随之提价，但立白却不提价，转而提高质量，仍以原价推出抢占市场。等到在市场占有一席之地后，在别人不提价的情况下立白却提价提质，包括其去污力的逐步提高，从提高15%到提高25%，几次不断提升产品质量，消费者也越来越信赖这个品牌。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">广告和营销双管齐下，仅三年时间立白在广东省就成为洗衣粉销量第一的品牌了。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59820&size=300x300&key=2a1e4ad0afd56563&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59820\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">危机和机遇，不同的人会看到不同的一面，陈凯旋在风险中逮住机会。</span></strong>两次反其道而行，使立白在广东站稳了脚跟，并取得行业的话语权，自此，曾经风头无两的高富力洗衣粉慢慢退出市场，业界人士都为之惊叹陈凯旋敏锐的商业嗅觉和当机立断的决策能力。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">陈凯旋指出了其中的关键一点，他们没有在价格升降大潮中被市场牵着鼻子走，不盲目跟随大品牌，坚持走自己的路。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59821&size=300x300&key=bc8c67b6f27ab114&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59821\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">1998年，在电视的黄金播出时段，由陈佩斯担纲的紧张又诙谐的广告煞是抢眼，很快就引起许多观众的注意，这是立白走向全国的标志，也是立白从地方性品牌向全国性品牌进军的关键一跳。随后十年，立白向全国稳健扩张，先在两广扎下根基，再往内陆发展，等全国布点完成，再开始进军北京、上海。2008年，北京奥运会面向全国招募产品专供商，陈凯旋抱定一个信念：就是中国人自己第一次举办的奥运盛事，无论如何也要争取成为专供商，这是为国人、为行业争光的事情。在奥组委多次考察后，立白以过硬的质量和业内良好的信誉度成为了北京2008奥运会洗涤用品专供商，这也是唯一一个获此资格的民族日化产品。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">近年，立白又以“百万助威团”支持广州亚运会，乘借两场体育盛会的巨大效应，立白飞速提升了品牌美誉度。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59822&size=300x300&key=94a014cd38bbdf29&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59822\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">如今，立白的产品营销网络星罗棋布，遍布全国各省、直辖市，被国家批准为“博士后科研工作站”和国内首家日化企业“院士企业工作站”。&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012623627188.png\" title=\"1460012623627188.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">来源/汕头电视台 《天下潮商》</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/博尔</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59779&size=300x300&key=88fd49408829028a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59779\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></span><br/></p>','2016-03-09 09:48:02',0,NULL,1,NULL,2216,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (353,'【广州潮商】一杯工夫茶架起通往成功的桥梁','201603090948406334.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012634600594.png\" title=\"1460012634600594.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">编者按：</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">创业神话很多，却仍有许多人栽在生意场上。但失败者未必就不是长袖善舞之人，论起精明经商，可能还比成功之人更胜一筹。但是事业成败还需人品的衡量，一个斤斤计较的狭窄的心胸又怎么能得到成功的垂青呢？而许多潮商成功的背后，支撑他们的是一种仁义精神，这是这种精神让他们在商海搏浪时如履平地，有凶无险。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59848&size=300x300&key=6c54e00672cfd9b7&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59848\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">一说到潮汕，最容易让人联想到的是生意人和工夫茶。</span></strong>波云诡谲的商场上，陈凯旋是叱咤风云的企业领路人。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而在生活中，他依然是爱喝家乡功夫茶的潮汕人，是低调谦和、喜欢用功夫茶广交人缘的生意伙伴。</span></strong>在潮汕人眼里，茶道如商，与客商喝茶，多了一份亲切感，可以让生意变得不那么仓促，有礼有节，考虑周全。茶道造就了人缘，人缘滋润了商道，这其中就蕴含了潮汕人特殊而有效的生意经。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">采访中，陈凯旋觉得是自己“重感情，讲义气，为别人着想和同享利益”的理念赢得了好人缘。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59847&size=300x300&key=8c8b17b941e0198c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59847\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">俗话说：“小才不知有缘，不懂用缘；中才知有缘，但是不善用缘；只有大才，知缘而且善用缘。”<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在立白的代理商和员工眼里，陈凯旋便是这样一位大才，为人毫无骄贵之气，只是一位朴实而有人情味的企业家。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59849&size=300x300&key=9a72641d0ed6b384&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59849\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">广州立白企业集团有限公司代理商佘先生觉得陈凯旋特别朴素，事事亲力亲为，心胸豁达，即使是跟经销商伙伴打交道也是如此。他记忆深刻的一次是在2007年，他刚刚经营立白经销行业，初涉此业，生意比较艰难。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">陈凯旋得知他的困境后，二话不说就借了50万元，帮助佘先生顺利度过难关。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59850&size=300x300&key=a7c8e6f85b04f3fb&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59850\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">对于合作伙伴如此热心的他，对于公司内部员工更是不在话下。</span></strong>2009年，陈凯旋和陈凯臣兄弟捐资200万元建立立白关爱基金，几年来已经为几十名员工及其直系家属提供了援助。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">迄今，立白集团在赈灾扶贫、助医助学、扶老救孤等公益事业已捐助超过一亿元。</span></strong>立白集团也连续8年成为中国私营企业纳税100强。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59851&size=300x300&key=ba53e773db278da6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59851\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59852&size=300x300&key=2362a38e2fc93588&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59852\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">陈凯旋说，企业越大，就越是社会的。因为企业的成功汲取于社会，成功了就理所当然要回报社会。</span></strong>这对于陈凯旋来说是条铁道理，他认为，每一家企业、每一个成功人士必须这样去做的，这也是社会的一个规律。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59853&size=300x300&key=0c2e18b2bb0f5ea6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59853\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(139, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">正如陈凯旋所说，他的奋斗过程所坚持的刻苦坚韧，在复杂市场博弈中所具备的胆识变通，其实就是潮商的精神、是潮汕人文特征的社会竞争力。</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012642128936.png\" title=\"1460012642128936.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">来源/汕头电视台 《天下潮商》</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/博尔</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59830&size=300x300&key=1fc0fd059d34e4be&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59830\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></span><br/></p>','2016-03-09 09:48:40',0,NULL,1,NULL,2428,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (354,'【广州潮商】看潮商如何“超级变变变”','201603090949155401.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012653594914.png\" title=\"1460012653594914.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">编者按：</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在急速变化的新潮世界里，如何求得变通，是很多商人为之头疼的问题。在风云诡谲的商圈里站定脚跟已属不易，更何况是“变”出一片天。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59870&size=300x300&key=c8f3e0dce56a5f0d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59870\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">广州是中国最具活力的城市之一，“快”和“新”是这座城市留给人们的直观印象。</span></strong>“快”，是都市生活的节奏快，根据2006年英国文化协会对生活节奏的调查，在中国参与调查的六个城市中，广州人走得最快，60步距离最快的只需要7秒多，就像小跑一样。而“新”，则是这座城市的活跃特质，作为我国改革开放的前沿城市，作为广东省政治经济文化的中心，广州及其所在的珠三角迄今保持着创新求变的活力。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59871&size=300x300&key=cf63514b91ae1dba&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59871\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而如果将这种“快”与“新”的特质放到了商场中，则是商人对市场快速反应、观念超前、敢于创新、能前瞻未知商业机会的精明之处。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮商，便是这样的一群人。在充满变数且竞争激烈的商业世界，“动于先机，便利尽沾；行于机后，受制于人”。</span></strong>这是他们的座右铭，于是，他们事事都力求走在别人前面。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">不断进行创造性的实践，是潮商最突出的秉性，也是潮商最具特色的性格。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">“工欲善其事，必先利其器”。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在秋鹿公司创办人方俊洪的眼里，设计团队便是他最为得意的利器之一，因为早在1991年，当很多人还对原创、对商标、对品牌意识相对模糊的时候，方俊洪已经从并不宽裕的资金中，硬是分拆一部分来组建设计团队。</span></strong>领先和创新，从来就是方俊洪最活跃的主题。1987年，广东服装已经与江浙、福建一带一样闻名全国。方俊洪用几千元的全副身家在潮南成立了峡山针织三厂，专做内裤供应给广州针织站。1988年，方俊洪在潮汕地区首家转型生产睡衣。1990年，注册了秋鹿商标。一年后，他在香港朋友家里第一次见到了家居服。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59869&size=300x300&key=6d2b24f36dee2e78&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59869\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59872&size=300x300&key=5e1979e66f1694b9&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59872\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">此时，方俊洪预感到，家居服——这个当时国内尚还少人问津的行业，必定具有广阔前景。从香港回来后，方俊洪马上做出了一个在当时让很多人费解的决定，就是将工厂瘦身，从内衣裤行业全身而退，转投于休闲家居服行业。也就是这个决定，让秋鹿公司成为我国家居服最早的缔造者之一。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">从淹没于同质化的内衣裤生产，到潮汕地区首家睡衣生产厂家，再到先于别人抢滩家居服市场，加上商标的注册、设计的跟进，秋鹿在1991之前就完成了几次华丽转身，将后来的模仿、或同质的竞争对手远远甩开。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59873&size=300x300&key=89b636326dbd3203&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59873\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59876&size=300x300&key=5e8cec55ec9c0d2c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59876\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">可是，他并没有就因此松懈了。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在大浪淘沙的行业竞争中，服装行业是变化最为频繁的，这给了方俊洪强烈的危机感，因而他总是未雨绸缪，很早就开始思考企业如何在这场竞赛中成为胜出者和领跑者。</span></strong>1988年，方俊洪就在广州成立秋鹿实业有限公司，将营销销售的中心放到了广州，在这里，他看中的是市场规模、便利的交通以及广州在全国的知名度、辐射力和影响力。当时在方俊洪面前，有一条现成的路，就是走批发市场薄利多销、货如轮转的模式，这种方式简便快捷。但方俊洪经过一番深思熟虑和缜密论证，选择了从一开始就跟零售百货公司合作、品牌化经营的方式。这对企业来说又是一场新的考验。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59874&size=300x300&key=e675b17a2ea9628e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59874\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">一方面，这是因为百货公司对产品质量要求比较严格，这种狠抓质量的要求对企业自我的提升有很好的促进作用。另一方面则是百货公司有很大的客流量，一旦品牌能够在百货公司上架的话群众接触面会比较广，能较快提升品牌知名度。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">就这样，秋鹿公司以领先和创新形成的竞争优势抢占市场份额，以市场促发展，不断创造新优势的良性发展态势，并逐步确立了企业在家居服行业内的话语权。</span></strong>&nbsp;如今，秋鹿公司旗下拥有包括秋鹿、侬媚儿、梦伴、增你姿等多个知名品牌，秋鹿家居服也成为“中国驰名商标”、“国家免检产品”、“广东著名商标”等，产品远销美国、加拿大及西欧等国家和地区。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">秋鹿领跑中国家居服产业由无到有，由小到大的发展，实至名归成为中国家居服行业的标杆企业。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59877&size=300x300&key=8a20c6aedd0bf9d9&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59877\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">同样从事服装行业，潮商佘旭锦的宾宝休闲服装也通过创新找到属于自己路。</span></strong>做宾宝品牌之前，佘旭锦创办的香港金信集团有限公司曾是多个香港服装品牌内地南方市场的销售代理商，最多时曾同时运作16个品牌，成为当时中国数一数二的代理公司。但佘旭锦敏锐地看到，眼前的成功其实隐藏着长期竞争的短板。费尽心思运作别人的品牌，一旦合同到期了对方就收回了代理权，这样对企业本身极不安全，无法掌握核心，让自己时时处于竞争的下风。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59878&size=300x300&key=99fa75de8217bd38&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59878\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">2002年，佘旭锦去了一趟欧洲，长期的服装销售代理生涯，使他敏锐地发现在欧洲已经流行的休闲时尚男装领域在国内还是空白，于是<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在德国的杜尔塞夫，佘旭锦将一眼相中的宾宝品牌买了回来，自己也从服装销售代理商转型成为品牌管理商。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59879&size=300x300&key=3ecca41e310e82cc&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59879\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">宾宝成立的第一年就有1亿元的销售收入，2006年实现翻番，2007年的销售额更达到了3.5亿元。不久，市场上男装时尚休闲风日趋流行，中国男装市场开始洗牌，单凭销售一个品种的产品风险较大。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">市场在变，消费者也在变，感知到行业的新动态，宾宝公司又一次重新定位，丰富了整个产品链。</span></strong>产品也从时尚装扩展到工作装休闲装等。2008年底，公司总部被转移到广州，一切又得从零开始，经历了两年的阵痛期，宾宝开始加速扩张，到记者采访时为止，宾宝在中国有300多家店面，今年，宾宝又开始在国内布局面积500平方米以上的4S店铺。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59880&size=300x300&key=9a28fd972c5b735e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59880\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">谈及自己的成功之道，佘旭锦归功于一个字，“变”。</span></strong>他说，自己身处一个“变革”的时代，在世界经济形势的影响下，中国服装行业也经历着“转承启合”的洗礼，不求新求变就难以立足，不看得更远迟早要出局。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012661957328.png\" title=\"1460012661957328.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">来源/汕头电视台《天下潮商》</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/博尔</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59854&size=300x300&key=1a4426bbc9e8a50e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59854\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></span><br/></p>','2016-03-09 09:49:15',0,NULL,1,NULL,2367,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (355,'【广州潮商】步穷于岭南 心却不止于兹','201603090950126402.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012673542415.png\" title=\"1460012673542415.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">编者按：</em></strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">步穷于岭南，心却不止于兹。广州之地，繁华多变，更何况是其中风云诡谲的商圈之内呢？但是，身在广州的潮人并没有因为惊险大潮而所退缩，他们劈波斩浪，最终在羊城博得一处登览。</em></strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59912&size=300x300&key=22341163e382dce6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59912\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在餐饮界，创立于2006年的大有轩虽然是后起之秀，但其卓尔不群的菜品却受到众多美食家和饕客的追捧，连法国美食协会也不远千里，亲自将国际杰出厨师奖和哥顿布厨师奖两大重量级嘉奖授予大有轩及它的创立人。2009年，上海大有轩开业才一年，便一跃成为上海最精贵的潮菜馆。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而这位大有轩的创立人，便是地道的潮汕人蔡昊。</span></strong>蔡昊最为人津道的，还是他西学中用，将西餐的标准化流程运用到中餐制作中，并身体力行积极推广潮菜。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59899&size=300x300&key=3bbbc8e463783a51&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59899\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59898&size=300x300&key=e3535b126a5900d3&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59898\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59900&size=300x300&key=59d65ea6cbcace38&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59900\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">曾经长时间在国外生活、有着经济管理硕士头衔的蔡昊，是一位海归人士。</span></strong>在风华正茂时，蔡昊便游历全球研究美食，形成对中西餐饮、品酒配菜的独特见解，如今亦是中国三位威士忌品酒师之一。印象中，中菜馆的厨房必是一排旺火猛炒、细火慢炖，一道菜可口与否全赖主厨的勺上功夫、拿手绝活，但大有轩的厨房却更像西餐的厨房，有计量、温度、时间的标准设备，对出品样式、颜色有严格的要求。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这就是蔡昊提出的：把中餐烹饪标准化、程序化。</span></strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59902&size=300x300&key=f3b7721c7309dba7&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59902\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">蔡昊认为，中国人对标准化作业的管理落实得不够彻底。比如一个做连锁的餐馆是一群厨师做同一个菜，这样同一道菜在不同师傅的手里出来就会有十几种味道。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">正是这一点给了他启发，如果要让更多人认识到中国菜或者潮州菜，它将来慢慢地要趋近于标准化管理。</span></strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59907&size=300x300&key=c1e2f98aa3e76fa7&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59907\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">早在十年前，蔡昊在美国肯德基洲开了一家化学工厂，期间，酷爱美食的他不断用食材在实验室里做研究，记录食材的冷热温度反应和纤维质变化，考量如何加工能让食材原汁原味。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">2006年1月，回国后的蔡昊在广州市番禺区创立了第一家“大有轩精细中菜馆”，把西方餐饮的合理流程与中菜的精细选材、制作工艺结合起来，从而保证了大有轩菜品的口感稳定性，也让慕名潮菜的客人从来没有失望而归。</span></strong></span></span></p><p>如今，蔡昊每年都会应邀参加法国、澳大利亚、美国、日本等地的美食或酒类的品鉴会、发布会，而他也不遗余力地将潮菜带到世界各地。</p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59904&size=300x300&key=a3a142f0e12d6fe2&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59904\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59905&size=300x300&key=f03e557284b2ebf2&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59905\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59906&size=300x300&key=8d49ca6bab63cb98&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59906\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而今，在广州商业的舞台上，新一代的潮商开始演绎自己的故事。</span></strong>2006年，还不到30岁的魏旭翔在广州世贸大厦也开了一家餐饮店，创业之初，他还必须自己到批发和农贸市场采购材料，但辛苦的创业很快摆脱曲折，5年过去了，他的餐厅从一家开到五家。到记者采访时，魏旭翔已联合几位股东投资2000多万，开办一家占地4000多平方米的喜客新店，他的目标是逐渐化零为整，向有规模的酒楼迈进。魏旭翔还在不断摸索，他希望有一天他们可以拥有更大型的餐饮店。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">他坦言，潮商吃苦耐劳的精神是值得他们这些年轻的潮汕人继续学习的。</span></strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59908&size=300x300&key=7fab0911ea8a618c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59908\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">正是这种吃苦耐劳、敢闯敢拼、灵活变通、快速出击的精神，成就了一个个白手起家、以小搏大、由弱变强的商场传奇。</span></strong>在广州商界，潮商绝对是浓墨重彩的一笔，房地产界的朱孟依、周泽荣、游德武，日化产业的陈凯旋、物流板块的刘武、塑料交易所的周奕丰、建筑行业的张钦洲、新兴文化产业的林佑钦、投资行业的马灶雄、王老吉的施少斌等等，他们活跃在房地产、装修、餐饮、批发、化工、服装、医药、物流、百货等领域，有的甚至在短短十几年中使成为资产数十亿乃至上百亿的大鳄。探究他们成功的背后，除了传统的潮商精神外，这一代的潮商自有他们的共通点。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59909&size=300x300&key=f16a84525c04556d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59909\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">时任中共广东省委党校副校长的陈鸿宇总结道，第一点，是他们的视野普遍很开阔，走出了潮汕三面环山一面面海的局限。第二点，传统的潮商是因为商贸特色较明显，一开始都是从事商业贸易，从小做生意，受到系统的、规范的、关于经济的、管理的理论和熏陶，就略显不足；但是新一代潮商不同以往，因为视野开阔，且在社会上经历从小到大、由弱到强、由草根到宏大视野的历程，一旦有机会，他们会充实自己，不再是单纯的生意人，而是企业家，内心认识有了一个飞跃，竞争能力也就更强。第三点，也是很重要的一点，就是潮商优秀的文化特质在这一代人更加发扬光大，依然很坚韧、愿意开拓、愿意冒风险，依然愿意选择多种经营策略。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59910&size=300x300&key=6a1176fd908f7817&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59910\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">有人说，广州姓“广”，所谓“广”，就应是包括东西南北、上下左右、内外里表、天上地下、高山海洋，非如此，不足语“广”。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这种宽广与包容的底气，也正是许多潮商不约而同选择扎根广州的主要原因。</span></strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59911&size=300x300&key=65b777a9bf1323b7&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59911\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">因为珠江三角洲与广州、香港、深圳已经形成了一个区域性的经济中心，背后有广阔的腹地——通过交通网络、市场网络、信息网络，一连接起来就会产生巨大的市场需求，而且珠三角是改革开放先行先试的地区，社会主义市场经济的体制在这里萌芽比较早，成形比较早，发育比较成熟，框架体系都比较稳固，它的文化的交流程度是比较宽泛的，就是说多元文化、多地域文化的交融，是统一的、开放的、竞争的市场体系形成的必备条件。最后一个竞争优势，珠三角地区在历史上一直到今天，跟潮汕地区的经济连接是特别地紧密。</span></span></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460012681134960.png\" title=\"1460012681134960.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台综合报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">来源/汕头电视台《天下潮商》</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵&nbsp;&nbsp;实习小编/博尔</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=59913&size=300x300&key=31093601f8149fa1&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_59913\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-03-09 09:50:12',0,NULL,1,NULL,2372,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (356,'【岭东民俗录】人面桃花','201603091029231842.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011634104222.png\" title=\"1460011634104222.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=110506&size=300x300&key=b03926404291c90a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_110506\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>去年今日此门中，人面桃花相映红。崔护先生春光之中的惆怅，传唱千年，人人感同身受，这其中，做为唯美回忆的背景图，就是那一片开到荼蘼的桃花。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=110520&size=300x300&key=3907b0d8abfa3f1d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_110520\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">最近几年，赏花成为一种时尚，岭东乡村也开始遍植桃花，妆扮村容，装点景色，曾经零落散布在山野之中的桃花，也被整合成春天的时尚元素，最近天气回暖，春意盎然，桃李春光，频频出现在朋友圈中。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=110521&size=300x300&key=22fad7bbaeafd910&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_110521\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而在岭东，桃花原本就是常见的乡土植物，每到腊月年底，市场上也常见很多花农，在山上砍了含苞欲放的桃枝，到市场售卖。城里人也大多喜欢它红色喜庆，带有春天气息，过年家里插一支，很有年味，所以生意一直不错。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=110529&size=300x300&key=b5ce33e6ef3786ad&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_110529\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">但是“桃”在民俗中也是一种很常用的植物，很早就被赋予了神性。春联的前身叫“桃符”，传说就是用桃木做的木板，十年前我在揭阳桃山乡逛村落，很惊奇地发现这里很多家庭门前，悬挂着木制的春联，恍然挂桃符古风。但是近几年再去，却遍寻不着，不知道是记忆出了差错还是我眼花了。道教法师做科仪的时候，要使用桃木剑做法器，因为根据《太平御览》引《典术》：桃者,五木之精也,古压伏邪气者，此仙木也。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">桃木可以制百鬼。所以桃木在民俗事项中是与驱邪联系在一起的</strong>。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=110508&size=300x300&key=3b028928823a48d9&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_110508\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=110511&size=300x300&key=134875b4d2763afa&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_110511\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在潮阳金浦乡，就有一个民俗是和桃花密切相关的，那就是“<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">正月廿四换桃花</strong>”。每年的正月二十四，村民们都要手持一支桃花，前往舍人爷庙中进行交换。因为金浦是一个大乡，人口将近五万，近年来也演变为村民手拿桃枝，到庙里祭献，或者等营老爷队伍到达每个“神厂”，再行敬献纳福。虽然这是一种普遍的接触纳福的做法，但是因为老老少少都手持桃花，这种听起来相当文艺的行为，出现在民俗的现场历经几百年，不免要让人产生特别的关注。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=110507&size=300x300&key=4dcbf93b24617a9a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_110507\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">金浦口语里称深浦，全村郑姓，是古潮阳县城郊的一个古老乡村。明朝大理寺卿峡山人周光镐曾经在深浦境内曾山书院寄读，与深浦郑氏交好。他为郑氏宗祠作记，记述深浦郑氏自北宋神宗年间即由兴化军莆田移居至此，至今已逾950多年。深浦乡人丁兴旺，自创乡始祖郑升以降，快速发展，人称“<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">半斗油麻郑</strong>”，子孙遍布潮汕各地，如今人口已多达5万余人，是潮阳郑氏的发源村之一。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=110505&size=300x300&key=1f89169d2bcd2de3&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_110505\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=110515&size=300x300&key=04d5ca416e6a9851&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_110515\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">舍人老爷是深浦三社南门、三堡、寨外共同供奉的社神“大老爷”。神源已经很难查考，村民相传，此神由创乡祖郑升自莆田涵头村分香火携带而来，卜居深浦之后，只是在家里祀奉，随着郑升科举得仕，郑氏族人日渐发展，便将原乡的神明移入村里的社庙。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=110510&size=300x300&key=e89c2e58861ee8f8&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_110510\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">随着郑氏的发展，元朝襄州路务使郑佐龙，清乾隆年间湖北兵备道郑之侨等致仕后裔的士大夫地位，渐使郑氏宗族成为深浦的主流，估计在这个时候，便将舍人老爷这个代表宗族的神明扶正成为深浦乡的社神。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而为了使其更为名正言顺，当地又流传“浸水老爷”的故事</strong>，称由练江漂来木头，至此不走，于是村民便刻为神像供奉。深浦乡背山面江，古时处练江入海口，村民耕三渔七，后来又发展盐业，靠天吃饭的成分很大。这种“水流神”的故事对村民的影响甚为深刻，从此郑氏舍人老爷的信仰上升为全村的信仰，这个过程也是岭东宗族社会结合地方信仰进行自治管理的一个普遍典型。应该是相对比较可信的。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=110516&size=300x300&key=bb2bd5e3f569dc3b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_110516\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">至于为何有换桃花的习俗，因为深浦乡人笃信易理风水之说，清兵备道郑之侨就是民间风传的风水专家，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">人称“道爷”的郑之侨府邸叫“99间厝”，</strong>传说非其本系子弟，进入其间如入迷宫，以此方法保存其房产府邸。传说郑之侨公子有一年在游神过程中将桃枝插到神像持剑之手，他这一系在清中期得到良好发展，因此全乡从此效仿，渐成风俗。实际情况是否如此，已无法深究，但是桃花是正月开放，又是民俗中的良好意象象征，而发展良好的宗族榜样在前，根据需要改造信仰以及细节，正是我们在岭东各地所看到的历史真实，这既是一个保守的族群，同时也是一个与时俱进的族群。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=110512&size=300x300&key=9985f467377b0ed7&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_110512\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">随着深浦乡的发展，为了提高在潮阳县的影响力，“深浦老爷向外乡”的说法也出现了，这种情况我们也已多次提及，一个乡村的社神能够庇佑到外乡，折射的当然是这个乡村的实力和对外影响力，同时也必然会受到挑战。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=110513&size=300x300&key=762ee54625274767&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_110513\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=110514&size=300x300&key=5ef994a17b93a49c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_110514\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">所以深浦乡的营老爷过程也出现了热闹的一景：当舍人老爷巡境回宫的时候，围观众人便要上前摸“老爷须”——这一幕我们在盐灶已经领略到——在人山人海面前，本乡人便必须护卫老爷回宫，护神队伍耍开杀威棍，从人群中打开一条通道，围观众人齐声高呼，蜂拥而上，这个有趣而刺激的场面如今也演变成深浦乡闹热的一个特色，由换桃花的文艺，到摸老爷须的尚武，这就是传统岭东乡村的两面。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011643666218.png\" title=\"1460011643666218.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/图&nbsp;&nbsp;岭东怒马&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011653799014.jpg\" title=\"1460011653799014.jpg\" alt=\"图片4.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-03-09 10:29:23',0,NULL,1,NULL,2594,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (357,'【岭东民俗录】 骊歌一曲','201603161628468713.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011605118018.png\" title=\"1460011605118018.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">知道贵屿的“街路棚”已经有许多许多年，因为我曾祖父客居并落葬于此，所以每年都会至少到贵屿一次扫墓，每次都惊诧于贵屿的古镇古风。但是几乎每过一年，贵屿镇的环境就会恶劣多一点，越被破坏就越显得古昔的古镇更为宝贵，心情不免沉重。好在还有各种古俗，还有在贵屿这个煌煌大镇生活的那么多年轻人，依然满怀热情地传承着源自中原，源自耕读传家，源自我武维扬，源自农耕文化的千年传统，在这一点上，总也让我心存感动。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111157&size=300x300&key=0b00fe8d17ab2c85&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111157\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">贵屿“街路棚”活动主要由贵屿镇内华美、南安、佳安、北林、玉窖、后望、新厝等村居主办。 “街路”是潮汕口语“街道”之意，明朝嘉靖年间官至大理寺少卿的陈洸离职回乡之后，改造家乡的春社活动，倡议以北方庙会的形式，举办书画展览。贵屿在明代发展成为一个繁华的商埠，展览就利用沿街商铺门前，两端搭起牌楼，露天处用布搭棚遮挡，所以称做“街路棚”。贵屿自唐文宗开成四年置寨至今，历史相当悠久，本属潮阳贵山都，因其繁华，故嘉靖四十五年置普宁县的时候，曾把县邑设置于此，及后才复归潮阳。及至晚清、民国初年，贵屿商贾尤为活跃，民间喜好收藏字画，这种“赛会”传统，就更为张扬，往往重金购得名家字画，以为彰显门闾，这在岭东乡村赛会中独树“文雅”风韵，称颂一时。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111156&size=300x300&key=ad558f0068e93c37&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111156\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111155&size=300x300&key=20070f0252e3dd94&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111155\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">贵屿春社营老爷有三日之期，每年都是通过掷珓选择二月某个日子进行，是四乡八里之盛事。今年选在今天二月初二到初四进行，而尤以初四日营“双忠公”为最。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111179&size=300x300&key=f5b486eb1c61a8d0&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111179\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111180&size=300x300&key=5573590a20cf4684&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111180\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">双忠公即为唐朝死守睢阳的张巡、许远，历朝均为官方做为“忠义报国”的典型而被列入官方祀典。在明代被以潮阳著名士绅，编修过隆庆版《潮阳县志》的林大春为代表的士大夫们，选择做为归化民众思想的主要力量，以种种灵验故事结合明代中叶盗贼蜂起，倭乱四处，潮阳各村寨均要建寨自卫的形势，从上到下直至清代中叶，渐至把双忠公塑造成为“香火遍棉阳”的几乎影响整个潮阳县及其周边的“大老爷”。明代隆庆《潮阳县志》附录的《遗爱碑》，清代光绪甲申《潮阳县志》等都有：“双忠之观甲于东南诸郡，而二月尤胜”的记载，甚至在潮州府城，清乾隆以前尤以双忠做为主神。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111133&size=300x300&key=81f2b5ae693cff89&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111133\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而贵山都贵屿这里的双忠庙建成甚早，与潮阳县城外东山的“双忠圣庙”均为潮邑最早的双忠庙之一，这也使这里的双忠庙成为远近驰名的祖庙之一。贵屿镇周边的村子，通过每年农历二月的游神与街路棚活动，进行组织整顿，也达到了增强管理贵屿商埠的目的。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111135&size=300x300&key=aa4519057ead6403&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111135\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111141&size=300x300&key=49d838cf4bf8fd32&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111141\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111136&size=300x300&key=70a35bde30277e5a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111136\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">做为在圩镇集中展示各村实力的面子工程，一直以来也被各村所重视，精选村中壮丁秀女，锣鼓英歌提前准备排练，在社日之际，旌旗飘扬，秀女如云，英歌队队，尤其全做古装打扮，此日自镇中走过，恍如回到宋明，古风盎然。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111154&size=300x300&key=af04237565110ddf&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111154\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111149&size=300x300&key=1740412c1192194a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111149\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">贵屿的英歌比较接近普宁，基本各村都有组织英歌队，所以这个社日也有一点竞赛的意味在内，各村青年均热情参加，为在社日一展风采。而尤为特别的是出现了少女英歌，与男英歌的尚武阳刚不同，少女英歌则展现了清丽明朗，英姿飒爽的一面，女孩们在队首旗手的指挥下，舞姿灵动，衣鬓飞扬，脆生生的清叱与男子们的有力的怒吼形成完美的配合，构成了贵屿风情中无可替代的一部分。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111146&size=300x300&key=0a64194930eddaff&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111146\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111152&size=300x300&key=89ab2969c6a5a06b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111152\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111139&size=300x300&key=4775afd18ca98b78&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111139\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">有一年我跟随营老爷的队伍绕村，发现抬着老爷轿的居然是外来的农民工，我的第一反应就是古风日下，难道连表达自己信仰都已经如此功利化，辛苦的事花钱雇人做，而自己动动手指烧烧香就想心想事成，天下难道有这么好的事情吗。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111132&size=300x300&key=fa25a5f92dad6bed&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111132\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111158&size=300x300&key=3e5121ab8c352168&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111158\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">从镜头里我看到这样一个场景，雇佣工们抬着神像经过村居，本地妇孺俯首磕头敬香，而外来务工者显然无视潮人的最高神祇，吃面，洗头，看热闹，他们现在是租住在这些破旧村居“下山虎”里的新主人。乡村神权，令人讶然地退位于人性。信仰，已不再坚固。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111131&size=300x300&key=258050af8296ce1a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111131\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">我把这个感慨发在微博上，后来吴真博士回了我一句“淡定淡定”，说在日本人手不足时也是雇人抬舆。吴真博士是我潮州杰出女青年，当年以《唐诗地图》《金庸地图》闻名文艺青年界，一纸风传，中州纸贵。后来潜心学术，深入香港与日本两个世界道教研究中心，由东京大学博士后载誉归来，现居南开教授。吴真博士道学精深，对人性显然报以十分善良的态度，然而从我的观察来看，伴随着商业中国发展的副作用，便是信仰弱化，我们在岭东很多乡村都看到，这种保持了很多年以神权封印普世价值的做法，是凌驾于私欲之上的道德，是要世人产生一种敬畏之心来行事，这是以前社会的自我约束和自我管理，然而贵屿这个地方民俗的变化，最起码会让我觉得，人的私欲已经渐无敬畏，所谓的信仰，就只剩下赤裸裸的人神交易了。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111145&size=300x300&key=1bbbcbff2ffeed9d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111145\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111144&size=300x300&key=184b2f41e56b89df&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111144\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">现在的贵屿是一个重金属污染的重灾区，前些年为了发展，以拆解金属废品为业，失去环保监管，造成现在污染严重。发了财的老板们已经撤离这个故乡，而为了生存的穷人们，为了梦想的外来工们渐渐成了乡村的主角。只有每年的节庆，才让这个曾经辉煌的商埠回到它曾经宜居的时代，然而那只不过是一曲骊歌，虽然年轻人们，依然有热情敲起英歌槌，但是生长在这里的土壤空气与水，都已经不再，何去何从，纵使双忠有灵，也难以回答吧。</span></p><p><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=111153&size=300x300&key=9c4ff0b61e5bd8a9&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_111153\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011613135980.png\" title=\"1460011613135980.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/图&nbsp;&nbsp;岭东怒马&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011620258104.jpg\" title=\"1460011620258104.jpg\" alt=\"图片4.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-03-16 16:28:46',0,NULL,1,NULL,2263,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (358,'【岭东民俗录】鸥汀——为神性加注','201603161629344159.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011579118612.png\" title=\"1460011579118612.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">鸥汀乡，现在是深藏于汕头市中心城区东北部的一个村庄。在明清以降，鸥汀因其扼守澄海县出海口，海陆两路通往揭阳县，潮州府城的要冲，成为乱世之中一个非常重要的关口，明末以来乡人陈君谔筑寨练兵，“鸥汀背寨”成为名闻当时的四大名寨。与郑成功军在清初的一场大战，寨破被屠，连同周围村庄避难的几万难民尽数被杀，成为“有鸥汀，无国姓”的晚明岭东一大惨案。清初斥界展复之后，鸥汀寨也迅速恢复生机，至同治四年（1865年）的时候，鸥汀上乡已经有张、李、郭、陈、辛五姓组成的十个“楼分”在这里生活。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112021&size=300x300&key=95c40361155529eb&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112021\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">鸥汀乡是一个长条形的村落，自古流传说是“蛇地”，以证果寺为中心点，分为上乡和下乡，这不是一个同姓的纯宗族村落，而是在长期的战乱与融合中形成一个多姓杂居的庞大村居。从现在资料看来，至迟在同治年间，已经有需要通过一定的规则和制度对整个村落进行管理。因此在那一年，鸥汀上乡的管理者们——就是那十个“楼分”的头人——通过创建三山国王庙，定下了一直延续到今天成为民俗的一个管理制度：灯首。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112024&size=300x300&key=d84c4e69425bb349&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112024\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112025&size=300x300&key=8d6fbced0147cfe1&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112025\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">今天我们看到的鸥上社区“灯首”是这样的：在农历二月初二至初五挑选一个日子做为“灯首”，根据“望海楼、治生楼、沙庭楼、靖西楼、拱北楼、顺玄楼、巷东楼、元丰楼、东宁楼、福南楼”这样的顺序进行轮值，每年轮到的楼分要负责举行祭神、游神的活动，并于翌年的正月十二再办一次“灯（首）尾”。这样每一个楼分十年轮一次“灯首”，循环往复，通过由“楼分”来主持春社的祭典，而保持整个庞大村落的自治秩序。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112012&size=300x300&key=f98e63ab2f571be3&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112012\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112020&size=300x300&key=6a7e1118856442c6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112020\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">所谓的“楼分”，根据我们的了解，是类似于“里甲”的聚落划分方式，清初继承了明代的方法，令民二三十家或四五十家聚居，是一个管理单位，遇农时或死丧疾病，需协力耕助。当然这种方式在乾隆以后就并不成为国家强制性的制度，但是这个单位通过“社庙”的方式在民间保留了下来，也就是说，在鸥上村，村民们是通过拜同一间土地庙的方式而来确定为是否同一个聚落的集体。而现在，他们通过设立一个全村共有的“三山国王庙”来联结所有的十个集体。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112022&size=300x300&key=cd83eba8cc2de67b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112022\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">根据记载，每年正月十六日，还有一个由上一次轮着灯头的楼分与本次轮着的楼分进行交接的程序。交接王宫的田契（9亩）、池契（大池面积的一半约5亩）。轮着灯头的楼分将田租和鱼池的收入作为灯首做大戏等费用。交灯头由上一年轮着的楼分，交给新一年轮着的楼分。两个楼分各备一副猪头五牲，更换楼分灯笼。交后由新楼分内老大从二月初二至初六内，以第一次“胜杯”之日为确定为灯首节日。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112026&size=300x300&key=446bc416f764f096&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112026\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112015&size=300x300&key=1b970e7c027ea442&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112015\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这是我们看到的在多姓聚居的岭东乡村中普遍存在的一个自治管理方式，而且相当有效。一个自然村落的居民，通过建设共同的主神“大老爷”宫，在大老爷宫设置理事会，当理事的都是一些“乡里老大”。理事会每年要组织全村人“营”一次大老爷。在举行盛大祭神礼典之后，抬着神明“巡境”，驱鬼净土，保佑合境平安。巡境确认了村落的地域范围，同时，“有份”参与游神的人，也通过游神活动，确认了自己在村落定居的身份。一个个人就是这样通过这样一层一层扩大的神明祭祀活动，让自己整合到由小而大的社会群体中间。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112010&size=300x300&key=b061611acc2e6d73&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112010\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112027&size=300x300&key=e99a933aa0af1134&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112027\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">于是我们看到，神明在这里，其实已经从很单纯的乡村护卫神的角色，上升到一个精神领袖式的管理者角色。这是中国农耕时代一种很有智慧的民间自治方式，不是通过国家强制性任命，而是民间自发认可并且组织，这使得这种组织跨越了朝代变更，跨越了国家政权的更替，而形成了与国家制度平行的一种管理方式，这种方式在乡村中得到强力有效的执行，是实际上的乡村管理制度。因为作为“神明”，不是一个实际存在的某个管理者，所以这又深刻地契合了老子所说“上上，不知有之”的最高明的管理方式，通过神权封印了不可违抗的秩序。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112014&size=300x300&key=ae2a173632518a38&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112014\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112018&size=300x300&key=e2334ebaa11d645b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112018\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">鸥上村十个楼分还不是一个宗族一个楼分，因为这个长期分分合合处于变化之中的大村居，没有办法保存单纯的单一宗族发展形式，所以很自然会出现一些分歧和摩擦，在田野调查中，我们也发现，随着楼分经济实力和社会地位发展的不同，到现在又演变出一些不同，例如像拱北楼与望海楼就联合在一起，凡是轮到他们两楼中的哪一个办灯首，他们都会联合出钱出力进行举办，而原来拱北楼中的李氏则退出加入到相邻的楼分一起承办灯首。而原来本是作为办灯首主要费用的祭田鱼池收入，也演变为楼分内村民的摊派和捐款，这又是增强楼分之间角色认同的一个行为，每年一次的通过神明祭祀的仪式活动，成为轮到楼分村民们的一种义务与光荣。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112019&size=300x300&key=a6f2661c9cec12d1&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112019\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这就是岭东乡村为神明加注的典型过程，很多人不明白，为什么农耕社会已经解体，科学普及实行多年，文化素质培养早已深入人心，但是不管是国家机器的强力推行，还是现代生活方式的不断影响，都没有办法让看似无稽之谈的游神拜神等民间习俗绝迹。实际上从人类学的角度上看，神明之所以在岭东乡村有如此强大的生命力，正是因为它代表了乡村社会的需要，为神性加注的过程，代表着一个社区不断发展的需要。所以我们说，神就是人的内心。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112017&size=300x300&key=7dda656c9fb655db&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112017\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112016&size=300x300&key=4174c30476b7ea3a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112016\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112028&size=300x300&key=b8a761f1d85467a1&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112028\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112023&size=300x300&key=405c1549e6539dd6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112023\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">明天是今年鸥上村东宁楼灯首最后一天，这一天在郭氏宗祠举行的祭祀庆典结束，神明将被文艺游行队伍簇拥着营遍整个村子，然后回宫。在这三天的灯首祭典中，东宁楼村民们以少牢之礼献神，摆大猪、全羊，请潮剧，布置祠堂鳌山，然后组织英歌队、醒狮队，村中秀女营标旗巡游，一如岭东乡村春社所熟识的内容，现在已成为汕头中心社区具有乡村年味的一大民俗活动。鸥上村三山国王庙只供奉三王爷和夫人，后来加祀妈祖。而能让我们更加深切感受到神明即内心的特别之处，就在于连这个村落最高神明，居然与邻村的国王庙中二王爷有夺妻之怨，说以前重塑神偶金身的时候，夫人经过鸥上王爷庙恋上二王爷，之后就不愿回到三王爷庙，村民便在二王爷庙放多一位夫人像。这种奇特的绯闻，完全就是乡长里短的农村爱情故事，当我们欣赏贵圈到这里，还会觉得神明真的只是一尊木偶吗？</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112013&size=300x300&key=735b3574561fb51b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112013\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112011&size=300x300&key=695e983bd43eef49&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112011\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011587617333.png\" title=\"1460011587617333.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>文/图&nbsp;&nbsp;岭东怒马&nbsp;<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>橄榄小编/立庵</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112029&size=300x300&key=0fd074d7ff095dcd&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112029\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-03-16 16:29:34',0,NULL,1,NULL,2550,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (359,'​【岭东民俗录】潮阳双忠公 人神共乐（多图）','201603161631093013.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011553135627.png\" title=\"1460011553135627.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">毫无疑问，今天二月初五，在潮阳棉城举行的“双忠文化节”，是当下岭东城乡最最盛大的一次民艺民俗大巡游，超过一万两千人的游行队伍，从早上6点到下午6点的超长巡游时间，12公里的绕城路线，旌旗飘扬，连绵不绝的恢弘场面，包含了英歌、武术、舞龙、舞狮、标旗、笛套音乐、花篮队，有多种潮汕非遗在内的各种民艺，绝对算得上一场国际级别的超级嘉年华。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112803&size=300x300&key=f115f44fe35c4e70&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112803\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112379&size=300x300&key=b7f047e408dee3f0&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112379\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这是远接民国初年传颂一时的府城安济圣王盛会故事，继承清代以来双忠会习俗，在中心城市里举办的一场超大型的“营大老爷”活动，充分显示了潮阳人民的经济实力、组织能力、执行能力、协调能力以及无所不能的超强实力，是一场民俗民艺的饕餮盛宴，潮阳千年古城的建筑早已名不副实，唯有这传承至今的飘扬旌旗，倾城而出的火热激情，方能承载这片土地的厚重。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112377&size=300x300&key=48b1e638c89a53c2&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112377\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112376&size=300x300&key=6f19700234fbdd8d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112376\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">双忠圣王，即唐代安史之乱时据守河南睢阳的睢阳太守许远和真源县令张巡，新唐书记述睢阳一战之惨烈，为死守城池，甚至易子而食。唐以后历代统治阶层均加封号，以彰其忠。潮阳民间传说此二神乃是宋熙宁间军校钟英自睢阳带回，而根据中山大学陈春声教授的研究成果，双忠成为一个比较有影响力的神祇，应该是元至大年间，在潮阳县城赵氏家族族长赵嗣助的策划下，通过官方力量而首建专庙，明代在以士绅林大春为首的士大夫阶层，通过改造完善其传说故事，使其成为官方认可并推动的正统信仰开始流传潮州府。而明清两季因为海盗山寇流民对潮阳县的巨大威胁，乡村自治组织急切需要一个凝聚力和神力的偶像对百姓进行鼓舞，张巡许远这种勇武无畏的特征，恰好适时地切入民间，因此被古潮阳县一带民众选择做为乡土保护神，而虔诚奉祀至今。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112355&size=300x300&key=459d599071db2bda&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112355\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112349&size=300x300&key=18806734363290e3&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112349\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112375&size=300x300&key=f3aed74b17603ddc&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112375\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">做为管理阶层和士大夫阶级，想灌输及培养给民众的是忠君爱国，但是做为民众来讲，一直以来对于“电影话”并不见得有多感冒，百姓注重的是灵验，是“显”，是与自己息息相关的体验。双忠这种崇拜，从忠于朝廷，到变成护境安民，到变成战神，水神，甚至能预示休咎的无所不能的大老爷，通过一代代官方民间神化故事的渲染和加持，也历经多年。从明嘉靖完成理论创建推行开始，一直到雍正年间出现闽人蓝鼎元署理潮阳县时候所记述的“穷乡僻壤皆有庙”；而就是到了乾隆《潮州府志》记载当时“海阳有双忠会，以庆张巡、许远。届三年小会，五年大会”的时候，只是记载“潮阳有土地会”。也就是说，双忠圣王要逆袭潮阳本地众多同功能的神明，成为民间的第一选择，像现在这样做为潮阳全城至高主神巡游的盛会，最早也要到清中叶之后。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112371&size=300x300&key=8479f87179026678&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112371\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112370&size=300x300&key=1e31ab4a135dbfa2&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112370\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112369&size=300x300&key=6b434b0a5f47c62e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112369\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">到了清代光绪甲申年，《潮阳县志》就已经记载了：“双忠之观甲于东南诸郡，而二月尤胜”，我们看到，清末二月营“双忠公”这个众神之主已经在潮阳县确立，所以今天我们看到的盛大的双忠圣会，正是基于那时。而清末已经是潮汕民艺十分成熟的时期，潮阳县的财力人力商业化也达到了一个巅峰，而商人商业做为推动城市大型游神活动，有着其本能的欲望，所以在官商民完全契合的情况之下，这样的巡游盛会便一年年开始发展起来。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112368&size=300x300&key=834e52d6a5e832cb&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112368\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112366&size=300x300&key=79d37a57e00caaa5&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112366\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">今天我们看到的双忠大巡游，已经褪去了很多信仰的因素，因为在城市的营老爷和乡村还有不同，许愿纳福的成分少了，而礼仪象征意味会更加浓烈一些。做为城市实力的折射，以及商业化的需要，狂欢和娱乐成为主要，这就是潮阳棉城双忠会的主要诉求“人神共乐”。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112361&size=300x300&key=c371f4c483a239a8&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112361\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112360&size=300x300&key=8fbba1dc1e01498e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112360\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">当我看到巨大的潮绣标旗绣着“人神共乐”的字样营过民国骑楼的那一个镜头的时候，一种巨大的冲击感涌上心头，这当然是不同时空穿越历史的镜头重叠，也是生活在原乡原土的岭东潮人的共同感受，操办参与这种无比盛大的全城巡游，对于个人而言，付出和辛苦至少不会比利益与获得少，而凭着信仰和热爱，链接着一个城市分散的个体，从而形成一个族群的特征特点和特色，在不同时空和年代，为他人所记的，为自己人所自豪与铭记，为乡愁写下背书，这虽然借助了神的名义，但依然是做为“人”的伟大事业。</span></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011565134388.png\" title=\"1460011565134388.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 19px;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 19px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 19px;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 19px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 19px;\">文/图&nbsp;&nbsp;岭东怒马&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 19px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 19px;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=112348&size=300x300&key=557ffc80ab4769cb&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_112348\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></p><p><br/></p>','2016-03-16 16:31:09',0,NULL,1,NULL,2523,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (360,'【岭东民俗录】百兽闹春','201603161631556709.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011522121155.png\" title=\"1460011522121155.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113368&size=300x300&key=4df1dae9adf0a489&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113368\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">去陈厝洲，原本是要看它的特色民间舞蹈－－双咬鹅的。那是一支诙谐而充满乡村气息的动物舞蹈，是澄海农民伯伯们在50年代创造出来的一种次新民俗。非常敬佩和怀念那个火红的年代，虽然物质贫瘠，但是他们的精神状态如此向上，组织能力如此出色，而且团队精神让人肃然起敬，而且创意出众，执行力高效，解决问题的能力一流，每每想到此处，总会让我重新再思考“信仰”这个问题。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113367&size=300x300&key=475ed92f96edd284&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113367\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113369&size=300x300&key=8f582ad018fb5c28&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113369\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">双咬鹅模仿潮汕著名鹅种，体型庞大的狮头鹅的生活习态，以赶鹅郎和两头鹅之间的日常动作为主，贴近村民们的日常生活，因此自首创之后便受到极大欢迎，一经推出海外，更引起华侨们双泪涟涟，那儿童时代的纯真快乐和万里乡愁的强烈情感，一发不可收拾，因此大获成功。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113364&size=300x300&key=96a0c3f71c920843&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113364\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113362&size=300x300&key=d643af9bcc9e6f27&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113362\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113356&size=300x300&key=c4e9d4b363bbceff&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113356\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">双咬鹅始创自澄海的陈厝洲，然而澄海民众自创动物舞蹈，却是一个由来已久的传统。澄海民间传统动物舞蹈有十余种，包括蜈蚣舞、鳌鱼舞、双咬鹅舞，龙虾舞、双龙舞等等，最为让人赞叹的，是每一种动物舞蹈的躯壳造型都是一头庞然大物，它采用竹子、藤条、绒布等原生态材料手工精制而成，最小的每一种也要两人多高，是一件精致的手工艺品，而在社日巡游之时，往往需要数人乃至数十人通力合作，方能演出，堪称民间的手工、舞技、音乐于一身的集大成者。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113372&size=300x300&key=ea2ab2e588e54db4&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113372\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113371&size=300x300&key=acca8ca518f4c674&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113371\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113370&size=300x300&key=dbb10c1aec2d63fc&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113370\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这其中自清光绪年间，由澄海县西门村人陈成锦创作，西门村在社日演出的极富特色的“蜈蚣舞”当为其中翘楚。蜈蚣舞模仿蜈蚣的神态和习性，设计出整套舞蹈动作，包括吐珠、喷焰、翻肚、咬斗等精彩动作和特技。此种舞蹈要相应组织一支规模庞大的队伍，甚至可以扩充至一二百人，非常适宜在大街上游行或在广场上表演。1925年西门蜈蚣舞舞蹈队曾应汕头市政厅邀请，在汕头市审判厅前表演，时任东征军总司令的蒋介石观看了演出。1939年3月应香港潮商八邑会馆邀请，赴香港参加英王加冕庆祝活动15天，港督亲自为“蜈蚣”开灯点目，并赠纪念品。2000年2月应新加坡政府和潮州八邑会馆的邀请，蜈蚣舞与双咬鹅舞一起参加新加坡第28届妆艺大游行，也引起狮城轰动。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113357&size=300x300&key=f9e0695f27fac610&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113357\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而相对于这些庞然大物，像体积相对较小，容易组织的鳌鱼舞、麒麟舞，则更为普遍，每年的乡里闹热，总少不了他们的身影，人神同乐的氛围，也正是在围观这些动物舞蹈欢乐出游的过程中达到高潮。许厝村的麒麟舞，是周边村子正月社日争相邀请的对象，因为麒麟送子这么个吉兆和彩头，正是乡村最为朴素的祈求。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113366&size=300x300&key=7cf7b5b3f55fd3ef&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113366\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113365&size=300x300&key=ee6086ae1deadcbc&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113365\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">许厝的麒麟，由一个非常活泼可爱的小女孩来扮演刚出生的“麒麟仔”，十年前我走村窜乡，经常遇到，而在许厝本村的社日中，更见她与小伙伴们娇憨合影，今天如果再遇到，应该是个年方二八的大姑娘了，这么些年的麒麟仔生涯，不知留给她什么样丰富的童年回忆。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113360&size=300x300&key=c2768a5416522abd&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113360\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113361&size=300x300&key=75b1c204f4286ea6&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113361\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113358&size=300x300&key=b1d42c852f2a0a1c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113358\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">澄海永新有鳌鱼舞，西门还有龙虾舞，过几天要进行巡游的东湖乡，则有壮观的金龙鱼舞，这些舞蹈需要组织人力物力，在农耕社会相对可能对经济比较头疼，而现代社会则更发愁于没有人力。随着生活方式的改变，这种累人的活计逐渐式微，年轻人很少有人愿意接上一辈人的衣钵，像双咬鹅舞的主力，已经只剩下年近50的两三个中年人。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113363&size=300x300&key=622f53d196c30701&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113363\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">事实上随着城市的扩张和乡村经济的发展，很多乡村都早已不象乡村。象澄海西门乡和东湖乡，现在已经是车水马龙的澄海区闹市中心。但是岭东潮人是一个传统古俗保存得较好的地区，所以二月初十将在东湖这里的游神，也并不因为成为都市的一部分而取消。由凌晨开始的活动，直到交通繁忙时段的中午时分，一条包含了龙、鳌鱼、金龙鱼、鲤鱼等动物道具的游庆队伍，穿街过坊，在潮汕大锣鼓、笛子、弦乐等的伴奏下迤旎而行，和四周的高楼与街口的红绿灯构成了一组奇异的镜头。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113359&size=300x300&key=48a9d3ebec2f7eb8&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113359\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">“桑柘影斜村社散,家家扶得醉人归”，这种桃花源式的和谐人际社会，让人何其向往！而集合全村人的力量，简单地作为一个人来一起合作做一件事情，在分工细化的今天，也已经成为一种奢侈。在岭东潮汕，人口繁衍太快，许多村落早已是数万的巨型乡村，而且朝着形式城市化、思想都市化的方向发展，冷漠和陌生已经代替了纯朴和热情，这种百兽闹春的春社或许已是最后一种可以让人追想这种无围墙式社会和交际的活动了。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011531533637.png\" title=\"1460011531533637.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>文/图&nbsp;&nbsp;岭东怒马&nbsp;<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>橄榄小编/立庵</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011538122102.jpg\" title=\"1460011538122102.jpg\" alt=\"图片4.jpg\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-03-16 16:31:55',0,NULL,1,NULL,2468,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (361,'【岭东民俗录】东湖搬塗戏','201603211554303365.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011502316283.png\" title=\"1460011502316283.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113847&size=300x300&key=5befab50f6f33d67&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113847\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113846&size=300x300&key=c513d8e8e9f502de&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113846\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113845&size=300x300&key=61e3a623a85515ef&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113845\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">岭东乡村，旧时民众习尚看戏，这与全国的风潮是一样的，戏剧的产生和发展，乡里闹热是他们的土壤。方志记载，&quot;正月十五日，有善歌者自为侪伍，妆演方阵，迎神衍巷，&quot;顺治庚子（1660年）吴颖《潮州府志》载：“潮俗民多力耕，士习之病，竞为奢侈，樗蒲歌舞，傅粉嬉游，于今渐甚。”“仲春祀先祖，乡坊多演戏”，谚曰：“孟月灯、仲月戏。”康熙雍正间人蓝鼎元作《潮州风俗考》说：“迎神赛会一年且居其半，梨园婆婆，无日无之。”作为地方戏剧潮剧，也就是用潮州白话演出的剧种，正是在这种背景下产生并走向它的巅峰的。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113843&size=300x300&key=bf91aaf31b1dd767&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113843\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113842&size=300x300&key=9faf4593b6f97bb2&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113842\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113841&size=300x300&key=0a7737991be79a01&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113841\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113840&size=300x300&key=1b2329b130c066e2&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113840\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而塗戏则是一种在露天表演的广场戏，它不是正规的戏剧，我们在前面说过英歌后棚，其实就是一种塗戏。一般是选择一些诙谐戏或者武戏，既要大家耳熟能详，又能搞热整个场面，起到神人共乐，社日同欢的效果。所谓的“塗”，就是“土”，因为塗戏是在游神的时候穿街走巷，在村落空阔地方表演的，地里田头之间，充满乡土气息，甚为群众所喜闻乐见。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113839&size=300x300&key=bf45624b262334b0&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113839\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113837&size=300x300&key=7c858635100445bd&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113837\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113835&size=300x300&key=87833a5ba1cfd37a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113835\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113834&size=300x300&key=17ec067d9b73dfca&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113834\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113833&size=300x300&key=34f777a50ea2bab2&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113833\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">塗戏是否是戏剧的前身，这个事情其实也是一个很值得研究的。旧志记载，以前岭东有“秧歌戏”，“摔桶戏”，均是乡村民间地间田头应景娱乐，草草搭台，戏服道具就放置于农民摔谷用的“摔桶”。民国萧遥天先生认为这便是潮音戏也即潮剧的滥觞。当然我们也无法据此简单地认定，因为潮剧是一个庞大的系统，由正字戏到外江戏，以及明显的弋阳腔影响等多方面来看，北方的影响是相当大的。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=114203&size=300x300&key=cf7e45a89ea6ea72&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_114203\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=114204&size=300x300&key=87ca90adf89766c2&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_114204\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=114206&size=300x300&key=e3e84c8b9ba87b6f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_114206\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">做为岭东潮人传统的潮剧，延续到今天，已经日渐式微，尤其在快节奏的城市，已经需要提到一个“遗产”作为保护的层面了。而像乡间不甚精致的“塗戏”，则更是稀见。东湖是澄海城郊的一个大乡，三年一次的社日巡游，则保留有著名塗戏“水漫金山寺”。这个塗戏在东湖表演，已有70多年的历史，据说是在1937年乡庆之时就排练了这个折子戏。这个戏脍炙人口，耳熟能详，角色众多，有很多水族，生旦净丑皆有，有武戏，诙谐搞怪，龟丞相能倒立，两粒蚶都会滚动，在社日游行搬演，热闹欢笑，一时风传，至今流传“锣鼓几班，输过东湖二粒蚶”，经过多年的完善，队伍里虾兵蟹将，龟丞相，螺婆，白娘子小青率领众水族大战法海，有单打、对打、群斗，潮剧以丑角闻名，这个塗戏里，海螺、龟丞相甚至二粒蚶，都是诙谐搞笑，最为出彩的角色，闹热队伍巡游到此，往往里外三层，锣鼓声声，欢声笑语，响彻云霄。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=114210&size=300x300&key=ed9453c42e7f39cd&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_114210\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=114209&size=300x300&key=3b43664bc3dd81e3&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_114209\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">搬，潮语读【波鞍6】，指的是在众人面前表演的意思，搬仙，就是指乡间潮剧开场戏“五福连”，因为内容有八仙贺寿，仙姬送子，所以人称“搬仙”，后来引申到生活用语，指刻意的撒娇或者讨好之类。所谓搬塗戏，也便是同一种意思了。东湖乡这里的“水漫金山”，在口语里正是在社日村里各个神前，各个宗祠，各个里社甚或工厂、商铺面前进行“搬”的，因为这个字还有一个类似故意妖娆作态，各种姿势表现的含义，岭东潮人往往由此一字，便可脑补精彩场面，往往会心一笑。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=114213&size=300x300&key=4669418e7b749198&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_114213\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这日社日巡游完毕，霞西布马队的姑娘们告辞回乡，杏花社的两条金龙鱼悠游回到杏花路口的蔡氏宗祠，金山寺的和尚和水族们依然冒着小雨，在村里各个神前为大家“搬仙”，这边厢，在英南体育场，三年一度的乡宴，乡间“做桌”的师傅们开始登场。木棉树下，宴开百席，虾蟹上炉，卤鹅飘香，一箱箱美酒，一张张笑脸，这正是盛世的嘉年华，这也是我们乐于看到的有血有肉的美好新农村。</span></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011511116723.png\" title=\"1460011511116723.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>文/图&nbsp;&nbsp;岭东怒马&nbsp;<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>橄榄小编/立庵</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=113828&size=300x300&key=28674dc98270fe61&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_113828\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></p>','2016-03-21 15:54:30',0,NULL,1,NULL,2532,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (364,'【岭东民俗录】 抢鸡头与宜生男','201603250913111408.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011484897944.png\" title=\"1460011484897944.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=115431&size=300x300&key=b77d6c130aa2fbb5&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_115431\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=115420&size=300x300&key=a5b30011a964f1d5&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_115420\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">岭东春社，既然是发源于中原汉人的古俗，承接上古时代贵族的礼仪而来，那么就必然延续着古代民众所祈于自然，所求于神灵的仪式和需求。作为庶民，自从宋元门阀贵族解体之后，通过程朱理学一步步地建构，一直到明嘉靖之后，才把原本属于贵族世家的祭祀，逐渐变成普罗大众都可以组织的仪式，这是中国民间社会的一个重大转折，自明朝中叶之后，中国乡村开始通过发展宗族这种形式，有效地对民众进行组织和自治，及至清中叶之后，已经形成了一个非常成熟而稳定的机构，而其影响甚至流播至今。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=115424&size=300x300&key=ffe64cb1c171a632&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_115424\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=115423&size=300x300&key=42db9958e95a2427&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_115423\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=115425&size=300x300&key=84d7adadb12e853d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_115425\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">岭东民系多自闽赣迁来，尤以闽地为多。但是明清以降，随着经济与人文的发展，已经形成一个独立于祖地之外的生活文化圈，虽然带着很多祖居地的痕迹，但是岭东潮人显示出保守与机变结合的一面，从某些方面来讲，甚至可以说极富创造力，根据岭东生活和自治的需要，造神变神，而士绅阶层尤为有魄力，通过重构组织民间信仰，将这种神权做为有效地管理手段，不着痕迹地影响了整个岭东基层社会。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=115430&size=300x300&key=e5a1c814c964ebbe&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_115430\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">对“神”的改造，是一个引领与接受的漫长过程，这其中经历很多失败，从成功的例子来看，基本上是贴近庶民们的生存生活，顺着大众的思维方式进行的那一些。像我们前面提到过的潮阳“双忠圣王”的改造，当士大夫们以“忠义”这种宽泛的大道理做为改造推手的时候，就很难接上岭东民众的频道；但是一旦通过渲染在洪水、战匪等重大灾害面前以“显灵”、“灵验”故事来重构神的角色，便马上引起群众的共鸣，并以难以想象的速度和广度进行传播，而围绕着民众的需要来做文章的组织行为，往往能够达成预设的目的，并成为一个自传播的风暴，在民间持续发酵，到了几百年后的今天，成为一个“自古有之”的传说和规则，并被广为遵守。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=115428&size=300x300&key=931a820160c62746&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_115428\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">农耕时代，男丁是所有家族的基础和实力的反映，就在同一个宗族当中，还有强房与弱房的分别，更不要说在一个商埠甚至是县城州府这样的大社会当中。因此很多民俗都包含着对“祈嗣”，对“千子万孙”的祈祷与求愿，每一地每一年的春社，这个内容成为民众们所自觉而热切的祈祷，并从中演化成花样繁多的仪式。普遍的“上灯”、“营灯”、“请翁仔（一种泥娃娃）”，这是源自巫术所谓的“接触”传播，从上一年生男丁者中接福的“荡丁秋”、“接花生”等等，到更为激烈的“抢红绸”“接鸟饼”“抢石榴”等等，都是要通过神的加持，已生男丁家庭的福气，都过仪式将神力赋予吉祥物，然后由民众接纳到自家。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=115429&size=300x300&key=104d30b41cc8dcab&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_115429\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这其中很特别的是抢“吉祥物”这种形式，抢地豆，抢鸟饼，抢石榴，都是将大量的献祭之后的食品撒向人群，虽然说是抢，但是其实就是分发，只是用了抢这个形式。但是在潮南沙陇仙家村，正月十六这天的“抢鸡头”，那就是非抢不可，因为鸡头只有一个。现场观摩这样的场景，我时常会猜想，这是否又是一个借助神力显圣的方式来培养训练后生子弟坚毅性格与强悍习性的过程？</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=115419&size=300x300&key=37c177f67807957a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_115419\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=115417&size=300x300&key=eb8e1cdd68e1af35&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_115417\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">仙家村处于沙陇的腹地，沙陇乡在清朝的时候是峡山都东部的中心重镇，仙家村便是沙陇的中心村落了。在这人口几万的大乡当中，如何生存以及发展，是一个现实的问题。因此抢鸡头这种习俗的产生，可能影射着一个残酷的社会现实。社会如丛林，竞争激烈，现实从无救世主，所以我们一直说岭东地方信神是功利性的，每一个信众心里非常清楚，尽管也从众许愿献祭了，但是还是要通过抢，才能在现实中结结实实得到好处。而抢，除了自身的强悍，要敢于出手，当然还要有运气。这是抢鸡头给我的一个观感。这也是古潮阳县民风的一个潜意识折射，讲究运气，胆略，强横，斗争，当仁不让，紧紧扼住雄鸡——哦不，是命运——的咽喉。这在上世纪初叶的过番闯南洋，三十年前改革开放在国内商海闯世界的历史场景中，得到了最好的体现。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=115427&size=300x300&key=756c0207b076261b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_115427\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=115426&size=300x300&key=f4ae5fc0b50b8ae4&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_115426\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">那年正月十六，来自广州的影友捕快与安静和我先后抵达仙家村，我追随着村庙里的三山国王老爷，赶着代表污秽的“香船”穿街过巷，后来我看照片才发现——仙家村的香船上面还有一身纸扎的小人——而来到陇尾爷宫前的大埕的时候，已经人山人海。村里主事者提着花篮，里面就是祭献已毕的熟鸡，面对严阵以待的村民，突然用手一抛——据说那个鸡头便正正落在捕快身前几厘米处，和这个一弯腰的距离失之交臂的原因，在于捕快心里的天人交战，鸡头在仙家村代表着“宜生男”，而捕快则在衡量着与这批彪悍壮丁们的肉搏取胜指数，幸福来得太快去得也太快，手拿相机的捕快瞬间被仙家村男挤出争夺圈。现在生活在雾都伦敦的捕快兄，在N胎无限的异国，闲暇又想造人之际，可有一念闪过这与送子“圣物”擦肩而过的那一瞬间？</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011491916792.png\" title=\"1460011491916792.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>文/岭东怒马 &nbsp;图/岭东怒马 安静声音<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>橄榄小编/立庵</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=115414&size=300x300&key=0151c7e8ef85a030&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_115414\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-03-25 09:13:11',0,NULL,1,NULL,2446,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (365,'【岭东民俗录】仲春鹅游，一相留声 ','201603280924122949.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011464681924.png\" title=\"1460011464681924.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116786&size=300x300&key=c68d332f1f1a028b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116786\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮州府太平路称“牌坊街”，近年恢复了以前的满街牌坊，其中有一块原来立在义安路，上题“十相留声”，意思是潮州府人杰地灵，唐宋时期曾经有十位位至宰辅的高官在此生活停留。这当然是一种宣传手段，虽然免不了有一些为自己脸上贴金的嫌疑，因为唐宋时候潮州府分属天涯海角，京官至此，多为被贬，基本上属于仕途失意的一段低落时光。当然能够位极人臣，必然有过人之处，如果以儒家至圣先师孔夫子为榜样，则即便失意，也会将其人格魅力和影响力留存在这东南一隅。位居“十相”之列的陈尧佐，便是这样一位人物。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116762&size=300x300&key=8a84217924310084&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116762\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">陈尧佐一家三兄弟，是科举时代非常成功的读书人代表。他的哥哥和弟弟参加殿试，均被皇帝钦点状元，而他自己，则比状元哥哥更早一年中举，早早踏上出仕的道路。我们知道，能在殿试中被皇帝相中为第一的，相貌与台风当然更为重要，像一家三兄弟这样高颜值、伟姿貌、口才便给的特殊例子，纵观科举时代，都属凤毛麟角。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116752&size=300x300&key=bacbb56d0875b5ed&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116752\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116757&size=300x300&key=8eda43690b70a746&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116757\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">陈尧佐因为谏言被贬潮州，做为一个儒家年轻才俊，居然与唐代大儒韩愈遭遇相似，轨迹相同，无疑对一时失意的陈尧佐是一个激励和安慰。因此到潮之后，陈先生便接过韩先生的大旗，复孔庙，立韩祠，兴州学，大搞文化复兴，这种科举状元家族出来的顶尖学霸，在潮州这个偏远地区，当然马上成为精神领袖。而陈尧佐更为韩江三角洲士民所津津乐道的，还在于他的杀鳄。韩愈以“祭鳄”打响他在潮州的头炮，而陈尧佐则发挥他的行动力，组织乡勇驾船拖网，在留隍的恶溪上，生捕吃人的巨鳄，并且拖到府城内示众斩杀，这对被恶溪鳄鱼所苦的沿岸士民，简直就是一个视为天人的神勇行动。短短两年潮州生涯，陈尧佐从思想文化到具体施政，均赢得满分，而他与潮州官民相处愉快，在此后回任京官，一路做到枢密使兼参知政事、同平章事等宰辅高官，依然“未曾一日忘潮”，可见他对这段下放生涯的怀念。而潮州最为自得的一个称谓，也是出自陈相的如掾大笔“从此方舆载人物，海滨邹鲁是潮阳”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116761&size=300x300&key=9cfad6325bd57fa5&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116761\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">陈尧佐做为官史有传的著名人物，什么时候成为民间供奉的神明，现在难以确证，但是从韩江中游三角洲腹地的几个大村所建供奉他们三兄弟的庙宇时间来看，至少在明初，陈尧佐便被尊为“灵护公王”而被村民奉为守护神明。灵护公王是个少见于记载的神名，据南宋赵与时《宾退录》 ：“余尝撮城隍爵号，后阅《国朝会要》，考西北诸郡，东京号‘灵护庙’。”则宋时开封城隍庙称为灵护庙，而陈尧佐通判潮州之前，正是开封府推官，此间是否有如此联系，则尚待考证。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116754&size=300x300&key=bd5cfc1b6dea0187&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116754\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">现在有奉祀陈尧佐并尊为村落大老爷的，是以鹳巢、塘湖两个大乡以及他们周边的辐射区，塘湖现在叫做龙湖，明清时代是韩江中游一个大码头，江西、闽北、梅州一带的木材粮食，下游榕江、练江一带的潮糖，都要通过这里进行南北往来，因此形成了“塘湖市”这样一个名噪潮州的商埠。龙湖乡自明朝中叶因为抵御海盗倭寇，在乡绅刘子兴的带领下筑寨自卫，城池坚固，实力不凡，因此也吸引了周围不少商民聚居于此，寨内三街六巷，有小潮州之称。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116767&size=300x300&key=23cdeab3ef1098ed&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116767\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116766&size=300x300&key=a717c41557ab367b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116766\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116768&size=300x300&key=b0b65db435b42583&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116768\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">龙湖寨自宋以来便文风慰藉，南宋科举考中了姚宏中这位探花，明清之季中举之士更多，龙湖既为商埠，人物殷实，鼎盛之时有43姓聚居。明清之际各个宗族通过科举、经商、联姻等方式，向官宦士大夫宗族方面发展，形成了如今宗祠遍布，官宅相邻的布局。而相邻的鹳巢乡，来自漳州南诏的李氏家族，也通过家族的奋斗，出现了“一门四进士、九举十八贡”的科举大捷，从此走上了诗书望族的道路。这两个地方乡村宗族的发展，和读书、科举、出仕密不可分，所以将陈尧佐三兄弟这个科举时代的“神人”奉为大老爷，学而优则仕，因寒窗苦读而拜相封侯，因此带动家族发展，成为影响一方的名门望族，这样剽悍的人生经历上升为普通庶民的榜样之神，实在是没有什么可以挑剔的地方。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116769&size=300x300&key=c11894b0d4830774&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116769\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">当然村民们选择陈尧佐做为保村护境的大老爷，也应当与其杀鳄的壮举有关。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116770&size=300x300&key=89e4c7253f02db3f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116770\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116771&size=300x300&key=b4532761e94393bd&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116771\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">龙湖寨濒临韩江，寨外江面开阔，如遇汛期，必然水祸凶险。很多临水村庄因为忧于水患，自然奉祀众多的能安澜平浪、预测水患的神灵。府城的大老爷安济圣王庙，坐镇南门外堤，而我们追溯过，它的原始崇拜其实就是青蛇，原因就是可以预测洪水，在人们无法与自然抗衡的时候做为神界的代表来压制洪水对村庄的威胁。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116772&size=300x300&key=559d89f0e13e8f18&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116772\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116773&size=300x300&key=9e0613dbef397722&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116773\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">现在龙湖寨的主神庙叫“龙首庙”，地处北门堤边，我们其实可以从它这个名字，甚至从塘湖改名叫龙湖，而猜测它原本就是一座祭祀“蛇”的神庙，这是古代普遍的从蛇到龙，再到人格化的一个信仰改造历程，而陈尧佐做为一个后来官至宰相的官员，被贬之时犹然敢于在波涛凶狠的恶溪中捕杀乡人谈之色变的巨鳄，这在偏远的潮州简直可以以“神”视之，所以将之升格为替代青蛇镇水镇土镇村的全能大神，既完全符合庶民们的思维逻辑，也是士大夫乡绅的愿望，同时也为官方正统学说所能接受，这是否就是韩江中游陈尧佐大老爷背后的历史呢？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116774&size=300x300&key=2c63c8b1891e2f4a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116774\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">陈尧佐是三兄弟一起作为神明而被这些村子奉祀的，大哥三弟均高中状元，陈尧佐虽不是殿试第一，然而封侯拜相，位极人臣，这也是我猜测是这些以科举出身而发展宗族的家族们推动陈氏三兄弟崇拜的一个原因，在学业和仕途上，他们三兄弟就是一个普通人所能做到的巅峰。顺便说一句，其实比起陈尧佐陈相爷，他的三弟更为我们熟知，在九年义务教育的语文书上，每一个初中生都背诵过的短篇散文《卖油翁》，那个被卖油老伯所教育的神箭手陈康肃公，就是我们相爷文武双全的状元弟弟陈尧咨。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116775&size=300x300&key=13c31b2136f25f91&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116775\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116776&size=300x300&key=180afe1338e2bb46&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116776\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116777&size=300x300&key=22b0c4426147c876&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116777\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">当然只有陈尧佐先生来过我们潮州府，一相留声，千古庙食。因此每年的二月十五，被称为二王公的陈老爷及其夫人——村民们说此日是夫人生——要在下午及晚上单独巡游塘湖市地界，在两年的海滨邹鲁生活之后，恐怕陈相爷再无空闲踏上路途遥远的南陲小镇，而塘湖村民们，则趁着“诰命夫人”的“寿诞”，赶着这个岭东小村特有的鹅灯，为陈相爷圆一圆再回潮州的梦。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116778&size=300x300&key=019b21d2661016f0&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116778\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116779&size=300x300&key=78fba5f268e519c1&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116779\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116784&size=300x300&key=af9a933dd7e5d899&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116784\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">像我们所预想的一样，这些鹅灯，同时也经过陈夫人的加持，有多子多孙的神力，因此即便是每一年几乎都是春雨绵绵，塘湖的这一小队虔诚的营灯队伍，依然顽强的保留至今。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116756&size=300x300&key=58c0c3047853143c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116756\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011471123643.png\" title=\"1460011471123643.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 19px;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 19px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 19px;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 19px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 19px;\">文/图&nbsp;&nbsp;岭东怒马&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 19px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 19px;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=116787&size=300x300&key=ceb6f4c5b6cc3b08&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_116787\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-03-28 09:24:12',0,NULL,1,NULL,2304,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (366,'【岭东民俗录】鸿江传奇 ','201604050926081121.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011440119021.png\" title=\"1460011440119021.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">岭东饶平县</span></strong>接近粤闽交界的柘林半岛，明清时属饶平县宣化都，现在是饶平东南部的所城、大埕、柘林三镇，一般俗称为“东界”，古代则称为“东里”。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=117916&size=300x300&key=fca34baad548fc22&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_117916\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这是一个有特别地方特色的一个区域，首先是<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">科举兴盛，</span></strong>仅在明一代，就出过37位举人和7位进士，以及大批生员，而其中就有人称“三达尊”，官至南明礼部尚书的黄锦。而官至湖广左布政使司的东里人陈天资，还专门撰写记述此一区域人文的方志《东里志》。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=117908&size=300x300&key=f8fe816e64c86305&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_117908\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而与文风鼎盛同时存在的另外一面，则是此地<span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">民风剽悍</span>。</strong>好勇斗狠，嗜利轻生等评语，不断见诸方志。而不但豪强村民接济番舶，劫掠行舟，就是官吏兵卫，也不保险，嘉靖四十三年，柘林海兵兵变，居然“扬帆直抵广城”（郭子章《潮中杂记》），像乡民通倭劫掠的事情则更为普遍。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=117912&size=300x300&key=cf4e3bb2e9e953f1&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_117912\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=117921&size=300x300&key=83328350e0e2f743&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_117921\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">究其原因，则在于这个地方地理僻远，又在闽粤之交，府城县城鞭长莫及，而其处于南北海运的航线干道，自古便有走私为利的吸引，而当地别有渔盐厚利，使得此地甚至“莠民藉以负固，敢于拒捕抗粮”，而“官吏捕治为难”，对于国家管理来说，是一个难题。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而明代倭寇流民经常为祸岭东沿海，海盗势力强大，时战时降。</span></strong>对于地方官府来说，除了武力战斗之外，更为头痛的是如何安置那些受招安的海盗兵众，即所谓的“抚民”。而东里因为有大城所这个“守御千户所”，所以经常也被就近做为安置抚民的地方，也<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">加剧了此地的动荡因素</strong>。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=117918&size=300x300&key=c803815bd38fa684&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_117918\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">然而事实上这些叙述，同样也是明清时代潮州府在中央视野上的印象。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">整个东南沿海，潮州府既有“海滨邹鲁“雅誉，同时也长期陷入与海寇拉锯的乱局之中</span></strong>，而治下之民，则好勇斗狠，“岭以南行省二，广东为难治。广东列郡九，潮州为难治”。这与东里在潮州府视野下的印象何其一致。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=117915&size=300x300&key=92a55eca44758993&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_117915\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">但是其实从乡村视野出发，做为庶民的家园，其实东里一带，并非总是如此兵荒马乱，危如累卵，处于高危地带<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">。至少在和平时代，既盛产鱼盐，又为闽粤商旅舟船停泊港口的东里鸿江，现在叫做大港村的大乡，就是闽粤交界各地眼中的理想家园。</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=117904&size=300x300&key=396df9dc24a71b8b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_117904\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">大港</span>，古称鸿江，处于东里半岛的西面，濒临内海。</strong>明代中期，这里成了连接整个半岛中心大城所和外界的水路枢纽，因为人口的增多，整个东里半岛资源缺乏，生活用品以及粮食，都要通过大港转运。而大港栅，则是东里四个产盐区里面条件最好的，一直到解放后围海造田方才停止。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=117917&size=300x300&key=c30de60a22de34a4&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_117917\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这里流传有吴氏“五龙”三下广的创乡传说。大港的主要居民均姓杨，然而他们都说是吴氏后人，而且祖先就是诏安四都梅州乡的著名士人吴大成。吴大成是南宋福建的“渐山七贤”之一，入读太学，与老师陈景肃在诏安的渐山屏山书院讲学，他们这一批人的学生有很多出仕做官，因此上在闽南一带颇负声望。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=117920&size=300x300&key=70046937c6c8b866&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_117920\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">吴大成后代“五龙三下广”的故事，记述了吴氏入粤创乡的历程，其中一支迁入大港，一支辗转迁到饶平长彬村，这是宋末自闽入潮的移民潮在民间传说中的反映，我们现在不知道这个传说的确切程度，因为在岭东存在太多宗族为了发展而人为重构的事实。但是吴氏在大港乡改姓杨氏，则被宗族祠堂建筑所明确。</span></p><p><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=117909&size=300x300&key=2c150282544ebfca&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_117909\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在大港流传一句俗话，“大祠不出姓， 中桁接二架”，因为他们尊祀共同祖先的大祠堂，大门匾额只有“大宗祠”三字，并没有冠上杨氏。而祠堂奉祀的祖先，除了始祖与一世祖吴清江之外，不再署姓氏。传说中是说族人在大港得到杨氏扶持而开枝散叶，杨氏无后，为报答杨氏的恩德，因此吴清江后代易姓为杨。大宗祠的前厅结构，主厅中桁接旁厅的第二桁；而旁厅的中桁则接主厅的第二桁，这奇特的建筑结构据说与他们易姓为杨姓有关。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=117914&size=300x300&key=67d8ef9f485ebbb4&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_117914\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=117923&size=300x300&key=614ddc01b519b161&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_117923\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">大港乡是一个人口逾两万的大乡，现在是一个杨氏村落，并且因为人口多而分拆成了两个行政村，但是每一年的二月十九至二十一日，他们都会举行盛大的游神仪式，把村外龙潭寺的观音请到大宗祠中接受村民祭拜，然后分两天巡游原来鸿江村的地界，巡游的时候各房头设立迎神香案，大宗祠的理事会则组织新婚丁壮抬轿，村里出动锣鼓班、布马队、旱船等娱乐队伍，成为东界地区知名的游神赛会活动，吸引了不少临近群众观看。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=117910&size=300x300&key=137330229bae35e1&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_117910\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=117905&size=300x300&key=358ba620a4a3fe03&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_117905\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=117906&size=300x300&key=e34a0e37f6b8d687&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_117906\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">二月十九是观音诞</strong>，龙潭寺是一个据传建自南宋的佛寺，在大港村外的琉璃岭下，其信众并非只有大港一村，而大港则另外有一座神庙，就在大宗祠附近不远，主祀不知来历的王公王妈，内配祀岭东常见的花公花妈，舍人老爷，巡抚总督，还有龙王爷等杂神。村里人称龙潭寺的观音为“佛祖”，香炉上则写“慈悲娘娘”，这是佛教世俗化为民间信仰的普遍例子，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在饶北山区，对观音称为“观音娘”“慈悲娘”，并当成俗神崇拜的比比皆是。而有一个说法就是，近海的疍民，原始的崇拜就是佛祖、妈祖和舍人爷。</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=117913&size=300x300&key=ab8a93e413d29c11&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_117913\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">然而，清王朝康熙元年到七年的迁海斥界行动，势必将划为界外的东里半岛各乡在明朝中叶以后的所有经营化为灰烬。比起其他地方幸运的是，因为大城所的存在，半岛居民们可以迁入所城而不必向澄海县民一样，远迁程乡。展界之后，一切重新洗牌。从现在大港乡主要以杨姓为主的情况，我们可以推测，展界之后由吴氏改姓杨氏的一族占据了这个盐区的话语权。到康熙五十七年，便有记载称诏安梅洲廪生吴逢因将兴龙公神主送归大港，神主题曰“梅洲三房大港开基祖兴龙公暨配三孺人”。随着明代中叶灶户余盐开禁，开始有“富灶”从产盐业获得暴利，像前面提到的陈天资就是灶户户籍。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=117919&size=300x300&key=587b3c8d3deade25&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_117919\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">我们现在的疑问就是，迅速积攒财富并且扩张的吴氏一族，和原来的杨氏，是否存在着盐场的租佃雇佣关系，这里面是否存在着不为人知的一个故事，而这个故事，是否就是明清四百年来东里半岛充满张力的一出传奇？</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=117907&size=300x300&key=fbbdc5d3cacb7874&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_117907\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011449551237.png\" title=\"1460011449551237.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: small; line-height: 19px;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: small; line-height: 19px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: small; line-height: 19px;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: small; line-height: 19px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: small; line-height: 19px;\">文/图&nbsp;&nbsp;岭东怒马&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: small; line-height: 19px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: small; line-height: 19px;\">橄榄小编/沐木</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=117927&size=300x300&key=fcfc180c1767d3aa&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_117927\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-04-05 09:26:08',0,NULL,1,NULL,2274,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (367,'【岭东民俗录】清明挂纸','201604050930359280.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011415704301.png\" title=\"1460011415704301.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118239&size=300x300&key=fb00af3aebd29960&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118239\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">今天我们翻开民国翁辉东所作的《风俗志》，其中记载清明岭东风俗：清明或上巳人家多上冢扫墓，祭以牲礼，又取朴子树叶舂粿，揭阳尤盛。祭墓者，多以冥镪压于坟头，及挂黄白纸条谓之挂纸，表示寒食禁烟遗意。所记百年以前风俗，于今竟无一不同，而考据清明节在我大中华的历史演化，便会从中看到一个充满趣味的庶民生活长卷。“<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">挂纸”的挂，口语白读为【求瓜3】，人皆以为“过”，事实上是潮语文白异读的原因，本字就是挂纸，这是寒食古俗在今天潮人口语中依然遗存的一个例子。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118228&size=300x300&key=0abde353d2dc1243&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118228\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118232&size=300x300&key=6e42987d0fc8274d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118232\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">清明，首先是中国传统二十四节气中的一个，代表着季春的来临，西汉《淮南子·天文训》：“春分后十五日，斗指乙，则清明风至。”《岁时百问》：“万物生长此时，皆清洁而明净。故谓之清明。”作为时序标志的清明节气，早在汉初《太初历》颁布的时候，就已经有明确记载。清明节气，春暖花开，是万物生长时节，所以农谚说：清明前后种瓜种豆，正是农时播种之时。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118231&size=300x300&key=7b38f7c18cf3234f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118231\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">然而做为潮人所讲的“时年八节”中重要日子的清明节，与节气的关系不是很大，其中大部分是继承了古代另外一个节日“寒食”的内容而形成的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118237&size=300x300&key=726739de7fdd4ca4&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118237\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">《荆楚岁时记》所述：“去冬节一百五日，即有疾风甚雨，谓之寒食。”这是一个古老的节日，它最初的内容就如同其名字所表现的一样，是“禁火冷食”。禁火最早是与五行星宿学说中的“龙忌”有关，因为心宿春天出现在东方，心为大火，惧火之盛，故为之禁火。（唐·李贤注引《新序》），而民俗中断火三日，则是为了清灶，以新火换旧火，这主要反映了古人改火习俗的遗存，上古时代，先民们钻木取火，火种来之不易，取火的树种往往因季节变化而不断变换，因此，改火与换取新火是古人生活中的一件大事。春三月正值改火的时节，人们在新火未到之时，要禁止生火。汉代称寒食节为禁烟节，因为这天百姓人家不得举火，到了晚上才由宫中点燃烛火，并将火种传至贵戚重臣家中。这就是所谓的：日暮汉宫传蜡烛，轻烟散入五侯家。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118240&size=300x300&key=f366405a3ed5879f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118240\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而有关介之推与晋文公的故事，其实并非事实，最早是神奇的浪漫主义大师庄子创造的，而将禁火与纪念介之推联系起来则要迟至西汉末期，桓谭在《新论·卷十一·离事》中，第一次明确了寒食节与介之推的关系：“太原郡民，以隆冬不火食五日，虽有疾病缓急，犹不敢犯，为介子推故也。”而到了南朝范晔的《后汉书·周举传》，寒食习俗和介之推传说就进入了正史：“太原一郡旧俗以介子推焚骸，有龙忌之禁，至其亡月咸言神灵不乐举火，由是士民每冬中辄一月寒食，莫敢烟爨。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118230&size=300x300&key=41b6c779be4c0678&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118230\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">介之推之说与寒食墓祭的联系因此也就顺理成章。但是寒食墓祭之风起于何时？宋代赵彦卫《云麓漫钞》载：“自汉世祖（指光武帝刘秀）令诸将出征拜墓以荣其乡，至唐开元，诏许寒食上墓同拜扫礼，沿袭至今，遂有墓祭。”清 赵翼 《陔馀丛考·墓祭》：“盖 三代 以上本无墓祭，故 辛有 见被发祭野者而以为异。”《唐会要》卷二十三《寒食拜埽》里唐玄宗开元二十年(732)“宜许上墓”诏令：“寒食上墓，礼经无文，近世相传，浸以成俗。士庶有不合庙享，何以用展孝思？宜许上墓……，仍编入礼典，永为常式”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118235&size=300x300&key=cfeaa52be98ad7cd&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118235\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">即唐玄宗时已经以官方法令形式将寒食墓祭定为礼制。而下这道诏令的原因，则是因为当时墓祭早已经蔚然成风，甚至影响到了公务员的工作，官吏回乡扫墓，时有耽误职守之事，因此朝廷顺应风俗，颁布政令解决假期的问题，寒食节放假从四天一直到贞元六年（790），假日加到七天。这样官员们可以从容地进行扫墓祭奠之事。由此可见，当时寒食节已经成为唐朝一个很隆重的全国性节日。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118276&size=300x300&key=5b89a5e0187a785c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118276\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;color:#808080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 19.5px;\">△</span>苏轼寒食帖（局部）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;color:#808080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">然而这个墓祭又是起于何时？汉时对此问题曾经讨论不休，有说“古不墓祭”， 因为周礼更为重视灵魂，对死去的先人，礼法要求要立庙而祭。而且宗法制度森严，只有贵族才可以建庙以祭，庶民只能够在家拜祭三代以内的祖先，对于先人埋葬更加规定严格，庶民“墓而不坟”，不能够在墓上面封土设置标志，以致孔子要将母亲和父亲合葬的时候，居然找不到父亲的墓，连墓都忘记在哪里，自然没有定时拜祭的可能。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118280&size=300x300&key=995ecde71d26e594&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118280\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;color:#808080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 19.5px;\">△</span>孔子墓（网络资料）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;color:#808080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">但是贵族因为可以设“冢”，也就是有封土的坟丘，这是一个可以显示后人地位的标志，很快在春秋时代礼制荒废时被庶民们仿效。《<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">礼记・檀弓上</span></strong>》载:“<span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">孔子既得合葬于防,曰:‘吾闻之:古也墓而不坟;今丘也,东西南北之人也,不可以弗识也。’于是封之。</strong></span>”孔子所言“古也墓而不坟”,是说在他生活的时代之前庶民墓上无封土,但现在既然大家都开始“坟”了,他也就接受了这种做法,在父母的墓葬上垒起了封土。连孔子都从俗了，庶民们从此有固定的祭拜先人的场所。据《史记》记载,孔子死后,“鲁世世相传以岁时奉祠孔子冢”,墓祭孔子年年都举行。《孟子・离娄》中有一则寓言也证明了庶民墓祭的普遍性。故事说的是齐国有一个男人,他每天都是早起就出门,酒足饭饱之后才回家。妻子跟踪他至城东的坟地,发现他竟像乞丐一样,向上坟祭奠的人乞讨祭毕的酒食,一处不够,又到别处去讨。这个寓言说明此时庶人有墓祭行为,而且祭祀行为较为频繁。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118236&size=300x300&key=5193ec2f7296a43b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118236\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">因此墓祭之风由此从春秋战国一直延续到汉唐，终于政府把寒食墓祭定为不刊之礼，并且颁布假日法令，遂为风俗。宋代以后，缘于寒食节与清明节长期处在同一节日期间，寒食展墓内容基本相沿不变，但寒食名称历经数百年演变，逐渐被“清明”所替代。南宋吴自牧撰《梦梁录》曰：“清明日，官员士庶俱出郊省坟”。之所以将墓祭称为扫墓，《清通礼》说得好：“岁，寒食及霜降节，拜扫圹茔，届期素服诣墓，具酒馔及芟剪草木之器，周胝封树，剪除荆草，故称扫墓。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118234&size=300x300&key=2dd3f43ca3b99b13&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118234\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">明《帝京景物略》载“三月清明日，男女扫墓，担提尊榼，轿马后挂楮锭，粲粲然满道也。拜者、酹者、哭者、为墓除草添土者，焚楮锭次，以纸钱置坟头。望中无纸钱，则孤坟矣。哭罢，不归也，趋芳树，择园圃，列坐尽醉。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118229&size=300x300&key=3b1e167160db1eb1&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118229\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这样的记载，则是又将古时候的“上巳节”的风俗合并到清明节了。古时在三月初三日为上巳节，主要内容是祓禊。祓禊就是以兰草洗浴，求神灵拂除不详，洗故洁新之意，后来演变为踏青。由于清明上坟都要到郊外去，在祭奠祖先之余，在明媚的春光里将祭献食物分而享之，既是纳福，同时也变成一个家族野外聚餐。因此，清明节也被人们称作踏青节。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118241&size=300x300&key=34fa530ce1466257&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118241\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在岭东潮人聚居地，清明仍然保持了中原古代倾家出动，数日内郊野间人群往来不绝的盛况。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">清明扫墓内容一是整修坟墓，二是挂烧纸钱、供奉祭品。扫墓时首先清除杂草，培添新土，然后在墓碑上妆字。由于寒食禁火古俗的影响，纸钱不焚烧，而是挂在墓地的小树上、竹竿上，或用石块、土疙瘩压在坟墓边。宋庄季裕《鸡肋篇》卷上：“寒食上冢，亦不设香火。纸钱挂于茔树。其去乡里者，皆登山望祭。裂帛于空中，谓之掰钱。”这样，凡是祭扫过的坟墓就有纸幡飘飘，构成清明前后的特有景观。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118238&size=300x300&key=e4e82e5324fdd040&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118238\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮语现在仍将扫墓称为“挂纸”既是来源于此。清版《揭阳县志 岁时》载：“清明扫墓，松楸邱陇间遍悬楮钱，谓之‘挂纸’。”“挂纸”作为墓祭的一个环节，就是将长条形纸镪用石头或者土疙瘩压在坟丘之上。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118233&size=300x300&key=dbd324b71e429c61&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118233\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">除了挂纸习俗，岭东潮人沿袭寒食“冷食”的食俗，有现在澄海一带居民，寒食要吃薄饼。薄饼以熟面为皮，内用豆芽、鸡蛋、韭菜等应时食物配以其他肉类等为馅，一如春饼，只是并不油炸。类似的小吃在潮汕地区发展为全年皆有的甜食“糖葱薄饼”，只不过糖葱为白糖加麦芽糖拉出的色白如葱的入口即化的糖霜，与清明澄海居民所吃的以咸馅为主的食品不同。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118513&size=300x300&key=450c24f494d5de1f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118513\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118514&size=300x300&key=dd0dc321ea613354&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118514\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; font-size: medium; line-height: 1.5;\">另外一个特殊的食品是朴子粿。朴子，即朴树的嫩叶，清明前后初生嫩芽，绞成汁与米浆混合，加入白糖与发酵粉，然后倒入圆型容器中蒸熟，成品是一个碧绿诱人的酵粿，朴子嫩叶清明前后有清热去湿，消除积食之效。而据福建《兴化府志》载：“清明各家以鼠曲和米粉为稞。”其俗也与潮俗同，潮俗自正月开始已经采鼠曲草做粿，所以民间有“清明食叶” 之说。此种习俗来自于江南，《荆楚岁时记》里就有记载：“是日（三月初三），取鼠曲菜汁作羹，以蜜和粉，谓之龙舌柈，以厌时气”，而流传在浙江福建的清明团，青精饭，便均类此。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118227&size=300x300&key=851cca9b29ea5c16&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118227\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color:#808080;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 19.5px;\">△</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family: Tahoma; font-size: small; line-height: 19.5px;\">鼠曲草</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118226&size=300x300&key=928c3eb60f7b91ce&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118226\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;color:#808080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">△朴子</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">岭东一带清明时节雨纷纷，因此踏青之俗现在已然不多，只是先祖墓茔多在山上，此时扫墓多有郊外行踏，然而雨多泥泞，天晴则气温又已升高，再者农事催人，扫墓之后，也要安排插秧农活，因此像江南一带的踏春赏花，秋千蹴鞠之类活动，也就因为不适应本地区的实际，而渐渐消失了。今天的清明节，以慎终追远为目的，联结宗族乡谊为需要的回乡扫墓大军，在清明前后，充斥深汕公路，往来于珠三角与原乡岭东之间，高速小车塞途，已经成为十几年来一个新的现象。潮人对家乡以及农耕时代家族的追慕，由此可见一斑。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011425237062.png\" title=\"1460011425237062.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道 &nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">文/ 岭东怒马 &nbsp;图/岭东怒马、安静声音</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118244&size=300x300&key=fa858c9cb1bf2607&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118244\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-04-05 09:30:35',0,NULL,1,NULL,2326,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (368,'【岭东民俗录】三山是谁的国王','201604050931259079.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011397103082.png\" title=\"1460011397103082.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119262&size=300x300&key=75f86c183cd181ec&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119262\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>三山国王做为岭东独有的神祇，一度被指为潮州人的信仰标志。这个神明在潮人乡村非常普遍，而且也被华侨带到南洋，同时在台湾也被广为奉祀。海外及台湾对三山国王的研究很多，但是做为神源地，岭东对它的记述和传说，却有很多版本，这些版本说法不一，而且甚多神话色彩，各个村落对之又有自己的阐释，所以很有必要就现有看到的资料，来对三山国王进行一番解读。<img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119247&size=300x300&key=b1fd56afb665ed4a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119247\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119249&size=300x300&key=75913b5d89c58b0a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119249\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>三山国王是岭东本土的神祇大抵是没有疑问的。首先三山指向岭东揭西境内的“巾、明、独”三座山，其次三山国王信仰的地域分布，在国内的，只在广东境内莲花山脉以东到福建境内梁山以西范围之内，大约在现今汕尾市以东，福建漳州市云霄漳浦以西的范围内，和初唐以前潮州的政区地域大致相当。现在可以读到的有关这个神祇的最早的文献，是元代刘希孟的《潮州路明贶三山国王庙记》。《庙记》记载神的起源，提到“石穴”、“枫树”、“莲花”、“界石”等等，这一些符号表明，初唐以前生活在这个地区的土著先民，和今天的壮侗苗瑶等南方少数民族之间存在某些可能的联系，而事实上，史籍地方志以及人类学者们的研究都表明，初唐以前本地为中央政权所不容的“蛮獠”，与如今的壮瑶各族，都有着千丝万缕的联系。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119240&size=300x300&key=31f5b437d4bc29d1&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119240\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119241&size=300x300&key=21387dffea9b7fab&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119241\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>随着国家力量的冲击以及汉民族移民大潮的来临，本地土著日渐融合与退出岭东地域，而现今依然留存的两支土著畲族和疍家，畲族对三山神的崇拜自然不用多所解释，疍家在地方志中也有乾隆《兴宁县志》“蛋……其称神云：明山、汉帝、有感大王”，所谓的明山，即指三山中的明山，可见不管是在山中的畲，还是水边的疍，三山国王都是这些原来岭东的土著居民的原生信仰。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119246&size=300x300&key=d776fccb6148cdf3&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119246\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">从岭东政区历史以及基层乡村的演变来看，三山国王从一个原住民的信仰，经过了多次的战争、移民、同化、融合等长期的变化，到了元朝之后，明显已经被南迁而至的汉人接受与改造，成为先人与土人互相融合的一个祖先印记。这就是元朝刘希孟在《明贶庙记》中说的&quot;潮之三邑，梅、惠二州，在在有祠，岁时走集，莫敢遑宁&quot;。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119238&size=300x300&key=0565b7ec199b5ad2&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119238\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119239&size=300x300&key=ac6e84ada18305b7&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119239\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>刘希孟这一篇庙记，陈春声先生认为是汉人为三山国王信仰正名并接上正统的一个改造工程。在当时的情况下，如何把一种已经广泛存在的民间信仰，引入到国家意志管理的轨道上，刘先生与其上司当然是煞费苦心。但是时移世易，当历史和时代的车轮走过近千年，当年路人皆知的事实已经如烟尘般飘走，而这么一篇真假莫辨的庙记，却把真相掩藏在文字的蛛丝马迹里面，而让后人陷入无法确知的迷雾之中。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119245&size=300x300&key=6eda565955fde298&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119245\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>《庙记》称三山国王，“肇迹于隋，灵显于唐，受封于宋”，这种神界的“隐语”，用人类学的眼光进行解码，就是显示了本地社区在隋唐之际，汉人移民开始迁入土著领域，而到了宋朝，则初步实现了南迁汉族对土著居民的同化。这样解读的佐证在于时间上正好同本地国家化的进程同步。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">换句话来说，三山国王身份显赫的历史，就是汉人同化土著，并最终成为岭东主导者的历史。而这个过程，与现在我们所说的潮州民系和客家民系并没有直接的关系。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119244&size=300x300&key=dc594d8575076434&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119244\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>将岭东民众分为潮州或者说福佬和客家两种民系，并不是明清以前的事实。事实上在清雍正十一年嘉应直隶州一州四县从潮州府分拆出以前，说福佬话和客家话两种方言的民众，都对本地区有统一的认同。换句话说，三山国王并不是划分为潮客的一个信仰，他是一个地域性信仰，而当时南迁生活在岭东这个地区的汉人，即便说的不是同一种方言，但都同时接受了这一种土著的山神崇拜，这也就解释了梅州客属地区的三山神以及为何三山国王祖庙坐落在揭西半山客属地区的问题。同时也反证了三山国王原本是岭东本土的土著信仰，早在潮客南来的时候就已经存在。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119242&size=300x300&key=22d84015427cc62a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119242\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119243&size=300x300&key=96aa96c79ab3a7d9&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119243\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>三山国王在明清两代并未再受到朝廷的册封，这当然是因为到了明清时候，本地的汉化已经基本定局，采用升格土著的信仰而达到管理的手段，已经不需要了。这个时候国家意志的注意力，转向了如何对付沿海的海寇，如何管理日渐蓬勃的商业浪潮对农耕村居稳定性的影响，因此，妈祖、关公、双忠公这类神祇，就代替了三山国王，成为王朝更为重视也更为实用的管理工具。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119250&size=300x300&key=c5613df46eb2a050&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119250\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>但是由于三山国王信仰此前随着本地民众从小到大的发展，早就成为根植血液之内的牢固祖先记忆，以致在喜欢追摹祖先生活的岭东族群里受到广泛的崇拜。民间信仰的功利性使得三山国王在社区中的地位一再下降，但是其先祖记忆的亲切度一直未能在民间磨灭，因此在岭东很多乡村中，三山国王便成为了一个“地头神”，成为主管普通村民们生老病死的一个社神角色。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119259&size=300x300&key=07d9f35ff783ce28&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119259\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>明末清初，潮州移民（包括客家和福老两个民系）东渡台湾，南下南洋，这个原来在同一区域被共同供奉的神，成为原乡的回忆，和系连同乡的纽带，也在台湾和东南亚有广泛的分布。庶民的历史再次被俗世的变迁淹没，现在的台湾人甚至将三山国王看做是客家人的独有神祇，而每年的二月二十五，就是三山国王诞辰，此前台湾客属进香团，已经多次远渡重洋，前往揭西霖田祖庙进香。这些台湾的香客们，带着他们的乩童，在三山祖庙前举行各种仪式，但是已经茫然不知，千年以前的沧海桑田了。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119260&size=300x300&key=d190f77415aa4d12&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119260\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119261&size=300x300&key=bfdf0844e633baf9&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119261\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">我们追神的目的或者说兴趣所在，主要是民间信仰中的神祇，其实反映了不同时代，不同历史社区中信仰他的民众的历史轨迹，文字记述的史记只是精英的历史，而庶民的历史，如花开花落，即便是繁华怒放的存在，也必然被无情的时光一次次践踏和淹没。但是借助于“神”这种载体，却神奇般地在口耳相传中一代代因袭而来。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">神明本是人创造出来作为现实的一种寄托，本身虚无缥缈，一经传播，更多荒诞不经。但是从这个意义上来说，作为庶民历史的见证者，神明超越时光和空间的存在，却恰恰成为其最有价值的地方，在我们看来，这才是神之所以“神”的地方——他们居然是人的永恒见证者。</span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(139, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119248&size=300x300&key=fa05942063b7658c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119248\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></strong></span><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011405112127.png\" title=\"1460011405112127.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/图&nbsp;&nbsp;岭东怒马</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119222&size=300x300&key=90557b8a2244a3f7&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119222\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/></span><br/></p>','2016-04-05 09:31:25',0,NULL,1,NULL,2631,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (369,'【清明词典】贵纸','201604050932092116.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011377451274.png\" title=\"1460011377451274.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span></p><p><em style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><strong style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\"color:#008080;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">【编者按】</span>又</strong></span><strong style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">是一年春草绿，又到一年清明时。</span></span></strong></em><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><em style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><strong style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">清明最初只是一个节气，演变成怀念祭祀先人的传统节日。有人说，清明是一个今人与古人、生者与逝者、现在与过去、人类与自然进行多重沟通与交流的特殊日子，饱含着中国人对生与死的哲学思考，对人生价值的道德评判。今天起，汕头橄榄台推出青年潮俗研究者林培阳的系列文章<span style=\"color:#8b0000;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">《清明词典》</span>。和之前推出的《过年词典》一样，《清明词典》名虽为词典，实则借词说事，讲是的作者寄予清明的情绪和记忆，以及潮汕地区浓厚的清明习俗。</strong></em></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118094&size=300x300&key=1c4240bf5fc8a952&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118094\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;max-width: 400px\"/><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">汫洲人称扫墓为贵纸，潮汕其他地方就叫过纸，贵纸并非洛阳纸贵，其实就是在祖先坟上过一次纸，表示一次拜祭。清明分古清明和现代清明，古清明是三月初三，有些人每年看特定的日子去贵纸，年年不同，一般来说是阳历4月4日或5日。所以清明时节，整个汫洲乡里的青山会发生有趣的变化。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118108&size=300x300&key=98c6c5c7f08db3dc&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118108\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;max-width: 400px\"/><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;font-family: Tahoma;letter-spacing: 0\">△</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;font-family: 宋体\">图片来自网络</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;font-family: 宋体\"><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">贵纸不仅是简单的集体活动，这种活动也令山河易色。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">清明前春天到了，青山、赤米山、狮山、虎头山、糜红栖、猫仔压篮饭、坑内、三屿、大北山、东灶山青青翠竹，郁郁黄花，高峰相连，深谷远径，深绿色的高树、各色野花、春草勃发，又风又绿江南岸，一个绿字写满漫山遍野。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118106&size=300x300&key=da84fbe2c025a9bc&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118106\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;max-width: 400px\"/><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">有一年古清明过后，我经过经山，背对大海，向群山望去，前边有几处白色，跟着靠近红山那边也有一小长条白色，整个山体绵延开去，就像一只黑鹤白翅白颈。清明节的那天，早上跟中午，整个山脉由青渐深，几乎每时每鹿刻都在发生变化，慰为大观。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">清明第二天，漫山遍野就都变成白色，整个山体变成一只白鹤。春风抖动着鹤身，春雨或艳阳下，群山像一只飞过大海的野鹤，翩翩飞向宁静的海村渔隅。如果有可能，应远距离拍下这个变化，我想必是一种奇观。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118115&size=300x300&key=8932c3d834ba10a7&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118115\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;max-width: 400px\"/><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">贵纸的纸都从街上买来。有制作成纸条的，有整张纸的。小时候父亲总在清明前一日买来一叠白纸，自己用剪刀割成一叠叠的长纸条。然后分成一串串，大概是祖父母分得多些。其他上祖每去一处，便拿起一叠连同祭拿到山上去。人多的祖墓，至处都是白纸条，一筐一筐的，祭毕后。由老人一筐筐献跪，然后一人拿起一叠白纸条，用一块山石压在坟头，老人拿起另一串白纸，压在伯爷公神位上。伯爷公是阴间的土地管理中心主任，地位相当高的。完了之后，小孩子们便拿起白纸在坟上玩。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118109&size=300x300&key=07f7f6b4a42ff59f&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118109\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;max-width: 400px\"/><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">记得有一次，玩着玩着，不知何故，我就跟一个亲人小女孩打起来了。还拿石块相互追遂，大概是争拿纸条吧。纸条总被反复拿起放下，在空中就像飞絮雪花浪涛。自已祖父的墓上，就要很仔细地将一条一条的纸深埋入坟土中。关于为什么要用白纸条，有一个传说来自秦始皇的。据说，这白纸原来叫“引魂幡”，秦始皇修万里长城，需要很多砖头和石头。这长城又修得特别急，砖烧不够快，石头也无处寻找，秦始皇就了道圣旨，把人家坟上的砖和石头全都扒了，抬来修长城。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">那时秦始皇的老爹刚死不久，如果扒坟，他爹的坟也要扒。于是他对负责扒坟的大臣说：“有记号的坟不扒。”按风俗，古代埋好人后，就有引魂幡插在新坟上，像西藏的经幡那种形式。引魂幡用的都是白色纸条，在新坟上被风吹得摇摇摆摆，很惹眼。扒坟的大臣走到秦始皇爹的坟前，看见挂有白纸条，认为是做的记号，便没扒坟。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118107&size=300x300&key=95505a4f86ad1e22&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118107\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;max-width: 400px\"/><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">老百姓们看见挂白纸条的坟不扒，便都剪白纸条挂在坟上。如此年复一年，都这么做。这样，一代代传下来，就成了风俗。汫洲人贵纸看来也是由这种风俗演变而来的。不过大部分风俗年代久远，已经没有人知道他的根据。所以像汕尾人钟敬文那样民俗学家需要再多点，潮汕文化才能更好地为传承下去。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118116&size=300x300&key=c6b8ddc4f0de41c0&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118116\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;max-width: 400px\"/><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">人们已经忘掉贵纸的来历，而纸也并不贵重，但人们总不忘自已的祖先，于是贵纸成就一种气氛。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">群山尽白，层峰皆染。清明，纸的世界。祖宗魂皆归来，海风起时，白纸颤动时，就是他们在说话。<img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011385134177.png\" title=\"1460011385134177.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">本文由青年民俗研究者林培阳先生授权橄榄台发表</span></span><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></span><br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">文/林培阳</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:12px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 19.5px\">图/网络<br style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\">橄榄小编/沐木</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;;padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118093&size=300x300&key=ebde8bbcb97e4453&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118093\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\";padding: 0px;word-wrap: break-word;max-width: 400px\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-04-05 09:32:09',0,NULL,1,NULL,2363,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (370,'【清明词典】记忆中那些，还留在故土的花草','201604050932469752.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011356772291.png\" title=\"1460011356772291.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118615&size=300x300&key=30d185721fed5442&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118615\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">其实我们都是乡下的花草，只是被动或主动移植到城里来。有没有水土不服，不知道。清明，我深深体味那些还留在故土的花草。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118611&size=300x300&key=1879f9ba1c93613d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118611\" width=\"293\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">我还不知道“盐酸仔草”能开那么美丽的蓝色小花。一朵朵像从叶子中间窜起来。一个个坟墓，布满了这种花。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">小时，很多人分不清“盐酸仔”和“白沥些”，许多人去山上挖可以吃的白沥些根子很费劲。其实很易分辨。“盐酸仔”叶子薄很多，也要高大一些。“白沥些”就十分厚实。“盐酸仔”较多。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118612&size=300x300&key=805408e6f702ff38&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118612\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">《幼学琼林》有古训，叫我们多识花鸟虫鱼之名。只是我们除了阳台山上几种常见常接触的，识不了多少种花木的名字。现在带小孩子进植物园，很多小孩子懂得比大人多。这种古训没有留下来。就地取材，在坟身上拨起“盐酸仔花”，束成两扎，放在墓碑上，格外美丽。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">祖父坟前的那棵苦楝树已经不见。过去，年复一年的有一棵苦楝树在坟前生长，每年都被父亲用锄头斫掉。春风吹又升，隔年又重新生枝发叶。有一年，那苦楝树不长了，恰是那年我考上大学，就很少回去祭祖。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">现在，祖父坟墓附近的苦楝树长得老高，还有一些枯藤横竖缠绕，让人真正体现墓木可拱的成语的真正意义。他过世时我虚岁才三，现在没有他的记忆。如果可以，我愿成为祖父墓前的那棵苦楝树，永远耸立在高山层林中。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118610&size=300x300&key=2e52fe9dc817796e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118610\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">仙脚迹祖路上的山芋已经不在，过去采撷一叶，顶住清明的烈日是常有的事。上年纪的男性不敢这样做，是怕人家说他们青头。人有时做的是非，倒顶不过别人一句话重要，这样多累。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">也许因为这样，老农也不知在我没回来的哪一年里，将山芋改种成一排排玉米。玉米初长成，已有趋形。我第一次在故里看见有人种玉米，黄色一片，就在一道溪旁，因此颇兴奋，去年还没注意过。其实，祖坟也是一棵玉米，供人们敬仰的同时，也供后人消费着。兴许后人的所有行为，都跟他们无关。因为他们只是一棵在另一个世界静静生长着的玉米。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118613&size=300x300&key=fd4e9e9965c02e6d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118613\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">东灶路始祖石碑角上竟然生长一棵高大翠绿的老榕树，远看像一根伞。墓地空旷，像稀树草原中的按树一样挺拔着。很好看，我不知道为什么墓碑角会有这么这棵树，也不知道因此那坟墓被叫“独角星牛”。因为后头那块石头很大，独角星牛应是那石头的称谓而非这棵榕树。始祖坐在这树下，该舒服很多罢。我不知道。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">转过始祖后山，见那梦境中的高路深处一片森林。勾起林泉高致的一种想像。森林是人类的开始或者结果，没有人清楚。但这森林深处，正因不可接近而神秘。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118614&size=300x300&key=3b58b6fde7193302&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118614\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">我还记上港祖母坟前面溪河边的高大大岩石和翠竹丛，只是多年没去看了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">清明到处生机勃发，草木最是。</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;color:#008080;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></strong></span></p><p><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; font-size: medium; line-height: 1.5;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></strong></em></p><p><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; font-size: medium; line-height: 1.5;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">3月30日起，汕头橄榄台推出青年潮俗研究者林培阳的系列文章<span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">《<span style=\"color:#FF0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">清明词典</span>》</span>。和之前推出的《过年词典》一样，《清明词典》名虽为词典，实则借词说事，讲是的作者寄予清明的情绪和记忆，以及潮汕地区浓厚的清明习俗。</strong></em></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011364237578.png\" title=\"1460011364237578.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者林培阳先生授权橄榄台发表</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/林培阳</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">图/网络<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/沐木</span></span></p><p><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=118609&size=300x300&key=de66d3b205ce3717&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_118609\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-04-05 09:32:46',0,NULL,1,NULL,2212,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (371,'【清明词典】清明，想起了诗词、祭祖与其他','201604050933221112.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011332699180.png\" title=\"1460011332699180.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119112&size=300x300&key=09a026ff043262ac&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119112\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">又是清明，想起了许多祖先，想许多祖坟，想起了拜祭和扫墓，想起分配供品，想起风水命运，竟然也想起诗词。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">诗词</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">诗人骚客最多事。所以，中国什么样的事情，都与诗词挂着关系。杜牧的《清明》传唱最广，影响也最大。清明时节雨纷纷，路上行人欲断魂。借问酒家何处有？牧童遥指杏花村。时间地点人物事情都说到了，这就是清明，我们的节日，生与死交汇。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119122&size=300x300&key=79b2305b587ab574&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119122\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">宋之问有《途中寒食》马上逢寒食，途中属暮春。可怜江浦望，不见洛桥人。北极怀明主，南溟作逐臣。故园肠断处，日夜柳条新。外出的人多了，当然只有少数人能回去祭祖，而更多的是在旅途，在另一个地方，在马上逢寒食，在途中属暮春。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">程颢的《郊行即事》芳草绿野恣行事，春入遥山碧四周；兴逐乱红穿柳巷，固因流水坐苔矶；莫辞盏酒十分劝，只恐风花一片红；况是清明好天气，不妨游衍莫忘归。清明只是游玩，只是花言巧语芳草和酒，而祭祖没有了点关系。倒是《送陈秀才还沙上省墓》，满衣血泪与尘埃，乱后还乡亦可哀。风雨梨花寒食过，几家墳上子孙来？乱后还乡，有多少子孙面向他们的先祖，说出什么，纪念什么。而今太平，这样的诗词，同样是有意义的。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">祭祖</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">祭祖，是清明的主题。孔子说慎终追远，也虽说不语怪力乱神，但终于还是说祭如在，祭神如神在。生命总在延续和代代相传，多少年过去了，中国人最明白什么是根本。中国人，打心理早就把自己与祖先和后代连接在一起，视为一个整体。所以中国人既重视后代，也敬怀先祖。而敬怀的一个最好的方式是祭祖。中国古代的继承中，主持祭祖仪式也是重要的一种，这是身份继承。现在，这个仪式已由兄弟间共同主持。身份已由社会取得好过于由宗族取得，因此不需继承，因为无人愿意取得这样无实际用处的东西，宗族结构的内容也就此消彼长。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119123&size=300x300&key=ee50f0026a5c4a2b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119123\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">小时祭祖，是令人高兴的事情，大清早便准备好了。中国民间小孩的宗族情绪，相信是从集体祭祖中培养出来的。由自家的公祖开始，一路祭拜到了始祖，一天不够，两天甚至三天都有。并不是祖多祖少，而是有些的的祖墓较分散，路途遥远，而拜祭祖先，一个也不能少。拜祭祖先还可以上山玩耍，山上有这个季节独有的李子，奈子，桃子也开始熟了，趁着果园的老农回家，偷几个果子解渴是常有的十分刺激的事情。什么东西最好吃，当然是偷吃的东西最好吃，与偷情是同种心理。扫墓回来，可以顺便从山上带回点青草，到家里煮水解毒去湿。扫墓完毕，分供品是最高兴的事情。通常是麦糖包，一个一份，我曾经混入有家的宗族中分得些麦包，为此高兴了半天。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">风水与坟</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">千里孤坟，无处话荒凉。老人们总讲，一德二行三命运四风水，其中的风水，潮汕人认为是只包括祖坟，虽然中国人一般认为还包括阳居。潮汕人最重视风水。其实就是祖坟的位置朝向周围环境对后代人的影响。当然还有具体而言的左边是对一四七排行的房头的影响，而右边是三六九，前后则是二五八。分得很细。中国人有在生不住向北厝，死后不葬向北坟的说法。虽然现代台湾和南迁的汉人总爱向北做坟，但总体是向面的多。这源于周易的坐北向南拱垂而治的说法。坟头的白纸是纪念祖先的最好礼品，当然还有牛羊。石碑是最好的传统书法艺术，内容则也特别讲究，如考与妣易点，而夫人儒人则不容许错的。而它的颜色，被认为决定后代命运的表征，如果石碑青腊色，则说明孙子得贵得财得丁。坟身必须有气势，坟前必须无杂草，旁边的百爷公就无关紧要了。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119124&size=300x300&key=3edae40097263053&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119124\" width=\"293\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">3月30日起，汕头橄榄台推出青年潮俗研究者林培阳的系列文章《清明词典》。和之前推出的《过年词典》一样，《清明词典》名虽为词典，实则借词说事，讲是的作者寄予清明的情绪和记忆，以及潮汕地区浓厚的清明习俗。</em></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011341867090.png\" title=\"1460011341867090.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者林培阳先生授权橄榄台发表</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/林培阳&nbsp; &nbsp;图/网络</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/沐木</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119111&size=300x300&key=3e29352478ea767b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119111\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><br/></p>','2016-04-05 09:33:22',0,NULL,1,NULL,2296,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (372,'【清明词典】那些人，那些事 ','201604050934129720.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011294120704.png\" title=\"1460011294120704.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119863&size=300x300&key=6fbefbfb5861e0a2&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119863\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">清明是一个弥足珍贵的节日，据说也是唯一起源于民间的重要节日。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#4169e1;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">人生复杂，对先人的纪念方式多多，时年八节都有，但清明这个节日最集中。</span></strong>旧里人称扫墓为贵纸。以前清明是最令人兴奋的节日，小孩子可以到山里去玩。一个先人就葬一处地方，很多人家要三日才能贵完纸。我们那个宗族是一天半，因此小时候总羡慕邻家其他宗族的小朋友，他们贵纸时间是二天甚至三天。相当于可以玩三天。以前清明没放假，中小学就放农忙，因为老师们也要扫墓。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119862&size=300x300&key=bffc93c664951ef4&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119862\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">中国宗族血亲制度，集中体现在贵纸上。小时候，可以体会浓浓的亲切感。每当清明过后，我总是喜欢躲在角落里，回味起那几天的快乐行程。可是，自从读高中开始，我便再也没去扫过墓。一是从高中开始便没有放假日，二是居处外地，诸多不便。今年放假，正好就去。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; font-size: medium; line-height: 24px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;font-size:18px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">多年不见，居然还有我小时的朋友</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">从北京回广州，马不停蹄就上车。三点钟出发，一路小堵，到县城黄岗已是十一点多。夜深沉一如旧时，只是汤溪东去，波澜微微映起沿河长长的灯饰，我才明白今非昔比。归心似箭，但林教授还有酒局。我无奈忝列其中，觥筹交错大概败坏了不少贵纸的心情。看来清明除了探看去世的人，也要会一会在生的好友。不过一些久未看见的面孔和久未听过的如“乌青队”一样的词语，颇让我高兴和亲切。不少是我认识的，多年不见，居然还有我小时的朋友，在乡里已经飞黄腾达。我暗地里佩服他。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">要我在乡里，我大概只愿做一个罾翁，网渔渡日，终老渔海。我们还是先撤退，路过红山，一边是海一边是山，夜进一步沉寂。海里面传出一声凄楚的鸟鸣，“鸟鸣山更幽”，山里面那么多往生的人，正集体等待着他们子孙几个小时后的贵纸。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119866&size=300x300&key=94f779f5a57abcfe&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119866\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">我的家人</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">回到家里，已是二点多钟。父亲起来，拉开厚重的木门，遂就响起一声沉闷而熟悉的门轴转声。我就在早起的渔夫转中木门的吱吱沉响中长大的。据说，我家的门轴下面，还藏着几个清朝的龙银。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">父亲不知道我到来，没有准备，我只好将就睡在我家几十年前的眠床上。对面就是斑驳的旧式床头柜，也是几十年前父亲结婚时的时尚物。我一上去，旧眠床便吱哑作响。床虽旧，但上面的鸳鸯咸草图案依旧清晰可见。眠床里头中间用于叠放衣物的架子还在。只是空空如也。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">不过，床头依旧有一件古老的双牌卡西装，那是大学时我跟一位港西同学换的。此刻，它跟着我沉重的肉身左右摇晃。拿起手机，做了一首词。想起汤恩比的叔父行的三帆船曾到过中国的，为什么我父亲也是行三帆船的，而我却只会用手机偶尔写一两首小诗，汤却能写影响那么大的《历史研究》。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">在不明白中睡去，一夜无梦，廿十年来，极少有如此的安稳感觉。感谢这张眠床。清早起来，周围已是村语童音。想起叶剑英故居里头的眠床，才明白为什么叶帅有一次回去坚持要睡一睡，原来就是为了回到过去。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119865&size=300x300&key=407282ffd4048479&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119865\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">早饭，我十几年前就喜欢的泥猛鱼很好吃。现在流行吃小鱼，我倒先知先觉。以前，我们是先到西山贵祖父母，然后才回到家里吃早餐的。现在显然改了。我毕竟二十年没回家贵过纸，一切早该变了。时间还早，厝边的老屋我一一去看了，年年如此，我小时就一碗饭，玩过这家玩那里。如今那暗淡潮湿的排排老屋，少了这么一个当时少年，也少了很多青年人，他们大多搬走，留下父母住在老屋。老屋因此仿如隔世。有一家还存在一块几十年前统一的门牌，上面写着“新祠堂前西巷五横六号”。读书的时候，我往家里写信，就经常写类似的地址。更小的时候，给在广州的舅父写信，就拿来小凳，倚在壁上，一字一字的将我家门牌抄下。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">早上要去贵的是仙脚迹祖，是我曾祖父的爷爷。就在红山路上，老盐埕桥一过，往山里七转八转，就到了。过去这里曾经有一块礁石，上面有仙脚迹。后来，围海造田，仙脚迹的礁石被破坏。先祖的那门风水就移到更靠近山的地方，但仍然叫仙脚迹。一般去贵纸对上祖的称呼有两种，一种是直呼其名加公字，如我先祖有叫高顺公的。一种是以坟墓的位置，如上面的仙脚迹。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">我小时候有个邻居，跟我不是同宗的，我到现在还记得，他清明那天早上去贵的是猪母头。猪母头是一个地方，就是他先祖坟墓所在地。时间还早，我没搭车，就步行去。过去，很多渔民为了省车费，就提早起床，沿着红山路步行到海里去。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">红山中总程是一铺路即五公里，仙脚迹祖是一半路程。我步行去一是领会过去的习惯，二是表达贵纸的诚意剀切。当然也能省几元车费。老盐埕到了，旧时是二条长麻麻石筑成的桥，现在已拓宽。走过去，水田里秧苗正摇曳在水中央。一头牛有意无意的在空地上吃草，见我走过，头抬起头来，仿佛见到多年不见的朋友。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">转入山脚，堂兄已将一车供品载到山下。几个嫂用网袋往仙脚迹祖墓地里挑。过去只有猪头和包，现在五花八门，什么都有。到了，轮值的房头的老大已经将墓地整理好。一斜坡下，仙脚迹祖就在那里。没有墓碑，大概也没有多少人记得这位先祖的名字。只是知道他有六个儿子，他的夫人就是葬在海山上港的老祖母，据说那块风水极好。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119867&size=300x300&key=61ad6bf34c9aacd0&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119867\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; font-size: medium; line-height: 24px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">吉先兄</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">下葬的时候风水先生说这块风水五房将出员外，现在据说应验，那就是大目兄台。几个廿十年不风的堂哥蹲坐在草堆上。我一一寒暄。有些是跟我小时候极好的。个个都老了，拖作带口的。大头兄以前跟我父亲跑船的时候二十出头，现在俨然一老头。他过得不好，去年我一个朋友捐赠儿童读书，名单中有他一个儿子的名字。吉先兄练过武术当过兵，我以前家里的药酒就是从他父亲蔼添叔那里得到配方的，只是蔼添叔已去世十几年了吧。他以前是在物资局工作的，也许因为是退伍军人，后来便没有了工作，只好靠养渔渡生。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">吉足兄是个兔唇，我一直以为他娶不了老婆，经了解，他已生了两个胖小子，我高兴。在同房头的堂兄中，我跟他们三个来往最多，感情也最深。很多堂叔显然已经老去。廿十年前，他们也就是我现在这个年龄。例如周雄叔，过去在经营一个酿酒厂，我经常见到他时他才三十几岁，下一手好棋，现在已经是满头白发。我问他还行棋不，他说多年不动了。他现在是林姓的老大，整天处理着宗族里各种各样的事情。我跟大目兄聊了一会，福布斯上市能源银行没完没了。一个堂叔将我拉到山坡上，聊起他儿子的事情。退伍，能开车，问我能否帮忙找个工作，我记在心里。有几个人在仙脚迹祖前面许愿，各有不同价钱。钱高者首先用白纸条压坟头。记得以前好像是生男仔的先压坟头，然后再轮到下最高价钱的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">最后，我站起来，向仙脚迹祖拜拜，也拜拜了。堂哥载我去教师楼，另一个堂弟就住在上面。昨天，他回来贵纸，听了北京一个叫西施的小女孩子的电话，因为高兴，其时他正在方便，没想就将腿弄伤了。我去看他，开玩笑说我为他下了二万元，让他明年去仙脚迹祖还。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119861&size=300x300&key=83ec2d9e8766a13e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119861\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#8b0000;font-size:18px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">我的祖父祖母</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">下午，去贵祖父母。和廿十年前一样，要整理墓地，需要带锄头镰刀去。我负锄走在西山上，就像一个老农，在春天里忙碌着，走过田垅，爬上西山。新旧坟越来越多，颇不易找。听说那天，一个同学去贵纸，旁边两家的墓地就认不出来。因为过去坟墓多不立碑，立不立碑听说也极讲究。结果呢，就只好混在一起贵了事。真是潮剧老三里头讲的“老热过义统埠，慢死葬无路。”还有，听说几年前，一家人迁坟，结果错将隔坟的一家迁了。险些打架。后来听说是迁坟的结果隔坟那家接受了，但搞错的这家白白给人家出了四成钱差不多一万元才了事。爷爷的墓地很难找，不过父亲掌握了方法。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">沿山上行，到麦某某的大灰坟向上两上山堑就到了。爷爷的墓地势头还好。只是前面那棵年年生长的苦楝树不在了。父亲跟以往一样，说起爷爷的往事。爷爷过世的时候，我两岁，因此现在一点也记不起来了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">多年前，爷爷还有一张照片在。显然是从船民证上拆下来的，已有些不清楚。父亲多次想请画家复原，画一幅大的作为纪念。不知怎的总没完成。因此我再也不认得爷爷的容颜。爷爷老实，但极讲义气。有一个被批斗的堂兄去世，别人是不敢近身的，只有爷爷背他到山上面去下葬。爷爷还会下棋，总在渔闲时躲在祠堂角跟人下棋，绝少对手。爷爷去世的时候是没有棺木的。国家说为了节省木材。用一口公用的水泥棺材抬到山上，爷爷便被从水泥棺材里抬出，入敛。水泥棺材便被大队里收回去重用。听说后来不忍爷爷没有棺木的结果，就用几块船板简单订了一件。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而早先准备好的一口木材棺材，被大队收去了。这件事，我是第一次听父亲说的。以前只是听他说如果重整坟地，不知道爷爷的尸骨是否还在。但总没说明原因，现在总算明白了。父亲很容易就整理好杂草，斫去几条藤萝。摆好供品，点起红烛。跪拜几次，烧银纸。撒白纸条时，母亲忽然念起来“贵均均（潮语读糟，与头字押韵），生仔生孙食火头”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">又转辗一处山头，到了祖母的墓地，比祖父的墓的较为向阳。但坟墓之间更为紧密。祖母的坟地左右各有一块看起来长年没有人过来纪念的。因为两个坟头都长起极高的树来，让人想起墓木可拱的成语来。碑头腊腊，据说这是好风水的反映和表征</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">祖母身材高大，但过世较早，我还没出生她就走了。不知生的是什么病，据说当时要有个花胶吃就能好。可是贫穷人家，那里找的花胶。小时候总听父亲说祖母生病的这件事。说邻居某某阿婆，生的也是一样的病，只是人家有华侨，华侨寄来药品和花胶，病就好了，到现在还健在呢。父亲说话时总有不无遗憾的感觉。我用手机拍了祖父母的墓的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">一坟青草，让我回想起儿时的清明节。在他俩坟前许下许多宏愿，至今也不知有没有实现。跪拜完毕，下山。抬头，西山和所有的山一样，已被白茫茫的纸条覆盖。据说，过去有拾荒的待人家扫完墓，就到坟身上将纸条收山去卖钱，也据说现在纸不值钱，很少人来拾了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">今天本来还要去海山贵纸的，但我没去。先祖永远在我心中。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; font-family: 宋体; font-size: medium; line-height: 24px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">3月30日起，汕头橄榄台推出青年潮俗研究者林培阳的系列文章《<span style=\"color:#FF0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">清明词典</span>》。和之前推出的《过年词典》一样，《清明词典》名虽为词典，实则借词说事，讲是的作者寄予清明的情绪和记忆，以及潮汕地区浓厚的清明习俗。</em></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011303131070.png\" title=\"1460011303131070.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者林培阳先生授权橄榄台发表</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/林培阳&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">图/网络</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/沐木</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011319682053.jpg\" title=\"1460011319682053.jpg\" alt=\"图片4.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-04-05 09:34:12',0,NULL,1,NULL,2338,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (373,'【岭东民俗录】 竹马绕青梅','201604061011327502.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011272110406.png\" title=\"1460011272110406.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120168&size=300x300&key=ad4eddd376099e7d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120168\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/>李白先生千古名句“郎骑竹马来，绕床弄青梅”，已经根植中华儿女心中千年。两小无猜的童年快乐，与农耕乐居场景，经过回忆美化，时常会成为我们脑海中原乡的美好。但是所谓的竹马，在岭东饶平县，则经过几百年来的推演，形成了一个由妙龄少女组成，服饰豪华，动作曼妙的民间舞蹈，时常在正二月的乡里闹热，神明出游中做为文艺巡游队伍，穿街过巷，成为乡村中一道靓丽的风景线。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120170&size=300x300&key=ec5ea5d8e4b91a51&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120170\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这种舞蹈，岭东称为“布马舞”。</strong></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120163&size=300x300&key=2ab3006724f6aca2&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120163\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120165&size=300x300&key=bdde0faa505e9ad8&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120165\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">布马制作原理相当简单，用竹篾纵横交织扎成马身，裹上彩纸或棉布，舞者将布马背围在腰间，看起来就像骑在马背上一样。布马舞表现形式与“旱船”“跑驴”等近似，都是一种一人扮演两角的舞蹈形式。这种布马舞最先是流行于饶平新丰九村一带，后来逐渐风靡整个北部山区，以“布马游村”做为社日村寨的驱邪纳福进行巡游。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120176&size=300x300&key=3d4cf37a2d161623&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120176\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120175&size=300x300&key=143b45eb887a530c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120175\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">饶北是产瓷区，民间传说布马起初是由江西来饶的瓷工艺人传入。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120166&size=300x300&key=4d4e9495f34905db&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120166\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">后来布马舞经县城黄冈一带整理加工，尤其在霞西村得到改造发展，改善道具布马服装，精心装饰，人以戎装，头戴冲天雉，肩披出征袍，手持七彩旗，人马角色以貌悦目，坐骑列阵齐舞，队伍齐整多变，并与潮州大锣鼓结合起来，或轻骑漫步，或疾蹄驰骋，舞动之际冠带鬓影，衣襟猎猎，裙影飘飘，姑娘们飒爽英姿，场面热闹养眼，现在已经成为霞西村的经典，经常被潮州乡村重金请去为社日巡游助阵。</span></strong>布马少则9骑，多则20余骑。以队形变换带来视觉享受，有“长蛇开阵”“双龙摆尾”“闯跳四门”“传花编索”“蝴蝶采花”等等花式，一经出动，遂成焦点。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120162&size=300x300&key=5e940109fabbfab0&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120162\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120164&size=300x300&key=52faf5a6c6303ec4&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120164\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">饶北为客家方言区域，原始的布马游村伴奏习用汉乐大八音锣鼓，以大唢呐领奏曲牌《过五关》、《将军令》等，其舞蹈形式最初表演人数只有五、七人，主要表现南宋康王《泥马渡江》的传说，以后又吸收戏曲的表演和音乐赋予《状元游街》的内容，以图吉祥之兆。相传宋代江西人文天祥高中状元，会同进士、榜眼、探花偕同各自的夫人及一名童子策马游街庆贺，故名为《状元游街》，共有布马九骑，并有锣鼓伴奏。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">后来，饶平上饶堡石井乡刘大力得中武进士，九村人因其是邻乡同姓，引以为荣，遂将原来布马九骑增进武进士及夫人共十一骑。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120167&size=300x300&key=3b19bc1bfdf54ffe&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120167\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">然而我们考究这种形式的来历，就会发现其实是中原古老的一种娱乐，唐代皇宫里就有优伶扮演竹马舞的娱乐活动，并逐渐流行到汉族民间。李白《长干行》诗云:“郎骑竹马来，绕床弄青梅。”杜牧《杜秋娘》诗曰:“渐抛竹马列，稍出舞鸡奇。”宋人孟元老笔记《东京梦华录》中，北宋汴京和南宋临安正月十五，“小儿竹马”、“踏跷竹马”、“男女竹马”已经是非常盛行的元宵文艺活动节目，而随着时间推移，竹马舞也日渐成为流行全国的民间舞蹈，从现在看来，无论是陕北抑或是江南江西一带，都有竹马形式的民间舞蹈遗存。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120174&size=300x300&key=8ec94bea5b7f8fbc&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120174\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">随着中原汉人南迁闽粤，竹马舞也流播到闽地。在明清时期，与饶平接壤的漳州府西南的漳浦南靖平和，一直相当盛行竹马舞。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120178&size=300x300&key=6df58efeacbdcb71&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120178\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">光绪年间王相主修的《平和县志》载:“岁时元日，诸少年装束狮猊、八仙、竹马等戏，踵门呼舞，鸣金击鼓，喧闹异常”。这种形式之盛行，还在漳浦发展成为一种杂剧“竹马戏”。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120177&size=300x300&key=f0f8907044c80ada&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120177\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">朱熹亲传弟子，漳州龙溪人陈淳于南宋庆元三年(1197年) 《上傅寺丞论淫戏书》称:&quot;某窃以此邦陋俗，当秋收之后，优人互凑诸乡保作淫戏，号‘乞冬’。群不逞少年……豢优人作戏，或弄傀儡，筑棚于居民丛萃之地，四通八达之郊，以广会观者。”这种在野外田头，就地演戏的情况，我们在以前探索英歌起源的时候，也看到在潮汕平原同样的发生，可见每个地方戏剧的产生，总是来源于民众的需要。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120169&size=300x300&key=a6d0de8618c8aa53&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120169\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120171&size=300x300&key=abee6caf726d9c58&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120171\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而漳州这种“乞冬”演戏的开场，通常是叫做“跑四喜” ，由四个旦角扮演春、夏、秋、冬四个角色，骑着竹马疾趋出场，边舞弄边开唱。这种形式后来经过发展，渐渐就形成了戏剧故事，由一生一旦，一旦一丑出演——从这个地方我们可以明确看到英歌后棚的拍布马的来源——而后来随着受欢迎程度增加，也便形成了行业，竹马戏就卸下身上的道具竹马，完全成为一个舞台表演的形式而盛行于漳州府一带。据说20世纪20年代，漳浦还有18台竹马戏子弟班，成为当地群众追捧的民间戏剧，曾流传有:“三日没火烟，也要看‘合春’”，“三日没米煮，也要看‘戊己’”的戏谣，合春和戊己就是当年竹马戏的当家花旦。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120172&size=300x300&key=ed4652f8ae0e8b12&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120172\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120173&size=300x300&key=e3824f7be13c5fa3&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120173\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">平和与漳浦，俱是初唐以前岭东潮州属县，从地域风俗来讲，同是大岭东文化影响的范围，竹马从这个地区向相邻的饶平传播，无有交流障碍，也是意料中事。这个地方的原住民，在明代之前，是所谓的俚獠洞畲。而在赣闽粤交界处，自唐到宋至明，一直进行着民族的融合与互相影响，中原汉族进入此地，带来先进的文化，同时影响本地的风俗。南靖平和一带的竹马，现在还保存着较为原始的方式，例如都用童子表演，有唱词的曲生，且多用纸糊竹马，游神完毕要烧化等；而在黄冈一带的布马舞，早已以服饰精美，容貌较好的少女编队，代替了童子，同时不再有唱词的过程，也不做戏剧表演，只纯用舞阵形式，在潮州大锣鼓伴奏下，敷演一场气势恢弘的演出。而这个演变的进程，早在明代中叶就已完成，现在流传在台湾客家乡村一带的“布马阵”，正是由那时候移民台湾的饶北客属民众将原乡记忆恢复而成。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#8b0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">由简易原生的竹马向豪华的布马进化的过程，其实也可以看做是岭东汉族移民文化在本地渐渐开花结果，走向昌盛的过程。</span></strong></span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011281136458.png\" title=\"1460011281136458.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/图&nbsp;&nbsp;岭东怒马</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120155&size=300x300&key=136670f73e36c4b1&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120155\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br/></p>','2016-04-06 10:11:32',0,NULL,1,NULL,2668,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (374,'【清明词典】打石铺的一声声清脆变成沉闷的响','201604061456228671.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011250124744.png\" title=\"1460011250124744.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119926&size=300x300&key=4a6452c6df538d1e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119926\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">鲁迅先生曾有《坟》的杂文集，其中在《题记》写道：“说话说到有人厌恶，比起毫无动静来，还是一种幸福。天下不舒服的人们多着，而有些人们却一心一意在造专给自己舒服的世界。”鲁迅的本意是“造成一座小小的新坟，一面是埋藏，一面是留恋。”依我看，鲁迅是在不舒服的基础上造就另一个不舒服，或者造专并破坏人家的舒服世界。但有没有人知道，最舒服的世界即是一处坟墓。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">清明节的时候，寻找先人，就是在拜祭一处处的坟墓。很少人如毛伟人：“埋骨何须桑梓地，世上何处不青山”，他就不须要坟，至今也无一坟。刘伶也一样，醉到路旁，高呼“死则埋我,死则埋我……”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119921&size=300x300&key=be7887e5aff13392&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119921\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">多数人还是要魂归故里的。</span></strong>小时候经常看见乡里外的榕树下摆有安歇好的尸体，因死者去世的时候在外地，按例俗不能入乡，葬礼只能由乡里外开始。生我长我的土地，乡愁无尽时，桑梓纪念处，最好的，就是埋在故里的青山。但不能入乡的例俗不知起于何时，起于何因，无从知道。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">小时候，坟是神秘的东西。骂人到毒辣时，就咒人家：死了不能埋（潮汕话：死了暮感）。读高中的时候，许多山内的同学说食饭用的菜盆习惯说成盆，盆与坟同音，他们就经常说“我的盆在哪里”。开头不习惯，我总理解成我的坟在哪里，每次听到都毛骨悚然。有一次，同班的山内同学问我：“我的盆（坟）在哪里？”我指向远方的一处山坟，他气得很，但拿我没办法。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#008080;font-size:18px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">各种各样的风水传说</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">坟，乡里人叫风水。风水好坏，关系家族兴衰成败。不是小问题。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">小时候家乡总有各种各样的风水传说。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#a0522d;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">最著名的是“胶漏（掉下去）厕羊敬先生”的故事</span></strong>。这个故事应是潮汕地区都有，小时候父亲总爱在清明节时向我讲这故事。故事人物自然也是汫洲人。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">某财主东家有一个老母，已是八、九十岁，吩咐儿子为她选风水宝地。请到高明的风水先生，找了三个灵穴：第一个灵穴可荫子孙平安，出人才但财气不厚；第二个灵穴，葬后要待隔代才能兴旺；第三个灵穴是一块水龟地，如果灵柩安葬在龟头并且树立阳碑，使它成为勃起的龟头，便可招四方财气福泽，葬后立即暴富，但风水先生会因此变成瞎子。财主恨不得立刻变成百万富翁并许诺下条件：如果风水先生果真瞎了，愿供养。风水先生答应了。风水先生老母葬在水龟地。葬礼刚完毕，风水先生果然就眼瞎。财主发迹，对待风水先生日渐冷淡。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这年，风水先生连续都吃到新鲜的羊肉，暗想：财主这样，确是一有情有义的人。于是便对仆人说：“谢谢财主。”婢子听到，十分同情风水先生的境遇，如实告诉他：“这羊是跌落厕池”。风水先生一听，十分恼火。不露声色，后对财主风水先生说：“俗话说，物极必反，我近日已想出永固基业的方法，容我再将风水一修，使财主你富贵永久。”风水先生带着财主和民工，把坟扒开，再在坟前“龟颈”位置上探挖三尺。风水先生来到坟沿，弯下腰，捧起坟水，朝自己眼睛一擦，睁开了眼睛，重见了光明，并说了些别人听不懂的话，下令把坟掩好，就扬长而去。</span></p><p><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119922&size=300x300&key=955a3785073e7760&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119922\" width=\"293\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">土坟经这么一开、一挖，灵气就涣散了，风水已遭破坏，再也没有什么财气福气。财主从此家道中衰，每况愈下。关于风水致盲的故事也发生在外祖父的坟墓上。据说外祖父迁坟时，叫一族亲帮忙。挖出时外祖父肉身完好，而没几天，那个帮忙的族亲便瞎了眼睛。这是母亲亲口告诉我的，千真万确。至于什么原因，不能了了。科学和迷信各有说法，不能辨别了。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#a0522d;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">另一个风水传说是关于汫洲林氏五房的</span></strong>。林铜棰祖是风水先生。在给他的先人做风水时，由于涉及自家祖先，不能亲自到场。所以他就坐在灰寨的那个地方一个店铺里。风水就看在大概今绿岛山庄万山红农场的地方。嘱咐挖掘人员每挖一层土，就拿土色给他看。多万山红农场到灰寨有好几里路。一层一层的土挖个不停，跑腿的人来回奔波了好多次。每一次林铜棰祖总是说还没到位呢。跑腿的人嫌麻烦，就减少回来汇报土色的次数。当挖到（虫习）的时候，也不拿来汇报了，索性挖掉。最后一次汇报土色时，林铜棰祖面如土色。他知道有（虫习）的那层土已被挖掉，叹一声气。然后嘱咐工作人员去买草鞋埋补坟坑，结局工作人员走遍潮汕地区，也就买了五百双草鞋。没办法也就下葬。据说那是一块冬瓜地的风水。每块（虫习）都是冬瓜郎即籽，一块出一男丁。挖掉了就没有了。买草鞋是一种替代方式，但不能言明。只买了五百又草鞋，就只能出五百男丁，现在汫洲林姓五房也就五百男丁左右。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119923&size=300x300&key=c318c6424fd83678&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119923\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#a0522d;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">再有风水的传说就蚤母仙传说。</span></strong>蚤母仙是风水先生，总给别人找风水。轻到他母亲去世，他爱理不理的，他姐生气了，责怪他。于是他就决心为自已母亲找一处风水。嘱咐家人背起母亲的棺材到山上去找。走到一处深坑，坑中小溪潺潺，溪中礁石处处，石隙中间大量小虾生崩乱跳。蚤母仙便对他姐说，就这里吧，快扔下去。他姐一听，更加恼说，大骂他不孝：风水不找就算了，还要将母亲棺材扔到溪流中。所以他姐不干。过了一会，风雨雷电大作，溪水大涨，又过了一回，忽然山崩地裂，伸手不见五指，等到天放光明，溪流就不见了。蚤母仙叹了一声，本来就没什么福气嘛。原来那溪流确是好风水，只是他姐不同意，就错过了天机。这样的故事还很多。小时候父亲还说潮汕目目是竹，到处是好风水，因此一定人文鼎盛。但有人用黑狗血破了潮汕的风水，使潮汕再没好风水，从此一落千丈。我想这大概是给一个地区奋斗失败的风险一种很好的心理安慰。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#008080;font-size:18px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">坟埤是最好的书法作品</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">坟埤是最好的书法作品。北大有一潮汕人学者，我记不起来了，应就是陈平原吧，他小时候就是跟他祖母上山放牛，从墓碑上识得许多字和得到启蒙教育的。可见墓碑也是习字的好工具，死者是老师。武则天的墓碑是无字的，要是个个是武则天，陈平原教授恐怕也成不了中文小说史家了吧。但“无字碑”并非无字，后来还是被密密麻麻刻了许多文字，这都是宋、金以来人们因“无字”之憾而添补的题识。为什么女皇武则天对唐高宗树碑立传，而对自己树碑而不立字?历史谜语多多，千载有余情。其实很多墓碑都是无字的。并非每墓有碑。我读中学的时候，学校石篱外就有块紧挨在一起的坟，坟碑就没有文字。每次清明经过，过会放些纸条上去。后来听说是众人公众人母。应是开垦荒地时从某些地方集中起来的无主坟，男女分开。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119924&size=300x300&key=f1edf5b0fe1964fe&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119924\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">我以前扫墓经虎头山，总会见到一些比丘比丘尼的墓地，一般是向北面的，不知里面有没有舍利子。但都没有他去拜祭和打理，荒草齐碑，都用了出家者的俗名加上法号，没有子孙，天地共祭也不错的。陈寅恪在在所作的王国维纪念碑铭首先提出的“独立之精神，自由之思想”，是这近代比较有名的碑文。我也从墓碑上学到不少知识。现在有些人连考妣都不知什么意思，更不用说墓碑上的夫人儒人祖妣的区别。如林姓始祖母就称夫人。夫人是级别比较高的了，夫人的老公可以建起家庙，其他人的只能称祠堂。我有一老祖母的墓碑上就写上儒人周氏，儒人大概相当于现在处级干部的老婆。其他的，漫山遍野的墓碑上都是只祖妣XX（名）X氏X母了，一般人都如此。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">乡里有刻石碑的作坊，有专门的字碑模样，大部分用的是宋体。字极漂亮，由于下葬一般离死时间短，所以要求制作速度极快。小时候村庄很宁静，后公路上打石铺的石工击打碑石，发出清脆的鸣响，有时候背着书包走近去看，地上放着一些墓碑，就知道谁谁去世了。读中学的时候，学校里有一些陈旧的石碑，被用来铺路，无数人走过。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119925&size=300x300&key=fb8727d257c14777&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119925\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">我总暗想一些坟里埋藏着一些多少人生沧桑旧事。一个个坟，就是一段段历史。但什么是历史，总不能挖起坟来寻找。清明到了，海隅村歌，打石铺的一声声清脆变成沉闷的响，一个个故事便被带进坟里。多少年后，荒草残碑里，又有谁再记起这些湮远的海隅村事和人生。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; font-size: medium; font-weight: bold; line-height: 24px;\">3月30日起，汕头橄榄台推出青年潮俗研究者林培阳的系列文章《<span style=\"color:#FF0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#FF0000;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">清明词典</span></span>》。和之前推出的《过年词典》一样，《清明词典》名虽为词典，实则借词说事，讲是的作者寄予清明的情绪和记忆，以及潮汕地区浓厚的清明习俗。</em></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011260644573.png\" title=\"1460011260644573.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者林培阳先生授权橄榄台发表</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道&nbsp;&nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/林培阳&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">图/网络</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/沐木</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=119929&size=300x300&key=a0d1ee50b4e4bb5d&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_119929\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-04-06 14:56:22',0,NULL,1,NULL,2479,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
insert  into `chaosky`(`tipid`,`tiptitle`,`tipimg1`,`tipcontent`,`stime`,`postflag`,`posttime`,`userid`,`post_user`,`readnum`,`proid`,`tipvideo`,`commentflag`,`delflag`,`draftflag`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) values (375,'【岭东民俗录】关公巡城','201604071113109990.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011199561995.png\" title=\"1460011199561995.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120491&size=300x300&key=5924323790b47df4&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120491\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">万历二十九年（1601），通判署揭阳县事何景宪，在县城北门外创建关帝庙。万历三十三年（1605），惠来关帝庙由城里的百姓方天福等捐资，建在县城西关中街。后来，知县游之光又重加修葺。此前的隆庆元年(1567)，潮阳知县陈王道又在北门外北城书院之上，另外建起一座“关王庙”。万历十一年（1583）由副总兵于嵩倡建的南澳镇城汉寿亭侯祠开始落成。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120488&size=300x300&key=79009e135cfc5783&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120488\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这个时候，整个岭东仿佛才从绵延20年的战火倭乱中得到喘息，通过建设一个个代表威猛勇武战神的关帝庙，似乎才能够让心有余悸的岭东士民们，告别惊魂未定的过去开始进入一个相对安定的太平时期。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120486&size=300x300&key=3a1cb7f6d0033669&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120486\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这是文献记载中岭东住民们把关羽做为一个主要神明进行供奉的开始，此前元代至正年间，据说潮阳新街城隍巷口也曾经建了一座“勇义行祠”，只是那个时代大约三国演义还未曾流播，岭东百姓们对之并不是很感兴趣。但是元末明初，尤其是嘉靖年间倭乱流寇对城镇乡村的劫掠，让岭东百姓苦不堪言，痛定思痛，不但双忠公这种守城护民之神确立了其地位，就是原本只在王朝统治阶级敬仰推广的关公，也被庶民们做为保境安民的大神，请进了庙里。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120489&size=300x300&key=dc9950f3d7f5fb6b&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120489\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">关羽成为神明被人崇拜，首先是从五代荆州地区开始的，关羽败走麦城而被孙权所杀，因此荆州一带流传有“关三郎”灵显之事，天台宗开山祖师智顗禅师晚年在故里荆州玉泉山修持，当时据说关羽因为死于孙权之手心有不甘，经常厉呼“还我头来”， 智顗禅师便点化关三郎，“你砍过的头又该向谁去讨”，关羽于是恍然大悟，皈依智顗禅师，这个故事是后来关公成为佛教中的护法伽蓝的由来。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120509&size=300x300&key=ead3d07a7c456fc0&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120509\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">后来到了元末明初，罗贯中先生《三国志通俗演义》一纸风行，同时经过元杂剧的搬演，让这一部俗称《三国演义》的小说故事，红遍全中国。而其中符合理学社会道德理想的完美“关公”形象，开始深入人心。明朝建国之后，朱元璋开始把关羽拉进国家祀典的正统行列，到了明神宗万历十八年，更加封为“协天护国忠义大帝” ，关羽荣升神界之帝。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120508&size=300x300&key=d93ba52ad9200197&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120508\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120505&size=300x300&key=dd8a4cdc0d30c065&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120505\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">此后明清换代，岭东又陷入一个异常惨烈的生灵涂炭之战场，郑成功视潮州府为粮仓，部属飞舟劫掠补充给养；而清王朝对本地武装降了又反，反了又降也完全失去耐心，康熙初年干脆采取三光政策，斥地禁海。内陆城市也不太平，客属居民和潮属居民矛盾加剧，以客属为主的“九军”盘踞霖田、蓝田两都，猛攻揭阳县榕江下游一带福老人聚居地，各处武装割据，陷城破寨，白骨累累，可谓哀鸿遍野。这时候，关公被绝望的岭东平民奉为救命之神，每次侥幸得到太平，就要拜祭流传关帝显灵之事。战争中无助的平民，只能寄望义勇盖天下的关公显灵护佑。从此到康乾之世，关羽和双忠公等神祇一样，成为寄托平民安全的希望，香火渐旺。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120499&size=300x300&key=acd159a61b187f9e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120499\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">而这个时候的岭东潮州府，开始酝酿发生着一系列和以往时代完全不同的变化。洪武初年为保持社会稳定，限制人口流动的里社制度，随着嘉靖朝的大动乱，已经名存实亡。随着万历朝之后的稳定，岭东开始了迅猛的发展，人口增多，需求开始活跃，商贸活动在社会生活中变得日益重要。随着工商业活动的频繁发生和规模的扩大，在城镇之外，岭东出现了众多市集，市集成了一种地理实体。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120492&size=300x300&key=2007d20dd2c86d2a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120492\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">市集是联结周边村庄的一个节点，对于一些大型的市集而言，甚至到后来发展成为可与县城分庭抗礼的地步。例如清嘉庆之后的揭阳县棉湖市，就设立揭阳县佐堂，主管揭阳西部的一应县务。市场网络的形成和不断扩大，也对岭东宗族的产生和发展，带来了远超前代的动力和支持。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120504&size=300x300&key=2b145634cb01dd5a&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120504\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">清代海上贸易的合法化之后，潮州的红头船千舻万艘，往来东西洋。潮商的生意做出了国门。潮商早在宋代就已经通过海运成为国内乃至国际知名的团体，在商业性的人际交往之中，需要守信用、讲义气。这时候，从《三国演义》走出的义薄云天的关公，就日渐被扩张起来的商人阶层所需要，从一位战神，变成商人们普遍供奉的神祇。而因为商人们普遍供奉，不知底细的民众传说，就把关公当做了财神，这种传说一发酵，从此关公更成了家喻户晓的武财神，从此走进了千家万户。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120493&size=300x300&key=e9d79365b04a3aad&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120493\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">入清以降，潮州商帮开始在国内外各大港口城市开设会馆。而潮商的会馆，必祀关公。潮商会馆崇祀的神明，除了普遍流行于岭东的妈祖、关帝之外，还有财神和魁星等。会馆是绅商共建的，绅士要升官，商人要发财，各有自己信奉的神明。而妈祖因为可以护佑出门人的人身安全和出入平安而得到奉祀，而关帝的原因则是因为“仰承高义”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120496&size=300x300&key=a33b36dbb1e85a4c&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120496\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">潮商对关公的崇拜，除了人格上的普世价值“忠义”之外，还有信和勇。勇字当头，潮商多为海商，负本逐利，审时度势，当然要有勇略才能做强做大。而“信”则是潮商赖以生存和发展的基本。在贸易往来中，潮商坚持“唯诚与信”的经营之道，始终不渝，以取得社会的公信度。同时把这种诚信做为他们的行为准则，贯穿在经营与做人的过程当中。中国从来不是一个商人社会，所以潮商这时候通过关公信仰，对内对外宣告自己对契约信用的尊重，甚至用信仰来为之封印。因此关公成为潮商的不二选择，既是对内培养这个行业的行为准则，又是对合作伙伴的一个表白，所以关公对与潮商而言，甚至已经超出了岭东普遍的“唯灵是验”的功利性，因为它是商人们立身立行的基本，是这个行业追求体面的标尺——如果你不按照这个仁义诚信的准则来，就意味着违背了行业规则，将会受到全行业全社会的抛弃。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120495&size=300x300&key=5c0ff5a1ef9d9cbe&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120495\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120518&size=300x300&key=485e6b11df8c4944&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120518\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">我们知道，到了清中叶以后，商人对民间信仰的推动，起到了非常重要的作用，尤其在城镇与商业市集之中。商人的经济实力，对于发展大规模的游神赛会，甚至建庙立祀，都是一个不可或缺的物质基础。而商人们靠神明佑护而发家致富的故事产生流播，又对普通民众产生了极大的感染力，在这个背景下，关公逐渐上升为不少大市集，城镇具备影响力的神祇，并且逐步渗入乡村，也就顺理成章了，商人们出于扩大影响的需要，也常常不遗余力地支持大规模的巡游活动。而这个时候，在广大的大中国地带，关公也业已开启从帝王到贩夫走卒，甚至会党盗贼——几乎所有中国人的偶像的时代。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120506&size=300x300&key=8b7efb0779a46b26&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120506\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120510&size=300x300&key=eeb77965dff798f2&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120510\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">揭阳榕城北门外的“古榕武庙”，是建在古榕城县城之外的一个关帝庙。揭阳县城的大老爷是城隍显佑伯，城隍庙设立颇早，明清之际已然成为不可撼动的县城主神。而万历年间首建的古榕武庙，我们推测与另外一座清初建在西门外的关帝庙一样，仍是取关公的勇武，以镇慑战乱中惨死的厉鬼冤魂，保县城平安之意。但是随着康乾盛世的到来，北门这座武庙，开始被地方有司及本土士绅，有意识地完善修葺，以资教化。乾隆四十二年知县刘业勤对该庙“广而深之”，搭建头门、戏台和后楼，并亲题门额“古榕武庙”。至此，北门关帝庙成为与城中城隍庙并驾齐驱的县城主神庙，成为在城以及揭阳县周边的镇境大老爷。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120513&size=300x300&key=5b7dcd34c60f2a41&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120513\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120512&size=300x300&key=523b5a69c1d3a29e&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120512\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120516&size=300x300&key=e43b55fc2a912aea&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120516\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">古榕武庙完善于清中叶到民初，此时揭阳民间手工艺水平达到一个巅峰，反映在关帝庙的装饰上，有岭东地区极少见的木雕藻井，梁架上的装饰木雕精细繁复，关帝因为受到商人们的信奉，因此在经济支持上颇显充裕，木雕雕刻也采用了几帮工匠“斗艺”的安排，更显示出其至高无上之地位。庙门正对面，设立了一个戏台，除了表演场地还有后建房屋以便戏班住宿，可见拜祀关公，长时间地请戏已经成为常态，而延续到今天的每年二月掷珓择日，全城巡游的营关公，也成了揭阳城暨营城隍之后的全城盛事，遗风所播，今日营关公请令旗回到商家店面供奉，也依然成为商人们争相追逐的纳福祈吉之举，根据我们上面的分析，这种折射潮人商业道德的“仁义诚信”之旗，借助民间信仰通俗易懂的形式，在潜意识中加固并影响这个行业的行为准则，就算到了今天，其实也是有其存在价值的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/uploads/20160407/1460011228252295.png\" title=\"1460011228252295.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">本文由青年民俗研究者岭东怒马先生授权汕头橄榄台发表</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头橄榄台原创报道 &nbsp;转载请标注下方图片与作者</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">文/图 &nbsp;岭东怒马</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Tahoma;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">橄榄小编/立庵</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://stapp.cutv.com/forum.php?mod=image&aid=120484&size=300x300&key=2d410551de7ed560&nocache=yes&type=fixnone\" border=\"0\" aid=\"attachimg_120484\" width=\"300\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 400px;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><br/></p>','2016-04-07 11:13:10',0,NULL,1,NULL,2714,1,NULL,0,0,0,'2016-05-04 16:10:54','2016-05-04 16:10:54');
